#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:112
msgid ""
"If the :ref:`default invoice layout <studio/pdf-reports/default-layout>` has "
"not been customized yet, a :guilabel:`Configure your document layout` pop-up "
"window appears. Configure the layout and click :guilabel:`Continue`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis det :ref:`standard fakturalayout <studio/pdf-reports/default-layout>` "
"endnu ikke er tilpasset, vises der et pop-op-vindue "
"med :guilabel:`Konfigurer dit dokumentlayout`. Konfigurer layoutet og klik "
"på :guilabel:`Fortsæt`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:117
msgid "The document layout can be changed at any time in the general settings."
msgstr ""
"Dokumentlayoutet kan ændres når som helst i de generelle indstillinger."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:118
msgid ""
"To add a QR code for banking app payments to the invoice, enable "
"the :guilabel:`QR Code` option in the :guilabel:`Configure Your Document "
"Layout` window. To modify this option, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Customer "
"Payments` section, and enable/disable the :guilabel:`QR Codes` option."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje en QR-kode til betalinger via bankapp på fakturaen skal du "
"aktivere indstillingen :guilabel:`QR-kode` i vinduet :guilabel:`Konfigurer "
"dit dokumentlayout`. For at ændre denne indstilling skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`, scrolle "
"ned til sektionen :guilabel:`Kundebetalinger` og aktivere/deaktivere "
"indstillingen :guilabel:`QR-koder`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:123
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Send` window:"
msgstr "I vinduet :guilabel:`Send`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:125
msgid ""
"If a preferred :guilabel:`Invoice sending` method was set in the contact "
"form, it is selected by default. Select another one if needed."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der blev angivet en foretrukken :guilabel:`Fakturaforsendelse`-metode i "
"kontaktformularen, vælges den som standard. Vælg en anden, hvis det er "
"nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:127
msgid ""
"If no preferred :guilabel:`Invoice sending` method was set in the contact "
"form, select the method to use for sending the invoice to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der ikke blev angivet nogen foretrukken :guilabel:`Fakturaforsendelse`-"
"metode i kontaktformularen, skal du vælge den metode, der skal bruges til at "
"sende fakturaen til kunden."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:130
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Send` if the :guilabel:`by Email` option is selected, or "
"click :guilabel:`Download`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Send`, hvis indstillingen :guilabel:`by Email` er valgt, "
"eller klik på :guilabel:`Download`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:136
msgid "Sending multiple invoices"
msgstr "Sende flere fakturaer"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:138
msgid ""
"To send multiple invoices, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --"
"> Invoices`, select them in the :guilabel:`Invoices` list view and "
"click :guilabel:`Send`. The :guilabel:`Send` window displays the number of "
"selected invoice to send by email."
msgstr ""
"For at sende flere fakturaer skal du gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> "
"Kunder --> Fakturaer`, vælge dem i listevisningen :guilabel:`Fakturaer` og "
"klikke på :guilabel:`Send`. Vinduet :guilabel:`Send` viser antallet af "
"valgte fakturaer, der skal sendes via e-mail."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:142
msgid ""
"After clicking :guilabel:`Send`, a banner is added to the selected invoices "
"to indicate they are part of an ongoing send batch. This helps prevent the "
"process from being triggered manually again, as it may take some time to "
"complete for exceptionally large batches."
msgstr ""
"Efter du har klikket på :guilabel:`Send`, tilføjes et banner til de valgte "
"fakturaer for at angive, at de er en del af en igangværende afsendelse. "
"Dette hjælper med at forhindre, at processen udløses manuelt igen, da det "
"kan tage nogen tid at fuldføre for usædvanligt store grupper."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:146
msgid ""
"To check all invoices that have not yet been sent, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Invoices`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Invoices` list view, click into the search bar and filter "
"on :guilabel:`Not Sent`."
msgstr ""
"For at kontrollere alle fakturaer, der endnu ikke er sendt, gå "
"til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Kunder --> Fakturaer`. I "
"listevisningen :guilabel:`Fakturaer` skal du klikke i søgefeltet og filtrere "
"på :guilabel:`Ikke sendt`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:153
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:197
msgid "Payment and reconciliation"
msgstr "Betaling og afstemning"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:155
msgid ""
"In Odoo, an invoice is considered :guilabel:`Paid` when the associated "
"accounting entry has been reconciled with a corresponding bank transaction."
msgstr ""
"I Odoo betragtes en faktura som :guilabel:`Betalt`, når den tilknyttede "
"regnskabspost er blevet afstemt med en tilsvarende banktransaktion."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:159
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:216
msgid ":doc:`payments`"
msgstr ":doc:`payments`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:160
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:19
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:217
msgid ":doc:`bank/reconciliation`"
msgstr ":doc:`bank/reconciliation`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:165
msgid "Payment follow-up"
msgstr "Betalingsopfølgning"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:167
msgid ""
"Odoo's :doc:`follow-up actions <payments/follow_up>` help companies follow "
"up on customer invoices. Different actions can be set up to remind customers "
"to pay their outstanding invoices, depending on how much the customer is "
"overdue. These actions are bundled into follow-up levels that trigger when "
"an invoice is overdue by a certain number of days. If there are multiple "
"overdue invoices for the same customer, the actions are performed on the "
"most overdue invoice."
msgstr ""
"Odoos :doc:`opfølgningshandlinger <payments/follow_up>` hjælper virksomheder "
"med at følge op på kundefakturaer. Forskellige handlinger kan indstilles for "
"at minde kunder om at betale deres udestående fakturaer, afhængigt af hvor "
"meget kunden er forsinket. Disse handlinger er samlet i opfølgningsniveauer, "
"der udløses, når en faktura er forsinket med et bestemt antal dage. Hvis der "
"er flere forsinket fakturaer for den samme kunde, udføres handlingerne på "
"den mest forsinkede faktura."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:181
msgid "Partner reports"
msgstr "Partnerrapporter"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:186
msgid "Partner Ledger"
msgstr "Kontoudtog"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:188
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Partner Ledger` report shows the balance of customers and "
"suppliers. To access it, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> "
"Partner Ledger`."
msgstr ""
"Rapporten :guilabel:`Partnerkontokort` viser saldoen for kunder og "
"leverandører. For at få adgang til den skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Rapportering --> Partnerkontokort`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:194
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:103
msgid "Aged Receivable"
msgstr "Forfaldne debitorer"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:196
msgid ""
"To review outstanding customer invoices and their related due dates, use "
"the :ref:`Aged Receivable <accounting/reporting/aged-receivable>` report. To "
"access it, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Aged "
"Receivable`."
msgstr ""
"For at gennemgå udestående kundefakturaer og deres relaterede forfaldsdatoer "
"skal du bruge rapporten :ref:`Kundeudestående fordelt efter alder "
"<accounting/reporting/aged-receivable>`. For at få adgang til den skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Rapportering --> Kundeudestående fordelt "
"efter alder`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:203
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:111
msgid "Aged Payable"
msgstr "Forfaldne kreditorer"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:205
msgid ""
"To review outstanding vendor bills and their related due dates, use "
"the :ref:`Aged Payable <accounting/reporting/aged-payable>` report. To "
"access it, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Aged Payable`."
msgstr ""
"For at gennemgå udestående leverandørfakturaer og deres relaterede "
"forfaldsdatoer skal du bruge rapporten :ref:`Leverandørgæld fordelt efter "
"forfaldstid <accounting/reporting/aged-payable>`. For at få adgang til den "
"skal du gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Rapportering --> Leverandørgæld "
"fordelt efter forfaldstid`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:212
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:49
msgid "Profit and Loss"
msgstr "Resultatopgørelse"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:214
msgid ""
"The :ref:`Profit and Loss <accounting/reporting/profit-and-loss>` statement "
"shows details of income and expenses."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Resultatopgørelsen <accounting/reporting/profit-and-loss>` viser "
"detaljer om indtægter og udgifter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:222
msgid ""
"The :ref:`Balance Sheet <accounting/reporting/balance-sheet>` summarizes the "
"company's assets, liabilities, and equity at a specific time."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Statusopgørelsen <accounting/reporting/balance-sheet>` opsummerer "
"virksomhedens aktiver, forpligtelser og egenkapital på et bestemt tidspunkt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:3
msgid "Cash discounts and tax reduction"
msgstr "Kontantrabatter og skattereduktion"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:5
msgid ""
"**Cash discounts** are reductions in the amount a customer must pay for "
"goods or services offered as an incentive for paying their invoice promptly. "
"These discounts are typically a percentage of the total invoice amount and "
"are applied if the customer pays within a specified time. Cash discounts can "
"help a company maintain a steady cash flow."
msgstr ""
"**Kontantrabatter** er reduktioner i det beløb, en kunde skal betale for "
"varer eller tjenester, der tilbydes som et incitament til at betale deres "
"faktura omgående. Disse rabatter er typisk en procentdel af det samlede "
"fakturabeløb og anvendes, hvis kunden betaler inden for en angivet tid. "
"Kontantrabatter kan hjælpe en virksomhed med at opretholde en stabil "
"pengestrøm."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:11
msgid ""
"You issue a €100 invoice on the 1st of January. The full payment is due "
"within 30 days, and you also offer a 2% discount if your customer pays you "
"within seven days."
msgstr ""
"Du udsteder en faktura på €100 den 1. januar. Den fulde betaling forfalder "
"inden for 30 dage, og du tilbyder også 2% rabat, hvis din kunde betaler dig "
"inden for syv dage."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:14
msgid ""
"The customer can pay €98 up to the 8th of January. After that date, they "
"would have to pay €100 by the 31st of January."
msgstr ""
"Kunden kan betale €98 indtil den 8. januar. Efter den dato skal de betale "
"€100 senest den 31. januar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:17
msgid ""
"A :ref:`tax reduction <cash-discounts/tax-reductions>` can also be applied "
"depending on the country or region."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Skattereduktion <cash-discounts/tax-reductions>` kan også anvendes "
"afhængigt af land eller region."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:21
msgid ":doc:`payment_terms`"
msgstr ":doc:`payment_terms`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:22
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:23
msgid ":doc:`../payments`"
msgstr ":doc:`../payments`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:29
msgid ""
"To grant cash discounts to customers, you must first verify the :ref:`gain "
"and loss accounts <cash-discounts/gain-loss-accounts>`. Then, "
"configure :ref:`payment terms <cash-discounts/payment-terms>` and add a cash "
"discount by checking the :guilabel:`Early Discount` checkbox and filling in "
"the discount percentage, discount days, and :ref:`tax reduction <cash-"
"discounts/tax-reductions>` fields."
msgstr ""
"For at give kontantrabatter til kunder skal du først "
"verificere :ref:`gevinstkonti og tabskonti <cash-discounts/gain-loss-"
"accounts>`. Konfigurer derefter :ref:`betalingsbetingelser <cash-discounts/"
"payment-terms>` og tilføj en kontantrabat ved at "
"markere :guilabel:`Førtidsrabat` og udfylde rabattprocent, rabatdage "
"og :ref:`skattereduktion <cash-discounts/tax-reductions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:38
msgid "Cash discount gain/loss accounts"
msgstr "Gevinstkonti/tabskonti for kontantrabat"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:40
msgid ""
"With a cash discount, the amount you earn depends on whether the customer "
"benefits from the cash discount or not. This inevitably leads to gains and "
"losses, which are recorded on default accounts."
msgstr ""
"Med en kontantrabat afhænger det beløb, du tjener, af, om kunden benytter "
"sig af kontantrabatten eller ej. Dette fører uundgåeligt til gevinster og "
"tab, som registreres på standardkonti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:43
msgid ""
"To modify these accounts, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Settings`, and, in the :guilabel:`Default Accounts` section, select the "
"accounts you want to use for the :guilabel:`Cash Discount Gain account` "
"and :guilabel:`Cash Discount Loss account`."
msgstr ""
"For at ændre disse konti skal du gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> "
"Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`, og i sektionen :guilabel:`Standardkonti` "
"vælge de konti, du vil bruge til :guilabel:`Gevinstkonto for kontantrabat` "
"og :guilabel:`Tabskonto for kontantrabat`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:50
msgid "Payment terms"
msgstr "Betalingsvilkår"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:52
msgid ""
"Cash discounts are defined on :doc:`payment terms <payment_terms>`. "
"Configure them to your liking by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Payment Terms`, and make sure to fill out the discount "
"percentage, discount days, and :ref:`tax reduction <cash-discounts/tax-"
"reductions>` fields."
msgstr ""
"Kontantrabatter defineres på :doc:`betalingsbetingelser <payment_terms>`. "
"Konfigurer dem efter behov ved at gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> "
"Konfiguration --> Betalingsbetingelser`, og sørg for at udfylde "
"rabattprocent, rabatdage og :ref:`skattereduktion <cash-discounts/tax-"
"reductions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:None
msgid ""
"Configuration of payment terms named \"2/7 Net 30\". The field \"Description "
"on Invoices\"\n"
"reads: \"Payment terms: 30 Days, 2% Early Payment Discount under 7 days\"."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguration af betalingsbetingelser med navnet \"2/7 Net 30\". Feltet "
"\"Beskrivelse på fakturaer\"\n"
"lyder: \"Betalingsbetingelser: 30 dage, 2% førtidsbetalingsrabat inden for 7 "
"dage\"."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:64
msgid "Tax reductions"
msgstr "Skattereduktioner"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:66
msgid ""
"Depending on the country or region, the base amount used to compute the tax "
"can vary, which can lead to a **tax reduction**. Since tax reductions are "
"set on individual payment terms, each term can use a specific tax reduction."
msgstr ""
"Afhængigt af land eller region kan grundbeløbet, der bruges til at beregne "
"skatten, variere, hvilket kan føre til en **skattereduktion**. Da "
"skattereduktioner angives på individuelle betalingsbetingelser, kan hver "
"betingelse bruge en specifik skattereduktion."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:70
msgid ""
"To configure how the tax reduction is applied, go to a payment term with "
"the :guilabel:`Early Discount` checkbox enabled, and select one of the three "
"following options:"
msgstr ""
"For at konfigurere, hvordan skattereduktionen anvendes, skal du gå til en "
"betalingsbetingelse med :guilabel:`Førtidsrabat` markeret og vælge en af "
"følgende tre muligheder:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:75
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:94
msgid "Always (upon invoice)"
msgstr "Altid (ved fakturering)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:74
msgid ""
"The tax is always reduced. The base amount used to compute the tax is the "
"discounted amount, whether the customer benefits from the discount or not."
msgstr ""
"Skatten reduceres altid. Grundbeløbet, der bruges til at beregne skatten, er "
"det nedsatte beløb, uanset om kunden benytter sig af rabatten eller ej."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:80
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:109
msgid "On early payment"
msgstr "Ved tidlig betaling"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:78
msgid ""
"The tax is reduced only if the customer pays early. The base amount used to "
"compute the tax is the same as the sale: if the customer benefits from the "
"reduction, then the tax is reduced. This means that, depending on the "
"customer, the tax amount can vary after the invoice is issued."
msgstr ""
"Skatten reduceres kun, hvis kunden betaler tidligt. Grundbeløbet, der bruges "
"til at beregne skatten, er det samme som salget: hvis kunden benytter sig af "
"reduktionen, reduceres skatten. Dette betyder, at skattebeløbet kan variere "
"efter fakturaudstedelsen afhængigt af kunden."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:84
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:124
msgid "Never"
msgstr "Aldrig"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:83
msgid ""
"The tax is never reduced. The base amount used to compute the tax is the "
"full amount, whether the customer benefits from the discount or not."
msgstr ""
"Skatten reduceres aldrig. Grundbeløbet, der bruges til at beregne skatten, "
"er det fulde beløb, uanset om kunden benytter sig af rabatten eller ej."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:88
msgid ""
"You issue a €100 invoice (tax-excluded) on the 1st of January, with a 21% "
"tax rate. The full payment is due within 30 days, and you also offer a 2% "
"discount if your customer pays you within seven days."
msgstr ""
"Du udsteder en faktura på €100 (ekskl. moms) den 1. januar med en momssats "
"på 21%. Den fulde betaling forfalder inden for 30 dage, og du tilbyder også "
"2% rabat, hvis din kunde betaler dig inden for syv dage."

