#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:99
msgid ""
"If you are using an access point from a previous provider, make sure to "
"deregister from it first, then register with your new access point, unless "
"it's Hermes (BOSA). If using Hermes (BOSA), no action is needed; the "
"migration is handled automatically."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du bruger et adgangspunkt fra en tidligere udbyder, skal du sørge for "
"først at afmelde dig fra det og derefter registrere dig hos dit nye "
"adgangspunkt, medmindre det er Hermes (BOSA). Hvis du bruger Hermes (BOSA), "
"er der ikke behov for handling; migreringen håndteres automatisk."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:104
msgid ""
"To manually trigger the scheduled action used to check the Peppol "
"registration status, enable :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`, open the "
"Settings app, go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> Scheduled "
"actions`, and search for :guilabel:`Peppol: update participant status`. Open "
"the scheduled action, then click :guilabel:`Run Manually`."
msgstr ""
"For at udløse den planlagte handling til kontrol af Peppol-"
"registreringsstatus manuelt skal du aktivere :ref:`udviklertilstand "
"<developer-mode>`, åbne appen Indstillinger, gå "
"til :menuselection:`Indstillinger --> Teknisk --> Planlagte handlinger` og "
"søge efter :guilabel:`Peppol: opdater deltagerstatus`. Åbn den planlagte "
"handling og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Kør manuelt`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:108
msgid ""
"To try Peppol without sending real data, enable demo mode by "
"selecting :guilabel:`Odoo Demo ID` as the Peppol endpoint identifier. To "
"switch back to production mode, change "
"the :guilabel:`account_peppol.edi.mode` system parameter to `prod` mode "
"before activating Peppol in production."
msgstr ""
"For at prøve Peppol uden at sende rigtige data skal du aktivere demotilstand "
"ved at vælge :guilabel:`Odoo Demo-ID` som Peppol-endepunktsidentifikator. "
"For at skifte tilbage til produktionstilstand skal du ændre "
"systemparameteren :guilabel:`account_peppol.edi.mode` til `prod`-tilstand, "
"før du aktiverer Peppol i produktionen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:112
msgid ""
"For advanced testing on Peppol's dedicated test network, use the test mode "
"by setting the :guilabel:`account_peppol.edi.mode` system parameter to "
"`test`. This option is intended for experienced users only."
msgstr ""
"Til avanceret testning på Peppols dedikerede testnetværk skal du bruge "
"testtilstand ved at indstille systemparameteren "
":guilabel:`account_peppol.edi.mode` til `test`. Denne mulighed er kun "
"beregnet til erfarne brugere."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:119
msgid "Contact verification"
msgstr "Kontaktverifikation"

