"customer's form."
msgstr ""
"Gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Kunder --> Kunder` og åbn kundens "
"formular."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:125
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Accounting tab`, check the following information in "
"the :guilabel:`Customer invoices` section:"
