msgstr ":guilabel:`E-fakturaformat`: Vælg det relevante format."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:129
msgid ""
"Using the :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(down arrow)` icon, make sure the "
"relevant country-specific Peppol endpoint identifier is selected in the "
"dropdown list, then enter the customer's endpoint identifier, usually a "
