"selskabsregister eller CVR-nummer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:133
msgid ""
"To verify the contact, enable :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` and "
"click :guilabel:`Verify`. Its :guilabel:`Peppol endpoint verification` is "
"marked as :guilabel:`Valid` if the contact is found on the Peppol network."
msgstr ""
"For at verificere kontakten skal du aktivere :ref:`udviklertilstand "
"<developer-mode>` og klikke på :guilabel:`Verificer`. Dens :guilabel:`Peppol-"
"slutpunktsverifikation` er markeret som :guilabel:`Gyldig`, hvis kontakten "
"findes på Peppol-netværket."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:None
msgid "verify contact registration"
msgstr "verificer kontaktregistrering"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:141
msgid ""
"While Odoo prefills the endpoint number based on the information available "
