#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:212
msgid ""
"In the Documents app, create a specific :ref:`folder <documents/folders>` or "
"enable :ref:`file centralization <documents/file-centralization>` "
"for :guilabel:`Accounting` documents."
msgstr ""
"Opret en specifik :ref:`mappe <documents/folders>` i Dokumenter-appen, eller "
"aktivér :ref:`filcentralisering <documents/file-centralization>` "
"for :guilabel:`Regnskab`-dokumenter."

