msgstr "Odoo elektronisk fakturering i Kroatien"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/croatia.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo Invoicing is our trusted partner for safe, efficient, and legally "
"compliant e-invoicing solutions tailored to Croatia's regulatory standards."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Fakturering er vores betroede partner til sikre, effektive og lovlige e-"
"fakturaløsninger tilpasset Kroatiens lovkrav."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/croatia.rst:11
msgid "Legal framework for e-invoicing in Croatia"
msgstr "Juridisk ramme for e-fakturering i Kroatien"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/croatia.rst:13
msgid ""
"In Croatia, businesses must comply with e-invoicing regulations to ensure "
"secure, authentic, and storable transactions. The main legal framework "
"governing e-invoicing in Croatia is the Fiscalization Act and its related "
"requirements for public procurement, which are aligned with `EU Directive "
"2014/55/EU <https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?"
"uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_ on e-invoicing in public procurement. Under these "
"regulations, all businesses involved in :abbr:`B2G (business-to-government)` "
"transactions are required to use electronic invoicing via the :abbr:`CIS "
"(Central Invoice System)`, Croatia’s official platform for public sector e-"
"invoicing. Croatia is also part of the Peppol network, facilitating "
"standardized cross-border e-invoicing within the European Union. "
"Furthermore, e-invoicing through the e-Račun platform is mandatory for B2B "
"transactions as of 1 January 2026."
msgstr ""
"I Kroatien skal virksomheder overholde regler for e-fakturering for at sikre "
"sikre, autentiske og opbevaringsegnede transaktioner. Den primære juridiske "
"ramme for e-fakturering i Kroatien er fiskalisationsloven og dens relaterede "
"krav til offentlige indkøb, som er tilpasset `EU-direktiv 2014/55/EU "
"<https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_ "
"om e-fakturering i offentlige indkøb. Under disse regler skal alle "
"virksomheder, der er involveret i :abbr:`B2G (business-to-government)`-"
"transaktioner, bruge elektronisk fakturering via :abbr:`CIS (Centralt "
"faktureringssystem)`, Kroatiens officielle platform til e-fakturering i den "
"offentlige sektor. Kroatien er også en del af Peppol-netværket, hvilket "
"letter standardiseret grænseoverskridende e-fakturering inden for Den "
"Europæiske Union. Desuden er e-fakturering via e-Račun-platformen "
"obligatorisk for B2B-transaktioner fra den 1. januar 2026."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/croatia.rst:25
msgid "Compliance with Croatian e-invoicing regulations"
msgstr "Overholdelse af kroatiske e-faktureringsregler"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/croatia.rst:30
msgid ""
"**Integrations**: Odoo can send invoices and report payments to the e-Račun "
"platform via an integration with third-party provider `moj-eRačun <https://"
"moj-eracun.hr>`_. As an accredited provider, mojeRačun is designed to handle "
"the differing technical requirements of the two parallel systems:"
msgstr ""
"**Integrationer**: Odoo kan sende fakturaer og rapportere betalinger til e-"
"Račun-platformen via en integration med tredjepartsudbyder `moj-eRačun "
"<https://moj-eracun.hr>`_. Som en akkrediteret udbyder er mojeRačun designet "
"til at håndtere de forskellige tekniske krav i de to parallelle systemer:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/croatia.rst:35
msgid ""
"**For Fiscalization 1.0 (B2C):** MojeRačun supports the real-time reporting "
"of receipts to the Croatian Tax Administration for all payment types (cash, "
"cards, and bank transfers)."
msgstr ""
"**For fiskalisering 1.0 (B2C):** MojeRačun understøtter realtidsrapportering "
"af kvitteringer til den kroatiske skatteforvaltning for alle betalingstyper "
"(kontanter, kort og bankoverførsler)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/croatia.rst:37
msgid ""
"**For Fiscalization 2.0 (B2B/B2G):** MojeRačun facilitates the exchange of "
"mandatory structured e-invoices (XML) through certified access points, "
"ensuring automatic fiscalization and real-time reporting to the Croatian Tax "
"Administration."
msgstr ""
