#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:11
msgid "Legal framework for e-invoicing in Estonia"
msgstr "Juridisk ramme for e-fakturering i Estland"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:13
msgid ""
"In Estonia, businesses must comply with e-invoicing regulations to ensure "
"secure, authentic, and storable transactions. The main legal framework "
"governing e-invoicing in Estonia is the `Accounting Act <https://"
"www.riigiteataja.ee/en/eli/ee/514052021001/consolide/current>`_ and its "
"provisions related to e-invoicing, which align with `EU Directive 2014/55/EU "
"<https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_ "
"on e-invoicing in public procurement. Since 2019, :abbr:`B2G (business-to-"
"government)` transactions must use electronic invoices via Estonia's Rik's e-"
"Invoicing System, the government's platform for public sector e-invoicing. "
"Estonia is also part of the Peppol network, which ensures standardized cross-"
"border e-invoicing across Europe. Additionally, the use of e-invoicing is "
"encouraged for B2B transactions, promoting better transparency, efficiency, "
"and compliance with VAT requirements."
msgstr ""
"I Estland skal virksomheder overholde e-faktureringsregler for at sikre "
"sikre, autentiske og lagringsbare transaktioner. Den primære juridiske ramme "
"for e-fakturering i Estland er `Accounting Act <https://www.riigiteataja.ee/"
"en/eli/ee/514052021001/consolide/current>`_ og dens bestemmelser relateret "
"til e-fakturering, som er i overensstemmelse med `EU-direktiv 2014/55/EU "
"<https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_ "
"om e-fakturering i offentlige indkøb. Siden 2019 skal :abbr:`B2G (business-"
"to-government)`-transaktioner bruge elektroniske fakturaer via Estlands "
"Rik's e-faktureringssystem, regeringens platform for e-fakturering i den "
"offentlige sektor. Estland er også en del af Peppol-netværket, som sikrer "
"standardiseret grænseoverskridende e-fakturering i hele Europa. Derudover "
"opfordres brugen af e-fakturering til B2B-transaktioner, hvilket fremmer "
"bedre gennemsigtighed, effektivitet og overholdelse af momskrav."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:24
msgid "Compliance with Estonian e-invoicing regulations"
msgstr "Overholdelse af estiske e-faktureringsregler"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:29
msgid ""
"**Supported formats**: Odoo supports standard e-invoice formats, such as XML "
"in :abbr:`UBL (Universal Business Language)` format, which is fully "
"compatible with Estonia's Rik’s e-Invoicing System for public procurement "
"transactions. Additionally, Odoo enables seamless transmission of e-invoices "
"through platforms connected to the Peppol network, ensuring compliance with "
"Estonian and EU e-invoicing standards."
msgstr ""
"**Understøttede formater**: Odoo understøtter standard e-fakturaformater, "
"såsom XML i :abbr:`UBL (Universal Business Language)`-format, som er fuldt "
"kompatibelt med Estlands Rik’s e-faktureringssystem til offentlige "
"indkøbstransaktioner. Derudover muliggør Odoo problemfri transmission af e-"
"fakturaer gennem platforme forbundet til Peppol-netværket, hvilket sikrer "
"overholdelse af estiske og EU-e-faktureringsstandarder."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:34
msgid ""
"**Secure storage and retrival**: In accordance with Estonian regulations to "
"store invoices for a minimum of seven years, Odoo securely archives all "
