#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/guatemala.rst:41
msgid ""
"**Secure storage and retrieval**: In accordance with Guatemalan regulations, "
"Odoo provides centralized and secure storage of certified documents, "
