#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/norway.rst:11
msgid "Legal framework for e-invoicing in Norway"
msgstr "Juridisk ramme for e-fakturering i Norge"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/norway.rst:13
msgid ""
"In Norway, e-invoicing is governed by regulations aligned with `EU Directive "
"2014/55/EU <https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?"
"uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_, requiring :abbr:`B2G (business-to-government)` "
"transactions to comply with mandatory e-invoicing standards. Norwegian "
"public sector entities mandate the use of the EHF (Elektronisk "
"Handelsformat) standard for e-invoices, ensuring uniformity and security. "
"Norway is a member of the Peppol network, which supports standardized and "
"interoperable cross-border e-invoicing throughout Europe. Although not "
"mandatory for B2B transactions, e-invoicing is widely encouraged and adopted "
"across the private sector to boost efficiency, transparency, and compliance."
msgstr ""
"I Norge er e-fakturering reguleret af regler, der er tilpasset `EU-direktiv "
"2014/55/EU <https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?"
"uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_, som kræver, at :abbr:`B2G (business-to-"
"government)`-transaktioner overholder obligatoriske e-"
"faktureringsstandarder. Norske offentlige enheder kræver brug af EHF-"
"standarden (Elektronisk Handelsformat) til e-fakturaer, hvilket sikrer "
"ensartethed og sikkerhed. Norge er medlem af Peppol-netværket, som "
"understøtter standardiseret og interoperabel grænseoverskridende e-"
"fakturering i hele Europa. Selvom det ikke er obligatorisk for B2B-"
"transaktioner, er e-fakturering bredt opmuntret og adopteret i den private "
"sektor for at øge effektivitet, gennemsigtighed og overholdelse."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/norway.rst:22
msgid "Compliance with Norwegian e-invoicing regulations"
msgstr "Overholdelse af norske e-faktureringsregler"

