msgid "Initially, the product stock is 0, so all values are $0."
msgstr "Til at begynde med er produktlageret 0, så alle værdier er $0."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/avg_price_valuation.rst:112
msgid ""
"In the first warehouse operation, `8` tables are received at `$10` each. The "
"average cost is calculated using the :ref:`formula <inventory/avg_cost/"
"formula>`:"
msgstr ""
"I den første lageroperation modtages `8` borde til `$10` hver. "
"Gennemsnitsprisen beregnes ved hjælp af :ref:`formlen <inventory/avg_cost/"
"formula>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/avg_price_valuation.rst:115
msgid ""
"Avg~Cost = \\frac{0 + 8 \\times $10}{8} = \\frac{$80}{8} = $10\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Avg~Cost = \\frac{0 + 8 \\times $10}{8} = \\frac{$80}{8} = $10\n"
"\n"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/avg_price_valuation.rst:118
msgid ""
"Since the *incoming quantity* of tables is `8` and the *purchase price* for "
"each is `$10`,"
msgstr ""
"Da den *indgående mængde* borde er `8`, og *indkøbsprisen* for hver er `$10`,"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/avg_price_valuation.rst:119
msgid "The inventory value in the numerator is evaluated to `$80`;"
msgstr "Lagerværdien i tælleren evalueres til `$80`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/avg_price_valuation.rst:120
msgid "`$80` is divided by the total amount of tables to store, `8`;"
msgstr "`$80` divideres med det samlede antal borde, der skal lagres, `8`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/avg_price_valuation.rst:121
msgid "`$10` is the average cost of a single table from the first shipment."
msgstr ""
"`$10` er den gennemsnitlige omkostning for et enkelt bord fra den første "
"forsendelse."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/avg_price_valuation.rst:123
msgid ""
"To verify this in Odoo, in the *Purchase* app, order `8` quantities of a new "
"product, `Table`, with no previous stock moves, for `$10` each."
msgstr ""
"For at verificere dette i Odoo, bestæl `8` enheder af et nyt produkt, "
"`Bord`, uden tidligere lagerbevægelser, til `$10` pr. styk i *Indkøb*-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/avg_price_valuation.rst:126
msgid ""
"In the table's :guilabel:`Product Category` field in the :guilabel:`General "
"Information` tab of the product form, click the :guilabel:`➡️ (arrow)` icon, "
"to open an :guilabel:`External Link` to edit the product category. Set "
"the :guilabel:`Costing Method` to `Average Cost (AVCO)` "
"and :guilabel:`Inventory Valuation` to `Automated`."
msgstr ""
"I bordets :guilabel:`Produktkategori`-felt på fanen :guilabel:`Generelle "
"oplysninger` på produktformularen skal du klikke på ikonet :guilabel:`➡️ "
"(pil)` for at åbne et :guilabel:`Eksternt link` til redigering af "
"produktkategorien. Indstil :guilabel:`Omkostningsmetode` til `Average Cost "
"(AVCO)` og :guilabel:`Lagerværdiansatte` til `Automated`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/avg_price_valuation.rst:131
msgid ""
"Then, return to the purchase order. Click :guilabel:`Confirm Order`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Receive Products` to confirm receipt."
msgstr ""
"Vend derefter tilbage til indkøbsordren. Klik på :guilabel:`Bekræft ordre`, "
"og klik på :guilabel:`Modtag produkter` for at bekræfte modtagelsen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/avg_price_valuation.rst:134
msgid ""
"Next, check the inventory valuation record generated by the product "
"reception by navigating to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Reporting --> "
"Inventory Valuation`. Select the drop-down for `Table`, and view "
"the :guilabel:`Total Value` column for the *valuation layer* "
"(:dfn:`inventory valuation at a specific point in time = on-hand quantity * "
"unit price`). The 8 tables in-stock are worth $80."
msgstr ""
"Kontroller derefter lagerværdiposten, der er genereret af "
"produktmodtagelsen, ved at navigere til :menuselection:`Lager --> "
"Rapportering --> Lagerværdiansatte`. Vælg rullemenuen for `Bord`, og se "
"kolonnen :guilabel:`Samlet værdi` for *værdiansættelseslaget* "
"(:dfn:`lagerværdiansatte på et bestemt tidspunkt = disponibelt antal * "
"enhedspris`). De 8 borde på lager er $80 værd."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/avg_price_valuation.rst:0
msgid "Show inventory valuation of 8 tables in Odoo."
msgstr "Vis lagerværdiansatte af 8 borde i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/avg_price_valuation.rst:145
msgid ""
"When the product category's :guilabel:`Costing Method` is set "
"to :guilabel:`AVCO`, then the average cost of a product is also displayed on "
"the :guilabel:`Cost` field, under the :guilabel:`General Information` tab, "
