#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:3
msgid "Multi-currency system"
msgstr "Multi-valutasystem"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo allows you to issue invoices, receive bills, and record transactions in "
"currencies other than the main currency configured for your company. You can "
"also set up bank accounts in other currencies and run reports on your "
"foreign currency activities."
msgstr ""
"Odoo giver dig mulighed for at udstede fakturaer, modtage regninger og "
"registrere transaktioner i andre valutaer end hovedvalutaen konfigureret for "
"din virksomhed. Du kan også oprette bankkonti i andre valutaer og køre "
"rapporter om dine aktiviteter i fremmed valuta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:10
msgid ":doc:`../bank/foreign_currency`"
msgstr ":doc:`../bank/foreign_currency`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:20
msgid "Main currency"
msgstr "Hovedvaluta"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:22
msgid ""
"The **main currency** is defined by default according to the company's "
"country. You can change it by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings --> Currencies` and changing the currency in "
"the :guilabel:`Main Currency` setting."
msgstr ""
"**Hovedvalutaen** defineres som standard i henhold til virksomhedens land. "
"Du kan ændre den ved at gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Konfiguration --"
"> Indstillinger --> Valutaer` og ændre valutaen i "
"indstillingen :guilabel:`Hovedvaluta`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:29
msgid "Enable foreign currencies"
msgstr "Aktiver fremmed valuta"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:31
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Currencies`, and "
"enable the currencies you wish to use by toggling the :guilabel:`Active` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Konfiguration --> Valutaer`, og aktiver "
"de valutaer, du ønsker at bruge, ved at skifte :guilabel:`Aktiv` knappen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:None
msgid "Enable the currencies you wish to use."
msgstr "Aktiver de valutaer, du ønsker at bruge."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:41
msgid "Currency rates"
msgstr "Valutakurser"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:44
msgid "Manual update"
msgstr "Manuel opdatering"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:46
msgid ""
"To manually create and set a currency rate, go to :menuselection:`Accounting "
"--> Configuration --> Currencies`, click on the currency you wish to change "
"the rate of, and under the :guilabel:`Rates` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a "
"line` to create a new rate."
msgstr ""
"For manuelt at oprette og indstille en valutakurs skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Konfiguration --> Valutaer`, klikke på den "
"valuta, du ønsker at ændre kursen for, og under fanen :guilabel:`Kurser` "
"klikke på :guilabel:`Tilføj en linje` for at oprette en ny kurs."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:None
msgid "Create or modify the currency rate."
msgstr "Opret eller rediger valutakursen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:55
msgid "Automatic update"
msgstr "Automatisk opdatering"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:57
msgid ""
"When you activate a second currency for the first time, :guilabel:`Automatic "
"Currency Rates` appears under :menuselection:`Accounting Dashboard --> "
"Configuration --> Settings --> Currencies`. By default, you have to click on "
"the **Update now** button (:guilabel:`🗘`) to update the rates."
msgstr ""
"Når du aktiverer en anden valuta for første gang, vises "
":guilabel:`Automatiske valutakurser` under :menuselection:`Bogføring "
"Dashboard --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger --> Valutaer`. Som standard "
"skal du klikke på knappen **Opdater nu** (:guilabel:`🗘`) for at opdatere "
"kurserne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:61
msgid ""
"Odoo can update the rates at regular intervals. To do so, change "
"the :guilabel:`Interval` from :guilabel:`Manually` "
"to :guilabel:`Daily`, :guilabel:`Weekly`, or :guilabel:`Monthly`. You can "
"also select the web service from which you want to retrieve the latest "
"currency rates by clicking on the :guilabel:`Service` field."
msgstr ""
"Odoo kan opdatere kurserne med regelmæssige intervaller. For at gøre dette "
"skal du ændre :guilabel:`Interval` fra :guilabel:`Manuelt` til "
":guilabel:`Dagligt`, :guilabel:`Ugentligt` eller :guilabel:`Månedligt`. Du "
"kan også vælge den webtjeneste, som du vil hente de seneste valutakurser "
"fra, ved at klikke på feltet :guilabel:`Tjeneste`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:69
msgid "Exchange difference entries"
msgstr "Valutadifferenceposteringer"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:71
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically records exchange differences entries on dedicated "
"accounts, in a dedicated journal."
msgstr ""
"Odoo registrerer automatisk valutadifferenceposteringer på dedikerede konti "
"i en dedikeret kladde."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:74
msgid ""
"You can define which journal and accounts to use to **post exchange "
"difference entries** by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings --> Default Accounts` and editing "
"the :guilabel:`Journal`, :guilabel:`Gain Account`, and :guilabel:`Loss "
"Account`."
msgstr ""
"Du kan definere, hvilken journal og konti der skal bruges til at **bogføre "
"valutakursdifferenceindtastninger** ved at gå til "
":menuselection:`Bogføring --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger --> "
"Standardkonti` og redigere :guilabel:`Journal`, :guilabel:`Gevinstkonto` og "
":guilabel:`Tabskonto`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:79
msgid ""
"If you receive a payment for a customer invoice one month after it was "
"issued, the exchange rate has likely changed since. Therefore, this "
"fluctuation implies some profit or loss due to the exchange difference, "
"which Odoo automatically records in the default **Exchange Difference** "
"journal."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du modtager en betaling for en kundefaktura en måned efter, den blev "
"udstedt, har valutakursen sandsynligvis ændret sig siden. Derfor medfører "
"denne udsving et vist overskud eller tab på grund af kursforskellen, som "
"Odoo automatisk registrerer i standardkladden **Kursforskel**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:89
msgid ""
"Each account can have a set currency. By doing so, all moves relevant to the "
"account are forced to have that account's currency."
msgstr ""
"Hver konto kan have en fastsat valuta. Ved at gøre dette tvinges alle "
"posteringer relateret til kontoen til at have denne kontos valuta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:92
msgid ""
"To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Charts of "
"Accounts` and select a currency in the field :guilabel:`Account Currency`. "
"If left empty, all active currencies are handled instead of just one."
msgstr ""
"For at gøre dette skal du gå til :menuselection:`Bogføring --> "
"Konfiguration --> Kontoplan` og vælge en valuta i feltet "
":guilabel:`Kontovaluta`. Hvis feltet efterlades tomt, håndteres alle aktive "
"valutaer i stedet for kun én."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:101
msgid ""
"If a currency is set on a **journal**, that journal only handles "
"transactions in that currency."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der er fastsat en valuta på en **kladde**, håndterer denne kladde kun "
"transaktioner i den pågældende valuta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:103
msgid ""
"To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals`, "
"open the journal you want to edit, and select a currency in the "
"field :guilabel:`Currency`."
msgstr ""
"For at gøre dette skal du gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Konfiguration "
"--> Kladder`, åbne den kladde, du vil redigere, og vælge en valuta i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Valuta`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:None
msgid "Select the currency for the journal to handle."
msgstr "Vælg valutaen, som kladden skal håndtere."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:113
msgid "Multi-currency accounting"
msgstr "Regnskab i flere valutaer"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:118
msgid "Invoices, bills, and other documents"
msgstr "Fakturaer, regninger og andre dokumenter"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:120
msgid ""
"For all documents, you can select the currency and journal to use for the "
"transaction on the document itself."
msgstr ""
"For alle dokumenter kan du vælge valutaen og kladden, der skal bruges til "
"transaktionen, direkte på selve dokumentet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:None
msgid "Select the currency and journal to use."
msgstr "Vælg valutaen og kladden, der skal bruges."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:130
msgid "Payment registration"
msgstr "Registrering af betaling"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:132
msgid ""
"To register a payment in a currency other than your company's main currency, "
"click on the :guilabel:`Register Payment` payment button of your document "
"and, in the pop-up window, select a **currency** in the :guilabel:`Amount` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"For at registrere en betaling i en anden valuta end din virksomheds "
"hovedvaluta skal du klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Registrer betaling` på dit "
"dokument, og i pop op-vinduet vælge en **valuta** i feltet :guilabel:`Beløb`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:None
msgid "Select the currency and journal to use before registering the payment."
msgstr ""
"Vælg valutaen og kladden, der skal bruges, før du registrerer betalingen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:143
msgid "Bank transactions"
msgstr "Banktransaktioner"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:145
msgid ""
"When creating or importing bank transactions, the amount is in the company's "
"main currency. To input a **foreign currency**, select a currency in "
"the :guilabel:`Foreign Currency`. Once selected, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Amount` in your main currency for it to automatically get "
"converted in the foreign currency in the :guilabel:`Amount in Currency "
"field`."
msgstr ""
"Når du opretter eller importerer banktransaktioner, er beløbet i "
"virksomhedens hovedvaluta. For at indtaste en **udenlandsk valuta** skal du "
"vælge en valuta i :guilabel:`Udenlandsk valuta`. Når den er valgt, skal du "
"indtaste :guilabel:`Beløbet` i din hovedvaluta, så det automatisk "
"konverteres til den udenlandske valuta i :guilabel:`Beløb i valuta-feltet`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:None
msgid "The extra fields related to foreign currencies."
msgstr "De ekstra felter relateret til udenlandske valutaer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:154
msgid ""
"When reconciling, Odoo displays both the foreign currency amount and the "
"equivalent amount in your company's main currency."
msgstr ""
"Ved afstemning viser Odoo både beløbet i udenlandsk valuta og det "
"tilsvarende beløb i din virksomheds hovedvaluta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:160
msgid "Exchange rate journal entries"
msgstr "Posteringer for valutakurser"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:162
msgid ""
"To see **exchange difference journal entries**, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting Dashboard --> Accounting --> Journals: "
"Miscellaneous`."
msgstr ""
"For at se **valutakursdifferencejournalindtastninger** skal du gå til "
":menuselection:`Bogføring Dashboard --> Bogføring --> Journaler: Diverse`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:None
msgid "Exchange rate journal entry."
msgstr "Postering for valutakurs."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:3
msgid "Tax units"
msgstr "Skatteenheder"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:6
msgid "This is only applicable to multi-company environments."
msgstr "Dette gælder kun for miljøer med flere virksomheder."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:8
msgid ""
"A **tax unit** is a group of VAT-taxable enterprises that are legally "
"independent of each other but are closely linked financially, "
"organizationally, and economically and therefore considered the same VAT-"
"taxable enterprise. **Tax units** are not mandatory, but if created, "
"constituent companies of the unit must belong to the same **country**, use "
"the same **currency**, and one company must be designated as the "
"**representative** company of the **tax unit**. **Tax units** receive a "
"specific **tax ID** intended only for **tax returns**. **Constituent** "
"companies keep their **tax ID** used for **commercial purposes**."
msgstr ""
"En **skatteenhed** er en gruppe momsregistrerede virksomheder, der er "
"juridisk uafhængige af hinanden, men er tæt forbundet økonomisk, "
"organisatorisk og økonomisk og derfor betragtes som den samme "
"momsregistrerede virksomhed. **Skatteenheder** er ikke obligatoriske, men "
"hvis de oprettes, skal de deltagende virksomheder i enheden tilhøre samme "
"**land**, bruge samme **valuta**, og én virksomhed skal udpeges som den "
"**repræsentative** virksomhed for **skatteenheden**. **Skatteenheder** "
"modtager et specifikt **skatte-id** beregnet kun til **selvangivelser**. "
"**Deltagende** virksomheder beholder deres **skatte-id** brugt til "
"**kommercielle formål**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:17
msgid ""
"Enterprise **A** owes €300.000,00 of VAT taxes and enterprise **B** can "
"recover €280.000,00 of VAT taxes. They form up as a **tax unit** so that the "
"two amounts balance out and must conjointly only pay €20.000,00 of VAT taxes."
msgstr ""
"Virksomhed **A** skylder €300.000,00 i momsskatter, og virksomhed **B** kan "
"inddrive €280.000,00 i momsskatter. De danner en **skatteenhed**, så de to "
"beløb udligner hinanden, og de skal samlet kun betale €20.000,00 i "
"momsskatter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:24
msgid ""
"To create a **tax unit**, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Tax Units`, and click :guilabel:`New`. Enter a **name** for the unit, "
"select a :guilabel:`Country`, the :guilabel:`Companies` to incorporate in "
"the unit, the :guilabel:`Main Company`, and the :guilabel:`Tax ID` of the "
"**constituent** company of that tax unit."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en **skatteenhed** skal du gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --"
"> Konfiguration --> Skatteenheder` og klikke på :guilabel:`Ny`. Indtast et "
"**navn** til enheden, vælg et :guilabel:`Land`, de :guilabel:`Virksomheder`, "
"der skal indgå i enheden, :guilabel:`Hovedvirksomhed` og :guilabel:`Skatte-"
"id` for den **deltagende** virksomhed i skatteenheden."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:30
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:343
msgid "Fiscal position"
msgstr "Finansposition"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:32
msgid ""
"As transactions between constituents of the same **tax unit** are not "
"subject to VAT, it is possible to create a :doc:`tax mapping (fiscal "
"position) <../taxes/fiscal_positions>` to avoid the application of VAT on "
"inter-constituent transactions."
msgstr ""
"Da transaktioner mellem deltagere i samme **skatteenhed** ikke er "
"momspligtige, er det muligt at oprette en :doc:`skattemapping "
"(skatteposition) <../taxes/fiscal_positions>` for at undgå anvendelse af "
"moms på transaktioner mellem deltagere."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:36
msgid ""
"Be sure a constituent company has been selected before, then go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Fiscal Positions`, "
"and :guilabel:`Create` a new **fiscal position**. Click the :guilabel:`Tax "
"Mapping` tab, select the :guilabel:`Tax on Product` usually applied for "
"**non-constituent** transactions, and in :guilabel:`Tax to Apply`, select "
"the 0% tax to apply for **constituent** transactions."
msgstr ""
"Sørg for, at en deltagende virksomhed er valgt først, gå derefter "
"til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Konfiguration --> Skattepositioner` "
"og :guilabel:`Opret` en ny **skatteposition**. Klik på "
"fanen :guilabel:`Skattemapping`, vælg den :guilabel:`Skat på produkt`, der "
"normalt anvendes til **ikke-deltagende** transaktioner, og vælg "
"i :guilabel:`Skat, der skal anvendes` 0%-skatten, der skal anvendes til "
"**deltagende** transaktioner."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:42
msgid ""
"Do the same for the :guilabel:`Account Mapping` tab if required, and repeat "
"this process for **each** constituent company on your database."
msgstr ""
"Gør det samme for fanen :guilabel:`Kontomapping`, hvis det er nødvendigt, og "
"gentag denne proces for **hver** deltagende virksomhed i din database."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:46
msgid ""
"Depending on your :doc:`localization package </applications/finance/"
"fiscal_localizations>`, taxes may vary from the screenshot displayed."
msgstr ""
"Afhængigt af din :doc:`lokaliseringspakke </applications/finance/"
"fiscal_localizations>` kan skatter afvige fra det viste skærmbillede."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:0
msgid "Tax mapping of fiscal position for tax unit"
msgstr "Skattemapping af skatteposition for skatteenhed"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:52
msgid ""
"Then, assign the fiscal position by opening the **Contacts** app. Search for "
"a **constituent** company, and open the contact's **card**. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab, and in the :guilabel:`Fiscal Position` "
"field, input the **fiscal position** created for the **tax unit**. Repeat "
"the process for each **constituent** company card form, on each company "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Tildel derefter skattepositionen ved at åbne appen **Adressebog**. Søg efter "
"en **deltagende** virksomhed, og åbn kontaktens **kort**. Klik på "
"fanen :guilabel:`Salg og indk\\u00f8b`, og indtast i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Skatteposition` den **skatteposition**, der er oprettet "
"til **skatteenheden**. Gentag processen for hver **deltagende** virksomheds "
"kortformular i hver virksomhedsdatabase."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:58
msgid ":doc:`../taxes/fiscal_positions`."
msgstr ":doc:`../taxes/fiscal_positions`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:61
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:88
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:128
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:38
msgid "Tax report"
msgstr "Momsrapport"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:63
msgid ""
"The **representative** company can access the aggregated tax report of the "
"**tax unit** by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Tax "
"Report`, and selecting the **tax unit** in :guilabel:`Tax Unit`. This report "
"contains the aggregated transactions of all **constituents** and the .XML "
"export contains the name and VAT number of the **main** company."
msgstr ""
"Den **repræsentative** virksomhed kan få adgang til den aggregerede "
"skatterapport for **skatteenheden** ved at gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --"
"> Rapportering --> Skatterapport` og vælge **skatteenheden** "
"i :guilabel:`Skatteenhed`. Denne rapport indeholder de aggregerede "
"transaktioner for alle **deltagere**, og .XML-eksporten indeholder navnet og "
"momsnummeret for **hoved**virksomheden."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:None
msgid "tax unit tax report"
msgstr "skatterapport for skatteenhed"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:7
msgid ""
"In Odoo, payments can either be automatically linked to an invoice or bill "
"or be stand-alone records for use at a later date:"
msgstr ""
"I Odoo kan betalinger enten automatisk knyttes til en faktura eller regning "
"eller være selvstændige poster til brug på et senere tidspunkt:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:10
msgid ""
"If a payment is **linked to an invoice or bill**, it reduces/settles the "
"amount due on the invoice. Multiple payments on the same invoice are "
"possible."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en betaling er **knyttet til en faktura eller regning**, reducerer/"
"afregner den det skyldige beløb på fakturaen. Flere betalinger på samme "
"faktura er mulige."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:13
msgid ""
"If a payment is **not linked to an invoice or bill**, the customer has an "
"outstanding credit with the company, or the company has an outstanding debit "
"with a vendor. Those outstanding amounts reduce/settle unpaid invoices/bills."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en betaling **ikke er knyttet til en faktura eller regning**, har "
"kunden en udestående kredit hos virksomheden, eller virksomheden har en "
"udestående debet hos en leverandør. Disse udestående beløb reducerer/"
"afregner ubetalte fakturaer/regninger."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:18
msgid ":doc:`Internal transfers <bank/internal_transfers>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Interne overførsler <bank/internal_transfers>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:20
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Bank Configuration <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/bank-"
"configuration-6832>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo-vejledninger: Bankkonfiguration <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/"
"bank-configuration-6832>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:26
#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:232
#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/nuvei.rst:51
msgid "Payment methods"
msgstr "Betalingsformer"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:28
msgid ""
"Several payment methods are available in Odoo to allow different "
"configurations for different types of payments. Examples of payment methods "
"include manual payments (such as cash), :doc:`checks <payments/pay_checks>`, "
"and batch payment files (such as :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/ach-electronic-"
"transfers>` and :doc:`SEPA <payments/sepa_payments>`). Payment methods can "
"be configured in the :guilabel:`Incoming Payments` and :guilabel:`Outgoing "
"Payments` tabs of a bank or cash journal."
msgstr ""
"Flere betalingsmetoder er tilgængelige i Odoo for at tillade forskellige "
"konfigurationer til forskellige typer af betalinger. Eksempler på "
"betalingsmetoder omfatter manuelle betalinger (såsom kontanter), "
":doc:`checks <payments/pay_checks>` og batch-betalingsfiler (såsom "
":ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/ach-electronic-transfers>` og :doc:`SEPA <payments/"
"sepa_payments>`). Betalingsmetoder kan konfigureres i fanerne "
":guilabel:`Indgående betalinger` og :guilabel:`Udgående betalinger` i en "
"bank- eller kontantjournal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:36
msgid ":doc:`../../sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods` for Point of Sale"
msgstr ":doc:`../../sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods` til POS"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:41
msgid "Preferred payment method"
msgstr "Foretrukken betalingsmetode"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:43
msgid ""
"A contact's preferred payment method can be set so that when a payment is "
"created for that contact, the payment method is automatically selected by "
"default. Invoices and bills can be filtered by :guilabel:`Payment Method` to "
"simplify :ref:`group <accounting/payments/group-payments>` payments."
msgstr ""
"En kontakts foretrukne betalingsmetode kan indstilles, så når der oprettes "
"en betaling for den pågældende kontakt, vælges betalingsmetoden automatisk "
"som standard. Fakturaer og regninger kan filtreres "
"efter :guilabel:`Betalingsmetode` for at forenkle :ref:`gruppe <accounting/"
"payments/group-payments>`betalinger."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:47
msgid ""
"To set a preferred :guilabel:`Payment Method` for a customer or a vendor, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Customers` "
"or :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Vendors` and select the "
"customer or vendor. In the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab of the contact "
"form, select the preferred :guilabel:`Payment Method` in "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` section for invoice payments or for vendor bill "
"payments in the :guilabel:`Purchase` section."
msgstr ""
"For at indstille en foretrukken :guilabel:`Betalingsmetode` for en kunde "
"eller en leverandør, gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Kunder --> Kunder` "
"eller :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Leverandører --> Leverandører` og vælg "
"kunden eller leverandøren. I fanen :guilabel:`Salg & Indkøb` i "
"kontaktformularen skal du vælge den foretrukne :guilabel:`Betalingsmetode` i "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Salg` for fakturabetalinger eller for "
"leverandørregningsbetalinger i sektionen :guilabel:`Indkøb`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:54
msgid ""
"Access a full list of all contacts from the :guilabel:`Customers` "
"or :guilabel:`Vendors` list view by removing the :guilabel:`Customers` "
"or :guilabel:`Vendors` filter. Alternatively, access the full contact list "
"through the Contacts app."
msgstr ""
"Få adgang til en komplet liste over alle kontakter fra :guilabel:`Kunder`- "
"eller :guilabel:`Leverandører`-listevisningen ved at fjerne "
"filteret :guilabel:`Kunder` eller :guilabel:`Leverandører`. Alternativt kan "
"du få adgang til den komplette kontaktliste via appen Adressebog."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:61
msgid "Checks"
msgstr "Kontrolpunkter"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:63
msgid ""
":doc:`Vendor bills can be paid by check <payments/pay_checks>` using a "
"dedicated outgoing payment method, which allows check numbers to be tracked "
"and checks to be printed directly from Odoo."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Leverandørregninger kan betales med check <payments/pay_checks>` ved "
"hjælp af en dedikeret udgående betalingsmetode, som gør det muligt at spore "
"checknumre og udskrive checks direkte fra Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:66
msgid ""
"For incoming customer check payments, you can use the "
"default :guilabel:`Manual Payment` payment method, or you can create a "
"payment method specifically for checks to help identify such payments "
"quickly. To create a *Check* payment method, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"For indgående kundecheck-betalinger kan du bruge "
"standardbetalingsmetoden :guilabel:`Manuel betaling`, eller du kan oprette "
"en betalingsmetode specifikt til checks for at hjælpe med hurtigt at "
"identificere sådanne betalinger. For at oprette en *Check*-betalingsmetode "
"skal du følge disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:70
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals` and select "
"the :guilabel:`Bank` journal."
msgstr ""
"Gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Konfiguration --> Journaler` og "
"vælg :guilabel:`Bank`-journalen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:72
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Incoming Payments` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a line`."
msgstr ""
"I fanen :guilabel:`Indgående betalinger` skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Tilføj "
"en linje`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:73
msgid ""
"As :guilabel:`Payment Method`, select :guilabel:`Manual`, then enter `Check` "
"as the :guilabel:`Name`."
msgstr ""
"Som :guilabel:`Betalingsmetode` skal du vælge :guilabel:`Manuel` og derefter "
"indtaste `Check` som :guilabel:`Navn`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:76
msgid ""
"When registering a customer payment :ref:`on an invoice <accounting/payments/"
"from-invoice-bill>` or :ref:`not related to an invoice <accounting/payments/"
"not-tied>`, use the new :guilabel:`Check` payment method."
msgstr ""
"Når du registrerer en kundebetaling :ref:`på en faktura <accounting/payments/"
"from-invoice-bill>` eller :ref:`ikke relateret til en faktura <accounting/"
"payments/not-tied>`, skal du bruge den nye :guilabel:`Check`-betalingsmetode."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:81
msgid ""
"Registering a customer payment by check in Odoo does not move funds. Checks "
"must be deposited in order to make the payment. Once deposited to your bank, "
"the check should appear as a :doc:`bank transaction <bank/transactions>`, at "
"which point it can be :doc:`reconciled <bank/reconciliation>` with the "
"registered payment."
msgstr ""
"Registrering af en kundebetaling med check i Odoo flytter ikke midler. "
"Checks skal indsættes for at gennemføre betalingen. Når checken er indsat på "
"din bank, bør den fremgå som en :doc:`banktransaktion <bank/transactions>`, "
"hvorefter den kan :doc:`afstemmes <bank/reconciliation>` med den "
"registrerede betaling."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:87
msgid ""
"For best practice, enter the check number as the :guilabel:`Memo` when "
"registering a customer payment by check."
msgstr ""
"Som god praksis skal du indtaste checknummeret som :guilabel:`Memo`, når du "
"registrerer en kundebetaling med check."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:89
msgid ""
":doc:`Batch payments <payments/batch>` can simplify reconciling deposits "
"containing multiple checks."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Massebetalinger <payments/batch>` kan forenkle afstemning af indskud, "
"der indeholder flere checks."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:97
msgid "Registering payment from an invoice or bill"
msgstr "Registrering af betaling fra en faktura eller regning"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:99
msgid "To register a payment for an invoice or a bill, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"For at registrere en betaling for en faktura eller en regning skal du følge "
"disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:101
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Pay` on a customer invoice or vendor bill. In "
"the :guilabel:`Pay` window, select the :guilabel:`Journal` and "
"the :guilabel:`Payment Date`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Betal` på en kundefaktura eller leverandørregning. I "
"vinduet :guilabel:`Betal` skal du vælge :guilabel:`Journal` "
"og :guilabel:`Betalingsdato`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:103
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:297
msgid ""
"If previously set, the contact's preferred :guilabel:`Payment Method` is "
"automatically selected by default but can be updated if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Hvis det tidligere er indstillet, vælges kontaktens "
"foretrukne :guilabel:`Betalingsmetode` automatisk som standard, men kan "
"opdateres om nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:105
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:299
msgid ""
"If using :doc:`payment terms <customer_invoices/payment_terms>`, "
"the :guilabel:`Amount` is automatically set based on the installment amounts "
"defined by the payment term. To pay the full amount instead, "
"click :guilabel:`full amount`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du bruger :doc:`betalingsbetingelser <customer_invoices/"
"payment_terms>`, indstilles :guilabel:`Beløb` automatisk baseret på "
"ratebeløbene defineret af betalingsbetingelsen. For at betale det fulde "
"beløb i stedet skal du klikke på :guilabel:`fuldt beløb`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:108
msgid "If necessary, edit the :guilabel:`Memo`."
msgstr "Hvis nødvendigt skal du redigere :guilabel:`Memo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:109
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Create Payment`."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Opret betaling`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:111
msgid ""
"After the payment is registered, the customer invoice or vendor bill is "
"marked as :guilabel:`In payment`."
msgstr ""
"Efter betalingen er registreret, markeres kundefakturaen eller "
"leverandørregningen som :guilabel:`Under betaling`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:116
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:174
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:206
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:231
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:255
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:308
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:359
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:387
msgid "Without outstanding accounts"
msgstr "Uden udestående regninger"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:118
msgid ""
"If no :ref:`outstanding accounts <accounting/journals/outstanding-accounts>` "
"are configured, no journal entry is created. To display more information "
"about the payment, click the :guilabel:`Payments` smart button."
msgstr ""
"Hvis ingen :ref:`udestående regninger <accounting/journals/outstanding-"
"accounts>` er konfigureret, oprettes der ingen journalpostering. For at vise "
"flere oplysninger om betalingen skal du klikke på den smarte "
"knap :guilabel:`Betalinger`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:122
msgid ""
"When the invoice or vendor bill is :doc:`reconciled <bank/reconciliation>` "
"with a bank transaction, its status is updated to :guilabel:`Paid`."
msgstr ""
"Når fakturaen eller leverandørfakturaen er :doc:`afstemt <bank/"
"reconciliation>` med en banktransaktion, opdateres dens status "
"til :guilabel:`Betalt`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:126
msgid ""
"If a bank transaction is reconciled in a different currency, a journal entry "
"is automatically created to post the currency exchange gains/loss amount."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en banktransaktion afstemmes i en anden valuta, oprettes der automatisk "
"en kassekladdepost for at bogføre valutakursgevinster/-tab."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:128
msgid ""
"When a bank transaction is reconciled with an invoice with cash-basis, a "
"journal entry is automatically created to post the cash-basis tax amount."
msgstr ""
"Når en banktransaktion afstemmes med en faktura med kontantafregning, "
"oprettes der automatisk en kassekladdepost for at bogføre "
"kontantafregningsmomsbeløbet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:131
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:182
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:211
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:236
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:264
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:313
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:365
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:394
msgid "Using outstanding accounts"
msgstr "Brug af udestående regninger"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:133
msgid ""
"By default, payments in Odoo do not create journal entries, but they can "
"easily be configured to create journal entries using :ref:`outstanding "
"accounts <accounting/journals/outstanding-accounts>`."
msgstr ""
"Som standard opretter betalinger i Odoo ikke journalposteringer, men de kan "
"nemt konfigureres til at oprette journalposteringer ved hjælp "
"af :ref:`udestående regninger <accounting/journals/outstanding-accounts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:137
msgid ""
"Registering a payment on a customer invoice or vendor bill generates a new "
"journal entry and reduces the :guilabel:`Amount Due` based on the payment "
"amount. The counterpart is reflected in an :ref:`outstanding <accounting/"
"journals/outstanding-accounts>` **receipts** or **payments** account. At "
"this point, the customer invoice or vendor bill is marked as :guilabel:`In "
"payment`. Then, when the payment is :doc:`reconciled <bank/reconciliation>` "
"with a bank transaction, the invoice or vendor bill status changes "
"to :guilabel:`Paid`."
msgstr ""
"Registrering af en betaling på en kundefaktura eller leverandørfaktura "
"genererer en ny journalpostering og reducerer :guilabel:`Forfaldent beløb` "
"baseret på betalingsbeløbet. Modposten afspejles på en :ref:`udestående "
"<accounting/journals/outstanding-accounts>` **kvitterings-** eller "
"**betalingskonto**. På dette tidspunkt markeres kundefakturaen eller "
"leverandørfakturaen som :guilabel:`Under betaling`. Når betalingen derefter "
"bliver :doc:`afstemt <bank/reconciliation>` med en banktransaktion, ændres "
"faktura- eller leverandørfakturaens status til :guilabel:`Betalt`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:144
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-info-circle` information icon next to the payment line "
"displays more information about the payment. To access additional "
"information, such as the related journal, click :guilabel:`View`."
msgstr ""
"Informationsikonet :icon:`fa-info-circle` ved siden af betalingslinjen viser "
"flere oplysninger om betalingen. For at få adgang til yderligere "
"oplysninger, såsom den relaterede kladde, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Vis`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:0
msgid "See detailed information of a payment."
msgstr "Se detaljerede oplysninger om en betaling."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:152
msgid ""
"Unreconciling a payment unlinks it from the invoice or bill but does not "
"delete the payment."
msgstr ""
"Annullering af afstemning af en betaling fjerner forbindelsen til fakturaen "
"eller regningen, men sletter ikke betalingen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:154
msgid ""
"If a payment is (un)reconciled in a different currency, a journal entry is "
"automatically created to post the currency exchange gains/losses (reversal) "
"amount."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en betaling afstemmes (eller afstemningen annulleres) i en anden "
"valuta, oprettes der automatisk en kassekladdepost for at bogføre "
"valutakursgevinster/-tab (tilbageførsels)beløbet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:156
msgid ""
"If a payment is (un)reconciled on an invoice with cash-basis taxes, a "
"journal entry is automatically created to post the cash-basis tax (reversal) "
"amount."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en betaling afstemmes (eller afstemningen annulleres) på en faktura med "
"kontantafregningsskat, oprettes der automatisk en kassekladdepost for at "
"bogføre kontantafregningsskat (tilbageførsels)beløbet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:160
msgid ""
"If the main bank account is set as the outstanding account on the bank "
"journal's payment method, registering the full payment on an invoice or bill "
"moves the invoice/bill directly to the :guilabel:`Paid` status without "
"requiring bank reconciliation."
msgstr ""
"Hvis hovedbankkontoen er angivet som den udestående regning på bankkladdens "
"betalingsmetode, flytter registrering af den fulde betaling på en faktura "
"eller regning fakturaen/regningen direkte til status :guilabel:`Betalt` uden "
"at kræve bankafstemning."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:167
msgid "Registering payments not tied to an invoice or bill"
msgstr ""
"Registrering af betalinger, der ikke er knyttet til en faktura eller regning"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:169
msgid ""
"When a new payment is registered via :menuselection:`Customers / Vendors --> "
"Payments`, it is not directly linked to an invoice or bill."
msgstr ""
"Når en ny betaling registreres via :menuselection:`Kunder / Leverandører --> "
"Betalinger`, er den ikke direkte knyttet til en faktura eller regning."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:176
msgid ""
"Payments that are not linked to an invoice or bill should not be registered "
"without using :ref:`outstanding accounts <accounting/journals/outstanding-"
"accounts>`, as there is no way to associate the payment with the invoice or "
"bill since no journal entry is created for the payment. The amount paid or "
"received is not reflected in the accounting and the :guilabel:`Amount Due` "
"is not updated based on the payment amount."
msgstr ""
"Betalinger, der ikke er knyttet til en faktura eller regning, bør ikke "
"registreres uden brug af :ref:`udestående regninger <accounting/journals/"
"outstanding-accounts>`, da der ikke er nogen måde at knytte betalingen til "
"fakturaen eller regningen, da der ikke oprettes nogen journalpostering for "
"betalingen. Det betalte eller modtagne beløb afspejles ikke i regnskabet, "
"og :guilabel:`Forfaldent beløb` opdateres ikke baseret på betalingsbeløbet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:184
msgid ""
"Instead, the payment's journal entry matches the :guilabel:`outstanding "
"account` with the account receivable or the account payable until the "
"payment is manually matched with its related invoice or bill. "
"Then, :doc:`reconciling <bank/reconciliation>` the payment with the bank "
"transaction completes the payment workflow."
msgstr ""
"I stedet matcher betalingens kassekladdepost den :guilabel:`udestående "
"regning` med debitorkontoen eller kreditorkontoen, indtil betalingen manuelt "
"matches med den relaterede faktura eller regning. Derefter "
"fuldfører :doc:`afstemning <bank/reconciliation>` af betalingen med "
"banktransaktionen betalingsarbejdsgangen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:192
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:334
msgid "Payments matching"
msgstr "Betalingsmatchning"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:195
msgid ""
"During the :doc:`bank reconciliation <bank/reconciliation>` process, a "
"remaining balance is identified if the total debits and credits do not match "
"when records are compared with bank transactions. This balance must either "
"be reconciled later or written off immediately."
msgstr ""
"Under :doc:`bankafstemningsprocessen <bank/reconciliation>` identificeres en "
"resterende saldo, hvis de samlede debiteringer og krediteringer ikke "
"matcher, når poster sammenlignes med banktransaktioner. Denne saldo skal "
"enten afstemmes senere eller afskrives med det samme."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:202
msgid "For a single invoice or bill"
msgstr "For en enkelt faktura eller regning"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:208
msgid ""
"By default, payments in Odoo do not create journal entries. As a result, "
"there is no payment to match."
msgstr ""
"Som standard opretter betalinger i Odoo ikke kassekladde poster. Derfor er "
"der ingen betaling at matche."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:213
msgid ""
"A blue banner appears when validating a new invoice/bill and an "
"**outstanding payment** exists for this specific customer or vendor. To "
"match it with the invoice or bill, click :guilabel:`Add` "
"under :guilabel:`Outstanding Credits` or :guilabel:`Outstanding Debits`."
msgstr ""
"Et blåt banner vises, når en ny faktura/regning valideres, og en "
"**udestående betaling** findes for denne specifikke kunde eller leverandør. "
"For at matche den med fakturaen eller regningen skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Tilføj` under :guilabel:`Udestående krediteringer` "
"eller :guilabel:`Udestående debiteringer`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:0
msgid "Shows the Add option to reconcile an invoice or a bill with a payment."
msgstr ""
"Viser muligheden Tilføj for at afstemme en faktura eller en regning med en "
"betaling."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:220
msgid ""
"The invoice or bill is then marked as :guilabel:`In payment` until the "
"payment is :doc:`reconciled <bank/reconciliation>` with its "
"corresponding :doc:`bank transaction(s) <bank/transactions>`."
msgstr ""
"Fakturen eller regningen markeres derefter som :guilabel:`Under betaling`, "
"indtil betalingen er :doc:`afstemt <bank/reconciliation>` med de "
"tilsvarende :doc:`banktransaktioner <bank/transactions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:227
msgid "For multiple invoices or bills"
msgstr "For flere fakturaer eller regninger"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:233
msgid ""
"By default, payments in Odoo do not create journal entries. As a result, "
"there is no payment to match, but this feature can still be used to match "
"miscellaneous journal items."
msgstr ""
"Som standard opretter betalinger i Odoo ikke kladdeposteringer. Der er "
"derfor ingen betaling at matche, men denne funktion kan stadig bruges til at "
"matche diverse kladdeposter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:238
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Payments matching` or :guilabel:`Auto-reconcile` tool allows "
"reconciling journal items with each other (i.e., payments with customer "
"invoices or vendor bills) either individually or in batches. Access "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard`, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
"(:guilabel:`ellipsis`) button from the :guilabel:`Customer Invoices` "
"or :guilabel:`Vendor Bills` journals, and select :guilabel:`Payments "
"Matching`. Alternatively, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --"
"> Reconcile`."
msgstr ""
"Værktøjet :guilabel:`Betalingsmatchning` eller :guilabel:`Auto-afstem` gør "
"det muligt at afstemme kladdeposter med hinanden (dvs. betalinger med "
"kundefakturaer eller leverandørregninger) enten individuelt eller i grupper. "
"Gå til :guilabel:`Regnskabs-dashboard`, klik på :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
"(:guilabel:`ellipse`) knappen fra :guilabel:`Kundefakturaer` "
"eller :guilabel:`Leverandørregninger` kladden, og "
"vælg :guilabel:`Betalingsmatchning`. Alternativt kan du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Regnskab --> Afstem`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:245
msgid ""
"To manually :guilabel:`Reconcile` journal items, select the individual items "
"from the list view and click :guilabel:`Reconcile`."
msgstr ""
"For manuelt at :guilabel:`afstemme` kladdeposter skal du vælge de enkelte "
"poster fra listevisningen og klikke på :guilabel:`Afstem`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:251
msgid "Auto-Reconcile Feature"
msgstr "Auto-afstem funktion"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:257
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:266
msgid "To use the :guilabel:`Auto-Reconcile` feature, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"For at bruge :guilabel:`Auto-afstem` funktionen skal du følge disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:259
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:268
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Journal Items to reconcile` list view, "
"click :guilabel:`Auto-Reconcile` next to the receivable or payable account "
"(or a specific contact's group of journal items in that account)."
msgstr ""
"I :guilabel:`Kladdeposter til afstemning` listevisningen skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Auto-afstem` ved siden af tilgodehavende- eller gældskontoen "
"(eller en bestemt kontakts gruppe af kladdeposter på den konto)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:262
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Reconcile automatically` window, "
"click :guilabel:`Reconcile`."
msgstr ""
"I vinduet :guilabel:`Afstem automatisk` skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Afstem`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:271
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Reconcile Automatically` window, set "
"the :guilabel:`Reconcile` field depending on how you want to match journal "
"items:"
msgstr ""
"I vinduet :guilabel:`Afstem automatisk` skal du indstille "
"feltet :guilabel:`Afstem` afhængigt af, hvordan du vil matche kladdeposter:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:274
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Perfect Match`: Each debit journal item will be matched with the "
"corresponding credit journal item of the same value."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Perfekt match`: Hver debetkladdepost vil blive matchet med den "
"tilsvarende kreditkladdepost af samme værdi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:276
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Clear Accounts`: All reconciled journal items will have the same "
"matching number, as they are selected from the same account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ryd konti`: Alle afstemte kladdeposter vil have det samme "
"matchningsnummer, da de vælges fra samme konto."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:279
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Reconcile`."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Afstem`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:281
msgid ""
"Invoices and bills are automatically matched to their corresponding payments "
"and marked as :guilabel:`In payment` until they are :doc:`reconciled <bank/"
"reconciliation>` with their corresponding :doc:`bank transactions <bank/"
"transactions>`."
msgstr ""
"Fakturaer og regninger matches automatisk med deres tilsvarende betalinger "
"og markeres som :guilabel:`Under betaling`, indtil de er :doc:`afstemt <bank/"
"reconciliation>` med deres tilsvarende :doc:`banktransaktioner <bank/"
"transactions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:288
msgid ""
"Registering payments on multiple invoices/credit notes or bills/refunds "
"(group payments)"
msgstr ""
"Registrering af betalinger på flere fakturaer/kreditnotaer eller regninger/"
"refusioner (gruppebetalinger)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:290
msgid ""
"To register payments on multiple invoices/credit notes or bills/refunds, "
"follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"For at registrere betalinger på flere fakturaer/kreditnotaer eller regninger/"
"refusioner skal du følge disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:292
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Invoices/Credit Notes` "
"or :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Bills/Refunds`."
msgstr ""
"Gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Kunder --> Fakturaer/kreditnotaer` "
"eller :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Leverandører --> Regninger/refusioner`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:294
msgid ""
"In the list view, click into the search bar, group by :guilabel:`Payment "
"Method`, select the relevant invoices/credit notes or bills/refunds and "
"click :guilabel:`Pay`."
msgstr ""
"I listevisningen skal du klikke i søgefeltet, gruppere "
"efter :guilabel:`Betalingsmetode`, vælge de relevante fakturaer/kreditnotaer "
"eller regninger/refusioner og klikke på :guilabel:`Betal`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:296
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Pay` window, select the :guilabel:`Journal` and "
"the :guilabel:`Payment Date`."
msgstr ""
"I vinduet :guilabel:`Betal` skal du vælge :guilabel:`Kladde` "
"og :guilabel:`Betalingsdato`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:302
msgid ""
"To combine all payments from the same contact into a single payment, enable "
"the :guilabel:`Group Payments` option, or leave it unchecked to create "
"separate payments."
msgstr ""
"For at kombinere alle betalinger fra samme kontakt til en enkelt betaling "
"skal du aktivere indstillingen :guilabel:`Gruppér betalinger`, eller lade "
"den være deaktiveret for at oprette separate betalinger."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:304
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Create payment`."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Opret betaling`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:310
msgid ""
"The invoices or bills are then marked as :guilabel:`In payment` until they "
"are :doc:`reconciled <bank/reconciliation>` with the bank transactions."
msgstr ""
"Fakturaer eller regninger markeres derefter som :guilabel:`In payment`, "
"indtil de :doc:`afstemmes <bank/reconciliation>` med banktransaktionerne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:315
msgid ""
"The invoices or bills are then marked as :guilabel:`In payment` until the "
"bank transactions are :doc:`reconciled <bank/reconciliation>` with the "
"payments."
msgstr ""
"Fakturaer eller regninger markeres derefter som :guilabel:`In payment`, "
"indtil banktransaktionerne :doc:`afstemmes <bank/reconciliation>` med "
"betalingerne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:321
msgid ""
"Registering a single payment for multiple customers or vendors (batch "
"payments)"
msgstr ""
"Registrering af en enkelt betaling for flere kunder eller leverandører "
"(samlebetalinger)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:323
msgid ""
"Batch payments allow grouping payments from multiple customers to "
"ease :doc:`reconciliation <bank/reconciliation>`. They are also useful when "
"depositing :doc:`checks <payments/pay_checks>` or cash payments to the bank "
"or for generating bank payment files such as :doc:`SEPA <payments/"
"sepa_payments>` or :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/nacha>`."
msgstr ""
"Batch-betalinger gør det muligt at gruppere betalinger fra flere kunder for "
"at lette :doc:`afstemning <bank/reconciliation>`. De er også nyttige ved "
"indsætning af :doc:`checks <payments/pay_checks>` eller kontante betalinger "
"til banken eller til generering af bankbetalingsfiler såsom :doc:`SEPA "
"<payments/sepa_payments>` eller :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/nacha>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:329
msgid ":doc:`payments/batch`"
msgstr ":doc:`payments/batch`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:336
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Payments matching` tool opens all unreconciled journal items "
"and allows them to be processed individually, matching all payments and "
"journal items. Go to the :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard`, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> Reconcile` or click "
"the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`ellipsis`) button from "
"the :guilabel:`Customer Invoices` or :guilabel:`Vendor Bills` journals, and "
"select :guilabel:`Payments Matching`."
msgstr ""
"Værktøjet :guilabel:`Payments matching` åbner alle ikke-afstemte "
"journalposter og giver mulighed for at behandle dem individuelt ved at "
"matche alle betalinger og journalposter. Gå til :guilabel:`Dashboard`, gå "
"til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Regnskab --> Reconcile`, eller klik på "
"knappen :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`ellipsis`) fra :guilabel:`Customer "
"Invoices` eller :guilabel:`Vendor Bills` journalerne, og "
"vælg :guilabel:`Payments Matching`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:None
msgid "Payments matching menu in the drop-down menu."
msgstr "Menuen Payments matching i rullelisten."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:346
msgid ""
"During the :doc:`reconciliation <bank/reconciliation>`, if the sum of the "
"debits and credits does not match, there is a remaining balance. This either "
"needs to be reconciled at a later date or written off directly."
msgstr ""
"Under :doc:`afstemningen <bank/reconciliation>`, hvis summen af debet og "
"kredit ikke stemmer overens, er der en resterende saldo. Denne skal enten "
"afstemmes på et senere tidspunkt eller afskrives direkte."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:353
msgid "Registering a partial payment"
msgstr "Registrering af en delvis betaling"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:355
msgid ""
"To register a partial payment, click on :guilabel:`Pay` from the related "
"invoice or bill."
msgstr ""
"For at registrere en delvis betaling skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Pay` fra "
"den relaterede faktura eller regning."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:361
msgid ""
"In the case of a partial payment (when the :guilabel:`Amount` paid is less "
"than the total remaining amount on the invoice or the bill), fill in "
"the :guilabel:`Amount` in the :guilabel:`Pay` window."
msgstr ""
"I tilfælde af en delvis betaling (når det betalte :guilabel:`Amount` er "
"mindre end det samlede resterende beløb på fakturaen eller regningen), skal "
"du udfylde :guilabel:`Amount` i vinduet :guilabel:`Pay`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:367
msgid ""
"In the case of a partial payment (when the :guilabel:`Amount` paid is less "
"than the total remaining amount on the invoice or the bill), "
"the :guilabel:`Payment Difference` field displays the outstanding balance. "
"There are two options:"
msgstr ""
"I tilfælde af en delvis betaling (når det betalte :guilabel:`Amount` er "
"mindre end det samlede resterende beløb på fakturaen eller regningen), viser "
"feltet :guilabel:`Payment Difference` den udestående saldo. Der er to "
"muligheder:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:371
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Keep open`: Keep the invoice or the bill open and mark it with "
"a :guilabel:`Partial` banner;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Keep open`: Hold fakturaen eller regningen åben og marker den med "
"et :guilabel:`Partial` banner."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:373
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Mark as fully paid`: Select an account in the :guilabel:`Post "
"Difference In` field and change the :guilabel:`Label` if needed. A journal "
"entry will be created to balance the accounts payable or receivable with the "
"selected account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Mark as fully paid`: Vælg en konto i feltet :guilabel:`Post "
"Difference In`, og ændre :guilabel:`Label`, hvis det er nødvendigt. Der "
"oprettes en journalpost for at balancere kreditorer eller debitorer med den "
"valgte konto."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:0
msgid "register a partial payment"
msgstr "registrer en delvis betaling"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:383
msgid "Reconciling payments with bank transactions"
msgstr "Afstemning af betalinger med banktransaktioner"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:389
msgid ""
"Once a payment has been registered, the status of the invoice or bill "
"is :guilabel:`In payment`. The next step is :doc:`reconciling <bank/"
"reconciliation>` the related :doc:`bank transaction <bank/transactions>` "
"line with the invoice or bill to finalize the payment workflow and mark the "
"invoice or bill as :guilabel:`Paid`."
msgstr ""
"Når en betaling er registreret, er status for fakturaen eller "
"regningen :guilabel:`In payment`. Det næste skridt er at :doc:`afstemme "
"<bank/reconciliation>` den relaterede :doc:`banktransaktion <bank/"
"transactions>`slinje med fakturaen eller regningen for at færdiggøre "
"betalingsworkflowet og markere fakturaen eller regningen "
"som :guilabel:`Paid`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:396
msgid ""
"Once a payment has been registered, the status of the invoice or bill "
"is :guilabel:`In payment`. The next step is :doc:`reconciling <bank/"
"reconciliation>` the payment with the related :doc:`bank transaction <bank/"
"transactions>` line to finalize the payment workflow and mark the invoice or "
"bill as :guilabel:`Paid`."
msgstr ""
"Når en betaling er registreret, er status for fakturaen eller "
"regningen :guilabel:`In payment`. Det næste skridt er at :doc:`afstemme "
"<bank/reconciliation>` betalingen med den relaterede :doc:`banktransaktion "
"<bank/transactions>`slinje for at færdiggøre betalingsworkflowet og markere "
"fakturaen eller regningen som :guilabel:`Paid`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:5
msgid ""
"Batch payments act as an organizational tool that groups multiple individual "
"customer or vendor payments into a single file. Rather than managing "
"transactions one by one, you can consolidate them to generate a detailed "
"deposit slip or a single electronic payment file. This significantly "
"simplifies :doc:`bank reconciliation <../bank/reconciliation>`: when a bulk "
"sum appears on your bank statement, Odoo uses the batch reference to "
"automatically match and reconcile all underlying payments in a single step."
msgstr ""
"Batch-betalinger fungerer som et organisatorisk værktøj, der grupperer flere "
"individuelle kunde- eller leverandørbetalinger i en enkelt fil. I stedet for "
"at administrere transaktioner én for én, kan du konsolidere dem for at "
"generere en detaljeret indbetalingsseddel eller en enkelt elektronisk "
"betalingsfil. Dette forenkler i væsentlig grad :doc:`bankafstemning <../bank/"
"reconciliation>`: når et samlet beløb vises på dit kontoudtog, bruger Odoo "
"batch-referencen til automatisk at matche og afstemme alle underliggende "
"betalinger i ét trin."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:12
msgid ""
"For customer payments, the feature supports both physical payments, such "
"as :doc:`checks <pay_checks>` and cash, and electronic transfers. Group "
"incoming cash or check payments into batches to print bank deposit slips to "
"ensure your internal records mirror the lump-sum deposit on your bank "
"statement. On the vendor side, batch payments streamline bulk electronic "
"transfers. Instead of processing supplier invoices manually, select multiple "
"bills and generate a single outgoing payment file to upload directly to your "
"banking portal. Because these file formats are region-specific "
"(e.g., :doc:`SEPA <sepa_payments>` in Europe, :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/nacha>` "
"in the U.S., or the global :ref:`ISO 20022 <accounting/sepa_payments/"
"iso20022>` standard), consult your country's :doc:`fiscal localization "
"<../../fiscal_localizations>` documentation to verify supported formats."
msgstr ""
"For kundebetalinger understøtter funktionen både fysiske betalinger, såsom "
":doc:`checks <pay_checks>` og kontanter, og elektroniske overførsler. "
"Gruppér indgående kontant- eller checkbetalinger i batches for at udskrive "
"bankindbetalingssedler for at sikre, at dine interne registre afspejler "
"engangsindsætningen på dit kontoudtog. På leverandørsiden strømliner batch-"
"betalinger masseelektroniske overførsler. I stedet for at behandle "
"leverandørfakturaer manuelt, vælg flere regninger og generér en enkelt "
"udgående betalingsfil til at uploade direkte til din bankportal. Fordi disse "
"filformater er regionsspecifikke (f.eks. :doc:`SEPA <sepa_payments>` i "
"Europa, :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/nacha>` i USA eller den globale :ref:`ISO 20022 "
"<accounting/sepa_payments/iso20022>`-standard), skal du konsultere dit lands "
":doc:`skattemæssige lokaliseringsdokumentation <../../fiscal_localizations>` "
"for at verificere understøttede formater."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:30
