#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:207
msgid "Phishing attacks"
msgstr "Phishing-angreb"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:209
msgid ""
"A **phishing attack** is an online scam designed to trick individuals or "
"companies into giving away sensitive information or money by sending out "
"fraudulent communication. Fraudsters pretend to be legitimate companies and "
"may use partial information to give credibility to their requests."
msgstr ""
"Et **phishing-angreb** er en online-svindel designet til at narre "
"enkeltpersoner eller virksomheder til at afgive følsomme oplysninger eller "
"penge ved at sende falsk kommunikation. Svindlere udgiver sig for at være "
"legitime virksomheder og kan bruge delvise oplysninger for at give "
"troværdighed til deres anmodninger."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:213
msgid ""
"There are several types of phishing attacks, including **invoice fraud**. In "
"this case, the fraudster pretends to be a genuine supplier following up on "
"unpaid bills or sending a new invoice, but with different payment "
"information than usual and with fake contact details."
msgstr ""
"Der er flere typer phishing-angreb, herunder **fakturabedrageri**. I dette "
"tilfælde udgiver svindleren sig for at være en ægte leverandør, der følger "
"op på ubetalte regninger eller sender en ny faktura, men med andre "
"betalingsoplysninger end normalt og med falske kontaktoplysninger."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:217
msgid ""
"To protect yourself from these types of phishing attacks, remain vigilant "
"when you receive unexpected invoices or payment requests."
msgstr ""
"For at beskytte dig selv mod disse typer phishing-angreb skal du forblive "
"årvågen, når du modtager uventede fakturaer eller betalingsanmodninger."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:221
msgid ""
"In case of doubt, **we recommend contacting the vendor by phone**. Make sure "
"to call an official phone number by searching yourself, as the URLs, email "
"addresses, and phone numbers written in the communication you received may "
"be fake."
msgstr ""
"I tvivlstilfælde **anbefaler vi at kontakte leverandøren telefonisk**. Sørg "
"for at ringe til et officielt telefonnummer ved selv at søge efter det, da "
"URL'er, e-mailadresser og telefonnumre skrevet i den kommunikation, du "
"modtog, kan være falske."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:3
msgid "Follow-up on invoices"
msgstr "Opfølgning på fakturaer"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:5
msgid ""
"Follow-up messages can be sent to customers when payments are overdue. Odoo "
"helps identify late payments and allows scheduling and sending the "
"appropriate reminders using **follow-up actions** according to the number of "
"overdue days. Follow-ups can be sent through different methods, including "
"email, post, or SMS."
msgstr ""
"Opfølgningsmeddelelser kan sendes til kunder, når betalinger er forfaldne. "
"Odoo hjælper med at identificere forsinkede betalinger og giver mulighed for "
"at planlægge og sende de passende påmindelser ved hjælp af "
"**opfølgningshandlinger** baseret på antallet af forfaldne dage. "
"Opfølgninger kan sendes gennem forskellige metoder, herunder e-mail, post "
"eller SMS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:11
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Payment Follow-up <https://www.youtube.com/watch?"
"v=50qy2ygS7eM>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo-vejledninger: Betalingsrykker <https://www.youtube.com/watch?"
"v=50qy2ygS7eM>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:12
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/payment_terms`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/payment_terms`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:19
msgid ""
"To configure :guilabel:`Follow-up actions`, go to :menuselection:`Accounting "
"--> Configuration --> Follow-up Levels`. In the :guilabel:`Follow-up Levels` "
"list view, several follow-up levels and actions are configured by default."
msgstr ""
"For at konfigurere :guilabel:`rykkerhandlinger` skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Konfiguration --> Rykkerniveauer`. I "
"listevisningen :guilabel:`Rykkerniveauer` er flere rykkerniveauer og "
"handlinger konfigureret som standard."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:23
msgid ""
"To modify a follow-up level, click on the record. From the form view, edit "
"the :guilabel:`Description` or adjust the number of days before a reminder "
"is sent. In the :guilabel:`Notification` tab, select :guilabel:`Actions` "
"such as :guilabel:`Send Email`, :ref:`Send a Letter <customer_invoices/"
"snailmail>`, and :ref:`Send SMS Message <pricing/pricing_and_faq>`."
msgstr ""
"For at ændre et opfølgningsniveau skal du klikke på posten. Fra "
"formularvisningen kan du redigere :guilabel:`Beskrivelse` eller justere "
"antallet af dage, før en påmindelse sendes. I fanen :guilabel:`Meddelelse` "
"skal du vælge :guilabel:`Handlinger`, såsom :guilabel:`Send e-mail`, "
":ref:`Send et brev <customer_invoices/snailmail>` og :ref:`Send SMS-besked "
"<pricing/pricing_and_faq>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:29
msgid ""
"Sending letters or SMS messages in Odoo requires :doc:`In-App Purchase (IAP) "
"</applications/essentials/in_app_purchase>` credit or tokens."
msgstr ""
"Afsendelse af breve eller SMS-beskeder i Odoo kræver :doc:`In-App Purchase "
"(IAP) </applications/essentials/in_app_purchase>` kredit eller tokens."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:32
msgid ""
"To use a pre-filled template when sending an email or letter, select "
"a :guilabel:`Content Template`. To modify it, click the :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`(internal link arrow)` icon next to the :guilabel:`Content "
"Template` field. If enabled, SMS messages use a specific :guilabel:`Sms "
"Template` field that can be modified by clicking the :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`(internal link arrow)` icon."
msgstr ""
"For at bruge en forudfyldt skabelon ved afsendelse af en e-mail eller et "
"brev skal du vælge en :guilabel:`Indholdsskabelon`. For at ændre den skal du "
"klikke på ikonet :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(internt linkpil)` ved "
"siden af feltet :guilabel:`Indholdsskabelon`. Hvis aktiveret bruger SMS-"
"beskeder et specifikt :guilabel:`Sms-skabelon`-felt, der kan ændres ved at "
"klikke på ikonet :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(internt linkpil)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:38
msgid ""
"Other options can be enabled in the :guilabel:`Options` section within the "
"specific follow-up level:"
msgstr ""
"Andre muligheder kan aktiveres i sektionen :guilabel:`Indstillinger` inden "
"for det specifikke rykkerniveau:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:40
msgid "Automate the reminder with the :guilabel:`Automatic` option."
msgstr "Automatiser rykkeren med indstillingen :guilabel:`Automatisk`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:41
msgid ":guilabel:`Attach Invoices` that are overdue in the reminder."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Vedhæft fakturaer`, der er overskredet i rykkeren."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:42
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add followers` on the related customer to receive notifications "
"about any email reply made on the reminder's email."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tilføj følgere` på den relaterede kunde for at modtage "
"meddelelser om ethvert e-mail-svar lavet på rykkerens e-mail."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:45
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Activity` tab, enable the option to automatically "
"schedule :doc:`activities </applications/essentials/activities>` when the "
"follow-up level is triggered. Select the :guilabel:`Responsible` user and "
"the :guilabel:`Activity Type`, and enter a :guilabel:`Summary`."
msgstr ""
"Under fanen :guilabel:`Aktivitet` skal du aktivere indstillingen for "
"automatisk at planlægge :doc:`aktiviteter </applications/essentials/"
"activities>`, når rykkerniveauet udløses. Vælg den :guilabel:`ansvarlige` "
"bruger og :guilabel:`aktivitetstypen`, og indtast et :guilabel:`resumé`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:49
msgid ""
"To add a new :guilabel:`Follow-up Level`, click :guilabel:`New` and fill in "
"the fields."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje et nyt :guilabel:`rykkerniveau` skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Ny` og udfylde felterne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:52
msgid ""
"Set a negative number of days to send a reminder before the invoice due date."
msgstr ""
"Indstil et negativt antal dage for at sende en rykker før "
"fakturaforfaldsdatoen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:57
msgid "Invoice follow-ups"
msgstr "Fakturarykker"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:60
msgid ""
"Reconcile all bank transactions before starting the follow-up process to "
"avoid sending reminders for invoices that have already been paid."
msgstr ""
"Afstem alle banktransaktioner, før du starter rykkerprocessen for at undgå "
"at sende rykkere for fakturaer, der allerede er betalt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:63
msgid ""
"To view all overdue invoices, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers "
"--> Invoices`. In the :guilabel:`Invoices` list view, click into the search "
"bar and filter on :guilabel:`Overdue`."
msgstr ""
"For at se alle overskredetfakturaer skal du gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab "
"--> Kunder --> Fakturaer`. I listevisningen :guilabel:`Fakturaer` skal du "
"klikke i søgebjælken og filtrere på :guilabel:`Overskredet`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:69
msgid "Follow-ups for one customer"
msgstr "Rykkere for én kunde"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:71
msgid ""
"For a detailed overview of a customer's invoice follow-up status, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Customers`. Open the "
"customer's form and click the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab. In "
"the :guilabel:`Invoice follow-ups` section, click on the different levels to "
"view the :guilabel:`Follow-up Status` of each level. If actions are needed, "
"click :guilabel:`Overdue Invoices` to have a detailed list of the overdue "
"invoices."
msgstr ""
"For at få en detaljeret oversigt over en kundes fakturaряккerstatus skal du "
"gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Kunder --> Kunder`. Åbn kundens formular "
"og klik på fanen :guilabel:`Regnskab`. I sektionen :guilabel:`Fakturarykker` "
"skal du klikke på de forskellige niveauer for at se :guilabel:`rykkerstatus` "
"for hvert niveau. Hvis der er behov for handlinger, skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Overskredetfakturaer` for at få en detaljeret liste over de "
"overskredetfakturaer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:77
msgid "Additional options can be set:"
msgstr "Yderligere muligheder kan indstilles:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:79
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reminders`: These are either :guilabel:`Automatic` "
"or :guilabel:`Manual`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Påmindelser`: Disse er enten :guilabel:`Automatiske` "
"eller :guilabel:`Manuelle`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:80
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Next reminder`: The date by which the next follow-up actions "
"should be taken is automatically set when follow-ups are processed, but can "
"be manually adjusted if needed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Næste påmindelse`: Datoen for næste opfølgningshandling sættes "
"automatisk, når opfølgninger behandles, men kan justeres manuelt om "
"nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:82
msgid ":guilabel:`Responsible`: The user who handles the follow-up actions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ansvarlig`: Den bruger, der håndterer opfølgningshandlingerne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:84
msgid ""
"To manually send a payment reminder to a customer, click :guilabel:`Send` "
"and select the actions in the :guilabel:`Send and Print` window:"
msgstr ""
"For manuelt at sende en betalingspåmindelse til en kunde skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Send` og vælge handlingerne i vinduet :guilabel:`Send og "
"udskriv`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:87
msgid ":guilabel:`Print`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Udskriv`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:89
msgid ":guilabel:`Sms`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Sms`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:90
msgid ":guilabel:`By post`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Med posten`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:92
msgid ""
"Enable the :guilabel:`Attach Invoices` option and change "
"the :guilabel:`Content Template` if needed. Then, click :guilabel:`Send` "
"or :guilabel:`Send & Print` to send the :ref:`follow-up report <accounting/"
"follow_up/follow-up-report>`."
msgstr ""
"Aktivér indstillingen :guilabel:`Vedhæft fakturaer`, og skift "
":guilabel:`Indholdsskabelon`, hvis det er nødvendigt. Klik derefter på "
":guilabel:`Send` eller :guilabel:`Send og udskriv` for at sende "
":ref:`opfølgningsrapporten <accounting/follow_up/follow-up-report>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:98
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:19
