"To add an API key to a **single** database, connect to the database, enable "
"the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`, click on the user menu, and "
"then :guilabel:`My Profile` / :guilabel:`Preferences`. Under "
"the :guilabel:`Account Security` tab, click on :guilabel:`New API Key`, "
"confirm your password, give a descriptive name to your new key, and copy the "
"API key."
msgstr ""
