#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_carryover.rst:3
msgid "Tax carryover"
msgstr "Fremførsel af moms"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_carryover.rst:5
msgid ""
"When performing tax reports, the **tax carryover** feature allows carrying "
"amounts from one period to another without creating new entries."
msgstr ""
"Ved udarbejdelse af momsrapporter gør funktionen **fremførsel af moms** det "
"muligt at overføre beløb fra en periode til en anden uden at oprette nye "
"posteringer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_carryover.rst:8
msgid ""
"It has been created to meet the legal requirements of specific locations, "
"where amounts must be transferred from period to period (for example, "
"because the total of the line is negative)."
msgstr ""
"Den er oprettet for at opfylde lovkravene på bestemte lokationer, hvor beløb "
"skal overføres fra periode til periode (for eksempel fordi liniens total er "
"negativ)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_carryover.rst:11
msgid ""
"The feature is activated by default in countries where it is required, such "
"as Belgium, France, and Italy. There is no specific configuration required."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen er aktiveret som standard i lande, hvor det er påkrævet, såsom "
"Belgien, Frankrig og Italien. Der kræves ingen specifik konfiguration."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_carryover.rst:14
msgid ""
"Let’s take an example of a Belgian company that created a credit note of 100 "
"for one of their customers. The due tax is 21%."
msgstr ""
"Lad os tage et eksempel med en belgisk virksomhed, der oprettede en "
"kreditnota på 100 til en af deres kunder. Den skyldige moms er 21%."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_carryover.rst:None
msgid "Illustration with a credit note"
msgstr "Illustration med en kreditnota"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_carryover.rst:21
msgid ""
"In this case, as per local regulation, grid 81 of the tax report may contain "
"a negative amount. But it must be declared to the government as zero, and "
"the negative amount should be carried over to the next period."
msgstr ""
"I dette tilfælde kan felt 81 i momsrapporten ifølge lokale regler indeholde "
"et negativt beløb. Men det skal angives til myndighederne som nul, og det "
"negative beløb skal fremføres til næste periode."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_carryover.rst:25
msgid ""
"If we go to :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Reporting --> Tax Report`, a "
"pop-up on line 81 explains that the amount will be carried over in the next "
"period."
msgstr ""
"Hvis vi går til :menuselection:`Regnskab-appen --> Rapportering --> "
"Momsrapport`, forklarer en pop-up på linje 81, at beløbet vil blive fremført "
"i næste periode."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_carryover.rst:None
msgid ""
"pop-up message stating the amount will be carried over to the next period"
msgstr "pop-up-meddelelse om, at beløbet vil blive fremført til næste periode"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_carryover.rst:32
msgid ""
"At the time of the tax closing period, the tax report shows that the amount "
"was carried over from the previous period. It also indicates the amount that "
"will be carried over to this line in the next period based on the existing "
"transactions and the carryover from the previous period."
msgstr ""
"På tidspunktet for periodens momsafslutning viser momsrapporten, at beløbet "
"blev fremført fra den forrige periode. Den angiver også det beløb, der vil "
"blive fremført til denne linje i næste periode baseret på de eksisterende "
"transaktioner og fremførslen fra den forrige periode."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_carryover.rst:None
msgid "Illustration of the tax return"
msgstr "Illustration af momsangivelsen"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:3
msgid "Tax return (VAT declaration)"
msgstr "Momsangivelse"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:5
msgid ""
"Companies with a registered :abbr:`VAT (Value Added Tax)` number must submit "
"a **tax return** on a monthly or quarterly basis, depending on their "
"turnover and the registration regulation. A tax return - or VAT return - "
"gives the tax authorities information about the taxable transactions made by "
"the company. The **output tax** is charged on the number of goods and "
"services sold by a business, while the **input tax** is the tax added to the "
"price when goods or services are purchased. Based on these values, the "
"company can calculate the tax amount they have to pay or be refunded."
msgstr ""
"Virksomheder med et registreret :abbr:`moms (merværdiafgift)`-nummer skal "
"indsende en **momsangivelse** på månedlig eller kvartalsbasis, afhængigt af "
"deres omsætning og registreringsreglerne. En momsangivelse giver "
"skattemyndighederne oplysninger om de momspligtige transaktioner, som "
"virksomheden har foretaget. **Udgående moms** opkræves af antallet af varer "
"og tjenesteydelser, der sælges af en virksomhed, mens **indgående moms** er "
"den moms, der lægges til prisen, når varer eller tjenesteydelser købes. "
"Baseret på disse værdier kan virksomheden beregne det momsbeløb, de skal "
"betale eller få refunderet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:14
msgid ""
"You can find additional information about VAT and its mechanism on this page "
"from the European Commission: `\"What is VAT?\" <https://ec.europa.eu/"
"taxation_customs/business/vat/what-is-vat_en>`_."
msgstr ""
"Du kan finde yderligere oplysninger om moms og dens mekanisme på denne side "
"fra Europa-Kommissionen: `\"What is VAT?\" <https://ec.europa.eu/"
"taxation_customs/business/vat/what-is-vat_en>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:18
msgid ""
"Different contacts sharing the same VAT ID may result in an incorrect VAT "
"report. If your contacts are related (e.g., related partners, divisions "
"within the same company, etc.), consider using :doc:`parent-type and "
"children-type contacts <../../../essentials/contacts>`."
msgstr ""
"Forskellige kontakter, der deler det samme momsnummer, kan resultere i en "
"ukorrekt momsrapport. Hvis dine kontakter er relaterede (f.eks. relaterede "
"partnere, afdelinger inden for samme virksomhed osv.), bør du overveje at "
"bruge :doc:`forældre-type og børne-type kontakter <../../../essentials/"
"contacts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:26
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:237
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:32
msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "Forudsætninger"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:31
msgid "Tax Return Periodicity"
msgstr "Selvangivelse periode"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:33
msgid ""
"The configuration of the **Tax Return Periodicity** allows Odoo to compute "
"your tax return correctly and also to send you a reminder to never miss a "
"tax return deadline."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurationen af **momsangivelsesperioden** gør det muligt for Odoo at "
"beregne din momsangivelse korrekt og også sende dig en påmindelse, så du "
"aldrig går glip af en frist for momsangivelse."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:36
msgid ""
"To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`. "
"Under the :guilabel:`Tax Return Periodicity`, you can set:"
msgstr ""
"For at gøre dette skal du gå til :menuselection:`Bogføring --> "
"Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`. Under :guilabel:`Momsangivelsesperiode` "
"kan du indstille:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:39
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Periodicity`: define here whether you submit your tax return on a "
"monthly or quarterly basis;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Periode`: definer her, om du indsender din momsangivelse "
"månedligt eller kvartalsvis;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:41
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reminder`: define when Odoo should remind you to submit your tax "
"return;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Påmindelse`: definer, hvornår Odoo skal minde dig om at indsende "
"din momsangivelse;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:42
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Journal`: select the journal in which to record the tax return."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kladde`: vælg den kladde, hvor momsangivelsen skal registreres."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:46
msgid ""
"This is usually configured during the :doc:`app's initial set up <../"
"get_started>`."
msgstr ""
"Dette konfigureres normalt under :doc:`appens indledende opsætning <../"
"get_started>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:51
msgid "Tax Grids"
msgstr "Momsrate"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:53
msgid ""
"Odoo generates tax reports based on the :guilabel:`Tax Grids` settings that "
"are configured on your taxes. Therefore, it is crucial to make sure that all "
"recorded transactions use the right taxes. You can see the :guilabel:`Tax "
"Grids` by opening the :guilabel:`Journal Items` tab of any invoice and bill."
msgstr ""
"Odoo genererer momsrapporter baseret på indstillingerne for "
":guilabel:`Momsgitter`, der er konfigureret på dine momssatser. Derfor er "
"det afgørende at sikre, at alle registrerede transaktioner bruger de "
"korrekte momssatser. Du kan se :guilabel:`Momsgittrene` ved at åbne fanen "
":guilabel:`Kladdeposter` på enhver faktura og regning."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:None
msgid "see which tax grids are used to record transactions in Odoo Accounting"
msgstr ""
"se hvilke momsgittre der bruges til at registrere transaktioner i Odoo "
"Bogføring"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:61
msgid ""
"To configure your tax grids, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Taxes`, and open the tax you want to modify. There, you "
"can edit your tax settings, along with the tax grids that are used to record "
"invoices or refunds."
msgstr ""
"For at konfigurere dine momsgittre skal du gå til "
":menuselection:`Bogføring --> Konfiguration --> Moms` og åbne den moms, du "
"vil ændre. Der kan du redigere dine momsindstillinger sammen med de "
"momsgittre, der bruges til at registrere fakturaer eller kreditnotaer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:66
msgid ""
"Taxes and reports are usually already pre-configured in Odoo: a :ref:`fiscal "
"localization package <fiscal_localizations/packages>` is installed according "
"to the country you select at the creation of your database."
msgstr ""
"Moms og rapporter er normalt allerede forudkonfigureret i Odoo: en "
":ref:`fiscal localization-pakke <fiscal_localizations/packages>` installeres "
"i henhold til det land, du vælger ved oprettelsen af din database."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:73
msgid "Close a tax period"
msgstr "Lukke en momsperiode"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:78
msgid "Tax lock date"
msgstr "Momslåsedato"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:80
msgid ""
"Any new transaction whose accounting date prior to the :guilabel:`Lock Tax "
"Return` date has its tax values moved to the next open tax period. This is "
"useful to make sure that no change can be made to a report once its period "
"is closed."
msgstr ""
"Enhver ny transaktion, hvis bogføringsdato er før :guilabel:`Lås "
"momsangivelse`-datoen, får sine momsværdier flyttet til den næste åbne "
"momsperiode. Dette er nyttigt for at sikre, at der ikke kan foretages "
"ændringer i en rapport, når perioden er lukket."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:84
msgid ""
"Therefore, we recommend locking your tax date before working on "
"your :guilabel:`Closing Journal Entry`. This way, other users cannot modify "
"or add transactions that would have an impact on the :guilabel:`Closing "
"Journal Entry`, which can help you avoid some tax declaration errors."
msgstr ""
"Derfor anbefaler vi, at du låser din momsdato, før du arbejder på din "
":guilabel:`Ultimokladde`. På denne måde kan andre brugere ikke ændre eller "
"tilføje transaktioner, der ville have indflydelse på "
":guilabel:`Ultimokladden`, hvilket kan hjælpe dig med at undgå nogle "
"momsangivelsesfejl."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:89
msgid ""
"To check the current :guilabel:`Lock Tax Return` date, or to edit it, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> Lock Dates`."
msgstr ""
"For at kontrollere den aktuelle :guilabel:`Lås momsangivelse`-dato eller for "
"at redigere den skal du gå til :menuselection:`Bogføring --> Bogføring --> "
"Låsedatoer`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:97
msgid ""
"Once all the transactions involving taxes have been posted for the period "
"you want to report, open the :guilabel:`Tax Return` report by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Tax Return`. Select the "
"period you want to declare using the date filter to have an overview of the "
"tax return. Then, click :guilabel:`Closing Entry` to create a tax closing "
"journal entry. Odoo automatically proposes the details of the journal entry. "
"Make any necessary changes and click :guilabel:`Post`."
msgstr ""
"Når alle transaktioner, der involverer moms, er bogført for den periode, du "
"vil rapportere, skal du åbne rapporten :guilabel:`Momsangivelse` ved at gå "
"til :menuselection:`Bogføring --> Rapportering --> Momsangivelse`. Vælg den "
"periode, du vil angive, ved hjælp af datofilteret for at få et overblik over "
"momsangivelsen. Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Ultimopost` for at oprette en "
"momsafstemningskladdepost. Odoo foreslår automatisk detaljerne for "
"kladdeposten. Foretag eventuelle nødvendige ændringer og klik på "
":guilabel:`Bogfør`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:104
msgid ""
"From the report, click :guilabel:`PDF` to download a PDF of the tax return. "
"Alternatively, click the :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`gear`) icon, then "
"click :guilabel:`Download Excel` to download an XLSX of the tax return. To "
"save the report to the Documents app, click the :icon:`fa-cog` "
"(:guilabel:`gear`) icon, then click :guilabel:`Copy to Documents`. Select "
"the format to :guilabel:`Export to`, the :guilabel:`Documents Name`, "
"the :guilabel:`Folder` to store it in, and add any :guilabel:`Tags`."
msgstr ""
"Fra rapporten skal du klikke på :guilabel:`PDF` for at downloade en PDF af "
"momsangivelsen. Alternativt kan du klikke på ikonet :icon:`fa-cog` "
"(:guilabel:`tandhjul`) og derefter klikke på :guilabel:`Download Excel` for "
"at downloade en XLSX af momsangivelsen. For at gemme rapporten i appen "
"Dokumenter skal du klikke på ikonet :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`tandhjul`) og "
"derefter klikke på :guilabel:`Kopier til Dokumenter`. Vælg det format, der "
"skal :guilabel:`Eksporteres til`, :guilabel:`Dokumentnavn`, den "
":guilabel:`Mappe`, det skal gemmes i, og tilføj eventuelle :guilabel:`Tags`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:110
msgid ""
"The report includes all the values to report to the tax authorities, along "
"with the amount to be paid or refunded."
msgstr ""
"Rapporten indeholder alle værdier, der skal rapporteres til "
"skattemyndighederne, samt det beløb, der skal betales eller refunderes."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:114
msgid ""
"If you forgot to lock your tax date before clicking on :guilabel:`Closing "
"Journal Entry`, then Odoo automatically locks your fiscal period on the same "
"date as the accounting date of your entry. This safety mechanism can prevent "
"some fiscal errors, but it is advised to lock your tax date manually before, "
"as described above."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du glemte at låse din skattedato, før du klikkede på "
":guilabel:`Afsluttende bilagspost`, låser Odoo automatisk din "
"regnskabsperiode på samme dato som bogføringsdatoen for din post. Denne "
"sikkerhedsmekanisme kan forhindre nogle regnskabsmæssige fejl, men det "
"anbefales at låse din skattedato manuelt først, som beskrevet ovenfor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:120
msgid ""
"Once the tax report for a period has been generated but not yet posted, "
"additional invoices or bills from that same period can still be posted and "
"included in the closing entry. To do so, click :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Refresh` in the :guilabel:`Proposition of tax closing "
"journal entry`, or click :guilabel:`Closing Entry` again from the tax report."
msgstr ""
"Når momsrapporten for en periode er blevet genereret, men endnu ikke "
"bogført, kan yderligere fakturaer eller regninger fra samme periode stadig "
"bogføres og inkluderes i den afsluttende post. For at gøre dette skal du "
"klikke på :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Opdater` i :guilabel:`Forslag "
"til momsafsluttende bilagspost`, eller klik på :guilabel:`Afsluttende post` "
"igen fra momsrapporten."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:124
msgid ""
"After the tax report has been posted for a period, Odoo locks the period and "
"prevents the creation of new journal entries involving VAT. Any corrections "
"to customer invoices or vendor bills must then be recorded in the following "
"period."
msgstr ""
"Efter at momsrapporten er blevet bogført for en periode, låser Odoo perioden "
"og forhindrer oprettelse af nye bilagsposter, der involverer moms. "
"Eventuelle rettelser til kundefakturaer eller leverandørregninger skal "
"derefter registreres i den følgende periode."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:130
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:151
msgid ":doc:`../get_started`"
msgstr ":doc:`../get_started`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:3
msgid "Year-end closing"
msgstr "Årsafslutning"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:5
msgid ""
"Year-end closing is vital for maintaining financial accuracy, complying with "
"regulations, making informed decisions, and ensuring transparency in "
"reporting."
msgstr ""
"Årsafslutning er afgørende for at opretholde økonomisk nøjagtighed, "
"overholde regler, træffe informerede beslutninger og sikre gennemsigtighed i "
"rapporteringen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:9
msgid ":doc:`Tax return <tax_returns>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Momsangivelse <tax_returns>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:14
msgid "Fiscal years"
msgstr "Finansår"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:16
msgid ""
"By default, the fiscal year is set to last 12 months and ends on December "
"31st. However, its duration and end date can vary due to cultural, "
"administrative, and economic considerations."
msgstr ""
"Som standard er regnskabsåret sat til at vare 12 måneder og slutter den 31. "
"december. Dog kan dets varighed og slutdato variere på grund af kulturelle, "
"administrative og økonomiske hensyn."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:19
msgid ""
"To modify these values, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --"
"> Settings`. Under the :guilabel:`Fiscal Periods` section, change "
"the :guilabel:`Last Day` field if necessary."
msgstr ""
"For at ændre disse værdier skal du gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> "
"Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`. Under "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Regnskabsperioder` skal du ændre "
"feltet :guilabel:`Sidste dag`, hvis det er nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:22
msgid ""
"If the period lasts *more* than or *less* than 12 months, "
"enable :guilabel:`Fiscal Years` and :guilabel:`Save`. Go back to "
"the :guilabel:`Fiscal Periods` section and click :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Fiscal Years`. Then, click :guilabel:`New`, give it "
"a :guilabel:`Name` and both a :guilabel:`Start Date` and :guilabel:`End "
"Date`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis perioden varer *mere* end eller *mindre* end 12 måneder, skal du "
"aktivere :guilabel:`Regnskabsår` og :guilabel:`Gem`. Gå tilbage til "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Regnskabsperioder` og klik på :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Regnskabsår`. Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Opret`, giv det "
"et :guilabel:`Navn` og både en :guilabel:`Startdato` og :guilabel:`Slutdato`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:28
msgid ""
"Once the set fiscal period is over, Odoo automatically reverts to the "
"default periodicity, considering the value specified in the :guilabel:`Last "
"Day` field."
msgstr ""
"Når den indstillede regnskabsperiode er forbi, vender Odoo automatisk "
"tilbage til standardperiodiciteten under hensyntagen til værdien angivet i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Sidste dag`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:34
msgid "Year-end checklist"
msgstr "Tjekliste for årsafslutning"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:39
msgid "Before closure"
msgstr "Før afslutning"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:41
msgid ""
"Before closing a fiscal year, ensure that everything is accurate and up-to-"
"date:"
msgstr ""
"Før du lukker et regnskabsår, skal du sikre, at alt er nøjagtigt og "
"opdateret:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:43
msgid ""
"Make sure all bank accounts are fully :doc:`reconciled <../bank/"
"reconciliation>` up to year-end, and confirm that the ending book balances "
"match the bank statement balances."
msgstr ""
"Sørg for, at alle bankkonti er fuldt ud :doc:`afstemt <../bank/"
"reconciliation>` frem til årets udgang, og bekræft, at de afsluttende "
"bogsaldi matcher bankkontoudtogets saldi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:45
msgid ""
"Verify that all :doc:`customer invoices <../customer_invoices>` have been "
"created and confirmed and that there are no draft invoices."
msgstr ""
"Kontroller, at alle :doc:`kundefakturaer <../customer_invoices>` er blevet "
"oprettet og bekræftet, og at der ikke er nogen kladderfakturaer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:47
msgid ""
"Confirm that all :doc:`vendor bills  <../vendor_bills>` have been created "
"and confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Bekræft, at alle :doc:`leverandørregninger  <../vendor_bills>` er blevet "
"oprettet og bekræftet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:48
msgid ""
"Ensure the accuracy of all :doc:`expenses <../../expenses>` and validate "
"them."
msgstr ""
"Sikr nøjagtigheden af alle :doc:`øvrige omkostninger <../../expenses>` og "
"valider dem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:49
msgid ""
"Check that all :doc:`received payments <../payments>` have been encoded and "
"confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Kontroller, at alle :doc:`modtagne betalinger <../payments>` er blevet "
"registreret og bekræftet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:50
msgid "Close all :ref:`suspense accounts <accounting/journals/bank-cash-cc>`."
msgstr ""
"Luk alle :ref:`mellemregningskonti <accounting/journals/bank-cash-cc>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:51
msgid ""
"Book all :doc:`depreciation <../vendor_bills/assets>` and :doc:`deferred "
"revenue <../customer_invoices/deferred_revenues>` entries."
msgstr ""
"Bogfør alle :doc:`afskrivninger <../vendor_bills/assets>` "
"og :doc:`forudmodtagne indtægter <../customer_invoices/deferred_revenues>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:57
msgid "Closing a fiscal year"
msgstr "Lukning af et regnskabsår"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:59
msgid "Then, to close the fiscal year:"
msgstr "Gør derefter følgende for at lukke regnskabsåret:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:61
msgid ""
"Run a :ref:`tax report <accounting/reporting/tax-report>`, and verify that "
"all tax information is correct."
msgstr ""
"Kør en :ref:`momsrapport <accounting/reporting/tax-report>`, og kontroller, "
"at alle momsoplysninger er korrekte."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:63
msgid ""
"Reconcile all accounts on the :ref:`balance sheet <accounting/reporting/"
"balance-sheet>`:"
msgstr ""
"Afstem alle konti i :ref:`statusopgørelsen <accounting/reporting/balance-"
"sheet>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:65
msgid ""
"Update the bank balances in Odoo according to the actual balances found on "
"the bank statements."
msgstr ""
"Opdater banksaldi i Odoo i henhold til de faktiske saldi, der findes på "
"bankkontoudtogene."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:66
msgid ""
"Reconcile all transactions in the cash and bank accounts by running "
"the :ref:`aged receivables <accounting/reporting/aged-receivable>` "
"and :ref:`aged payables <accounting/reporting/aged-payable>` reports."
msgstr ""
"Afstem alle transaktioner på kasse- og bankkonti ved at køre rapporterne "
"for :ref:`aldersfordelte tilgodehavender <accounting/reporting/aged-"
"receivable>` og :ref:`aldersfordelt gæld <accounting/reporting/aged-"
"payable>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:69
msgid ""
"Audit all accounts, fully understanding all transactions and their nature, "
"including :doc:`loans <../bank/loans>` and :doc:`fixed assets <../"
"vendor_bills/assets>`."
msgstr ""
"Gennemgå alle konti og forstå alle transaktioner og deres karakter fuldt ud, "
"herunder :doc:`lån <../bank/loans>` og :doc:`anlægsaktiver <../vendor_bills/"
"assets>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:71
msgid ""
"Optionally, :ref:`match payments <accounting/payments/payments-matching>` to "
"validate any open vendor bills and customer invoices with their payments. "
"While this step is optional, it could assist the year-end closing process if "
"all outstanding payments and invoices are reconciled, potentially finding "
"errors or mistakes in the system."
msgstr ""
"Valgfrit kan du :ref:`matche betalinger <accounting/payments/payments-"
"matching>` for at validere eventuelle åbne leverandørfakturaer og "
"kundefakturaer med deres betalinger. Selvom dette trin er valgfrit, kan det "
"hjælpe med årsafslutningsprocessen, hvis alle udestående betalinger og "
"fakturaer er afstemt, hvilket potentielt kan afsløre fejl eller mangler i "
"systemet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:76
msgid ""
"Next, the accountant likely verifies balance sheet items and book entries "
"for:"
msgstr ""
"Derefter verificerer bogholderen sandsynligvis statusopgørelsesposter og "
"bogføringer for:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:78
msgid "year-end manual adjustments,"
msgstr "manuelle årsafslutningsjusteringer,"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:79
msgid "work in progress,"
msgstr "igangværende arbejde,"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:80
msgid "depreciation journal entries,"
msgstr "afskrivningsposteringer,"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:81
msgid "loans,"
msgstr "lån,"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:82
msgid "tax adjustments,"
msgstr "momsjusteringer,"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:83
msgid "etc."
msgstr "osv."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:85
msgid ""
"During the year-end audit, the accountant may print paper copies of all "
"balance sheet items (e.g., loans, bank accounts, prepayments, sales tax "
"statements) to compare them against the balances recorded in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Under årsafslutningsrevisionen kan bogholderen udskrive papirkopier af alle "
"statusopgørelsesposter (f.eks. lån, bankkonti, forudbetalinger, "
"momsangivelser) for at sammenligne dem med de saldi, der er registreret i "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:90
msgid ""
"As part of this process, setting a :ref:`Lock Everything <year-end/lock-"
"everything-date>` date to the last day (inclusive) of the preceding fiscal "
"year is good practice. This ensures that journal entries with an accounting "
"date on or before the lock date cannot be created or modified during the "
"audit. Users with *administrator* access rights can still create and edit "
"entries if an exception is configured."
msgstr ""
"Som en del af denne proces er det god praksis at sætte en :ref:`Lås alt "
"<year-end/lock-everything-date>`-dato til den sidste dag (inklusive) i det "
"foregående regnskabsår. Dette sikrer, at bilagsposter med en bogføringsdato "
"på eller før låsedatoen ikke kan oprettes eller ændres under revisionen. "
"Brugere med *administrator*-adgangsrettigheder kan stadig oprette og "
"redigere poster, hvis en undtagelse er konfigureret."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:99
msgid "Lock everything date"
msgstr "Lås alt-dato"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:101
msgid ""
"Setting a lock date prevents modifications to any posted journal entries "
"with an accounting date on or before the lock date. It also prevents posting "
"new entries with an accounting date on or before the lock date. In such "
"cases, the system automatically sets the accounting date to the day after "
"the lock date."
msgstr ""
"Indstilling af en låsedato forhindrer ændringer af alle bogførte "
"bilagsposter med en bogføringsdato på eller før låsedatoen. Det forhindrer "
"også bogføring af nye posteringer med en bogføringsdato på eller før "
"låsedatoen. I sådanne tilfælde indstiller systemet automatisk "
"bogføringsdatoen til dagen efter låsedatoen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:106
msgid ""
"To set a :guilabel:`Lock Everything` date, go to :menuselection:`Accounting "
"--> Accounting --> Lock Dates`. In the :guilabel:`Lock Journal Entries` "
"window, set the :guilabel:`Lock Everything` date and :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"For at indstille en :guilabel:`Lås alt`-dato, gå "
"til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Regnskab --> Låsedatoer`. I "
"vinduet :guilabel:`Lås bilagsposter`, indstil :guilabel:`Lås alt`-datoen "
"og :guilabel:`Gem`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:111
msgid ""
"Users with :guilabel:`Administrator` access rights to the Accounting app can "
"create exceptions. To do so:"
msgstr ""
"Brugere med :guilabel:`Administrator`-adgangsrettigheder til Bogføring-appen "
"kan oprette undtagelser. For at gøre dette:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:114
msgid ""
"After setting the :guilabel:`Lock Everything` date, reopen "
"the :guilabel:`Lock Journal Entries` window and remove the :guilabel:`Lock "
"Everything` date."
msgstr ""
"Efter indstilling af :guilabel:`Lås alt`-datoen skal du genåbne "
":guilabel:`Lås bilagsposter`-vinduet og fjerne :guilabel:`Lås alt`-datoen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:116
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Exception` banner, choose if this exception should be "
"set :guilabel:`for me` (the current user) or :guilabel:`for everyone` and "
"how long it should last."
msgstr ""
"I :guilabel:`Undtagelse`-banneret skal du vælge, om denne undtagelse skal "
"indstilles :guilabel:`for mig` (den aktuelle bruger) eller :guilabel:`for "
"alle`, og hvor længe den skal vare."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:118
msgid "A :guilabel:`Reason` for this exception can be added."
msgstr "En :guilabel:`Årsag` til denne undtagelse kan tilføjes."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:119
msgid ""
"All of this information is logged in the chatter of the :doc:`company record "
"</applications/general/companies>`."
msgstr ""
"Alle disse oplysninger logges i chatteren for :doc:`virksomhedsposten </"
"applications/general/companies>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:123
msgid ""
"To remove the :guilabel:`Lock Everything` date after it has been saved, "
"configure the exception to apply :guilabel:`for everyone` and set the "
"duration to :guilabel:`forever`."
msgstr ""
"For at fjerne :guilabel:`Lås alt`-datoen, efter at den er blevet gemt, skal "
"du konfigurere undtagelsen til at gælde :guilabel:`for alle` og indstille "
"varigheden til :guilabel:`for evigt`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:129
msgid "Current year's earnings"
msgstr "Indeværende års indtjening"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:131
msgid ""
"Odoo uses a unique account type called **current year's earnings** to "
"display the difference between the **income** and **expense** accounts."
msgstr ""
"Odoo bruger en unik kontotype kaldet **indeværende års indtjening** til at "
"vise forskellen mellem **indtægts-** og **udgiftskontiene**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:135
msgid ""
"The chart of accounts can only contain one account of this type. By default, "
"it is a 999999 account named :guilabel:`Undistributed Profits/Losses`."
msgstr ""
"Kontoplanen kan kun indeholde én konto af denne type. Som standard er det en "
"999999-konto med navnet :guilabel:`Ufordelt overskud/underskud`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:138
msgid ""
"To allocate the current year's earnings, create a new miscellaneous entry "
"with a date set to the end of the fiscal year to book them to any equity "
"account."
msgstr ""
"For at allokere indeværende års indtjening skal du oprette en ny diversepost "
"med en dato sat til slutningen af regnskabsåret for at bogføre dem til en "
"vilkårlig egenkapitalkonto."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:141
msgid ""
"Then, verify whether the current year's earnings on the **balance sheet** "
"correctly show a zero balance. If so, a :guilabel:`Hard Lock date` can be "
"set to the last day of the fiscal year in :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Accounting --> Lock Dates`."
msgstr ""
"Kontroller derefter, om indeværende års indtjening på **statusopgørelsen** "
"korrekt viser en nulsaldo. Hvis det er tilfældet, kan en :guilabel:`Hård "
"låsedato` sættes til den sidste dag i regnskabsåret under "
":menuselection:`Bogføring --> Bogføring --> Låsedatoer`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:146
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Hard Lock date` field is irreversible and is intended to "
"ensure data inalterability required to comply with accounting regulations in "
"certain countries. If such compliance is not applicable, setting this field "
"may not be necessary. However, if required, the date should only be set once "
"it is confirmed to be correct, as it **cannot be changed or overridden**, "
"regardless of access rights."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Hård låsedato`-feltet er irreversibelt og er beregnet til at "
"sikre datauforanderlighed, der kræves for at overholde regnskabsregler i "
"visse lande. Hvis en sådan overholdelse ikke er gældende, er det måske ikke "
"nødvendigt at indstille dette felt. Hvis det er påkrævet, bør datoen dog "
"først sættes, når det er bekræftet at være korrekt, da den **ikke kan ændres "
"eller tilsidesættes**, uanset adgangsrettigheder."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:7
msgid ""
"Tax regulations generally require companies to compute tax amounts on sales, "
"keep a record of accumulated tax debit and credit, and periodically file "
"this information in tax returns."
msgstr ""
"Skatteregler kræver generelt, at virksomheder beregner skattebeløb på salg, "
"fører register over akkumuleret skattedebet og -kredit og periodisk "
"indberetter disse oplysninger i selvangivelser."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:11
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Oversigt"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:13
msgid "In general, managing taxes in Odoo involves the following steps:"
msgstr "Generelt involverer håndtering af skatter i Odoo følgende trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:15
msgid ""
"Taxes are added on individual lines of documents created via the Sales, "
"Purchase, Accounting, and Point of Sale apps."
msgstr ""
"Skatter tilføjes på individuelle linjer af dokumenter oprettet via Salg-, "
"Indkøbs-, Regnskabs- og POS-apps."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:17
msgid "Odoo automatically computes tax amounts on the documents."
msgstr "Odoo beregner automatisk skattebeløb på dokumenterne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:18
msgid ""
"On accounting documents, Odoo generates journal items to keep track of tax "
"debit and tax credit."
msgstr ""
"På regnskabsdokumenter genererer Odoo posteringer for at holde styr på "
"skattedebet og skattekredit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:19
msgid ""
"The total base, tax debit, and tax credit for a period can be viewed in the "
"tax return report and used to file a tax return."
msgstr ""
"Den samlede base, skattedebet og skattekredit for en periode kan ses i "
"momsangivelsesrapporten og bruges til at indgive en selvangivelse."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:23
msgid "Taxes on sales and purchases"
msgstr "Skatter på salg og indkøb"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:25
msgid ""
"Most sales and purchase documents have a :guilabel:`Taxes` field where taxes "
"can be applied to individual lines. This includes :doc:`invoices "
"<customer_invoices>` and :doc:`vendor bills <vendor_bills>` in the "
"Accounting app, :doc:`sales quotations <../../sales/sales/sales_quotations>` "
"in the Sales app, and :doc:`purchase orders <../../inventory_and_mrp/"
"purchase/manage_deals/rfq>` in the Purchase app."
msgstr ""
"De fleste salgs- og indkøbsdokumenter har et :guilabel:`Skatter`-felt, hvor "
"skatter kan anvendes på individuelle linjer. Dette "
"inkluderer :doc:`fakturaer <customer_invoices>` og :doc:`kreditorfakturaer "
"<vendor_bills>` i Regnskab-appen, :doc:`salgstilbud <../../sales/sales/"
"sales_quotations>` i Salg-appen og :doc:`indkøbsordrer <../../"
"inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq>` i Indkøbs-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "Adding a 21% tax on an invoice line."
msgstr "Tilføjelse af 21% skat på en fakturalinje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:35
msgid ""
"When adding a product to a sale or purchase line, the taxes :ref:`assigned "
"to the product <taxes/product>` are automatically applied to the line."
msgstr ""
"Når et produkt tilføjes til en salgs- eller indkøbslinje, anvendes de "
"skatter, der er :ref:`knyttet til produktet <taxes/product>`, automatisk på "
"linjen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:38
msgid ""
"In the :doc:`Point of Sale <../../sales/point_of_sale>` app, the "
"taxes :ref:`assigned to the products <taxes/product>` are applied directly "
"to the order and cannot be changed except by a :doc:`fiscal position <taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>`."
msgstr ""
"I appen :doc:`POS <../../sales/point_of_sale>` anvendes de skatter, der "
"er :ref:`tildelt produkterne <taxes/product>`, direkte på ordren og kan ikke "
"ændres undtagen ved en :doc:`skatteposition <taxes/fiscal_positions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:43
msgid "Automatic computation of tax amounts"
msgstr "Automatisk beregning af skattebeløb"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:45
msgid ""
"Applying a tax to a sale or purchase line allows Odoo to automatically "
"compute the tax amount based on the sale or purchase line's subtotal and the "
"tax's configuration. The details of the computation are explained in "
"the :doc:`Tax computation documentation <taxes/tax_computation>`."
msgstr ""
"Anvendelse af en skat på en salgs- eller indkøbslinje gør det muligt for "
"Odoo automatisk at beregne skattebeløbet baseret på salgs- eller "
"indkøbslinjens subtotal og skattens konfiguration. Detaljerne i beregningen "
"forklares i :doc:`dokumentationen for skatteberegning <taxes/"
"tax_computation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "Odoo automatically computes a tax amount for the 21% tax."
msgstr "Odoo beregner automatisk et skattebeløb for skatten på 21%."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:53
msgid "Automatic generation of tax journal items"
msgstr "Automatisk generering af skatteposter"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:55
msgid ""
"Upon applying a tax on an :doc:`invoice <customer_invoices>` or :doc:`vendor "
"bill <vendor_bills>`, a tax payable journal item is automatically generated "
"with the tax amount. This keeps track of the tax debit or credit associated "
"with the transaction."
msgstr ""
"Ved anvendelse af en skat på en :doc:`faktura <customer_invoices>` "
"eller :doc:`leverandørfaktura <vendor_bills>` genereres automatisk en "
"skyldigt skattepost med skattebeløbet. Dette holder styr på skattedebet "
"eller -kredit forbundet med transaktionen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:59
msgid ""
"Furthermore, the tax amount is added to the amount due on the receivable or "
"payable journal item."
msgstr ""
"Desuden lægges skattebeløbet til det skyldige beløb på debitor- eller "
"kreditorposten."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:61
msgid ""
"Finally, :ref:`Tax Grids <tax-returns/tax-grids>` are added both to the "
"automatically created tax payable journal item and to the invoice line on "
"which the tax is applied. These tags are used to retrieve the journal items "
"corresponding to the tax's base and tax amount in the :doc:`Tax Return "
"<reporting/tax_returns>` report."
msgstr ""
"Nakonec jsou :ref:`daňové mřížky <tax-returns/tax-grids>` přidány jak k "
"automaticky vytvořené položce deníku splatné daně, tak k řádku faktury, na "
"kterém je daň aplikována. Tyto štítky se používají k získání položek deníku "
"odpovídajících základu daně a výši daně v sestavě :doc:`daňové přiznání "
"<reporting/tax_returns>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically generates a tax payable journal item for the 21% tax."
msgstr "Odoo genererer automatisk en skyldigt skattepost for skatten på 21%."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:70
msgid ""
"If :doc:`Cash Basis <taxes/cash_basis>` is enabled, upon reconciling the "
"invoice or vendor bill with the payment, an additional journal entry is "
"created to represent the creation of the tax debit or credit at that point "
"in time."
msgstr ""
"Hvis :doc:`likviditetsbaseret skat <taxes/cash_basis>` er aktiveret, "
"oprettes der ved afstemning af fakturaen eller leverandørfakturaen med "
"betalingen en ekstra bilagspost for at repræsentere oprettelsen af "
"skattedebet eller -kredit på det tidspunkt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:75
msgid "Filing tax returns"
msgstr "Indgivelse af skatteangivelser"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:77
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Tax Return <reporting/tax_returns>` report aggregates the base and "
"tax amounts from invoices and vendor bills over a given period and presents "
"it in a format tailored to the :doc:`fiscal localization <../"
"fiscal_localizations>`."
msgstr ""
"Rapporten :doc:`skatteangivelse <reporting/tax_returns>` aggregerer grundlag "
"og skattebeløb fra fakturaer og leverandørfakturaer over en given periode og "
"præsenterer det i et format tilpasset den :doc:`regnskabslokalisering <../"
"fiscal_localizations>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:81
msgid ""
"The amounts presented in the tax return report can be used to complete tax "
"declarations that need to be periodically submitted to the government. In "
"most cases, there is a one-to-one correspondence between the lines of the "
"tax return and the official tax declaration, allowing amounts to simply be "
"copied from one to the other."
msgstr ""
"De beløb, der præsenteres i skatteangivelsesrapporten, kan bruges til at "
"udfylde skatteindberetninger, der periodisk skal indsendes til "
"myndighederne. I de fleste tilfælde er der en en-til-en-sammenhæng mellem "
"linjerne i skatteangivelsen og den officielle skatteindberetning, hvilket "
"gør det muligt blot at kopiere beløbene fra den ene til den anden."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "The base section of the tax return report for Belgium."
msgstr "Grundlagsdelen af skatteangivelsesrapporten for Belgien."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "The tax section of the tax return report for Belgium."
msgstr "Skattedelen af skatteangivelsesrapporten for Belgien."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:95
msgid "Basic tax configuration"
msgstr "Grundlæggende skattekonfiguration"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:97
msgid "Follow these basic steps to set up taxes:"
msgstr "Følg disse grundlæggende trin for at opsætte skatter:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:99
msgid ""
"Enable any relevant :ref:`company-wide options <taxes/configuration/"
"company>`."
msgstr ""
"Aktivér alle relevante :ref:`virksomhedsdækkende indstillinger <taxes/"
"configuration/company>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:100
msgid ""
"Activate any needed :ref:`pre-configured taxes <taxes/list_activation>`."
msgstr ""
"Aktivér alle nødvendige :ref:`prækonfigurerede skatter <taxes/"
"list_activation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:101
msgid "Assign taxes on your :ref:`products <taxes/product>`."
msgstr "Tildel skatter på dine :ref:`produkter <taxes/product>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:106
msgid "Company-wide options"
msgstr "Virksomhedsdækkende indstillinger"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:108
msgid ""
"To access these configuration options, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` and scroll down to :guilabel:`Taxes`."
msgstr ""
"For at få adgang til disse konfigurationsindstillinger skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger` og rulle "
"ned til :guilabel:`Skatter`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:116
msgid ""
"The default :guilabel:`Sales Tax` and :guilabel:`Purchase Tax` are "
"automatically set on products when creating new products."
msgstr ""
"Standard :guilabel:`salgsskat` og :guilabel:`købsmoms` indstilles automatisk "
"på produkter, når der oprettes nye produkter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:119
msgid ""
"If :ref:`Accounting Firms <accounting/fiduciaries>` mode is enabled, the "
"default sales tax is automatically set on new invoice lines, and the default "
"purchase tax is automatically set on new vendor bill lines."
msgstr ""
"Hvis tilstanden :ref:`revisionsvirksomheder <accounting/fiduciaries>` er "
"aktiveret, indstilles standardsalgsskatten automatisk på nye fakturalinjer, "
"og standardkøbsmomsen indstilles automatisk på nye leverandørfakturalinjer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:123
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Prices` can be changed to :guilabel:`Tax Included` to treat all "
"taxes as :ref:`tax included <taxes/included-in-price>` by default. This "
"would be appropriate if all of a company's pricing is done tax-included. If "
"only some of a company's pricing is tax-included, individual taxes can be "
"set as :guilabel:`Tax Included`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Priser` kan ændres til :guilabel:`Inkl. moms` for at behandle "
"alle afgifter som :ref:`inkluderet i prisen <taxes/included-in-price>` som "
"standard. Dette ville være passende, hvis alle virksomhedens priser er "
"inklusive moms. Hvis kun nogle af virksomhedens priser er inklusive moms, "
"kan individuelle afgifter indstilles som :guilabel:`Inkl. moms`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:129
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/eu_distance_selling.rst:3
msgid "EU intra-community distance selling"
msgstr "EU-internt fjernsalg"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:131
msgid ""
"Activate this option if you are based in the EU and sell to consumers in "
"other EU countries to apply local VAT rates."
msgstr ""
"Aktiver denne indstilling, hvis du er baseret i EU og sælger til forbrugere "
"i andre EU-lande for at anvende lokale momssatser."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:135
msgid ":doc:`EU intra-community distance selling<taxes/eu_distance_selling>`"
msgstr ":doc:`EU-fjernsalg inden for fællesskabet<taxes/eu_distance_selling>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:138
msgid "Cash basis"
msgstr "Kontantbasis"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:140
msgid ""
"Activate this option if taxes must be accounted for on a cash rather than "
"accruals basis. Some countries mandate cash basis accounting; in that case, "
"this option will be activated by default by the :doc:`fiscal localization "
"package <../fiscal_localizations>`."
msgstr ""
"Aktiver denne indstilling, hvis afgifter skal bogføres på kontantbasis frem "
"for periodiseringsbasis. Nogle lande kræver regnskab på kontantbasis; i så "
"fald vil denne indstilling være aktiveret som standard af :doc:`skattepakken "
"<../fiscal_localizations>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:145
msgid ":doc:`Cash basis <taxes/cash_basis>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Kontantbasis <taxes/cash_basis>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:150
msgid "Activate pre-configured taxes"
msgstr "Aktiver prækonfigurerede afgifter"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:152
msgid ""
"The list of taxes can be accessed by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Taxes`."
msgstr ""
"Listen over afgifter kan tilgås ved at gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> "
"Konfiguration --> Afgifter`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:155
msgid ""
"Generally, inactive taxes are created for most sales tax rates by "
"the :doc:`fiscal localization <../fiscal_localizations>` package, but only "
"the main tax rate is active by default. To activate an inactive tax, click "
"the toggle in the :guilabel:`Active` column."
msgstr ""
"Generelt oprettes inaktive afgifter for de fleste momssatser "
"af :doc:`skattepakken <../fiscal_localizations>`, men kun hovedmomssatsen er "
"aktiv som standard. For at aktivere en inaktiv afgift skal du klikke på slå "
"til/fra i kolonnen :guilabel:`Aktiv`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:162
msgid "Assign taxes on products"
msgstr "Tildel afgifter på produkter"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:164
msgid ""
"To configure the taxes used for each product, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Products`, select the "
"product to configure, and fill the :guilabel:`Sales Taxes` "
"and :guilabel:`Purchase Taxes` fields. These taxes are automatically applied "
"when adding the product to an invoice, vendor bill, sales order, purchase "
"order, or point of sale order."
msgstr ""
"For at konfigurere de afgifter, der bruges for hvert produkt, skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Kunder --> Produkter`, vælge det produkt, "
"der skal konfigureres, og udfylde felterne :guilabel:`Salgsafgifter` "
"og :guilabel:`Indkøbsafgifter`. Disse afgifter anvendes automatisk, når "
"produktet tilføjes til en faktura, kreditorfaktura, salgsordre, indkøbsordre "
"eller POS-ordre."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:170
msgid ""
"Use the :ref:`Default Taxes <taxes/default>` company-wide setting to "
"automatically fill these fields on new products."
msgstr ""
"Brug virksomhedsindstillingen :ref:`Standardafgifter <taxes/default>` til "
"automatisk at udfylde disse felter på nye produkter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:176
msgid "Advanced tax configuration"
msgstr "Avanceret afgiftskonfiguration"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:178
msgid "The following aspects of a tax can be customized:"
msgstr "Følgende aspekter af en afgift kan tilpasses:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:180
msgid ""
"How the tax :ref:`appears in the backend <taxes/configuration/back-end>`"
msgstr "Hvordan afgiften :ref:`vises i backend <taxes/configuration/back-end>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:181
msgid "How the tax :ref:`appears to customers <taxes/configuration/customer>`"
msgstr ""
"Hvordan afgiften :ref:`vises for kunder <taxes/configuration/customer>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:182
msgid "The details of the :doc:`tax computation <taxes/tax_computation>`"
msgstr "Detaljerne i :doc:`afgiftsberegningen <taxes/tax_computation>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:183
msgid "How tax payable journal items are :ref:`created <taxes/definition-tab>`"
msgstr ""
"Hvordan bogføringsposter for skyldig afgift :ref:`oprettes <taxes/definition-"
"tab>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:184
msgid ""
":doc:`Fiscal positions <taxes/fiscal_positions>` (how to replace a tax by "
"another tax under certain conditions)"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Skattepositioner <taxes/fiscal_positions>` (jak nahradit jednu daň "
"jinou daní za určitých podmínek)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:187
msgid ""
"To open a tax's configuration, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Taxes`, then click the tax name."
msgstr ""
"For at åbne en afgifts konfiguration skal du gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab "
"--> Konfiguration --> Afgifter` og derefter klikke på afgiftens navn."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:193
msgid "Configure backend appearance and availability"
msgstr "Konfigurer backend-udseende og tilgængelighed"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:195
msgid ""
"The following options determine how a tax is displayed to users in the Odoo "
"back-end."
msgstr ""
"Følgende indstillinger bestemmer, hvordan en skat vises for brugere i Odoo "
"backend."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:200
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:158
msgid "Tax name"
msgstr "Skattenavn"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:202
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Tax Name` appears for backend users in the :guilabel:`Taxes` "
"field in :doc:`sales orders <../../sales/sales>`, :doc:`invoices "
"<customer_invoices>`, product forms, etc."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Skattenavn` vises for backend-brugere i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Skatter` i :doc:`salgsordrer <../../sales/"
"sales>`, :doc:`fakturaer <customer_invoices>`, produktformularer osv."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:208
msgid "Tax type"
msgstr "Skattetype"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:210
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Tax Type` determines where the tax is available to be "
"selected."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Skattetype` bestemmer, hvor skatten kan vælges."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:212
msgid "**Sales**: Customer invoices, product customer taxes, etc."
msgstr "**Salg**: Kundefakturaer, produktkundeskatter osv."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:213
msgid "**Purchase**: Vendor bills, product vendor taxes, etc."
msgstr "**Indkøb**: Leverandørfakturaer, produktleverandørskatter osv."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:214
msgid "**None**"
msgstr "**Ingen**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:217
msgid ""
"Use :guilabel:`None` for taxes that you want to include in a :ref:`Group of "
"Taxes <taxes/computation>` but that you do not want to list along with other "
"sales or purchase taxes."
msgstr ""
"Brug :guilabel:`Ingen` til skatter, du vil inkludere i en :ref:`skattegruppe "
"<taxes/computation>`, men som du ikke vil vise sammen med andre salgs- eller "
"indkøbsskatter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:223
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Description` can be edited for the purpose of internal "
"documentation."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Beskrivelse` kan redigeres til intern dokumentation."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:228
msgid "Configure how the tax appears to customers"
msgstr "Konfigurer, hvordan skatten vises for kunder"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:233
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:78
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:106
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:81
msgid "Label on invoices"
msgstr "Etiket på fakturaer"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:235
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Label on Invoices` appears on invoice lines in invoice PDFs "
"and on the customer portal."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Etiket på fakturaer` vises på fakturalinjer i faktura-PDF'er og "
"på kundeportalen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Label on Invoice shows on the invoice line when viewed in the customer "
"portal."
msgstr ""
"Etiketten på faktura vises på fakturalinjen, når den ses i kundeportalen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:244
msgid "Tax group"
msgstr "Skattegruppe"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:246
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Tax Group` is shown in the totals section of the invoice, in "
"invoice PDFs and on the customer portal. Multiple taxes that belong to the "
"same tax group are aggregated together into a single tax amount."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Skattegruppe` vises i totalsektionen på fakturaen, i faktura-"
"PDF'er og på kundeportalen. Flere skatter, der tilhører samme skattegruppe, "
"samles til et enkelt skattebeløb."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Tax Group shows in the totals section when viewed in the customer portal."
msgstr "Skattegruppen vises i totalsektionen, når den ses i kundeportalen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:256
msgid "Configure how tax journal items are created"
msgstr "Konfigurer, hvordan skatteposteringer oprettes"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:258
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Distribution for Invoices` and :guilabel:`Distribution for "
"Refunds` sections control the generation of tax payable journal items in "
"invoices and credit notes, respectively. They also determine which :ref:`tax "
"grids <tax-returns/tax-grids>` are set on invoice lines when this tax is "
"applied."
msgstr ""
"Sekce :guilabel:`Rozdělení pro faktury` a :guilabel:`Rozdělení pro "
"dobropisy` řídí generování položek deníku splatné daně ve fakturách a "
"dobropisech. Také určují, které :ref:`daňové mřížky <tax-returns/tax-grids>` "
"jsou nastaveny na řádcích faktury, když je tato daň aplikována."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:263
msgid ""
"Each of these sections should contain one :guilabel:`Base` line, one or "
"more :guilabel:`% of tax` lines amounting to 100% (e.g. one 100% line, or "
"two 50% lines), and optionally, one or more :guilabel:`% of tax` lines "
"amounting to -100.00%."
msgstr ""
"Hver af disse sektioner skal indeholde én :guilabel:`Basis`-linje, én eller "
"flere :guilabel:`% af skat`-linjer, der udgør 100 % (f.eks. én 100 %-linje "
"eller to 50 %-linjer), og eventuelt én eller flere :guilabel:`% af skat`-"
"linjer, der udgør -100,00 %."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:267
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Base` line can have one or more :guilabel:`Tax Grids` set, "
"which are added to the invoice line on which the tax is applied."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Basis`-linjen kan have én eller flere :guilabel:`Skatterubriker` "
"angivet, som tilføjes til den fakturalinje, som skatten anvendes på."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:270
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`% of tax` lines control the creation of tax payable journal "
"items. The tax amount is distributed according to the percentages on these "
"lines, and each line is then used as a template to create a tax payable "
"journal item with the same :guilabel:`Account` and :guilabel:`Tax Grids`. If "
"the :guilabel:`Account` is not specified, it defaults to the account of the "
"original invoice line on which the tax is applied."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`% af skat`-linjerne styrer oprettelsen af skatteposteringer. "
"Skattebeløbet fordeles i henhold til procenterne på disse linjer, og hver "
"linje bruges derefter som skabelon til at oprette en skattepostering med "
"samme :guilabel:`Konto` og :guilabel:`Skatterubriker`. "
"Hvis :guilabel:`Konto` ikke er angivet, bruges standardkontoen fra den "
"oprindelige fakturalinje, som skatten anvendes på."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:276
msgid "Typical cases include:"
msgstr "Typiske tilfælde omfatter:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:278
msgid ""
"one :guilabel:`100% of tax` line: this is the most common case where the tax "
"amount should appear on a single tax payable journal item."
msgstr ""
"én :guilabel:`100 % af skat`-linje: dette er det mest almindelige tilfælde, "
"hvor skattebeløbet skal vises på en enkelt skattepostering."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:280
msgid ""
"one :guilabel:`100% of tax` and one :guilabel:`-100% of tax` line: this is "
"appropriate if the tax simultaneously generates both a tax debit and a tax "
"credit which cancel each other out (e.g. EU intra-community reverse-charge "
"VAT)."
msgstr ""
"én :guilabel:`100 % af skat`- og én :guilabel:`-100 % af skat`-linje: dette "
"er passende, hvis skatten samtidig genererer både en skattedebet og en "
"skattekredit, der udligner hinanden (f.eks. EU-intrakommunitær omvendt "
"betalingspligtig moms)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:283
msgid ""
"one :guilabel:`50% of tax` line that specifies a tax payable account and "
"another :guilabel:`50% of tax` line that does not specify an account: this "
"is appropriate for partially deductible purchase VAT, where part of the tax "
"must be considered an expense rather than a tax credit asset that can offset "
"tax liability."
msgstr ""
"én :guilabel:`50 % af skat`-linje, der angiver en skattekonto, og en "
"anden :guilabel:`50 % af skat`-linje, der ikke angiver en konto: dette er "
"passende for delvist fradragsberettiget købs-moms, hvor en del af skatten "
"skal betragtes som en udgift snarere end et skattefradragsaktiv, der kan "
"modregne skattepligt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "The Distribution for Invoices of a 21% VAT tax."
msgstr "Fordeling for fakturaer med en moms på 21%."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "The Distribution for Refunds of a 21% VAT tax."
msgstr "Fordeling for kreditnotaer med en moms på 21%."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:295
msgid "Extra taxes"
msgstr "Ekstra skatter"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:297
msgid ""
"\"Extra taxes\" is a broad term referring to additional taxes beyond the "
"standard or basic taxes imposed by governments. These extra taxes can be "
"**luxury** taxes, **environmental** taxes, **import** or **export duties** "
"taxes, etc."
msgstr ""
"\"Ekstra skatter\" er et bredt begreb, der henviser til yderligere skatter "
"ud over de standard- eller basisskatter, som regeringer pålægger. Disse "
"ekstra skatter kan være **luksus**skatter, **miljø**skatter, **import**- "
"eller **eksport**afgifter osv."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:302
msgid ""
"The method to compute these taxes varies across different countries. We "
"recommend consulting your country's regulations to understand how to "
"calculate them for your business."
msgstr ""
"Metoden til at beregne disse skatter varierer på tværs af forskellige lande. "
"Vi anbefaler at konsultere dit lands regler for at forstå, hvordan du "
"beregner dem for din virksomhed."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:305
msgid ""
"To compute an extra tax in Odoo, :ref:`create a tax <taxes/configuration>`, "
"enter a tax name, select a :ref:`Tax Computation <taxes/configuration>`, set "
"an :guilabel:`Amount`, and in the :guilabel:`Advanced Options` tab, "
"enable :guilabel:`Affect Base of Subsequent Taxes`. Then, drag and drop the "
"taxes in the :ref:`order they should be computed <taxes/base-subsequent>`."
msgstr ""
"For at beregne en ekstra skat i Odoo skal du :ref:`oprette en skat <taxes/"
"configuration>`, indtaste et skattenavn, vælge en :ref:`Skatteberegning "
"<taxes/configuration>`, angive et :guilabel:`Beløb` og under "
"fanen :guilabel:`Avancerede indstillinger` aktivere :guilabel:`Påvirk "
"grundlag for efterfølgende skatter`. Træk derefter skatterne i "
"den :ref:`rækkefølge, de skal beregnes i <taxes/base-subsequent>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:311
msgid ""
"In Belgium, the formula to compute an environmental tax is: `(product price "
"+ environmental tax) x sales tax`. Therefore, our environmental tax has to "
"come *before* the sales tax in the computation sequence."
msgstr ""
"V Belgii je vzorec pro výpočet environmentální daně: `(cena produktu + "
"environmentální daň) × daň z prodeje`. Proto musí naše environmentální daň "
"přijít *před* daní z prodeje ve výpočetním pořadí."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:314
msgid ""
"In our case, we created a 5% environmental tax (Ecotax) and put it *before* "
"the Belgian base tax of 21%."
msgstr ""
"V našem případě jsme vytvořili 5% environmentální daň (ekotax) a umístili ji "
"*před* belgickou základní daň 21 %."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:0
msgid "Environmental tax sequence in Belgium."
msgstr "Pořadí environmentální daně v Belgii."

