"Hvis :guilabel:`Included in Price` er :guilabel:`Tax Excluded`, er "
"beregningen :math:`\\text{tax amount} = \\text{sales price} \\times "
"\\text{tax rate}`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:71
