"In the **Expense** app, specify the invoicing policy for each expense "
"category. Navigate to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Configuration --> "
"Expense Categories`. Click on the desired expense category or :doc:`create a "
"new one <expense_categories>`."
msgstr ""
"I **Udgifter**-appen skal du angive faktureringspolitikken for hver "
"udgiftskategori. Naviger til :menuselection:`Udgifter-app --> "
"Konfiguration --> Udgiftskategorier`. Klik på den ønskede udgiftskategori, "
"eller :doc:`opret en ny <expense_categories>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:40
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Invoicing` section, click the radio button next to the "
"desired selection for :guilabel:`Re-Invoice Costs`:"
msgstr ""
