#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:None
msgid "Sample of the Expense Category form in the Expense app."
msgstr "Eksempel på formularen Udgiftskategori i appen Udgifter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:65
msgid "Create an expense"
msgstr "Opret en udgift"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:67
msgid ""
"To re-invoice an expense, first :doc:`create an expense record "
"<log_expenses>`. In the :guilabel:`Customer to Reinvoice` field, use the "
"drop-down menu to select the :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` to add the expense to."
msgstr ""
"For at refakturere en udgift skal du først :doc:`oprette en udgiftspost "
"<log_expenses>`. I feltet :guilabel:`Kunde til refakturering` skal du bruge "
"rullemenuen til at vælge den :abbr:`SO (Salgsordre)`, som udgiften skal "
"tilføjes til."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:72
msgid ""
"Selecting the proper :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` in the :guilabel:`Customer to "
"Reinvoice` field is **critical**, since this is how expenses are "
"automatically invoiced after an expense report is approved."
msgstr ""
"Valg af den korrekte :abbr:`SO (Salgsordre)` i feltet :guilabel:`Kunde til "
"refakturering` er **kritisk**, da det er sådan udgifter automatisk "
"faktureres, efter at en udgiftsrapport er godkendt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:77
msgid ":doc:`Detailed instructions on completing an expense <log_expenses>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Detaljerede instruktioner om udfyldning af en udgift <log_expenses>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:80
msgid "Analytic Distribution"
msgstr "Analytisk fordeling"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:83
msgid ""
"For the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` field to be visible the "
"**Accounting** app must be installed, :guilabel:`Analytic Accounting`, "
"and :guilabel:`Analytic Plans` must be configured. Refer to :doc:`../"
"accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting` for more information."
msgstr ""
"For at feltet :guilabel:`Analytisk fordeling` er synligt, skal appen "
"**Bogføring** være installeret, :guilabel:`Analytisk bogføring` og "
":guilabel:`Analytiske planer` skal være konfigureret. Se :doc:`../accounting/"
"reporting/analytic_accounting` for flere oplysninger."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:87
msgid ""
"As an optional step, select the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` the "
"expense is posted to. Multiple accounts can be selected, if desired."
msgstr ""
"Som et valgfrit trin skal du vælge den :guilabel:`Analytiske fordeling`, som "
"udgiften bogføres til. Der kan vælges flere konti, hvis ønsket."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:None
msgid "Sample of a complete expense form in the Expense app."
msgstr "Eksempel på en komplet udgiftsformular i appen Udgifter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:93
msgid ""
"To add another :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution`, click on the line to "
"reveal the :guilabel:`Analytic` pop-over window. Click :guilabel:`Add a "
"line`, then select the desired :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` from the "
"drop-down field."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje endnu en :guilabel:`Analytisk fordeling` skal du klikke på "
"linjen for at vise pop op-vinduet :guilabel:`Analytisk`. Klik på "
":guilabel:`Tilføj en linje`, og vælg derefter den ønskede "
":guilabel:`Analytiske fordeling` fra rullefeltet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:97
msgid ""
"If selecting more than one :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution`, "
"the :guilabel:`Percentage` fields **must** be modified. By default, both "
"fields are populated with `100%`. Adjust the percentages for all the fields, "
"so the total of all selected accounts equals `100%`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du vælger mere end én :guilabel:`Analytisk fordeling`, **skal** "
"felterne :guilabel:`Procent` ændres. Som standard er begge felter udfyldt "
"med `100%`. Juster procentsatserne for alle felterne, så totalen for alle "
"valgte konti svarer til `100%`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:102
msgid ""
"A painting company agrees to paint an office building that houses two "
"different companies. During the estimate, a meeting is held at the office "
"location to discuss the project."
msgstr ""
"Et malerfirma accepterer at male en kontorbygning, der huser to forskellige "
"virksomheder. Under udarbejdelsen af tilbuddet afholdes et møde på "
"kontorlokationen for at drøfte projektet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:105
msgid ""
"Both companies agree to pay for the travel expenses for the painting company "
"employees. When creating the expenses for the mileage and hotels, **both "
"companies** are listed in the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` line, for "
"50% each."
msgstr ""
"Begge virksomheder accepterer at betale for rejseudgifterne for "
"malerfirmaets medarbejdere. Ved oprettelse af udgifterne til "
"kilometergodtgørelse og hoteller angives **begge virksomheder** i linjen "
":guilabel:`Analytisk fordeling` med 50% hver."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:112
msgid "Create an expense report"
msgstr "Opret en udgiftsrapport"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:114
msgid ""
"After the expenses are created, click :guilabel:`Create report`. Once the "
"expense report is submitted, the :icon:`fa-money` :guilabel:`Sales Orders` "
"and :icon:`fa-file-text-o` :guilabel:`Expenses` smart buttons appear at the "
"top of the expense report. The smart buttons will display the number "
"of :abbr:`SOs (Sales Orders)` and expenses linked to the expense report."
msgstr ""
"Når udgifterne er oprettet, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Opret rapport`. Når "
"udgiftsrapporten er indsendt, vises de smarte knapper :icon:`fa-money` "
":guilabel:`Salgsordrer` og :icon:`fa-file-text-o` :guilabel:`Udgifter` "
"øverst på udgiftsrapporten. De smarte knapper viser antallet af :abbr:`SO'er "
"(Salgsordrer)` og udgifter, der er knyttet til udgiftsrapporten."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:119
msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Submit to Manager` to request approval from the "
"assigned Manager."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na :guilabel:`Odeslat manažerovi`, abyste požádali o schválení "
"přiřazeného manažera."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:122
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Customer to Reinvoice` field can be modified *only* until an "
"expense report is **approved**. After an expense report is approved, "
"the :guilabel:`Customer to Reinvoice` field is no longer able to be modified."
msgstr ""
"Feltet :guilabel:`Kunde til refakturering` kan *kun* ændres, indtil en "
"udgiftsrapport er **godkendt**. Efter at en udgiftsrapport er godkendt, kan "
"feltet :guilabel:`Kunde til refakturering` ikke længere ændres."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:None
msgid "Sample of an expense report in the Expense app."
msgstr "Ukázka výdajového reportu v aplikaci Výdaje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:130
msgid ""
":doc:`Detailed instructions to create and submit an expense report "
"<expense_reports>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Podrobný návod k vytvoření a odeslání výdajového reportu "
"<expense_reports>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:135
msgid "Approve and post expenses"
msgstr "Godkend og bogfør udgifter"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:137
msgid ""
"Before approving an expense report, ensure all the information for every "
"expense line is correct, then click :guilabel:`Approve`."
msgstr ""
"Před schválením výdajového reportu se ujistěte, že všechny informace u "
"každého řádku výdajů jsou správné, poté klikněte na :guilabel:`Schválit`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:None
msgid "The expense report with all the Analytic Distribution lines populated."
msgstr "Výdajový report se všemi vyplněnými řádky analytické distribuce."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:144
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Approve` button **only** appears after an expense report has "
"been :ref:`submitted <expenses/submit>`."
msgstr ""
"Tlačítko :guilabel:`Schválit` se zobrazí **pouze** poté, co byl výkaz výdajů "
":ref:`odeslán <expenses/submit>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:147
msgid ""
"The accounting department is typically responsible for :doc:`posting journal "
"entries <post_expenses>`. To post expenses to an accounting journal, "
"click :guilabel:`Post Journal Entries`. Once an expense report is approved, "
"it can then be posted."
msgstr ""
"Za :doc:`zaúčtování položek deníku <post_expenses>` obvykle odpovídá účetní "
"oddělení. Chcete-li zaúčtovat výdaje do účetního deníku, klikněte na "
":guilabel:`Zaúčtovat položky deníku`. Po schválení výdajového reportu jej "
"lze zaúčtovat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:151
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` is **only** updated *after* the journal entries "
"are posted. Once the journal entries are posted, the expenses now appear on "
"the referenced :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)`."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`SO'en (Salgsordren)` opdateres **kun** *efter*, at "
"kladdeposteringerne er bogført. Når kladdeposteringerne er bogført, vises "
"udgifterne nu på den refererede :abbr:`SO (Salgsordre)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:155
msgid ""
":doc:`Detailed instructions to approve an expense report <approve_expenses>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Podrobný návod ke schválení výdajového reportu <approve_expenses>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:160
msgid "Invoice expenses to the customer"
msgstr "Fakturovat výdaje zákazníkovi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:162
msgid ""
"Once the expense report is approved and the corresponding journal entries "
"are posted, the :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` is automatically updated, allowing "
"the customer to be invoiced. The accounting department is typically "
"responsible for generating the final invoice."
msgstr ""
"Po schválení výdajového reportu a zaúčtování příslušných položek deníku se "
":abbr:`SO (prodejní objednávka)` automaticky aktualizuje, což umožňuje "
"zákazníkovi vystavit fakturu. Za vytvoření konečné faktury obvykle odpovídá "
"účetní oddělení."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:166
msgid ""
"Select the desired expense report, and click the :icon:`fa-"
"money` :guilabel:`Sales Orders` smart button to open the :abbr:`SO (Sales "
"Order)`. The expenses to be re-invoiced now appear on the :abbr:`SO (Sales "
"Order)`."
msgstr ""
"Vyberte požadovaný výdajový report a klikněte na chytré tlačítko :icon:`fa-"
"money` :guilabel:`Prodejní objednávky`, abyste otevřeli :abbr:`SO (prodejní "
"objednávku)`. Výdaje, které mají být znovu fakturovány, se nyní zobrazí na "
":abbr:`SO (prodejní objednávce)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:171
msgid ""
"More than one :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` can be referenced on an expense "
"report. If more than one :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` is referenced, clicking "
"the :icon:`fa-money` :guilabel:`Sales Orders` smart button opens a list "
"displaying all the :abbr:`SOs (Sales Order)` associated with that expense "
"report. Click on a :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` to open the individual :abbr:`SO "
"(Sales Order)` details."
msgstr ""
"Na jeden výdajový report může odkazovat více než jedna :abbr:`SO (prodejní "
"objednávka)`. Pokud je odkazováno více než jedna :abbr:`SO (prodejní "
"objednávka)`, kliknutím na chytré tlačítko :icon:`fa-money` "
":guilabel:`Prodejní objednávky` se otevře seznam zobrazující všechny "
":abbr:`SO (prodejní objednávky)` spojené s tímto výdajovým reportem. "
"Klikněte na :abbr:`SO (prodejní objednávku)`, abyste otevřeli podrobnosti "
"jednotlivé :abbr:`SO (prodejní objednávky)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:178
msgid ""
"A electronics repair company has a large customer base. Their service "
"charges vary depending on the product they service. A technician uses "
"different components depending on the product they service and services five "
"customers per day on average."
msgstr ""
"Firma zabývající se opravami elektroniky má velkou zákaznickou základnu. "
"Poplatky za služby se liší v závislosti na produktu, který opravují. Technik "
"používá různé komponenty v závislosti na produktu, který opravuje, a v "
"průměru obslouží pět zákazníků denně."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:182
msgid ""
"After each job the technician submits an expense and associates the "
"appropriate :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` for each. At the end of the day, the "
"technician selects all of the expenses and creates an expense report for the "
"manager to review and approve."
msgstr ""
"Po každé zakázce technik odešle výdaj a přiřadí odpovídající :abbr:`SO "
"(prodejní objednávku)` pro každou zakázku. Na konci dne technik vybere "
"všechny výdaje a vytvoří výdajový report, který manažer zkontroluje a "
"schválí."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:186
msgid ""
"When the expense report gets created, several :abbr:`SOs (Sales Order)` are "
"linked to it. The :icon:`fa-file-text-o` :guilabel:`Expenses` and :icon:`fa-"
"money` :guilabel:`Sales Orders` smart buttons display the number of linked "
"records on the top of the expense report."
msgstr ""
"Při vytvoření výdajového reportu je k němu připojeno několik :abbr:`SO "
"(prodejních objednávek)`. Chytrá tlačítka :icon:`fa-file-text-o` "
":guilabel:`Výdaje` a :icon:`fa-money` :guilabel:`Prodejní objednávky` "
"zobrazují počet připojených záznamů v horní části výdajového reportu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:0
#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:None
msgid "See the expenses listed on the sales order after clicking into it."
msgstr "Se udgifterne opført på salgsordren efter at have klikket ind på den."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:193
msgid ""
"On the :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` form, the expenses are now line items in "
"the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, with their :guilabel:`Delivered` column "
"filled in, and ready to be invoiced."
msgstr ""
"Na formuláři :abbr:`SO (prodejní objednávky)` jsou nyní výdaje řádkovými "
"položkami na kartě :guilabel:`Řádky objednávky` s vyplněným sloupcem "
":guilabel:`Dodáno` a připravené k fakturaci."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:199
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Create Invoice`, and a :guilabel:`Create invoices` pop-up "
"window appears."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na :guilabel:`Vytvořit fakturu` a zobrazí se vyskakovací okno "
":guilabel:`Vytvořit faktury`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:201
msgid ""
"Select if the invoice is a :guilabel:`Regular invoice`, a :guilabel:`Down "
"payment (percentage)`, or a :guilabel:`Down payment (fixed amount)`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Create Draft Invoice`. A customer invoice draft window "
"displays the products and expenses in the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab."
msgstr ""
"Vyberte, zda má být faktura :guilabel:`Běžná faktura`, :guilabel:`Záloha "
"(procento)`, nebo :guilabel:`Záloha (pevná částka)`, a klikněte na "
":guilabel:`Vytvořit návrh faktury`. Zobrazí se okno návrhu faktury pro "
"zákazníka s produkty a výdaji na kartě :guilabel:`Řádky faktury`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:206
msgid ""
"For an :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` with a product and a expense, if the product "
"has not been delivered to the customer, only the expense is listed in "
"the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab of the invoice. Creating two invoices for "
"one :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` is possible."
msgstr ""
"U :abbr:`SO (prodejní objednávky)` s produktem a výdajem, pokud produkt "
"ještě nebyl zákazníkovi dodán, je na kartě :guilabel:`Řádky faktury` faktury "
"uveden pouze výdaj. Pro jednu :abbr:`SO (prodejní objednávku)` je možné "
"vytvořit dvě faktury."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:210
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm` to change the invoice status "
"from :guilabel:`Draft` to :guilabel:`Posted`."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na :guilabel:`Potvrdit`, čímž změníte stav faktury z "
":guilabel:`Kladde` na :guilabel:`Zaúčtováno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:212
msgid ""
"To email the invoice to the customer, click :guilabel:`Send`. "
"A :guilabel:`Print & Send` pop-up window with a pre-configured email message "
"and a PDF invoice in its body is displayed. The message can be reviewed and "
"modified, if needed."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li odeslat fakturu zákazníkovi e-mailem, klikněte na "
":guilabel:`Odeslat`. Zobrazí se vyskakovací okno :guilabel:`Tisk a odeslání` "
"s předkonfigurovanou e-mailovou zprávou a fakturou ve formátu PDF v jejím "
"těle. Zprávu lze v případě potřeby zkontrolovat a upravit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:216
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Send` to email the invoice to the customer. The pop-up "
"window disappears, and a PDF of the invoice is automatically downloaded for "
"record-keeping and printing purposes."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na :guilabel:`Odeslat` a odešlete fakturu zákazníkovi e-mailem. "
"Vyskakovací okno zmizí a PDF faktura se automaticky stáhne pro účely "
"archivace a tisku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:220
msgid "Invoice payment"
msgstr "Platba faktury"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:222
msgid ""
"Depending on the payment configuration in the **Accounting** app, there are "
"several ways to process payment for an invoice. This workflow incorporates "
"the customer portal and manual verification. The customer is responsible for "
"submitting the invoice payment and the accounting department is responsible "
"for verification."
msgstr ""
"V závislosti na konfiguraci plateb v aplikaci **Bogføring** existuje několik "
"způsobů, jak zpracovat platbu za fakturu. Tento pracovní postup zahrnuje "
"zákaznický portál a manuální ověření. Zákazník je zodpovědný za odeslání "
"platby faktury a účetní oddělení je zodpovědné za ověření."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:228
msgid ""
"For online payments through the customer portal, the :doc:`Invoice Online "
"Payment <../../finance/payment_providers>` feature must be enabled on the "
"**Accounting** app. Also a payment method must be set up."
msgstr ""
"Pro online platby prostřednictvím zákaznického portálu musí být v aplikaci "
"**Bogføring** povolena funkce :doc:`fakturace online plateb <../../finance/"
"payment_providers>`. Také musí být nastavena platební metoda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:232
msgid ""
"Navigate to the invoice by clicking :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Expense "
"Reports` and select the desired expense report."
msgstr ""
"Přejděte na fakturu kliknutím na :menuselection:`aplikace Udgifter --> "
"Výkazy výdajů` a vyberte požadovaný výkaz výdajů."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:235
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-money` :guilabel:`Sales Orders` smart button, then "
"select the desired :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)`. Click the :icon:`fa-pencil-"
"square-o` :guilabel:`Invoices` smart button."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na :icon:`fa-money` :guilabel:`Salgsordrer` chytré tlačítko, poté "
"vyberte požadovaný :abbr:`SO (salgsordre)`. Klikněte na :icon:`fa-pencil-"
"square-o` :guilabel:`Faktury` chytré tlačítko."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:238
msgid ""
"After clicking :guilabel:`Send`, the invoice is emailed to the customer and "
"published online on the customer portal. Click :guilabel:`Preview` to see "
"the customer's view of the invoice and payment methods."
msgstr ""
"Po kliknutí na :guilabel:`Odeslat` je faktura odeslána e-mailem zákazníkovi "
"a zveřejněna online na zákaznickém portálu. Klikněte na :guilabel:`Náhled` a "
"zobrazí se zákazníkovo zobrazení faktury a platebních metod."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:242
msgid ""
"Once the customer pays online, the invoice gets an :guilabel:`In Payment` "
"banner. The :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`Payments` and :icon:`fa-"
"money` :guilabel:`Payment Transaction` smart buttons display at the top of "
"the invoice form."
msgstr ""
"Jakmile zákazník zaplatí online, faktura získá banner :guilabel:`V platbě`. "
"Chytrá tlačítka :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`Platby` a :icon:`fa-money` "
":guilabel:`Platební transakce` se zobrazí v horní části formuláře faktury."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:246
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`Payments` smart button to go to "
"the :guilabel:`Pay` form. Click :guilabel:`Validate` to confirm that the "
"invoice payment has been received. The Pay form is automatically updated "
"to :guilabel:`Paid`."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`Platby` chytré tlačítko a přejděte na "
"formulář :guilabel:`Zaplatit`. Klikněte na :guilabel:`Ověřit` a potvrďte, že "
"platba faktury byla přijata. Formulář platby se automaticky aktualizuje na "
":guilabel:`Zaplaceno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:5
msgid "Fiscal localizations"
msgstr "Skattelokalisationer"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:7
msgid ""
"Fiscal localizations are country-specific modules that allow you to be "
"compliant with a country's fiscal requirements. Most of these modules are "
"related to the Accounting app, but they can also be necessary for other apps "
"such as Point of Sale, eCommerce, etc., depending on a country's fiscal "
"requirements."
msgstr ""
"Fiskální lokalizace jsou moduly specifické pro jednotlivé země, které vám "
"umožňují dodržovat fiskální požadavky dané země. Většina těchto modulů se "
"vztahuje k aplikaci Bogføring, ale mohou být také nezbytné pro další "
"aplikace, jako jsou POS, e-Handel atd., v závislosti na fiskálních "
"požadavcích země."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:13
msgid ":doc:`../hr/payroll/payroll_localizations` are documented separately."
msgstr ":doc:`../hr/payroll/payroll_localizations` er dokumenteret særskilt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:20
msgid ""
"Odoo should automatically install the fiscal localization's core modules "
"based on the company's country when the related app is installed. The rest "
"can be manually :ref:`installed <general/install>`. Refer to the :ref:`list "
"of countries <fiscal_localizations/countries-list>` to view the currently "
"supported countries and access their specific documentation."
msgstr ""
"Odoo bør automatisk installere skattelokaliseringens kernemoduler baseret på "
"virksomhedens land, når den relaterede app installeres. Resten "
"kan :ref:`installeres <general/install>` manuelt. Se :ref:`listen over lande "
"<fiscal_localizations/countries-list>` for at se de aktuelt understøttede "
"lande og få adgang til deres specifikke dokumentation."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:26
msgid ""
"Each company in a multi-company environment can use different fiscal "
"localization modules."
msgstr ""
"Hver virksomhed i et multi-virksomhedsmiljø kan bruge forskellige "
"skattelokaliseringsmoduler."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:28
msgid ""
"Verify the right package of modules is installed by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and checking "
"the :guilabel:`Package` field under the :guilabel:`Fiscal Localization` "
"section. Select another one if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Kontrollér, at den korrekte pakke af moduler er installeret ved at gå "
"til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger` og "
"kontrollere feltet :guilabel:`Pakke` under "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Skattelokalisering`. Vælg en anden, hvis det er "
"nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:33
msgid "Selecting another package is only possible if no entry has been posted."
msgstr ""
"Valg af en anden pakke er kun muligt, hvis ingen post er blevet bogført."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:35
msgid ""
"These packages require fine-tuning the chart of accounts, activating the "
"taxes to be used, configuring the country-specific statements and "
"certifications, and sometimes more."
msgstr ""
"Disse pakker kræver finjustering af kontoplanen, aktivering af de skatter, "
"der skal bruges, konfigurering af de landespecifikke opgørelser og "
"certifikater, og nogle gange mere."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:41
msgid "List of countries"
msgstr "Liste over lande"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:43
msgid ""
"Fiscal localization modules are available for the countries listed below."
msgstr ""
"Skattelokaliseringsmoduler er tilgængelige for de lande, der er opført "
"nedenfor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations.rst:46
msgid ""
"New countries are frequently added to this list and Odoo keeps expanding and "
"improving existing localizations and the related documentation."
msgstr ""
"Nye lande tilføjes hyppigt til denne liste, og Odoo fortsætter med at udvide "
"og forbedre eksisterende lokaliseringer og den relaterede dokumentation."

