#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:500
msgid ""
"For SME invoices, there are several document types that are classified as "
"**MiPyME**, which are also known as **Electronic Credit Invoice** (or "
"**FCE** in Spanish). This classification develops a mechanism that improves "
"the financing conditions for small and medium-sized businesses, and allows "
"them to increase their productivity, through the early collection of credits "
"and receivables issued to their clients and/or vendors."
msgstr ""
"For SMV-fakturaer findes der flere dokumenttyper, der er klassificeret som "
"**MiPyME**, som også er kendt som **elektronisk kreditfaktura** (eller "
"**FCE** på spansk). Denne klassificering udvikler en mekanisme, der "
"forbedrer finansieringsvilkårene for små og mellemstore virksomheder og "
"giver dem mulighed for at øge deres produktivitet gennem tidlig opkrævning "
"af kreditter og tilgodehavender udstedt til deres kunder og/eller "
"leverandører."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:506
msgid ""
"For these transactions it's important to consider the following requirements:"
msgstr "For disse transaktioner er det vigtigt at overveje følgende krav:"

