"Once payments are created, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> "
"Payments`, select the payments to be included in the batch, and "
"click :guilabel:`Create Batch`. Verify all information is correct and "
"click :guilabel:`Validate`. Once validated, the ABA file is available in the "
"**chatter** on the right."
msgstr ""
"Når betalinger er oprettet, gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Leverandører "
"--> Betalinger`, vælg de betalinger, der skal inkluderes i batchen, og klik "
"på :guilabel:`Opret batch`. Verificer at alle oplysninger er korrekte og "
"klik på :guilabel:`Valider`. Når den er valideret, er ABA-filen tilgængelig "
"i **chatteren** til højre."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:475
msgid ""
"After uploading the file to your bank's portal, an ABA transaction line will "
"appear in your bank feed at the following bank feed iteration. You will need "
"to reconcile it against the **batch payment** made in Odoo."
msgstr ""
