#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:306
msgid "Starshipit shipping"
msgstr "Forsendelse med Starshipit"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:485
msgid ""
"Starshipit is a shipping service operator that facilitates the integration "
"of Australasian shipping couriers with Odoo. Refer to the :doc:`Starshipit "
