#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:496
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:318
msgid "Buy Now, Pay Later solutions"
msgstr "Køb nu, betal senere-løsninger"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:498
msgid ""
"*Buy Now, Pay Later* solutions are popular payment methods for eShops in "
"Australia. Some of these solutions are available via `Stripe <https://"
"stripe.com/en-au/payments/payment-methods>`_ and `AsiaPay <https://"
"www.asiapay.com.au/payment.html#option>`_."
msgstr ""
"*Køb nu, betal senere*-løsninger er populære betalingsmetoder til eShops i "
"Australien. Nogle af disse løsninger er tilgængelige via `Stripe <https://"
"stripe.com/en-au/payments/payment-methods>`_ og `AsiaPay <https://"
"www.asiapay.com.au/payment.html#option>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:503
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:517
msgid ":doc:`Stripe payment provider <../payment_providers/stripe>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Stripe betalingsudbyder <../payment_providers/stripe>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:504
msgid ":doc:`AsiaPay payment provider <../payment_providers/asiapay>`"
msgstr ":doc:`AsiaPay betalingsudbyder <../payment_providers/asiapay>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:507
msgid "POS terminals"
msgstr "POS-terminaler"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:509
msgid ""
"To establish a direct connection between Odoo and a POS terminal in "
"Australia, a **Stripe** payment terminal is required. Odoo supports the "
"**EFTPOS** payment solution in Australia."
msgstr ""
"For at etablere en direkte forbindelse mellem Odoo og en POS-terminal i "
"Australien kræves en **Stripe** betalingsterminal. Odoo understøtter "
"**EFTPOS** betalingsløsningen i Australien."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:513
msgid ""
"A Stripe payment terminal is not required to use Odoo as the main POS "
"system. However, without one, cashiers must manually enter the final payment "
"amount on the terminal."
msgstr ""
"En Stripe betalingsterminal er ikke påkrævet for at bruge Odoo som det "
