msgstr "Intrastat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:174
msgid ""
"You can access Belgian-specific versions of reports by clicking on the "
"**book** icon when on a report and selecting its Belgian version: **(BE)**."
msgstr ""
"Du kan få adgang til belgiskspecifikke versioner af rapporter ved at klikke "
"på **bog**-ikonet, når du er i en rapport, og vælge dens belgiske version: "
"**(BE)**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:None
