#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:81
msgid ""
"The Brazilian localization package ensures compliance with Brazilian fiscal "
"and accounting regulations. It includes tools for managing taxes, fiscal "
"positions, reporting, and a predefined chart of accounts tailored to "
"Brazil’s standards."
msgstr ""
"Den brasilianske lokaliseringspakke sikrer overholdelse af brasilianske "
"skattemæssige og regnskabsmæssige regler. Den inkluderer værktøjer til "
"håndtering af skatter, skattepositioner, rapportering og en foruddefineret "
"kontoplan tilpasset Brasiliens standarder."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:85
msgid ""
"The Brazilian localization package provides the following key features to "
"ensure compliance with local fiscal and accounting regulations:"
msgstr ""
"Den brasilianske lokaliseringspakke giver følgende nøglefunktioner for at "
"sikre overholdelse af lokale skattemæssige og regnskabsmæssige regler:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:88
msgid ""
":ref:`Chart of accounts <localizations/brazil/chart-of-accounts>`: a "
"predefined structure tailored to Brazilian accounting standards"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Kontoplan <localizations/brazil/chart-of-accounts>`: en foruddefineret "
"struktur tilpasset brasilianske regnskabsstandarder"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:90
msgid ""
":ref:`Taxes <localizations/brazil/taxes>`: pre-configured tax rates, "
"including standard VAT, zero-rated, and exempt options."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Skatter <localizations/brazil/taxes>`: prækonfigurerede skattesatser, "
"herunder standardmoms, nulsats og fritagne muligheder."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:92
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:86
msgid ":doc:`Payroll </applications/hr/payroll>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Løn </applications/hr/payroll>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:93
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:50
msgid ":doc:`Reporting <../accounting/reporting>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Rapportering <../accounting/reporting>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:100
msgid ""
"In the :doc:`chart of accounts <../accounting/get_started/"
"chart_of_accounts>`, the accounts are mapped automatically to their "
"corresponding taxes, and the default account payable and account receivable "
"fields."
msgstr ""
"I :doc:`kontoplanen <../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts>` bliver "
"konti automatisk tilknyttet deres tilhørende skatter samt standardfelterne "
"for kreditorkonto og debitorkonto."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:105
msgid ""
"The Brazil chart of accounts is based on the SPED CoA, which provides a "
"baseline of the necessary accounts."
msgstr ""
"Den brasilianske kontoplan er baseret på SPED CoA, som giver en baseline af "
"de nødvendige konti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:113
msgid ""
":doc:`Taxes <../accounting/taxes>` are automatically created and configured "
"when installing the Brazilian localization. Avalara uses some to compute "
"taxes on sales orders or invoices."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Skatter <../accounting/taxes>` oprettes og konfigureres automatisk, "
"når den brasilianske lokalisering installeres. Avalara bruger nogle af dem "
"til at beregne skatter på salgsordrer eller fakturaer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:116
msgid ""
"Taxes used for services must be manually added and configured, as the rate "
"may differ depending on the city where the service is offered."
msgstr ""
"Skatter for ydelser skal tilføjes og konfigureres manuelt, da satsen kan "
"variere afhængigt af den by, hvor ydelsen leveres."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:120
msgid ""
"NFS-e can't be issued for service taxes created manually. "
"To :ref:`electronically send an NFS-e <localizations/brazil/e-invoice-"
"services>`, compute taxes using Avalara."
msgstr ""
"NFS-e kan ikke udstedes for skatter oprettet manuelt. For at :ref:`sende en "
"NFS-e elektronisk <localizations/brazil/e-invoice-services>`, skal du "
"beregne skatter ved hjælp af Avalara."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:124
msgid ""
"Do not delete taxes, as they are used for the AvaTax tax computation. If "
"deleted, Odoo creates them again when used in an |SO| or invoice, computing "
"taxes with AvaTax. However, the account used to register the tax must be "
"reconfigured in the tax's :guilabel:`Definition` tab, under "
"the :guilabel:`Distribution for invoices` and :guilabel:`Distribution for "
"refunds` sections."
msgstr ""
"Slet ikke skatter, da de bruges til AvaTax skatteberegning. Hvis de slettes, "
"opretter Odoo dem igen, når de bruges i en |SO| eller faktura, og beregner "
"skatter med AvaTax. Kontoen, der bruges til at registrere skatten, skal dog "
"omkonfigureres i skattens fane :guilabel:`Definition` under "
"sektionerne :guilabel:`Fordeling for fakturaer` og :guilabel:`Fordeling for "
"kreditnotaer`."

