#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:637
msgid "Point of sale NFC-e"
msgstr "POS NFC-e"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:639
msgid ""
"The NFC-e is a legal document that supports selling goods or merchandise to "
"the final customer. Like the :ref:`NF-e <localizations/brazil/e-invoice-"
"goods-nf-e>`, the electronic customer invoice is also issued in XML file "
"format and has an auxiliary document (DANFC-e) known as the *NFC-e Summary*. "
"This electronic document can be issued through **Odoo Point of Sale**."
msgstr ""
"NFC-e je právní dokument, který podporuje prodej zboží nebo produktů "
"konečnému zákazníkovi. Stejně jako :ref:`NF-e <localizations/brazil/e-"
"invoice-goods-nf-e>` je i elektronická faktura zákazníka vystavena ve "
"formátu XML a má pomocný dokument (DANFC-e) známý jako *Souhrn NFC-e*. Tento "
"elektronický dokument lze vystavit prostřednictvím **Odoo POS**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:644
msgid ""
"Its legal validity is guaranteed by the digital signature and by each "
"Brazilian state's SEFAZ (Secretaria da Fazenda)."
msgstr ""
"Jeho právní platnost je zaručena digitálním podpisem a úřadem SEFAZ "
"(Secretaria da Fazenda) každého brazilského státu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:648
msgid ""
"The :ref:`Avalara integration <localizations/brazil/avatax-account>` "
"operates on a credit-based system. Each operation that involves "
"communication with Avalara consumes one credit. The following operations "
"within the **Point of Sale** (POS) application are subject to credit "
"consumption:"
msgstr ""
"Integrace :ref:`Avalara <localizations/brazil/avatax-account>` funguje na "
"systému kreditů. Každá operace zahrnující komunikaci s Avalarou spotřebuje "
"jeden kredit. Následující operace v aplikaci **POS** podléhají spotřebě "
"kreditů:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:653
msgid "Tax calculation at the time of sale"
msgstr "Beregning af moms på salgstidspunktet"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:654
msgid "Electronic invoice issuance (NFC-e)"
msgstr "Udstedelse af elektronisk faktura (NFC-e)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:657
msgid ""
"Each step is billed separately. For example, calculating taxes and issuing "
"an invoice for the same POS transaction consumes two credits."
msgstr ""
"Hvert trin faktureres særskilt. For eksempel forbruger beregning af moms og "
"udstedelse af en faktura for samme POS-transaktion to kreditter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:661
msgid ":doc:`Point of Sale <../../sales/point_of_sale>`"
msgstr ":doc:`POS <../../sales/point_of_sale>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:668
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the :guilabel:`Brazilian Accounting EDI for "
"POS` (`l10nbr_edi_pos`) module and make sure to activate :doc:`AvaTax <../"
"accounting/taxes/avatax>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Installer <general/install>` modulet :guilabel:`Brazilian Accounting "
"EDI for POS` (`l10nbr_edi_pos`), og sørg for at aktivere :doc:`AvaTax <../"
"accounting/taxes/avatax>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:674
msgid "CSC details"
msgstr "CSC-oplysninger"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:676
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and scroll "
"to the :guilabel:`Taxes` section. In the :guilabel:`NFC-e configuration` "
"section, complete the following CSC (Taxpayer Security Code) fields:"
msgstr ""
"Gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`, og rul "
"ned til sektionen :guilabel:`Moms`. I sektionen :guilabel:`NFC-e-"
"konfiguration` skal du udfylde følgende CSC-felter (Taxpayer Security Code):"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:680
msgid ""
":guilabel:`CSC ID`: The *CSC ID* or *CSC Token* is an identification of the "
"taxpayer security code, which can have 1 to 6 digits and is available on the "
"official website of your state’s Department of Finance (SEFAZ)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`CSC ID`: *CSC ID* eller *CSC Token* er en identifikation af "
"skatteyderens sikkerhedskode, som kan have 1 til 6 cifre og er tilgængelig "
"på den officielle hjemmeside for din stats finansministerium (SEFAZ)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:683
msgid ""
":guilabel:`CSC Number`: The *CSC Number* is a code of up to 36 characters "
"that only you and the Department of Finance know. It is used to generate the "
"QR Code of the NFC-e and ensure the authenticity of the DANFE."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`CSC-nummer`: *CSC-nummeret* er en kode på op til 36 tegn, som kun "
"du og finansministeriet kender. Det bruges til at generere QR-koden for NFC-"
"e og sikre ægtheden af DANFE."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:688
msgid ""
"The information required for these fields can be generated through the SEFAZ "
"website of each Brazilian State by the company's accountant."
msgstr ""
"Oplysningerne, der kræves til disse felter, kan genereres via SEFAZ-"
"hjemmesiden for hver brasiliansk stat af virksomhedens bogholder."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:696
msgid ""
"Access the relevant :doc:`product form in POS <../../sales/point_of_sale/"
"configuration>`, then configure the :ref:`product <localizations/brazil/"
"products>`'s :guilabel:`Brazil Accounting` fields."
msgstr ""
"Åbn den relevante :doc:`produktformular i POS <../../sales/point_of_sale/"
"configuration>`, og konfigurer derefter :ref:`produktets <localizations/"
"brazil/products>` felter under :guilabel:`Brasiliansk regnskab`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:703
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:889
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1132
msgid "Point of sale"
msgstr "POS"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:705
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration --> Settings` and make "
"sure that the relevant Point of Sale is :doc:`selected at the top of the "
"screen <../../sales/point_of_sale/configuration>`. Then, scroll to "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting` section and configure the :guilabel:`Brazilian "
"EDI` fields:"
msgstr ""
"Gå til :menuselection:`POS --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`, og sørg "
"for, at det relevante salgssted er :doc:`valgt øverst på skærmen <../../"
"sales/point_of_sale/configuration>`. Rul derefter til sektionen "
":guilabel:`Bogføring`, og konfigurer felterne under :guilabel:`Brasiliansk "
"EDI`:"

