msgid "If the NFC-e returns an error, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Hvis NFC-e returnerer en fejl, følg disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:765
msgid "Correct the error."
msgstr "Ret fejlen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:766
msgid ""
"Re-issue the NFC-e by clicking the :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`(menu)` icon "
"and selecting :guilabel:`Orders`."
msgstr ""
"Genudsted NFC-e ved at klikke på :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`(menu)` ikonet "
"og vælge :guilabel:`Ordrer`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:768
msgid ""
"Filter the list to show only :guilabel:`Paid` orders and "
"click :guilabel:`Details`. The error is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Filtrér listen til kun at vise :guilabel:`Betalt` ordrer og klik "
"på :guilabel:`Detaljer`. Fejlen vises."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:770
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Send NFC-e`."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Send NFC-e`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:773
msgid ""
"If the error has been corrected and the PoS session is closed, Odoo logs the "
"tax adjustment in the chatter of the related journal entry. The journal "
"entry for the order indicates that the taxes were incorrectly calculated. In "
"this case, reprocessing the NFC-e is required."
msgstr ""
"Hvis fejlen er blevet rettet, og PoS-sessionen er lukket, logger Odoo "
"skattejusteringen i chatteren for den relaterede bilagspostering. "
"Bilagsposteringen for ordren angiver, at skatterne blev beregnet forkert. I "
"dette tilfælde er genbehandling af NFC-e påkrævet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:None
msgid "Point of sale order view form."
msgstr "POS-ordrevisningsformular."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:783
msgid "NFC-e refunds & cancellations"
msgstr "NFC-e refusioner og annulleringer"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:785
msgid ""
":ref:`Refunds can be processed directly in Odoo <pos/refund>`, but "
"*cancellations* must be performed through the official government portal."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Refusioner kan behandles direkte i Odoo <pos/refund>`, men "
"*annulleringer* skal udføres gennem den officielle offentlige portal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:788
msgid ""
"When the process is finalized, the approved return NF-e is created, meaning "
"the **previous NFC-e is canceled**."
msgstr ""
"Når processen er afsluttet, oprettes den godkendte retur-NF-e, hvilket "
"betyder at **den tidligere NFC-e er annulleret**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:None
msgid "Return of Goods NF-e Approved."
msgstr "Retur af varer NF-e godkendt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:795
msgid ""
"SEFAZ only allows cancellation of an NFC-e **within 30 minutes** of its "
"issuance on the SEFAZ website. After this period, a manual refund must be "
"processed, along with the issuance of a *Return of Goods NF-e*."
msgstr ""
"SEFAZ tillader kun annullering af en NFC-e **inden for 30 minutter** efter "
"dens udstedelse på SEFAZ hjemmesiden. Efter denne periode skal en manuel "
"refusion behandles sammen med udstedelse af en *Retur af varer NF-e*."

