#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:1131
msgid ""
"When clients request an electronic invoice, it is possible to select or "
"create the required contact with their fiscal information. When the payment "
"is being made, select the option :guilabel:`Invoice` to generate the "
"document."
msgstr ""
"Når klienter anmoder om en elektronisk faktura, er det muligt at vælge eller "
"oprette den nødvendige kontakt med deres skatteoplysninger. Når betalingen "
"foretages, skal du vælge muligheden :guilabel:`Faktura` for at generere "
"dokumentet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Selection of invoice option at payment."
msgstr "Valg af fakturamulighed ved betaling."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:1139
msgid ""
"For both the electronic receipts and invoices, if the product is not "
"affected by taxes, Odoo detects this and generates the correct type of "
"document for tax-exempt sales."
msgstr ""
"For både de elektroniske kvitteringer og fakturaer, hvis produktet ikke er "
"påvirket af skatter, opdager Odoo dette og genererer den korrekte type "
"dokument til skattefrit salg."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:1143
msgid "Returns"
msgstr "Returneringer"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:1145
msgid ""
"For electronic receipts (not generated for the *Consumidor Final Anónimo*) "
"and electronic invoices, it is possible to manage the process to return "
"products sold in a :abbr:`POS (Point of Sale)` order by selecting "
"the :guilabel:`Refund` button."
msgstr ""
"For elektroniske kvitteringer (ikke genereret for *Consumidor Final "
"Anónimo*) og elektroniske fakturaer er det muligt at håndtere processen for "
"returnering af produkter solgt i en :abbr:`POS (Point of Sale)`-ordre ved at "
"vælge knappen :guilabel:`Kredit`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Refund option in the POS application."
msgstr "Kreditmulighed i POS-applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:1152
msgid ""
"Orders can be searched by the order status or by contact, and be selected "
"for the refund to be based on the client's original order."
msgstr ""
"Ordrer kan søges efter ordrestatus eller efter kontakt og vælges, så "
"kreditnotaen kan baseres på klientens oprindelige ordre."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Selection of order for the refund process."
msgstr "Valg af ordre til kreditprocessen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:1158
msgid ""
"When the return payment is validated, Odoo generates the necessary credit "
"note, referencing the original receipt or invoice, partially or fully "
"cancelling the document."
msgstr ""
"Når returbetalingen valideres, genererer Odoo den nødvendige kreditnota, der "
"refererer til den oprindelige kvittering eller faktura, og delvist eller "
"fuldt ud annullerer dokumentet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:1162
msgid ""
"`Smart tutorial - Electronic invoicing for point of sale <https://"
"www.youtube.com/watch?v=B2XuWmtlmno&t=360s>`_."
msgstr ""
"`Smart tutorial - Elektronisk fakturering til salgssted <https://"
"www.youtube.com/watch?v=B2XuWmtlmno&t=360s>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:1168
msgid "Factoring"
msgstr "Factoring"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:1171
msgid ""
"Make sure the :guilabel:`Chile - Localization: Factoring Extension` "
"(`l10n_cl_edi_factoring`) module is :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Sørg for, at modulet :guilabel:`Chile - Lokalisering: Factoringudvidelse` "
"(`l10n_cl_edi_factoring`) er :ref:`installeret <general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:1174
msgid ""
"**Factoring** is a financial strategy where accounts receivable invoices are "
"sold to a factoring company to receive immediate liquidity (less an agreed "
"commission) before the actual due date. The **AEC (Archivo Electrónico de "
"Cesión)** is the document that formalizes and registers the assignment of a "
"DTE to a third party (Factoring company) through the SII system."
msgstr ""
"**Factoring** er en finansiel strategi, hvor fakturaer med tilgodehavender "
"sælges til et factoringselskab for at modtage øjeblikkelig likviditet (minus "
"en aftalt kommission) før den faktiske forfaldsdato. **AEC (Archivo "
"Electrónico de Cesión)** er det dokument, der formaliserer og registrerer "
"overdragelsen af en DTE til en tredjepart (factoringselskab) gennem SII-"
"systemet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:1179
msgid "**Factoring of sales invoices**:"
msgstr "**Factoring af salgsfakturaer**:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:1181
msgid "*Does not apply to tickets (boletas)*."
msgstr "*Gælder ikke for kvitteringer (boletas)*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:1182
msgid "Can be multi-currency."
msgstr "Kan være i flere valutaer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:1183
msgid "Does not require :abbr:`CAFs (Folio Authorization Code)`."
msgstr "Kræver ikke :abbr:`CAF'er (Folio Authorization Code)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:1184
msgid ""
"Generates an :abbr:`AEC (Archivo Electrónico de Cesión)` for each document "
"that is factored."
msgstr ""
"Genererer en :abbr:`AEC (Archivo Electrónico de Cesión)` for hvert dokument, "
"der er faktoreret."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:1187
msgid ""
"This module supports companies transferring invoice ownership to a third "
