"verifikationscifret til sidst, præfikset med en bindestreg (`-`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:198
msgid ""
":ref:`Fiscal Information fields <localization/colombia/configuration/"
"company>` in the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Skatteoplysningsfelter <localization/colombia/configuration/company>` "
"under fanen :guilabel:`Salg og indkøb`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:206
msgid ""
"Access the product's form via :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> "
"Products` and ensure that either the :guilabel:`UNSPSC Category` field "
"(found in the :guilabel:`Accounting tab`) or the :guilabel:`Internal "
"Reference` field (in the :guilabel:`General Information` tab) is configured."
msgstr ""
"Åbn produktets formular via :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Kunder --> "
"Produkter`, og sørg for, at enten feltet :guilabel:`UNSPSC-kategori` (findes "
"under fanen :guilabel:`Regnskab`) eller feltet :guilabel:`Intern reference` "
"(under fanen :guilabel:`Generelle oplysninger`) er konfigureret."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:215
msgid ""
"To create or modify taxes, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Taxes`, and select the related tax."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette eller ændre skatter skal du gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --"
"> Konfiguration --> Skatter` og vælge den relevante skat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:218
msgid ""
"If sales transactions include products with taxes, configure "
"the :guilabel:`Value Type` field in the :guilabel:`Advanced Options` tab. "
"Retention tax types (:guilabel:`ICA`, :guilabel:`IVA`, :guilabel:`Fuente`) "
"are also included. This configuration is used to display taxes correctly on "
"the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Hvis salgstransaktioner inkluderer produkter med skatter, skal du "
"konfigurere feltet :guilabel:`Værditype` under fanen :guilabel:`Avancerede "
"indstillinger`. Skattetyper for tilbageholdelse "
"(:guilabel:`ICA`, :guilabel:`IVA`, :guilabel:`Fuente`) er også inkluderet. "
"Denne konfiguration bruges til at vise skatter korrekt på fakturaen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:None
msgid "Specific tax configurations per DIAN regulations."
msgstr "Specifikke skattekonfigurationer i henhold til DIAN-regler."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:229
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:86
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:275
msgid "Sales journals"
msgstr "Salgskladder"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:231
msgid ""
"Once the |DIAN| has assigned the official sequence and prefix for the "
"electronic invoice resolution, the sales journals related to the invoices "
"**must** be updated in Odoo. To do so, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals` and select an "
"existing sales journal or create a new one with the :guilabel:`Create` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Når |DIAN| har tildelt den officielle sekvens og præfiks for den "
"elektroniske fakturaresolution, **skal** salgskladderne relateret til "
"fakturaerne opdateres i Odoo. Gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> "
"Konfiguration --> Kladder`, og vælg en eksisterende salgskladde, eller opret "
"en ny med knappen :guilabel:`Opret`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:236
msgid ""
"On the sales journal form, enter the :guilabel:`Journal Name` "
"and :guilabel:`Type`, then set a unique :guilabel:`Short Code` in "
"the :guilabel:`Journals Entries` tab. Then, configure the following data in "
"the :guilabel:`Advanced Settings` tab:"
msgstr ""
"På salgsjournalformularen skal du indtaste :guilabel:`Journalnavn` "
"og :guilabel:`Type`, og derefter angive en unik :guilabel:`Kort kode` under "
"fanen :guilabel:`Journalposteringer`. Konfigurer derefter følgende data "
"under fanen :guilabel:`Avancerede indstillinger`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:240
msgid ":guilabel:`Electronic invoicing`: enable UBL 2.1 (Colombia)."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Elektronisk fakturering`: aktivér UBL 2.1 (Colombia)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:241
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invoicing Resolution`: resolution number issued by |DIAN| to the "
"company via their test set."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Faktureringsbeslutning`: beslutningsnummer udstedt af |DIAN| til "
"virksomheden via deres testsæt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:243
msgid ":guilabel:`Resolution Date`: initial effective date of the resolution."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Beslutningsdato`: beslutningens første ikrafttrædelsesdato."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:244
msgid ":guilabel:`Resolution End Date`: end date of the resolution's validity."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Beslutningens slutdato`: slutdato for beslutningens gyldighed."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:245
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Range of Numbering (minimum)`: first authorized invoice number."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nummereringsområde (minimum)`: første autoriserede fakturanummer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:246
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Range of Numbering (maximum)`: last authorized invoice number."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nummereringsområde (maksimum)`: sidste autoriserede fakturanummer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:247
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Technical Key`: control key received from the |DIAN| portal test "
"set or from their web service in case of the production environment."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Teknisk nøgle`: kontrolnøgle modtaget fra |DIAN|-portalens "
"testsæt eller fra deres webtjeneste i tilfælde af produktionsmiljøet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:250
msgid ""
"When the database is configured for the :ref:`production environment "
"<localization/colombia/einvoice-configuration>`, instead of configuring "
"these fields manually, click the :guilabel:`Reload DIAN configuration` "
"button to obtain the |DIAN| resolution information from the |DIAN| web "
"service."
msgstr ""
"Når databasen er konfigureret til :ref:`produktionsmiljøet <localization/"
"colombia/einvoice-configuration>`, skal du i stedet for at konfigurere disse "
"felter manuelt klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Genindlæs DIAN-konfiguration` "
"for at hente |DIAN|-beslutningsoplysningerne fra |DIAN|-webtjenesten."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:None
msgid "Reload DIAN configuration button in sale journals."
msgstr "Knappen Genindlæs DIAN-konfiguration i salgsjournaler."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:259
msgid ""
"The short code and resolution of the journal **must** match the ones "
"received in the |DIAN| portal test set or from the MUISCA portal."
msgstr ""
"Den korte kode og beslutningen for journalen **skal** matche dem, der er "
"modtaget i |DIAN|-portalens testsæt eller fra MUISCA-portalen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:261
msgid ""
"The :ref:`invoice sequence and prefix <localization/colombia/invoice-"
"creation>` **must** be correctly configured when the first invoice is "
"created. Odoo automatically assigns a prefix and sequence to the following "
"invoices."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Fakturaens sekvens og præfiks <localization/colombia/invoice-"
"creation>` **skal** være korrekt konfigureret, når den første faktura "
"oprettes. Odoo tildeler automatisk et præfiks og en sekvens til de følgende "
"fakturaer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:268
msgid "Purchase journals"
msgstr "Indkøbsjournaler"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:270
msgid ""
"Once the |DIAN| has assigned the official sequence and prefix for the "
"*support document* related to vendor bills, the purchase journals related to "
"their supporting documents need to be updated in Odoo. The process is "
"similar to the configuration of the :ref:`sales journals <localization/"
"colombia/co-journals>`."
msgstr ""
"Når |DIAN| har tildelt den officielle sekvens og præfiks til "
"*supportdokumentet* relateret til kreditorfakturaer, skal indkøbsjournalerne "
"relateret til deres supportdokumenter opdateres i Odoo. Processen ligner "
"konfigurationen af :ref:`salgsjournalerne <localization/colombia/co-"
"journals>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:276
msgid ""
"For more information on support document journals using the Carvajal "
"solution, review the `Documento Soporte - Localización de Colombia video "
"<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UmYsFcD7xzE&list=PL1-"
"aSABtP6ABxZshems3snMjx7bj_7ZsZ&index=8>`_."
msgstr ""
"For mere information om supportdokumentjournaler ved brug af Carvajal-"
"løsningen kan du gennemgå videoen `Documento Soporte - Localización de "
"Colombia <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UmYsFcD7xzE&list=PL1-"
"aSABtP6ABxZshems3snMjx7bj_7ZsZ&index=8>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:285
msgid ""
"The :doc:`chart of accounts </applications/finance/accounting/get_started/"
"chart_of_accounts>` is installed by default as part of the localization "
"module. The accounts are mapped automatically in taxes, default account "
"payable, and default account receivable. The chart of accounts for Colombia "
"is based on the PUC (Plan Unico de Cuentas)."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Kontoplanen </applications/finance/accounting/get_started/"
"chart_of_accounts>` installeres som standard som en del af "
"lokaliseringsmodulet. Kontiene tilknyttes automatisk i skatter, "
"standardkreditorkonto og standarddebitorkonto. Kontoplanen for Colombia er "
"baseret på PUC (Plan Unico de Cuentas)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:295
msgid ""
"The official exchange rate for Colombia is provided by the `Banco de la "
"República <https://suameca.banrep.gov.co/estadisticas-economicas/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Den officielle valutakurs for Colombia leveres af `Banco de la República "
"<https://suameca.banrep.gov.co/estadisticas-economicas/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:298
msgid "To enable automatic exchange rate updates, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"For at aktivere automatiske valutakursopdateringer skal du følge disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:301
msgid ""
"Navigate to the :guilabel:`Currencies` section and "
"enable :guilabel:`Automatic Currency Rates`."
msgstr ""
"Naviger til sektionen :guilabel:`Valutaer` og aktivér :guilabel:`Automatiske "
"valutakurser`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:302
msgid ""
"Ensure that :guilabel:`[CO] Bank of the Republic` is selected as "
"the :guilabel:`Service`."
msgstr ""
"Sørg for, at :guilabel:`[CO] Bank of the Republic` er valgt "
"som :guilabel:`Service`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:303
msgid ""
"Select an :guilabel:`Interval` for how frequently the currency rate should "
"be automatically updated."
msgstr ""
"Vælg et :guilabel:`Interval` for, hvor ofte valutakursen skal opdateres "
"automatisk."

