"Fakturaer` og vælge :guilabel:`Opret`. Konfigurer følgende felter i "
"fakturaformularen:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:342
msgid ":guilabel:`Customer`: customer's information."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Kunde`: kundens oplysninger."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:343
msgid ":guilabel:`Journal`: journal used for electronic invoices."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Journal`: journal, der bruges til elektroniske fakturaer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:344
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Electronic Invoice Type`: Select the type of document. By "
"default, :guilabel:`Factura de Venta` is selected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Elektronisk fakturatype`: Vælg dokumenttypen. Som standard "
"er :guilabel:`Factura de Venta` valgt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:346
msgid ":guilabel:`Invoice Lines`: Specify the products with the correct taxes."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Fakturalinjer`: Angiv produkterne med de korrekte skatter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:349
msgid ""
"When creating the first invoice related to an electronic invoicing journal, "
"it is required to manually change the *sequence* of the invoice to the |"
"DIAN| format: `Prefix + Sequence`."
msgstr ""
"Når du opretter den første faktura relateret til en elektronisk "
"faktureringsjournal, er det nødvendigt manuelt at ændre fakturaens *sekvens* "
"til |DIAN|-formatet: `Præfiks + Sekvens`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:352
msgid "For example, format the sequence from `SETP/2024/00001` to `SETP1`."
msgstr "Formater f.eks. sekvensen fra `SETP/2024/00001` til `SETP1`."

