msgstr "Fanen :guilabel:`DIAN` viser derefter følgende:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:377
msgid ":guilabel:`Signed Date`: timestamp recorded of the XML creation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Underskrevet dato`: registreret tidsstempel for XML-oprettelsen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:378
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Status`: Status result obtained in the |DIAN| response. If the "
"invoice was rejected, the error messages can be seen here."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Status`: statusresultat opnået i |DIAN|-svaret. Hvis fakturaen "
"blev afvist, kan fejlmeddelelserne ses her."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:380
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Testing Environment`: To know if the document sent was delivered "
"to the |DIAN| testing environment."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Testmiljø`: For at vide, om det afsendte dokument blev leveret "
"til |DIAN|-testmiljøet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:382
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Certification Process`: To know if the document was sent as part "
"of the certification process with the |DIAN|."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Certificeringsproces`: For at vide, om dokumentet blev sendt som "
"en del af certificeringsprocessen med |DIAN|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:384
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Download`: To download the sent XML file, even if the |DIAN| "
"result was rejected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Download`: For at downloade den sendte XML-fil, selvom |DIAN|-"
"resultatet blev afvist."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:386
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Fetch Attached Document`: To download the generated attached "
"document file included in the delivered :file:`.zip` file to the client."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Hent vedhæftet dokument`: For at downloade den genererede "
"vedhæftede dokumentfil inkluderet i den leverede :file:`.zip`-fil til "
"klienten."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:None
msgid "EDI document record available in DIAN tab."
msgstr "EDI-dokumentpost tilgængelig i DIAN-fanen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:397
msgid ""
"The process for credit notes is the same as for invoices. To create a credit "
"note with reference to an invoice, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Customers --> Invoices`. On the invoice, click :guilabel:`Add Credit Note`, "
"and complete the following information:"
msgstr ""
"Processen for kreditnotaer er den samme som for fakturaer. For at oprette en "
"kreditnota med reference til en faktura, gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> "
"Kunder --> Fakturaer`. På fakturaen klik på :guilabel:`Tilføj kreditnota`, "
"og udfyld følgende oplysninger:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:401
msgid ":guilabel:`Credit Method`: Select the type of credit method."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Kreditmetode`: Vælg typen af kreditmetode."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:403
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Partial Refund`: Use this option when it is a partial amount."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Delvis refusion`: Brug denne mulighed, når det er et delvist "
"beløb."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:404
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Full Refund`: Use this option if the credit note is for the full "
"amount."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fuld refusion`: Brug denne mulighed, hvis kreditnotaen er for det "
"fulde beløb."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:405
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Full refund and new draft invoice`: Use this option if the credit "
"note is auto-validated and reconciled with the invoice. The original invoice "
"is duplicated as a new draft."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fuld kreditnota og ny kladdefaktura`: Brug denne mulighed, hvis "
"kreditnotaen automatisk valideres og udlignes med fakturaen. Den oprindelige "
"faktura duplikeres som en ny kladde."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:409
msgid ":guilabel:`Reason`: Enter the reason for the credit note."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Årsag`: Angiv årsagen til kreditnotaen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:410
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reversal Date`: Select if you want a specific date for the credit "
"note or if it is the journal entry date."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tilbageførselsdato`: Vælg, om du ønsker en specifik dato for "
"kreditnotaen, eller om det er posteringsdatoen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:412
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Use Specific Journal`: Select the journal for your credit note or "
"leave it empty if you want to use the same journal as the original invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Brug specifik journal`: Vælg journalen til din kreditnota, eller "
"lad den være tom, hvis du vil bruge samme journal som den oprindelige "
"faktura."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:414
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Refund Date`: If you chose a specific date, select the date for "
"the refund."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kreditnotadato`: Hvis du valgte en specifik dato, skal du vælge "
"datoen for kreditnotaen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:416
msgid "Once reviewed, click the :guilabel:`Reverse` button."
msgstr ""
"Når den er gennemgået, skal du klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Tilbagefør`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:423
msgid ""
"The process for debit notes is similar to credit notes. To create a debit "
"note with reference to an invoice, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Customers --> Invoices`. On the invoice, click the :guilabel:`Add Debit "
"Note` button, and enter the following information:"
msgstr ""
"Processen for debetnotaer ligner kreditnotaer. For at oprette en debetnota "
"med reference til en faktura skal du gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> "
"Kunder --> Fakturaer`. På fakturaen skal du klikke på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Tilføj debetnota` og indtaste følgende oplysninger:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:427
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:336
msgid ":guilabel:`Reason`: Type the reason for the debit note."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Årsag`: Indtast årsagen til debetnotaen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:428
msgid ":guilabel:`Debit note date`: Select the specific options."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Debetnotadato`: Vælg de specifikke muligheder."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:429
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Copy lines`: Select this option if you need to register a debit "
"note with the same lines of invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kopiér linjer`: Vælg denne mulighed, hvis du skal registrere en "
"debetnota med samme linjer som fakturaen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:431
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Use Specific Journal`: Select the printer point for your debit "
"note, or leave it empty if you want to use the same journal as the original "
"invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Brug specifik journal`: Vælg printpunktet til din debetnota, "
"eller lad den være tom, hvis du vil bruge samme journal som den oprindelige "
"faktura."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:434
msgid "When done, click :guilabel:`Create Debit Note`."
msgstr "Når du er færdig, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Opret debetnota`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:439
msgid "Support document for vendor bills"
msgstr "Støttedokument til leverandørfakturaer"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:441
msgid ""
"With master data, credentials, and the purchase journal configured for "
"support documents related to vendor bills, you can start using *support "
"documents*."
msgstr ""
"Med stamdata, legitimationsoplysninger og indkøbsjournalen konfigureret til "
"støttedokumenter relateret til leverandørfakturaer kan du begynde at bruge "
"*støttedokumenter*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:444
msgid ""
"Support documents for vendor bills can be created from your purchase order "
"or manually. Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Bills` and "
"fill in the following data:"
msgstr ""
"Støttedokumenter til leverandørfakturaer kan oprettes fra din indkøbsordre "
"eller manuelt. Gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Leverandører --> "
"Fakturaer` og udfyld følgende data:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:447
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:590
msgid ":guilabel:`Vendor`: Enter the vendor's information."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Leverandør`: Indtast leverandørens oplysninger."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:448
msgid ":guilabel:`Bill Date`: Select the date of the bill."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Fakturadato`: Vælg datoen for fakturaen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:449
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Journal`: Select the journal for support documents related to the "
"vendor bills."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Journal`: Vælg journalen til støttedokumenter relateret til "
"leverandørfakturaerne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:450
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invoiced Lines`: Specify the products with the correct taxes."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fakturerede linjer`: Angiv produkterne med de korrekte afgifter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:452
msgid ""
"Once reviewed, click the :guilabel:`Confirm` button. Upon confirmation, an "
"XML file is created and automatically sent to Carvajal."
msgstr ""
"Når den er gennemgået, skal du klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Bekræft`. Ved "
"bekræftelse oprettes en XML-fil og sendes automatisk til Carvajal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:460
msgid ""
"During the XML validation, the most common errors are related to "
"missing :ref:`master data <localization/colombia/master-data>`. In such "
"cases, a validation error message is displayed and sending is blocked."
msgstr ""
"Under XML-valideringen er de mest almindelige fejl relateret til "
"manglende :ref:`masterdata <localization/colombia/master-data>`. I sådanne "
"tilfælde vises en valideringsfejlmeddelelse, og afsendelse blokeres."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:464
msgid ""
"If the invoice was sent and set as *Rejected* by the |DIAN|, the error "
"messages are visible by clicking the :icon:`fa-info-circle` :guilabel:`(info "
"circle)` icon next to the :guilabel:`Status` field in the :guilabel:`DIAN` "
"tab. Using the reported error codes, it is possible to review solutions to "
"apply before re-sending."
msgstr ""
"Hvis fakturaen blev sendt og sat som *Afvist* af |DIAN|, er "
"fejlmeddelelserne synlige ved at klikke på :icon:`fa-info-"
"circle` :guilabel:`(info-cirkel)` ikonet ved siden af "
"feltet :guilabel:`Status` i fanen :guilabel:`DIAN`. Ved hjælp af de "
"rapporterede fejlkoder er det muligt at gennemgå løsninger, der skal "
"anvendes, før der sendes igen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:None
msgid "Example of error messages on rejected invoices."
msgstr "Eksempel på fejlmeddelelser på afviste fakturaer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:472
msgid ""
"After the master data or other issues are corrected, it is possible to "
"reprocess the XML again. Do so by following the :ref:`electronic invoice "
"sending <localization/colombia/send-electronic-invoice>` flow."
msgstr ""
"Efter at masterdata eller andre problemer er rettet, er det muligt at "
"genbehandle XML'en igen. Gør dette ved at følge :ref:`afsendelse af "
"elektronisk faktura <localization/colombia/send-electronic-invoice>` flowet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:484
msgid "Certificado de Retención en ICA"
msgstr "Certificado de Retención en ICA"

