#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:123
msgid ""
"If products have any :doc:`withholding taxes <../accounting/taxes/"
"retention>`, they must be configured on the product form. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Products`. On "
"the :guilabel:`General Information` tab, specify both :guilabel:`Purchase "
"Taxes` and :guilabel:`Profit Withhold`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis produkter har nogen :doc:`indeholdelsesafgifter <../accounting/taxes/"
"retention>`, skal de konfigureres på produktformularen. For at gøre dette, "
"gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Leverandører --> Produkter`. På "
"fanen :guilabel:`Generelle oplysninger` skal du angive "
"både :guilabel:`Købsskatter` og :guilabel:`Fortjenesteindeholdelse`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:133
msgid ""
"To manage taxes, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --"
"> Taxes`. Depending on the tax type, the following options may be required "
