#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/egypt.rst:0
msgid ""
"Your company's products should be coded and matched with their **GS1** or "
"**EGS** codes."
msgstr ""
"Dine virksomheds produkter bør være kodet og matchet med deres **GS1**- "
"eller **EGS**-koder."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/egypt.rst:0
msgid "Tax Codes"
msgstr "Skattekoder"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/egypt.rst:0
msgid ""
"Most of the taxes codes are already configured on Odoo in the :guilabel:`ETA "
"Code (Egypt)` field. We advise you to make sure these codes match your "
"company's taxes."
msgstr ""
"De fleste af skattekoderne er allerede konfigureret i Odoo i "
"feltet :guilabel:`ETA-kode (Egypten)`. Vi anbefaler, at du sikrer dig, at "
"disse koder matcher din virksomheds skatter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/egypt.rst:123
msgid ""
"`Egyptian eInvoicing & eReceipt SDK - Code Tables <https://"
"sdk.preprod.invoicing.eta.gov.eg/codes/>`_"
msgstr ""
