"sdk.preprod.invoicing.eta.gov.eg/codes/>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/egypt.rst:132
msgid ""
"Create a contact and a journal for each branch of your company and configure "
"its ETA settings."
msgstr ""
"Opret en kontakt og en journal for hver filial i din virksomhed, og "
"konfigurer dens ETA-indstillinger."

