"operations, such as B2C and cross-border B2B operations :ref:`(e-reporting) "
"<localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-reporting>`"
msgstr ""
"store virksomheder (GE) og mellemstore virksomheder (ETI) skal sende "
"indenlandske B2B e-fakturaer :ref:`(e-fakturering) <localizations/france/e-"
"invoicing-fac-elec-einvoicing>` og skal indsende data til "
"skattemyndighederne om visse transaktioner, såsom B2C og grænseoverskridende "
"B2B-transaktioner :ref:`(e-rapportering) <localizations/france/e-invoicing-"
"fac-elec-reporting>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:130
msgid ""
"From **September 1, 2027**, every company, including small and medium-sized "
"enterprises (PME) and micro-enterprises are subject to the same :ref:`e-"
"invoicing <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-einvoicing>` "
"and :ref:`e-reporting <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-reporting>` "
"requirements."
msgstr ""
"Fra **1. september 2027** er enhver virksomhed, herunder små og mellemstore "
"virksomheder (PME) og mikrovirksomheder, underlagt de samme krav til :ref:`e-"
"fakturering <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-einvoicing>` og "
":ref:`e-rapportering <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-reporting>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:135
msgid ""
"Odoo is officially certified as a *plateforme agréée* (approved platform) on "
"the e-invoicing network. It supports the receipt of documents in various "
"formats (Facture-X, UBL, and CII) and the sending of documents exclusively "
"in UBL format."
msgstr ""
"Odoo er officielt certificeret som en *plateforme agréée* (godkendt "
"platform) på e-faktureringsnetværket. Platformen understøtter modtagelse af "
"dokumenter i forskellige formater (Factur-X, UBL og CII) og afsendelse af "
"dokumenter udelukkende i UBL-format."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:140
msgid "VAT-exempt transactions under Articles 261-261E are excluded."
msgstr "Momsfritagne transaktioner i henhold til artikel 261-261E er undtaget."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:147
msgid ""
"To activate the e-invoicing and e-reporting features, follow these "
"configuration steps:"
msgstr ""
"For at aktivere e-fakturerings- og e-rapporteringsfunktionerne skal du følge "
"disse konfigurationstrin:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:149
msgid ""
"Make sure the :guilabel:`France - E-Invoicing (Approved Platform)` "
"(`l10n_fr_pdp`) module is :doc:`installed </applications/general/"
"apps_modules>`."
msgstr ""
"Sørg for, at modulet :guilabel:`France - E-Invoicing (Approved Platform)` "
"(`l10n_fr_pdp`) er :doc:`installeret </applications/general/apps_modules>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:151
msgid ""
"In the **Accounting** or **Invoicing** app, go "
"to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`French Electronic Invoicing` section, and "
"click :guilabel:`Activate Electronic Invoicing`."
msgstr ""
"I appen **Bogføring** eller **Fakturering** skal du gå til "
":menuselection:`Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`, rulle ned til sektionen "
":guilabel:`French Electronic Invoicing` og klikke på :guilabel:`Activate "
"Electronic Invoicing`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:154
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Send via French electronic invoicing` window, fill in "
"the :guilabel:`Email` field with the email address of a legal representative "
"and click :guilabel:`Authenticate`:"
msgstr ""
"I vinduet :guilabel:`Send via French electronic invoicing` skal du udfylde "
"feltet :guilabel:`Email` med emailadressen på en juridisk repræsentant og "
"klikke på :guilabel:`Authenticate`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:157
msgid "In the pop-up window, click :guilabel:`Begin authentication`."
msgstr "I pop op-vinduet skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Begin authentication`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:158
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Accessing the legal representatives of your company` "
"window, click :guilabel:`Check status`, then select your name in "
"the :guilabel:`Please select who you are` list, and :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"I vinduet :guilabel:`Accessing the legal representatives of your company` "
"skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Check status`, derefter vælge dit navn på "
"listen :guilabel:`Please select who you are` og klikke på "
":guilabel:`Confirm`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:161
msgid ""
"To verify your identity, click :icon:`oi-launch` :guilabel:`Open "
"authentication page`."
msgstr ""
"For at verificere din identitet skal du klikke på :icon:`oi-launch` "
":guilabel:`Open authentication page`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:162
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Authentication` window, click :guilabel:`Receive a code`, "
"then enter the 5-digit code received by email and :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"I vinduet :guilabel:`Authentication` skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Receive a "
"code`, derefter indtaste den 5-cifrede kode, du har modtaget via email, og "
"klikke på :guilabel:`Confirm`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:164
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Identity verification` window, click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr ""
"I vinduet :guilabel:`Identity verification` skal du klikke på "
":guilabel:`Next`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:165
msgid ""
"To complete verification, click the :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`(plus)` icon "
"under :guilabel:`Add your document here` to upload a copy of your ID card, "
"passport, or residence permit, then click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr ""
"For at fuldføre verificeringen skal du klikke på ikonet :icon:`fa-plus` "
":guilabel:`(plus)` under :guilabel:`Add your document here` for at uploade "
"en kopi af dit ID-kort, pas eller opholdstilladelse, og derefter klikke på "
":guilabel:`Next`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:168
msgid ""
"To electronically sign the :guilabel:`Attestation de désignation de "
"plateforme agréée` (certificate of designation of an approved platform), "
"click :guilabel:`Next` to review it, then click :guilabel:`Next` again and "
"enable both options:"
msgstr ""
"For at underskrive :guilabel:`Attestation de désignation de plateforme "
"agréée` (certifikat for udpegning af en godkendt platform) elektronisk skal "
"du klikke på :guilabel:`Next` for at gennemgå det, derefter klikke på "
":guilabel:`Next` igen og aktivere begge muligheder:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:172
msgid ":guilabel:`I acknowledge having read all the documents`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`I acknowledge having read all the documents`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:173
msgid ""
":guilabel:`I accept the general conditions of use of VIALNIK 360 and the "
"signature certificate`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jeg accepterer de generelle betingelser for brug af VIALNIK 360 "
"og signaturcertifikatet`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:176
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Sign`."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`e-Signatur`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:177
msgid ""
"Once the signature is confirmed, the signed attestation and terms and "
"conditions can be downloaded, if needed."
msgstr ""
"Når signaturen er bekræftet, kan den underskrevne attestation og vilkår og "
"betingelser downloades, hvis det er nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:180
msgid "Authentication is then successful, and the page can be closed."
msgstr "Autentificeringen er herefter vellykket, og siden kan lukkes."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:182
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Send via French electronic invoicing` window, "
"click :guilabel:`Refresh`."
msgstr ""
"I vinduet :guilabel:`Send via fransk elektronisk fakturering` klikkes på "
":guilabel:`Opdater`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:183
msgid ""
"Verify that the :guilabel:`Identifier` field is filled in with "
"your :abbr:`SIREN (Système d'identification du répertoire des entreprises, "
"Business Directory Identification System)` number, enable "
"the :guilabel:`Pilot Phase` option if you are configuring electronic "
"invoicing before September 1, 2026, and click :guilabel:`Validate "
"Registration`."
msgstr ""
"Kontroller, at feltet :guilabel:`Identifikator` er udfyldt med dit "
":abbr:`SIREN (Système d'identification du répertoire des entreprises, "
"virksomhedsregisterets identifikationssystem)`-nummer, aktiver indstillingen "
":guilabel:`Pilotfase`, hvis du konfigurerer elektronisk fakturering før den "
"1. september 2026, og klik på :guilabel:`Valider registrering`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:187
msgid ""
"Your French e-invoicing ID is now ready to send and receive e-invoices and "
"credit notes. Enable the following options, as needed:"
msgstr ""
"Dit franske elektroniske fakturerings-ID er nu klar til at sende og modtage "
"e-fakturaer og kreditnotaer. Aktiver følgende indstillinger efter behov:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:190
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Incoming Invoices Journal`: Automatically set, update if "
"necessary."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Journal for indgående fakturaer`: Indstilles automatisk, opdater "
"om nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:191
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Enable e-reporting & sending of invoices to the PPF`: Enable this "
"option if e-reporting and e-invoicing are :ref:`required for your company "
"<localizations/france/b2b-b2c>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Aktiver e-rapportering og afsendelse af fakturaer til PPF`: "
"Aktiver denne indstilling, hvis e-rapportering og e-fakturering er "
":ref:`påkrævet for din virksomhed <localizations/france/b2b-b2c>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:194
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Participate in the pilot phase`: This option should only be "
"enabled until the pilot phase ends on September 1, 2026."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Deltag i pilotfasen`: Denne indstilling bør kun være aktiveret, "
"indtil pilotfasen slutter den 1. september 2026."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:198
msgid ""
"Changes to enable or disable this option will take effect the following day."
msgstr ""
"Ændringer for at aktivere eller deaktivere denne indstilling træder i kraft "
"dagen efter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:200
msgid ""
":guilabel:`E-Reporting Periodicity`: Set the periodicity of the :ref:`e-"
"reporting <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-reporting>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`E-rapporteringsperiode`: Indstil perioden for :ref:`e-"
"rapportering <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-reporting>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:203
msgid ""
"Registration in the `annuaire de la facturation électronique (electronic "
"invoicing directory) <https://facturation.chorus-pro.gouv.fr/annuaire/#/>`_ "
"is effective the day after the configuration is completed."
msgstr ""
"Registrering i `annuaire de la facturation électronique (elektronisk "
"faktureringsregister) <https://facturation.chorus-pro.gouv.fr/annuaire/#/>`_ "
"træder i kraft dagen efter, at konfigurationen er gennemført."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:208
msgid ""
"To disconnect from the e-invoicing network, click :guilabel:`Remove from "
"Approved Platform`."
msgstr ""
"For at afbryde forbindelsen til e-faktureringsnetværket klikkes på "
":guilabel:`Fjern fra godkendt platform`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:211
msgid ""
"Once registered on the e-invoicing network, users are automatically "
"registered on Peppol. No separate Peppol registration is then needed."
msgstr ""
"Når du er registreret på e-faktureringsnetværket, registreres brugere "
"automatisk på Peppol. Der er derefter ikke behov for separat Peppol-"
"registrering."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:219
msgid ""
"Before sending an e-invoice to a contact, make sure the contact is "
"registered on the e-invoicing network and ready to receive e-invoices. To do "
"so, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Før du sender en e-faktura til en kontakt, skal du sikre dig, at kontakten "
"er registreret på e-faktureringsnetværket og klar til at modtage e-"
"fakturaer. Følg disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:222
msgid ""
"In the **Accounting** or **Invoicing** app, go to :menuselection:`Customers "
"--> Customers` and access the customer's form."
msgstr ""
"I appen **Bogføring** eller **Fakturering** gå til "
":menuselection:`Kunder --> Kunder` og åbn kundens formular."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:224
msgid "Make sure the customer's :guilabel:`Country` is set to `France`."
msgstr "Sørg for, at kundens :guilabel:`Land` er indstillet til `Frankrig`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:225
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab, under the :guilabel:`Misc` section, "
"ensure the :guilabel:`Company ID` field is completed."
msgstr ""
"I fanen :guilabel:`Salg og indkøb` under sektionen :guilabel:`Diverse` skal "
"du sikre dig, at feltet :guilabel:`Virksomheds-ID` er udfyldt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:229
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Company ID` number is then automatically added in "
"the :guilabel:`France FRCTC Electronic Address` field in "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting tab`, under the :guilabel:`Customer Invoices` "
"section."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Virksomheds-ID`-nummeret tilføjes derefter automatisk i feltet "
":guilabel:`Fransk FRCTC elektronisk adresse` i fanen :guilabel:`Bogføring` "
"under sektionen :guilabel:`Kundefakturaer`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:233
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Accounting tab`, under the :guilabel:`Customer Invoices` "
"section, click :guilabel:`Verify` to verify the contact. If the contact is "
"found on the e-invoicing network, :guilabel:`Partner is in the annuaire` is "
"shown."
msgstr ""
"Under fanen :guilabel:`Bogføring` i sektionen :guilabel:`Kundefakturaer` "
"skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Verificer` for at verificere kontakten. Hvis "
"kontakten findes på e-fakturanetværket, vises :guilabel:`Partner is in the "
"annuaire`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:238
msgid ""
"Set the preferred :ref:`Invoice sending <accounting/invoice/sending>` method "
"for a customer to :guilabel:`French E-Invoicing` in the :guilabel:`Customer "
"Invoices` section of the customer form's :guilabel:`Accounting` tab."
msgstr ""
"Indstil den foretrukne :ref:`afsendelsesmetode for fakturaer <accounting/"
"invoice/sending>` for en kunde til :guilabel:`French E-Invoicing` i "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Kundefakturaer` under fanen :guilabel:`Bogføring` på "
"kundeformularen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:247
msgid ""
"E-invoices for domestic B2B operations can be :ref:`sent <localizations/"
"france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-invoices>` and :ref:`received <localizations/"
"france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-bills>` via the e-invoicing network."
msgstr ""
"E-fakturaer for indenlandske B2B-transaktioner kan :ref:`sendes "
"<localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-invoices>` og :ref:`modtages "
"<localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-bills>` via e-fakturanetværket."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:252
msgid ""
"B2C invoices or cross-border B2B invoices cannot be sent via the e-invoicing "
"network. However, once confirmed in Odoo, these invoices are submitted to "
"the tax authorities via :ref:`e-reporting <localizations/france/e-invoicing-"
"fac-elec-reporting>`."
msgstr ""
"B2C-fakturaer eller grænseoverskridende B2B-fakturaer kan ikke sendes via e-"
"fakturanetværket. Når disse fakturaer er bekræftet i Odoo, indsendes de dog "
"til skattemyndighederne via :ref:`e-rapportering <localizations/france/e-"
"invoicing-fac-elec-reporting>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:255
msgid ""
"Domestic B2B invoices that are paid in cash are also submitted to the tax "
"authorities via :ref:`e-reporting <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-"
"reporting>`."
msgstr ""
"Indenlandske B2B-fakturaer, der betales kontant, indsendes også til "
"skattemyndighederne via :ref:`e-rapportering <localizations/france/e-"
"invoicing-fac-elec-reporting>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:261
msgid "Send customer invoices"
msgstr "Send kundefakturaer"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:263
msgid ""
"Posted domestic B2B invoices to be sent via the e-invoicing network are "
"marked as :guilabel:`Ready to send` in the invoice's :guilabel:`E-invoicing "
"Status` field."
msgstr ""
"Bogførte indenlandske B2B-fakturaer, der skal sendes via e-fakturanetværket, "
"er markeret som :guilabel:`Klar til afsendelse` i fakturaens felt "
":guilabel:`E-Invoicing Status`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:267
msgid ""
"All invoices that are ready to be sent via the e-invoicing network can be "
"viewed in the following ways:"
msgstr ""
"Alle fakturaer, der er klar til at blive sendt via e-fakturanetværket, kan "
"ses på følgende måder:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:270
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Invoices` list view, use the :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` "
"(:guilabel:`adjust settings`) button to add the :guilabel:`E-invoicing "
"Status` column or apply the :guilabel:`E-Invoicing Ready` filter in the "
"search bar."
msgstr ""
"I listevisningen :guilabel:`Fakturaer` skal du bruge knappen :icon:`oi-"
"settings-adjust` (:guilabel:`juster indstillinger`) til at tilføje kolonnen "
":guilabel:`E-Invoicing Status` eller anvende filteret :guilabel:`E-Invoicing "
"Ready` i søgefeltet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:273
msgid ""
"In the Accounting dashboard, click :guilabel:`E-invoicing ready invoices` on "
"the relevant sales journal."
msgstr ""
"I Dashboard for Bogføring skal du klikke på :guilabel:`E-invoicing ready "
"invoices` på den relevante salgskladde."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:276
msgid ""
"Once an invoice is :ref:`created <accounting/invoice/creation>` "
"and :ref:`confirmed <accounting/invoice/confirmation>`, follow these steps "
"to send the invoice to the customer via the e-invoicing network:"
msgstr ""
"Når en faktura er :ref:`oprettet <accounting/invoice/creation>` og "
":ref:`bekræftet <accounting/invoice/confirmation>`, skal du følge disse trin "
"for at sende fakturaen til kunden via e-fakturanetværket:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:280
msgid ""
"Check that the :ref:`contact is registered in the electronic invoicing "
"directory <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-contacts>`."
msgstr ""
"Kontroller, at :ref:`kontakten er registreret i kataloget for elektronisk "
"fakturering <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-contacts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:282
msgid ""
"Make sure each invoice line includes at least one product or label, and "
"exactly one tax."
msgstr ""
"Sørg for, at hver fakturalinje indeholder mindst ét produkt eller en etiket "
"og præcis én moms."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:283
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Send` on the confirmed invoice form."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Send` på den bekræftede fakturaformular."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:284
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Print & Send` window, make sure the :guilabel:`French E-"
"Invoicing` option is enabled and click :guilabel:`Send`."
msgstr ""
"I vinduet :guilabel:`Udskriv & Send` skal du sikre dig, at indstillingen "
":guilabel:`French E-Invoicing` er aktiveret, og klik på :guilabel:`Send`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:288
msgid ""
"To avoid selecting the sending method each time, verify that "
"a :ref:`preferred method has been set on the contact form <localizations/"
"france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-contacts>`."
msgstr ""
"For at undgå at vælge afsendelsesmetoden hver gang skal du verificere, at "
":ref:`en foretrukken metode er blevet indstillet på kontaktformularen "
"<localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-contacts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:290
msgid ""
":ref:`Multiple invoices <accounting/invoice/sending-multiple-invoices>` can "
"also be sent in batches via the e-invoicing network."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Flere fakturaer <accounting/invoice/sending-multiple-invoices>` kan "
"også sendes i batches via e-fakturanetværket."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:293
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`French Invoicing Info` section of the :guilabel:`Other "
"Info` tab, the :guilabel:`E-Invoicing Status` is updated to :guilabel:`Done` "
"once the invoices have been successfully delivered to the contact’s approved "
"platform."
msgstr ""
"I sektionen :guilabel:`French Invoicing Info` under fanen :guilabel:`Andet "
"Info` opdateres :guilabel:`E-Invoicing Status` til :guilabel:`Udført`, når "
"fakturaerne er blevet leveret til kontaktens godkendte platform."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:298
msgid ""
"The invoice delivery status is also displayed in the :guilabel:`E-Invoicing "
"Status` column of the :guilabel:`Invoices` list view."
msgstr ""
"Fakturaens leveringsstatus vises også i kolonnen :guilabel:`E-Invoicing "
"Status` i listevisningen :guilabel:`Fakturaer`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:300
msgid ""
"If an error occurs during the tax authority's delivery of the invoice, the "
"error details are displayed in the invoice's chatter."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der opstår en fejl under skattemyndighedens levering af fakturaen, "
"vises fejldetaljerne i fakturaens chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:304
msgid ""
"To manually trigger the scheduled action used to check the delivery status "
"of invoices, go to the Accounting dashboard and click :guilabel:`Fetch E-"
"invoicing Status` on the corresponding sales journal."
msgstr ""
"For manuelt at udløse den planlagte handling, der bruges til at kontrollere "
"leveringsstatus for fakturaer, gå til Bogføring-dashboardet og klik "
":guilabel:`Hent E-faktureringsstatus` på den tilsvarende salgsjournal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:309
msgid ""
"For domestic B2B invoices, the :guilabel:`Reset to Draft` option is not "
"available for invoices that have already been sent via :ref:`e-reporting "
"<localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-reporting>`."
msgstr ""
"For indenlandske B2B-fakturaer er :guilabel:`Nulstil til kladde`-muligheden "
"ikke tilgængelig for fakturaer, der allerede er sendt via :ref:`e-"
"rapportering <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-reporting>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:318
msgid ""
"Odoo checks for new documents received via the e-invoicing network multiple "
"times a day, and automatically imports vendor bills into the purchase "
"journal set in the :guilabel:`Incoming Invoices Journal` field "
"during :ref:`configuration <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-"
