msgid ":ref:`Storage <localizations/france/pos-storage>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Lagring <localizations/france/pos-storage>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:949
msgid "Inalterability"
msgstr "Uforanderlighed"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:951
msgid ""
"All methods to cancel or modify key data in POS orders, invoices, and "
"journal entries are deactivated for companies located in France or any DOM-"
"TOM."
msgstr ""
"Alle metoder til at annullere eller ændre nøgledata i POS-ordrer, fakturaer "
"og kladdeposteringer er deaktiveret for virksomheder beliggende i Frankrig "
"eller i DOM-TOM."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:955
msgid ""
"In a multi-company environment, only the documents of such companies are "
"impacted."
msgstr ""
"I et miljø med flere virksomheder påvirkes kun dokumenterne fra sådanne "
"virksomheder."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:960
msgid "Security"
msgstr "Sikkerhed"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:962
msgid ""
"To ensure inalterability, every order or journal entry is encrypted upon "
"validation. This number (or hash) is calculated from the document's key data "
"and the hash of the precedent documents. The module introduces an interface "
"to test the data's inalterability. The test will fail if any information is "
"modified on a document after its validation. The algorithm recomputes all "
"the hashes and compares them against the initial ones. In case of failure, "
"the system points out the first corrupted document recorded in the system."
msgstr ""
"For at sikre uforanderlighed krypteres hver ordre ellerkladdepostering ved "
"validering. Dette nummer (eller hash) beregnes ud fra dokumentets nøgledata "
"og hashen fra de foregående dokumenter. Modulet introducerer en grænseflade "
"til at teste dataenes uforanderlighed. Testen vil fejle, hvis nogen "
"information ændres på et dokument efter dets validering. Algoritmen "
"genberegner alle hashværdierne og sammenligner dem med de oprindelige. I "
"tilfælde af fejl påpeger systemet det første beskadigede dokument, der er "
"registreret i systemet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:969
msgid ""
"Only users with :doc:`administrator </applications/general/users/"
"access_rights>` access rights can initiate the inalterability check:"
msgstr ""
"Kun brugere med :doc:`administrator </applications/general/users/"
"access_rights>`-adgangsrettigheder kan igangsætte kontrollen af "
"uforanderlighed:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:972
msgid ""
"For POS orders, go to :menuselection:`Point of Sales --> Reporting --> POS "
"Inalterability Check`;"
msgstr ""
"For POS-ordrer, gå til :menuselection:`Salgssted --> Rapportering --> POS-"
"kontrol af uforanderlighed`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:973
msgid ""
"For journal entries, in the **Accounting** or **Invoicing** app, go "
"to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Settings`. In the :guilabel:`Reporting` "
"section, click :guilabel:`Download the Data Inalterability Check Report`."
msgstr ""
"For kladdeposteringer skal du i appen **Bogføring** eller **Fakturering** gå "
"til :menuselection:`Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`. I sektionen "
":guilabel:`Rapportering` skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Download "
"datauænderligheds-kontrolrapport`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:980
msgid "Storage"
msgstr "Lager"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:982
msgid ""
"The system also processes automatic sales closings daily, monthly, and "
"annually. Such closings compute the sales total for the period and the "
"cumulative grand totals from the very first sales entry recorded in the "
"system."
msgstr ""
"Systemet behandler også automatiske salgsafslutninger dagligt, månedligt og "
"årligt. Sådanne afslutninger beregner salgstotalen for perioden og de "
"kumulative hovedtotaler fra den allerførste salgspostering, der er "
"registreret i systemet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:986
msgid ""
"To access closings, either go to :menuselection:`Point of Sales --> "
"Reporting --> Sales Closings` or in the **Accounting** or **Invoicing** app, "
"go to :menuselection:`Reporting --> Sales Closings`."
msgstr ""
"For at få adgang til afslutninger skal du enten gå til "
":menuselection:`POS --> Rapportering --> Salgsafslutninger` eller i appen "
"**Bogføring** eller **Fakturering** gå til :menuselection:`Rapportering --> "
"Salgsafslutninger`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:990
msgid ""
"Closings compute the totals for journal entries of sales journals (Journal "
"Type = Sales)."
msgstr ""
"Afslutninger beregner totalerne for bilagsposteringer i salgskladder "
"(kladdetype = salg)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:991
msgid ""
"For multi-companies environments, such closings are performed by company."
msgstr "I multifirma-miljøer udføres sådanne afslutninger pr. firma."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:992
msgid ""
"POS orders are posted as journal entries at the closing of the POS session. "
"Closing a POS session can be done anytime. To prompt users to do it daily, "
"the module prevents them from resuming a session that was opened more than "
"24 hours ago. Such a session must be closed before selling again."
msgstr ""
"Objednávky z POS jsou zaúčtovány jako účetní položky při uzavření POS "
"session. Uzavření POS session lze provést kdykoli. Aby byli uživatelé "
"vyzváni k dennímu uzavření, modul jim brání v obnovení session, která byla "
"otevřena před více než 24 hodinami. Taková session musí být před dalším "
"prodejem uzavřena."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:996
msgid ""
"A period’s total is computed from all the journal entries posted after the "
"previous closing of the same type, regardless of their posting date. "
"Recording a new sales transaction for a period already closed will be "
"counted in the very next closing."
msgstr ""
"En periodes total beregnes ud fra alle kladdeposteringer bogført efter den "
"forrige afslutning af samme type, uanset deres bogføringsdato. Registrering "
"af en ny salgstransaktion for en periode, der allerede er afsluttet, vil "
"blive talt med i den næste afslutning."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:1001
msgid ""
"For test & audit purposes, closings can be manually generated "
"in :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> Scheduled Actions`. In the "
"scheduled actions list view, open the desired :guilabel:`Sale Closing` "
"action and click :guilabel:`Run manually`."
msgstr ""
"Til test- og revisionsformål kan afslutninger genereres manuelt "
"i :ref:`udviklertilstand <developer-mode>`. Gå "
"til :menuselection:`Indstillinger --> Teknisk --> Planlagte handlinger`. I "
"listevisningen over planlagte handlinger, åbn den "
"ønskede :guilabel:`Salgsafslutning`-handling og klik på :guilabel:`Kør "
"manuelt`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:1009
msgid "Responsibilities"
msgstr "Ansvar"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:1011
msgid ""
"Uninstalling this module will reset the security hashes. This means the "
"system will no longer guarantee the integrity of the past data."
msgstr ""
"Afinstallering af dette modul vil nulstille sikkerhedshashværdierne. Dette "
"betyder, at systemet ikke længere vil garantere integriteten af de tidligere "
"data."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:1014
msgid ""
"Users are responsible for their Odoo system and must operate it carefully. "
"Modifying source code responsible for ensuring data integrity is not allowed."
msgstr ""
"Brugerne er ansvarlige for deres Odoo-system og skal betjene det "
"omhyggeligt. Ændring af kildekode, der er ansvarlig for at sikre "
"dataintegritet, er ikke tilladt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:1017
msgid ""
"Odoo is not responsible for any issues with this module's functionality if "
"caused by uncertified third-party applications."
msgstr ""
"Odoo er ikke ansvarlig for nogen problemer med dette moduls funktionalitet, "
"hvis de er forårsaget af ikke-certificerede tredjepartsapplikationer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:3
msgid "Germany"
msgstr "Tyskland"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:11
msgid ""
"Both SKR03 and SKR04 charts of accounts are supported in Odoo. When you "
"create a new Odoo Online database, SKR03 is installed by default."
msgstr ""
"Både SKR03 og SKR04 kontoplaner understøttes i Odoo. Når du opretter en ny "
"Odoo Online-database, installeres SKR03 som standard."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:14
msgid ""
"Verify which is installed by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` and checking the :guilabel:`Package` field under "
"the :guilabel:`Fiscal Localization` section."
msgstr ""
"Kontrollér, hvilken der er installeret, ved at gå "
"til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger` og tjekke "
"feltet :guilabel:`Pakke` under afsnittet :guilabel:`Skattemæssig "
"lokalisering`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:18
msgid ""
"Selecting another package is only possible if you have not created an "
"accounting entry. If one was posted, a new company or database must be set "
"up to select another package. In addition, all journal entries will need to "
"be created again."
msgstr ""
"Valg af en anden pakke er kun muligt, hvis du ikke har oprettet en "
"regnskabspost. Hvis en er blevet bogført, skal en ny virksomhed eller "
"database oprettes for at vælge en anden pakke. Derudover skal alle "
"journalposteringer oprettes igen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:25
msgid "The following German-specific reports available on Odoo Enterprise:"
msgstr ""
"Følgende Tyskland-specifikke rapporter er tilgængelige på Odoo Enterprise:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:29
msgid "Tax Report (Umsatzsteuervoranmeldung)"
msgstr "Momsrapport (Umsatzsteuervoranmeldung)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:30
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:122
msgid "EC Sales List"
msgstr "EC Salgsliste"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:34
msgid "Exporting entries from Odoo to DATEV"
msgstr "Eksportere posteringer fra Odoo til DATEV"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:36
msgid ""
"Provided that one of the German :ref:`fiscal localization packages "
"<fiscal_localizations/packages>` is installed, you can export your "
"accounting entries from Odoo to DATEV from the general ledger."
msgstr ""
"Forudsat at en af de tyske :ref:`regnskabslokalisationspakker "
"<fiscal_localizations/packages>` er installeret, kan du eksportere dine "
"regnskabsposteringer fra Odoo til DATEV fra hovedbogen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:40
msgid ""
"Two types of exports are needed: first the DATEV ATCH export, then the DATEV "
"DATA export."
msgstr ""
"To typer eksporter er nødvendige: først DATEV ATCH-eksporten, derefter DATEV "
"DATA-eksporten."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:43
msgid ""
"Both are needed at different stages to transfer the data correctly to DATEV, "
"as DATEV works with two interfaces, one for clients (DUO - DATEV Unternehmen "
"Online) and one for tax advisors (DATEV Rechnungswesen)."
msgstr ""
"Begge er nødvendige på forskellige stadier for at overføre dataene korrekt "
"til DATEV, da DATEV arbejder med to grænseflader, en til klienter (DUO - "
"DATEV Unternehmen Online) og en til skatterådgivere (DATEV Rechnungswesen)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:48
msgid "1. DATEV ATCH"
msgstr "1. DATEV ATCH"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:50
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> General Ledger`, click "
"the :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`Actions`) button, and select :guilabel:`Datev "
"ATCH (zip)`."
msgstr ""
"Gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Rapportering --> Hovedbog`, klik på "
"knappen :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`Handlinger`), og vælg :guilabel:`Datev "
"ATCH (zip)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:None
msgid "General ledger's actions menu with DATEV exports"
msgstr "Hovedbogens handlingsmenu med DATEV-eksporter"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:56
msgid ""
"Upload the downloaded ZIP file via the `DATEV Belegtransfer software "
"<https://www.datev.de/web/de/berufsgruppenuebergreifend/mydatev/cloud-"
"anwendungen/datev-upload-online>`_."
msgstr ""
"Upload den downloadede ZIP-fil via `DATEV Belegtransfer-softwaren <https://"
"www.datev.de/web/de/berufsgruppenuebergreifend/mydatev/cloud-anwendungen/"
"datev-upload-online>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:59
msgid ""
"If you do not have the DATEV Belegtransfer software `installed <https://"
"apps.datev.de/myupdates/download/products/ddc1adec-4b1e-4581-"
"b5b0-504fe0d68fd2>`_ on your computer, ask your tax advisor to help you with "
"this."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du ikke har DATEV Belegtransfer-softwaren `installeret <https://"
"apps.datev.de/myupdates/download/products/ddc1adec-4b1e-4581-"
"b5b0-504fe0d68fd2>`_ på din computer, bed din skatterådgiver om at hjælpe "
"dig med dette."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:63
msgid ""
"The DATEV ATCH ZIP file includes the files (reports) linked to an Odoo "
"invoice or bill. For customer invoices, the file must have been generated by "
"using the :guilabel:`Send` button. For vendor bills, the file must have been "
"received via an email alias or uploaded by using the :guilabel:`Upload` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"DATEV ATCH ZIP-filen inkluderer filerne (rapporter) knyttet til en Odoo-"
"faktura eller -regning. For kundefakturaer skal filen være blevet genereret "
"ved at bruge knappen :guilabel:`Send`. For leverandørregninger skal filen "
"være blevet modtaget via et e-mailalias eller uploadet ved at bruge "
"knappen :guilabel:`Upload`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:68
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:90
msgid "DATEV ATCH ZIP file"
msgstr "DATEV ATCH ZIP-fil"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:70
msgid "The ZIP file contains two types of files:"
msgstr "ZIP-filen indeholder to typer filer:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:72
msgid ""
"the individual invoice/bill files (PDF, JPEG, etc.) for the selected period "
"on the general ledger, and"
msgstr ""
"de individuelle faktura-/regningsfiler (PDF, JPEG osv.) for den valgte "
"periode i hovedbogen, og"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:74
msgid ""
"a :file:`document.xml` file used to generate a unique ID (GUID) for each "
"file."
msgstr ""
"en :file:`document.xml`-fil, der bruges til at generere et unikt ID (GUID) "
"for hver fil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:76
msgid ""
"These unique IDs are essential as they allow DATEV to automatically link the "
"files to the individual journal items, which will be imported with the DATEV "
"DATA file in the next step."
msgstr ""
"Disse unikke ID'er er essentielle, da de gør det muligt for DATEV automatisk "
"at linke filerne til de individuelle journalposteringer, som vil blive "
"importeret med DATEV DATA-filen i næste trin."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:80
msgid "2. DATEV DATA"
msgstr "2. DATEV DATA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:82
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> General Ledger`, click "
"the :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`Actions`) button, and select :guilabel:`Datev "
"DATA (zip)`."
msgstr ""
"Gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Rapportering --> Hovedbog`, klik på "
"knappen :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`Handlinger`), og vælg :guilabel:`Datev "
"DATA (zip)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:85
msgid ""
"Transfer the downloaded ZIP file to your tax advisor. They should import the "
"ZIP file into DATEV Rechnungswesen."
msgstr ""
"Overfør den downloadede ZIP-fil til din skatterådgiver. De bør importere ZIP-"
"filen til DATEV Rechnungswesen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:88
msgid "Check with your tax advisor how often they need these files."
msgstr ""
"Kontroller med din skatterådgiver, hvor ofte de har brug for disse filer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:92
msgid "The ZIP file contains three CSV files:"
msgstr "ZIP-filen indeholder tre CSV-filer:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:94
msgid ""
"the :file:`EXTF_customer_accounts.csv` file containing all information "
"related to your customers,"
msgstr ""
":file:`EXTF_customer_accounts.csv`-filen, der indeholder alle oplysninger "
"relateret til dine kunder,"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:96
msgid ""
"the :file:`EXTF_vendor_accounts.csv` file containing all information related "
"to your vendors, and"
msgstr ""
":file:`EXTF_vendor_accounts.csv`-filen, der indeholder alle oplysninger "
"relateret til dine leverandører, og"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:98
msgid ""
"the :file:`EXTF_accounting_entries.csv` containing all journal items for the "
"period defined on the general ledger, as well as the unique IDs (GUID) so "
"that the journal items can be linked to the files inside the DATEV ATCH ZIP "
"file."
msgstr ""
":file:`EXTF_accounting_entries.csv`, der indeholder alle bilagsposter for "
"perioden defineret i hovedbogen, samt de unikke ID'er (GUID), så "
"bilagsposterne kan knyttes til filerne i DATEV ATCH ZIP-filen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:105
msgid "GoBD compliance"
msgstr "GoBD-overholdelse"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:107
msgid ""
"**GoBD** stands for *Grundsätze zur ordnungsmäßigen Führung und Aufbewahrung "
"von Büchern, Aufzeichnungen und Unterlagen in elektronischer Form sowie zum "
"Datenzugriff*. In short, it is a guideline for the proper management and "
"storage of books, records, and documents in electronic form, as well as for "
"data access, that is relevant for the German tax authority, tax declaration, "
"and balance sheet."
msgstr ""
"**GoBD** står for *Grundsätze zur ordnungsmäßigen Führung und Aufbewahrung "
"von Büchern, Aufzeichnungen und Unterlagen in elektronischer Form sowie zum "
"Datenzugriff*. Kort sagt er det en retningslinje for korrekt håndtering og "
"opbevaring af bøger, registreringer og dokumenter i elektronisk form samt "
"for dataadgang, der er relevant for de tyske skattemyndigheder, "
"selvangivelse og statusopgørelse."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:113
msgid ""
"These principles have been written and published by the Federal Ministry of "
"Finance (BMF) in November 2014. Since January 2015, **they have become the "
"norm** and have replaced previously accepted practices linked to computer-"
"based accounting. Several changes have been made by the BMF in 2019 and "
"January 2020 to specify some of the content due to the development of "
"digital solutions (cloud hosting, paperless companies, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Disse principper er blevet skrevet og offentliggjort af det tyske "
"finansministerium (BMF) i november 2014. Siden januar 2015 **er de blevet "
"normen** og har erstattet tidligere accepterede praksisser knyttet til "
"computerbaseret regnskab. Flere ændringer er blevet foretaget af BMF i 2019 "
"og januar 2020 for at præcisere noget af indholdet på grund af udviklingen "
"af digitale løsninger (cloud-hosting, papirløse virksomheder osv.)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:120
msgid "Odoo is certified **GoBD-compliant**."
msgstr "Odoo er certificeret **GoBD-overholdende**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:123
msgid "Understanding GoBD in relation to accounting software"
msgstr "Forståelse af GoBD i forhold til regnskabssoftware"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:125
msgid ""
"The **GoBD is binding for companies that have to present accounts**, which "
"includes SMEs, freelancers, and entrepreneurs, to the financial authorities. "
"As such, **the taxpayer himself is the sole responsible** for the complete "
"and exhaustive keeping of fiscal-relevant data (above-mentioned financial "
"and related data)."
msgstr ""
"**GoBD er bindende for virksomheder, der skal aflægge regnskab**, hvilket "
"omfatter SMV'er, freelancere og iværksættere, over for de finansielle "
"myndigheder. Som sådan **er skatteyderen selv den eneste ansvarlige** for "
"den fuldstændige og udtømmende opbevaring af skatterelevante data "
"(ovennævnte finansielle og relaterede data)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:130
msgid ""
"Apart from software requirements, the user is required to ensure internal "
"control systems (*in accordance with sec. 146 of the Fiscal Code*):"
msgstr ""
"Udover softwarekrav er brugeren forpligtet til at sikre interne "
"kontrolsystemer (*i overensstemmelse med § 146 i skatteloven*):"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:133
msgid "access rights control;"
msgstr "adgangsrettighedskontrol;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:134
msgid "segregation of duties, functional separating;"
msgstr "funktionsadskillelse, opgavesegregering;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:135
msgid "entry controls (error notifications, plausibility checks);"
msgstr "indtastningskontrol (fejlmeddelelser, plausibilitetstjek);"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:136
msgid "reconciliation checks at data entry;"
msgstr "afstemningskontrol ved dataindtastning;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:137
msgid "processing controls; and"
msgstr "behandlingskontrol; og"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:138
msgid ""
"measures to prevent intentional or unintentional manipulation of software, "
"data, or documents."
msgstr ""
"foranstaltninger til at forhindre forsætlig eller utilsigtet manipulation af "
"software, data eller dokumenter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:140
msgid ""
"The user must distribute tasks within their organization to the relevant "
"positions (*control*) and verify that the tasks are properly and completely "
"performed (*supervision*). The result of these controls must be recorded "
"(*documentation*), and should errors be found during these controls, "
"appropriate measures to correct the situation should be put into place "
"(*prevention*)."
msgstr ""
"Brugeren skal fordele opgaver inden for deres organisation til de relevante "
"stillinger (*kontrol*) og verificere, at opgaverne udføres korrekt og "
"fuldstændigt (*tilsyn*). Resultatet af disse kontroller skal registreres "
"(*dokumentation*), og hvis der findes fejl under disse kontroller, skal "
"passende foranstaltninger til at rette situationen iværksættes "
"(*forebyggelse*)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:146
msgid "Data security"
msgstr "Datasikkerhed"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:148
msgid ""
"The taxpayer must **secure the system against any data loss** due to "
"deletion, removal, or theft of any data. If the entries are not sufficiently "
"secured, the bookkeeping will be regarded as not in accordance with the GoBD "
"guidelines."
msgstr ""
"Skatteyderen skal **sikre systemet mod ethvert datatab** på grund af "
"sletning, fjernelse eller tyveri af data. Hvis posterne ikke er "
"tilstrækkeligt sikret, vil bogføringen blive betragtet som ikke i "
"overensstemmelse med GoBD-retningslinjerne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:152
msgid ""
"Once bookings have been finally posted, they can no longer be changed or "
"deleted via the application."
msgstr ""
"Når bogføringer er endegyldigt posteret, kan de ikke længere ændres eller "
"slettes via applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:155
msgid ""
"If Odoo is used in the cloud, regular backups are part of the Odoo Online "
"service. In addition, regular backups can be downloaded and backed up on "
"external systems."
msgstr ""
"Hvis Odoo bruges i skyen, er regelmæssige backups en del af Odoo Online-"
"tjenesten. Derudover kan regelmæssige backups downloades og "
"sikkerhedskopieres på eksterne systemer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:159
msgid ""
"`Odoo Cloud Hosting - Service Level Agreement <https://www.odoo.com/cloud-"
"sla>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo Cloud Hosting - Service Level Agreement <https://www.odoo.com/cloud-"
"sla>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:161
msgid ""
"If the server is operated locally, the user is responsible for creating the "
"necessary backup infrastructure."
msgstr ""
"Pokud je server provozován lokálně, je uživatel odpovědný za vytvoření "
"potřebné zálohovací infrastruktury."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:165
msgid ""
"In some cases, data has to be kept for ten years or more, so always have "
"backups saved. It is even more important if you decide to change software "
"provider."
msgstr ""
"I nogle tilfælde skal data opbevares i ti år eller mere, så gem altid "
"sikkerhedskopier. Det er endnu vigtigere, hvis du beslutter at skifte "
"softwareudbyder."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:169
msgid "Responsibility of the software editor"
msgstr "Softwareudgiverens ansvar"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:171
msgid ""
"Considering GoBD applies only to the taxpayer, **the software editor can by "
"no means be held responsible for the accurate and compliant documentation of "
"their users' financial transactional data**. It can merely provide the "
"necessary tools for the user to respect the software-related guidelines "
"described in the GoBD."
msgstr ""
"Vzhledem k tomu, že GoBD se vztahuje pouze na daňového poplatníka, **editor "
"softwaru nemůže být v žádném případě zodpovědný za přesnou a vyhovující "
"dokumentaci finančních transakčních dat svých uživatelů**. Může pouze "
"poskytnout potřebné nástroje, aby uživatel mohl respektovat pokyny týkající "
"se softwaru popsané v GoBD."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:177
msgid "Ensuring compliance through Odoo"
msgstr "Zajištění souladu prostřednictvím Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:179
msgid ""
"The keywords, when it comes to GoBD are: **traceable, verifiable, true, "
"clear, and continuous**. In short, you need to have audit-proof archiving in "
"place, and Odoo provides you with the means to achieve all of these "
"objectives:"
msgstr ""
"Klíčová slova, pokud jde o GoBD, jsou: **sledovatelný, ověřitelný, pravdivý, "
"jasný a nepřetržitý**. Stručně řečeno, potřebujete mít zavedenu archivaci "
"odolnou vůči auditu a Odoo vám poskytuje prostředky k dosažení všech těchto "
"cílů:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid "**Traceability and verifiability**"
msgstr "**Sporbarhed og verificerbarhed**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid ""
"Each record in Odoo is stamped with the creator of the document, the "
"creation date, the modification date, and who modified it. In addition, "
"relevant fields are tracked. Thus, it can be seen which value was changed by "
"whom in the chatter of the relevant object."
msgstr ""
"Každý záznam v Odoo je označen tvůrcem dokumentu, datem vytvoření, datem "
"úpravy a tím, kdo jej upravil. Kromě toho jsou sledována relevantní pole. "
"Díky tomu lze v chatteru příslušného objektu vidět, která hodnota byla "
"změněna kým."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid "**Completeness**"
msgstr "**Fuldstændighed**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid ""
"All financial data must be recorded in the system, and there can be no gaps. "
"Odoo ensures that there is no gap in the numbering of the financial "
"transactions. It is the responsibility of the user to encode all financial "
"data in the system. As most financial data in Odoo is generated "
"automatically, it remains the responsibility of the user to encode all "
"vendor bills and miscellaneous operations completely."
msgstr ""
"Všechna finanční data musí být zaznamenána v systému a nesmí být žádné "
"mezery. Odoo zajišťuje, že v číslování finančních transakcí nejsou žádné "
"mezery. Je odpovědností uživatele zakódovat všechna finanční data do "
"systému. Jelikož většina finančních dat v Odoo je generována automaticky, "
"zůstává odpovědností uživatele zakódovat všechny faktury od dodavatelů a "
"různé operace kompletně."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid "**Accuracy**"
msgstr "**Nøjagtighed**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid ""
"Odoo ensures that, with the correct configuration, the correct accounts are "
"used. In addition, the control mechanisms between purchase orders and sales "
"orders and their respective invoices reflect the reality of the business. It "
"is the responsibility of the user to scan and attach the paper-based vendor "
"bill to the respective record in Odoo. *Odoo Documents helps you automate "
"this task*."
msgstr ""
"Odoo zajišťuje, že při správné konfiguraci jsou použity správné účty. Kromě "
"toho kontrolní mechanismy mezi nákupními objednávkami a prodejními "
"objednávkami a jejich příslušnými fakturami odrážejí realitu podniku. Je "
"odpovědností uživatele naskenovat a připojit papírovou fakturu od dodavatele "
"k příslušnému záznamu v Odoo. *Odoo Dokumenty vám pomáhají tento úkol "
"automatizovat*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid "**Timely booking and record-keeping**"
msgstr "**Rettidig bogføring og journalføring**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid ""
"As most financial data in Odoo is generated by the transactional objects "
"(for example, the invoice is booked at confirmation), Odoo ensures out-of-"
"the-box timely record-keeping. It is the responsibility of the user to "
"encode all incoming vendor bills in a timely manner, as well as the "
"miscellaneous operations."
msgstr ""
"Da de fleste finansielle data i Odoo genereres af transaktionsobjekter "
"(f.eks. bogføres fakturaen ved bekræftelse), sikrer Odoo rettidig "
"journalføring ud af boksen. Det er brugerens ansvar at indtaste alle "
"indgående leverandørfakturaer rettidigt samt diverse operationer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid "**Order**"
msgstr "**Orden**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid ""
"Financial data stored in Odoo is, per definition, ordered and can be "
"reordered according to most fields present in the model. A specific ordering "
"is not enforced by the GoBD, but the system must ensure that a given "
"financial transaction can be quickly found by a third-party expert. Odoo "
"ensures this out-of-the-box."
msgstr ""
"Finanční data uložená v Odoo jsou z definice uspořádána a mohou být "
"přeuspořádána podle většiny polí přítomných v modelu. Konkrétní uspořádání "
"není vynuceno GoBD, ale systém musí zajistit, že danou finanční transakci "
"může rychle najít nezávislý odborník. Odoo to zajišťuje ihned po instalaci."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid "**Inalterability**"
msgstr "**Uforanderlighed**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:0
msgid ""
"With the German Odoo localization, Odoo is in standard configured in such a "
"way that the inalterability clause can be adhered to without any further "
"customization."
msgstr ""
"Med den tyske Odoo-lokalisering er Odoo som standard konfigureret på en "
"sådan måde, at uforanderlighedsklausulen kan overholdes uden yderligere "
"tilpasning."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:214
msgid "GoBD export"
msgstr "Export GoBD"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:216
msgid ""
"In the case of fiscal control, the fiscal authority can request three levels "
"of access to the accounting system (Z1, Z2, Z3). These levels vary from "
"direct access to the interface to the handover of the financial data on a "
"storage device."
msgstr ""
"I tilfælde af skattekontrol kan skattemyndigheden anmode om tre niveauer af "
"adgang til regnskabssystemet (Z1, Z2, Z3). Disse niveauer varierer fra "
"direkte adgang til grænsefladen til overdragelse af de finansielle data på "
"en lagerenhed."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:220
msgid ""
"In the case of a handover of financial data to a storage device, the GoBD "
"does **not** enforce the format. It can be, for example, in XLS, CSV, XML, "
"Lotus 123, SAP-format, AS/400-format, or else. Odoo supports the CSV and XLS "
"export of financial data out of the box. The GoBD **recommends** the export "
"in a specific XML-based GoBD format (see \"Ergänzende Informationen zur "
"Datenträgerüberlassung\" §3), but it is not binding."
msgstr ""
"V případě předání finančních dat na paměťové médium GoBD **nevyžaduje** "
"formát. Může to být například XLS, CSV, XML, Lotus 123, SAP-formát, AS/400-"
"formát nebo jiný. Odoo podporuje export finančních dat do CSV a XLS ihned po "
"instalaci. GoBD **doporučuje** export do specifického XML-based GoBD formátu "
"(viz \"Ergänzende Informationen zur Datenträgerüberlassung\" §3), ale není "
"to závazné."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:227
msgid "Non-compliance"
msgstr "Nedodržení předpisů"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:229
msgid ""
"In the event of an infringement, you can expect a fine and a court order "
"demanding the implementation of specific measures."
msgstr ""
"V případě porušení můžete očekávat pokutu a soudní příkaz požadující "
"zavedení konkrétních opatření."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:235
msgid "Point of Sale"
msgstr "POS"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:238
msgid "Technical security system"
msgstr "Technický bezpečnostní systém"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:240
msgid ""
"The **Kassensicherungsverordnung** (The Act on Protection against "
"Manipulation of Digital Records) requires that electronic record-keeping "
"systems - including the :doc:`point of sale </applications/sales/"
"point_of_sale>` systems - must be equipped with a **technical security "
"system** (also called **TSS** or **TSE**)."
msgstr ""
"**Kassensicherungsverordnung** (Zákon o ochraně před manipulací s "
"digitálními záznamy) vyžaduje, aby elektronické systémy vedení záznamů - "
"včetně :doc:`pokladních </applications/sales/point_of_sale>` systémů - "
"musely být vybaveny **technickým bezpečnostním systémem** (nazývaný také "
"**TSS** nebo **TSE**)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:245
msgid ""
"Odoo offers a service that is compliant with the help of `fiskaly <https://"
"fiskaly.com>`_, a *cloud-based solution*."
msgstr ""
"Odoo nabízí službu, která je vyhovující s pomocí `fiskaly <https://"
"fiskaly.com>`_, *cloudového řešení*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:249
msgid ""
"Since this solution is cloud-based, a working internet connection is "
"required."
msgstr ""
"Vzhledem k tomu, že je toto řešení cloudové, je vyžadováno funkční připojení "
"k internetu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:252
msgid ""
"The only VAT rates allowed are given by fiskaly. You can check these rates "
"by consulting `fiskaly DSFinV-K API: VAT Definition <https://"
"developer.fiskaly.com/api/dsfinvk/v0/#tag/VAT-Definition>`_."
msgstr ""
"Jediné povolené sazby DPH jsou dány společností fiskaly. Tyto sazby můžete "
"zkontrolovat konzultací `fiskaly DSFinV-K API: VAT Definition <https://"
"developer.fiskaly.com/api/dsfinvk/v0/#tag/VAT-Definition>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:259
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the **Germany - Certification for Point of "
"Sale** (`l10n_de_pos_cert`) and **Germany - Certification for Point of Sale "
"of type restaurant** (`l10n_de_pos_res_cert`) modules."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Nainstalujte <general/install>` moduly **Germany - Certification for "
"Point of Sale** (`l10n_de_pos_cert`) a **Germany - Certification for Point "
"of Sale of type restaurant** (`l10n_de_pos_res_cert`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:264
msgid ""
"If these modules are not listed, :ref:`update the app list <general/"
"install>`."
msgstr ""
"Pokud tyto moduly nejsou uvedeny, :ref:`aktualizujte seznam aplikací "
"<general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:267
msgid "Company registration at the financial authority"
msgstr "Registrace společnosti u finančního úřadu"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:269
msgid ""
"To register your company, open the :guilabel:`Settings` app, "
"click :guilabel:`Update Info` under the :guilabel:`Companies` section, and "
"fill in the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"For at registrere din virksomhed skal du åbne "
"appen :guilabel:`Indstillinger`, klikke på :guilabel:`Opdater info` under "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Virksomheder` og udfylde følgende felter:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:273
msgid ":guilabel:`Address`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Adresse`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:274
msgid ":guilabel:`VAT`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Moms`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:275
msgid ""
":guilabel:`St.-Nr.` (Steuernummer) this number is assigned by the tax office "
"to every taxable natural or legal person (e.g., `2893081508152`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`St.-Nr.` (Steuernummer) dette nummer tildeles af "
"skattemyndighederne til enhver skattepligtig fysisk eller juridisk person "
"(f.eks. `2893081508152`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:277
msgid ""
":guilabel:`W-IdNr.` (Wirtschafts-Identifikationsnummer) this number is used "
"as a permanent identification number for economically active persons."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`W-IdNr.` (Wirtschafts-Identifikationsnummer) dette nummer bruges "
"som et permanent identifikationsnummer for økonomisk aktive personer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:280
msgid ""
"You can then **register your company through fiskaly** by opening "
"the :guilabel:`Fiskaly` tab and clicking the :guilabel:`Fiskaly "
"Registration` button."
msgstr ""
"Du kan derefter **registrere din virksomhed via fiskaly** ved at åbne "
"fanen :guilabel:`Fiskaly` og klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Fiskaly-"
"registrering`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:284
msgid ""
"If you do not see the :guilabel:`Fiskaly Registration` button, make sure "
