"derefter markere feltet :guilabel:`Opret TSS` under "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Fiskaly API`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:308
msgid "Once the creation of the TSS is successful, you can find the:"
msgstr "Når oprettelsen af TSS er lykkedes, kan du finde:"

