#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:49
msgid ""
"To use the :ref:`e-Invoicing <india/e-invoicing>`, :ref:`E-Way bill <india/e-"
"waybill>`, and :ref:`GST return filing <india/gstr>` services in Odoo, "
"configure :guilabel:`BVM IT Consulting Services India Private Limited` as "
"the :abbr:`GSP (GST Suvidha Provider)`. To do so, follow these steps :"
msgstr ""
"For at bruge tjenesterne :ref:`e-fakturering <india/e-invoicing>`, :ref:`E-"
"Way bill <india/e-waybill>` og :ref:`GST-returindberetning <india/gstr>` i "
"Odoo skal du konfigurere :guilabel:`BVM IT Consulting Services India Private "
"Limited` som :abbr:`GSP (GST Suvidha Provider)`. Følg disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:54
msgid ""
":ref:`Upgrade <general/upgrade>` the :guilabel:`Indian - Accounting` "
"(`l10n_in`) module."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Opgrader <general/upgrade>` modulet :guilabel:`Indien - Bogføring` "
"(`l10n_in`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:56
msgid ""
"Scroll down to the :guilabel:`Select GSP Provider` section, and set "
"the :guilabel:`GSP` field to :guilabel:`BVM IT Consulting`."
msgstr ""
"Rul ned til sektionen :guilabel:`Select GSP Provider`, og sæt "
"feltet :guilabel:`GSP` til :guilabel:`BVM IT Consulting`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:57
msgid ""
":ref:`Log into the NIC e-invoice portal <india/e-invoicing-api>` "
"and :ref:`NIC E-Way bill portal <india/e-waybill-api>` and create a new API "
"user for each."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Log ind på NIC e-invoice-portalen <india/e-invoicing-api>` "
"og :ref:`NIC E-Way bill-portalen <india/e-waybill-api>`, og opret en ny API-"
"bruger til hver."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:59
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll "
"down to the :guilabel:`Indian Integration` section, and enter the "
"new :guilabel:`Username` and :guilabel:`Password` for the :ref:`e-Invoicing "
"<india/e-invoicing-configuration>` and :ref:`E-Way bill <india/e-waybill-"
"configuration>` features."
msgstr ""
"Gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`, rul "
"ned til sektionen :guilabel:`Indian Integration`, og indtast det "
"nye :guilabel:`brugernavn` og den nye :guilabel:`adgangskode` til "
"funktionerne :ref:`e-fakturering <india/e-invoicing-configuration>` "
"og :ref:`E-Way bill <india/e-waybill-configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:65
msgid "Indian Configuration"
msgstr "Indisk konfiguration"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:67
msgid ""
"In :menuselection:`Settings --> Users & Companies --> Companies`, add "
"your :guilabel:`PAN` and :guilabel:`GSTIN`. The PAN is essential for "
"determining the type of taxpayer, while GSTIN is required for generating e-"
"Invoices and E-waybills."
msgstr ""
"V :menuselection:`Nastavení --> Uživatelé a společnosti --> Společnosti` "
"přidejte své :guilabel:`PAN` a :guilabel:`GSTIN`. PAN je nezbytné pro určení "
"typu daňového poplatníka, zatímco GSTIN je vyžadováno pro generování e-"
"faktur a elektronických průvodních listů."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:72
msgid "e-Invoice system"
msgstr "E-fakturasystem"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:74
msgid ""
"Odoo is compliant with the **Indian Goods and Services Tax (GST) e-Invoice "
"system** requirements."
msgstr ""
"Odoo overholder kravene i **det indiske system for vare- og tjenesteskat "
"(GST) e-faktura**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:82
msgid "NIC e-Invoice registration"
msgstr "Registrering af NIC e-faktura"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:84
msgid ""
"You must register on the :abbr:`NIC (National Informatics Centre)` e-Invoice "
"portal to get your **API credentials**. You need these credentials "
"to :ref:`configure your Odoo Accounting app <india/e-invoicing-"
"configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Du skal registrere dig på :abbr:`NIC (National Informatics Centre)` e-"
"fakturaportal for at få dine **API-legitimationsoplysninger**. Du har brug "
"for disse legitimationsoplysninger til at :ref:`konfigurere din Odoo "
"Regnskab-app <india/e-invoicing-configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:88
msgid ""
"Log in to the `NIC e-Invoice portal <https://einvoice1.gst.gov.in/>`_ by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Login` and entering your :guilabel:`Username` "
"and :guilabel:`Password`;"
msgstr ""
"Log ind på `NIC e-fakturaportal <https://einvoice1.gst.gov.in/>`_ ved at "
"klikke på :guilabel:`Login` og indtaste dit :guilabel:`Brugernavn` og "
"din :guilabel:`Adgangskode`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:92
msgid ""
"If you are already registered on the NIC portal, you can use the same login "
"credentials."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du allerede er registreret på NIC-portalen, kan du bruge de samme "
"loginoplysninger."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "Register Odoo ERP system on e-invoice web portal"
msgstr "Registrer Odoo ERP-system på e-faktura webportal"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:97
msgid ""
"From the dashboard, go to :menuselection:`API Registration --> User "
"Credentials --> Create API User`;"
msgstr ""
"Gå fra dashboardet til :menuselection:`API Registration --> User Credentials "
"--> Create API User`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:99
msgid ""
"After that, you should receive an :abbr:`OTP (one-time password)` code on "
"your registered mobile number. Enter the OTP code and "
"click :guilabel:`Verify OTP`;"
msgstr ""
"Derefter skulle du modtage en :abbr:`OTP (engangsadgangskode)` kode på dit "
"registrerede mobilnummer. Indtast OTP-koden og klik på :guilabel:`Verify "
"OTP`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:101
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Through GSP` for the API interface, set :guilabel:`BVM IT "
"Consulting Services India Private Limited` as GSP, and type in "
"a :guilabel:`Username` and :guilabel:`Password` for your API. Once it is "
"done, click :guilabel:`Submit`."
msgstr ""
"Vælg :guilabel:`Via GSP` til API-grænsefladen, indstil :guilabel:`BVM IT "
"Consulting Services India Private Limited` som GSP, og indtast "
"et :guilabel:`Brugernavn` og :guilabel:`Adgangskode` til din API. Når det er "
"gjort, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Send`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "Submit API specific Username and Password"
msgstr "Indsend API-specifikt brugernavn og adgangskode"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:111
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:299
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:142
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:126
#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/paypal.rst:42
msgid "Configuration in Odoo"
msgstr "Konfigurace v Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:113
msgid ""
"To enable the e-Invoice service in Odoo, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --"
"> Configuration --> Settings --> Indian Electronic Invoicing`, and enter "
"the :guilabel:`Username` and :guilabel:`Password` previously set for the API."
msgstr ""
"Pro aktivaci služby e-faktur v Odoo přejděte do "
":menuselection:`Bogføring --> Konfigurace --> Nastavení --> Indické "
"elektronické fakturace` a zadejte :guilabel:`Uživatelské jméno` a "
":guilabel:`Heslo`, které byly dříve nastaveny pro API."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:None
msgid "Setup e-invoice service"
msgstr "Nastavení služby e-faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:120
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:308
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:475
msgid ""
"Additionally, make sure the :ref:`GSP field is configured <india/"
"gsp_configuration>` in the Accounting settings."
msgstr ""
"Sørg desuden for, at :ref:`GSP-feltet er konfigureret <india/"
"gsp_configuration>` i regnskabsindstillingerne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:128
msgid ""
"To automatically send e-Invoices to the NIC e-Invoice portal, you must first "
"configure your *sales* journal by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Journals`, opening your *sales* journal, and in "
"the :guilabel:`Advanced Settings` tab, under :guilabel:`Electronic Data "
"Interchange`, enable :guilabel:`E-Invoice (IN)` and save."
msgstr ""
"Pro automatické odesílání e-faktur na portál NIC e-Invoice musíte nejprve "
"nakonfigurovat svůj *prodejní* deník v :menuselection:`Bogføring --> "
"Konfigurace --> Deníky`, otevřít svůj *prodejní* deník a na kartě "
":guilabel:`Pokročilá nastavení` v sekci :guilabel:`Elektronická výměna dat` "
"povolit :guilabel:`E-faktura (IN)` a uložit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:141
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:330
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:447
msgid "Invoice validation"
msgstr "Fakturavalidering"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:143
msgid ""
"Once an invoice is validated, a confirmation message is displayed at the "
"top. Odoo automatically uploads the JSON-signed file of validated invoices "
"to the NIC e-Invoice portal after some time. If you want to process the "
"invoice immediately, click :guilabel:`Process now`."
msgstr ""
"Jakmile je faktura ověřena, zobrazí se v horní části potvrzovací zpráva. "
"Odoo po určité době automaticky nahraje JSON soubor s podpisem ověřených "
"faktur na portál NIC e-Invoice. Pokud chcete fakturu zpracovat okamžitě, "
"klikněte na :guilabel:`Zpracovat nyní`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:None
msgid "Indian e-invoicing confirmation message"
msgstr "Indisk e-faktura bekræftelsesbesked"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:151
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:339
msgid "You can find the JSON-signed file in the attached files in the chatter."
msgstr "Du kan finde den JSON-signerede fil i de vedhæftede filer i chatten."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:152
msgid ""
"You can check the document's :abbr:`EDI (electronic data interchange)` "
"status under the :guilabel:`EDI Document` tab or the :guilabel:`Electronic "
"invoicing` field of the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Du kan tjekke dokumentets :abbr:`EDI (elektronisk dataudveksling)` status "
"under fanen :guilabel:`EDI-dokument` eller feltet :guilabel:`Elektronisk "
"fakturering` på fakturaen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:160
msgid ""
"Once an invoice is validated and submitted, the invoice PDF report can be "
"printed. The report includes the :abbr:`IRN (Invoice Reference "
"Number)`, :guilabel:`Ack. No` (acknowledgment number) and :guilabel:`Ack. "
"Date` (acknowledgment date), and QR code. These certify that the invoice is "
"a valid fiscal document."
msgstr ""
"Når en faktura er valideret og indsendt, kan faktura-PDF-rapporten "
"udskrives. Rapporten inkluderer :abbr:`IRN (Invoice Reference Number)`, "
":guilabel:`Ack. No` (bekræftelsesnummer) og :guilabel:`Ack. Date` "
"(bekræftelsesdato) samt QR-kode. Disse certificerer, at fakturaen er et "
"gyldigt regnskabsdokument."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:None
msgid "IRN and QR code"
msgstr "IRN og QR-kode"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:171
msgid "e-Invoice cancellation"
msgstr "Annullering af e-faktura"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:173
msgid ""
"If you want to cancel an e-Invoice, go to the :guilabel:`Other info` tab of "
"the invoice and fill out the :guilabel:`Cancel reason` and :guilabel:`Cancel "
"remarks` fields. Then, click :guilabel:`Request EDI cancellation`. The "
"status of the :guilabel:`Electronic invoicing` field changes "
"to :guilabel:`To Cancel`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du vil annullere en e-faktura, skal du gå til fanen :guilabel:`Anden "
"info` på fakturaen og udfylde felterne :guilabel:`Annulleringsårsag` og "
":guilabel:`Annulleringsbemærkninger`. Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Anmod om "
"EDI-annullering`. Status for feltet :guilabel:`Elektronisk fakturering` "
"ændres til :guilabel:`Til annullering`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:179
msgid ""
"Doing so cancels both the :ref:`e-Invoice <india/e-invoicing>` and "
"the :ref:`E-Way bill <india/e-waybill>`."
msgstr ""
"Dette annullerer både :ref:`e-fakturaen <india/e-invoicing>` og :ref:`E-Way-"
"sedlen <india/e-waybill>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:None
msgid "cancel reason and remarks"
msgstr "annulleringsårsag og bemærkninger"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:186
msgid ""
"If you want to abort the cancellation before processing the invoice, then "
"click :guilabel:`Call Off EDI Cancellation`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du vil afbryde annulleringen, før fakturaen behandles, skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Tilbagekald EDI-annullering`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:188
msgid ""
"Once you request to cancel the e-Invoice, Odoo automatically submits the "
"JSON-signed file to the NIC e-Invoice portal. You can "
"click :guilabel:`Process now` if you want to process the invoice immediately."
msgstr ""
"Når du anmoder om at annullere e-fakturaen, indsender Odoo automatisk den "
"JSON-signerede fil til NIC e-fakturaportal. Du kan klikke på "
":guilabel:`Behandl nu`, hvis du vil behandle fakturaen med det samme."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:195
msgid "Management of negative lines in e-Invoices"
msgstr "Håndtering af negative linjer i e-fakturaer"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:197
msgid ""
"Negative lines are typically used to represent discounts or adjustments "
"associated with specific products or global discounts. The government portal "
"prohibits the submission of data with negative lines, which means they need "
"to be converted based on the HSN code and GST rate. This is done "
"automatically by Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Negative linjer bruges typisk til at repræsentere rabatter eller justeringer "
"forbundet med specifikke produkter eller globale rabatter. Regeringsportalen "
"forbyder indsendelse af data med negative linjer, hvilket betyder, at de "
"skal konverteres baseret på HSN-kode og GST-sats. Dette gøres automatisk af "
"Odoo."

