msgstr ""
"**Forkert anvendelse af skat:** Skattetypen matcher ikke :guilabel:`Fiscal "
"Position` (:guilabel:`CGST/SGST` anvendt i stedet for :guilabel:`IGST` til "
"transaktioner mellem stater, eller :guilabel:`IGST` anvendt i stedet for "
":guilabel:`CGST/SGST` til transaktioner inden for staten)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:510
msgid "**Missing HSN Code:** No HSN Code is defined for the product."
msgstr ""
"**Manglende HSN-kode:** Der er ikke defineret nogen HSN-kode for produktet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:511
msgid ""
"**Invalid HSN Code for Services:** The HSN Code for a service does not start "
"with \"99\" or is incorrect."
msgstr ""
"**Ugyldig HSN-kode for tjenesteydelser:** HSN-koden for en tjenesteydelse "
"starter ikke med \"99\" eller er forkert."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:513
msgid ""
"**Non-compliant UQC:** The Unit Quantity Code (UQC) does not meet Indian GST "
"standards."
msgstr ""
"**Ikke-overensstemmende UQC:** Unit Quantity Code (UQC) opfylder ikke "
"indiske GST-standarder."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:515
msgid ""
"If any validation fails, the system alerts users with a warning, "
"highlighting the discrepancies and providing a direct link to the affected "
"lines."
msgstr ""
"Hvis nogen validering fejler, advarer systemet brugerne med en advarsel, "
"fremhæver uoverensstemmelserne og giver et direkte link til de berørte "
"linjer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-1 validation warning"
msgstr "GSTR-1-valideringsadvarsel"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:521
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Generate` to view the report in **Spreadsheet view**."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Generate` for at se rapporten i **Spreadsheet-visning**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-1 generate"
msgstr "GSTR-1-generering"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-1 Spreadsheet View"
msgstr "GSTR-1-regnearksvisning"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:529
msgid ""
"If the **GSTR-1** report is correct, then click :guilabel:`Push to GSTN` to "
"send it to the **GST portal**. The status of the :guilabel:`GSTR-1` report "
"changes to :guilabel:`Sending`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis **GSTR-1**-rapporten er korrekt, så klik på :guilabel:`Push to GSTN` "
"for at sende den til **GST-portalen**. Status for :guilabel:`GSTR-1`-"
"rapporten ændres til :guilabel:`Sending`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-1 in the Sending Status"
msgstr "GSTR-1 i Sending-status"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:535
msgid ""
"After a few seconds, the status of the **GSTR-1** report changes "
"to :guilabel:`Waiting for Status`. It means that the **GSTR-1** report has "
"been sent to the :guilabel:`GST Portal` and is being verified on "
"the :guilabel:`GST Portal`;"
msgstr ""
"Efter et par sekunder ændres statusen for **GSTR-1**-rapporten til "
":guilabel:`Venter på status`. Det betyder, at **GSTR-1**-rapporten er sendt "
"til :guilabel:`GST-portalen` og bliver verificeret på :guilabel:`GST-"
"portalen`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-1 in the Waiting for Status"
msgstr "GSTR-1 i Venter på status"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:542
msgid ""
"Once more, after a few seconds, the status either changes "
"to :guilabel:`Sent` or :guilabel:`Error in Invoice`. The "
"status :guilabel:`Error in Invoice` indicates that some of the invoices are "
"not correctly filled out to be validated by the **GST portal**;"
msgstr ""
"Endnu en gang, efter et par sekunder, ændres statusen til enten "
":guilabel:`Sendt` eller :guilabel:`Fejl i faktura`. Statusen :guilabel:`Fejl "
"i faktura` indikerer, at nogle af fakturaerne ikke er korrekt udfyldt til at "
"blive valideret af **GST-portalen**;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:546
msgid ""
"If the state of the **GSTR-1** is :guilabel:`Sent`, it means your **GSTR-1** "
"report is ready to be filed on the **GST portal**."
msgstr ""
"Hvis tilstanden for **GSTR-1** er :guilabel:`Sendt`, betyder det, at din "
"**GSTR-1**-rapport er klar til at blive indsendt på **GST-portalen**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-1 Sent"
msgstr "GSTR-1 sendt"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:552
msgid ""
"If the state of the **GSTR-1** is :guilabel:`Error in Invoice`, invoices can "
"be checked for errors in the chatter. Once issues have been resolved, the "
"user can click :guilabel:`Push to GSTN` to submit the file again on the "
"**GST portal**."
msgstr ""
"Hvis tilstanden for **GSTR-1** er :guilabel:`Fejl i faktura`, kan fakturaer "
"kontrolleres for fejl i chatteren. Når problemerne er løst, kan brugeren "
"klikke på :guilabel:`Send til GSTN` for at indsende filen igen på **GST-"
"portalen**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-1 Error in Invoice"
msgstr "GSTR-1 fejl i faktura"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:559
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Mark as Filed` after filing the **GSTR-1** report on the "
"**GST portal**. The status of the report changes to :guilabel:`Filed` in "
"**Odoo**."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Markér som indsendt` efter indsendelse af **GSTR-1**-"
"rapporten på **GST-portalen**. Rapportens status ændres til "
":guilabel:`Indsendt` i **Odoo**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-1 in the Filed Status"
msgstr "GSTR-1 i status Indsendt"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:568
msgid "Receive GSTR-2B"
msgstr "Modtag GSTR-2B"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:570
msgid ""
"Users can retrieve the **GSTR-2B Report** from the **GST portal**. This "
"automatically reconciles the **GSTR-2B** report with your Odoo bills;"
msgstr ""
"Brugere kan hente **GSTR-2B-rapporten** fra **GST-portalen**. Dette "
"afstemmer automatisk **GSTR-2B**-rapporten med dine Odoo-fakturaer;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:573
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Fetch GSTR-2B Summary` to retrieve the **GSTR-2B** summary. "
"After a few seconds, the status of the report changes to :guilabel:`Waiting "
"for Reception`. This means Odoo is trying to receive the **GSTR-2B** report "
"from the **GST portal**;"
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Hent GSTR-2B-sammendrag` for at hente **GSTR-2B**-"
"sammendraget. Efter et par sekunder ændres rapportens status til "
":guilabel:`Venter på modtagelse`. Det betyder, at Odoo forsøger at modtage "
"**GSTR-2B**-rapporten fra **GST-portalen**;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-2B in Waiting for Reception"
msgstr "GSTR-2B i Venter på modtagelse"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:580
msgid ""
"Once more, after a few seconds, the status of the **GSTR-2B** changes to "
"the :guilabel:`Being Processed`. It means Odoo is reconciling the "
"**GSTR-2B** report with your Odoo bills;"
msgstr ""
"Endnu en gang, efter et par sekunder, ændres statusen for **GSTR-2B** til "
":guilabel:`Behandles`. Det betyder, at Odoo afstemmer **GSTR-2B**-rapporten "
"med dine Odoo-fakturaer;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:586
msgid ""
"Once it is done, the status of the **GSTR-2B** report changes to "
"either :guilabel:`Matched` or :guilabel:`Partially Matched`;"
msgstr ""
"Når det er færdigt, ændres statusen for **GSTR-2B**-rapporten til enten "
":guilabel:`Matchet` eller :guilabel:`Delvist matchet`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:589
msgid "If the status is :guilabel:`Matched`:"
msgstr "Hvis statusen er :guilabel:`Matchet`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-2B Matched"
msgstr "GSTR-2B matchet"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:594
msgid ""
"If the status is :guilabel:`Partially Matched`, you can review and modify "
"the bills by clicking :guilabel:`View Reconciled Bills`. This will display "
"categorized discrepancies, such as bills missing in Odoo or GSTR-2. After "
"making the necessary corrections, click :guilabel:`re-match` to update the "
"reconciliation and ensure accuracy before finalizing the report."
msgstr ""
"Hvis statusen er :guilabel:`Delvist matchet`, kan du gennemgå og ændre "
"fakturaerne ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Vis afstemte fakturaer`. Dette vil "
"vise kategoriserede uoverensstemmelser, såsom fakturaer der mangler i Odoo "
"eller GSTR-2. Efter at have foretaget de nødvendige rettelser skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`genmatch` for at opdatere afstemningen og sikre nøjagtighed "
"før færdiggørelse af rapporten."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-2B Partially Matched"
msgstr "GSTR-2B delvist matchet"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:606
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:651
msgid "GSTR-3 report"
msgstr "GSTR-3-rapport"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:608
msgid ""
"The :ref:`GSTR-3 <india/gstr-3_report>` report is a monthly summary of "
"**sales** and **purchases**. This return is auto-generated by extracting "
"information from **GSTR-1** and **GSTR-2**."
msgstr ""
":ref:`GSTR-3 <india/gstr-3_report>`-rapporten er en månedlig oversigt over "
"**salg** og **køb**. Denne rapport genereres automatisk ved at udtrække "
"oplysninger fra **GSTR-1** og **GSTR-2**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:611
msgid ""
"Users can compare the **GSTR-3** report with the **GSTR-3** report available "
"on the **GST portal** to verify if they match by clicking :guilabel:`GSTR-3 "
"Report`;"
msgstr ""
"Brugere kan sammenligne **GSTR-3**-rapporten med **GSTR-3**-rapporten, der "
"er tilgængelig på **GST-portalen**, for at verificere, om de stemmer "
"overens, ved at klikke på :guilabel:`GSTR-3 Report`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:614
msgid ""
"Once the **GSTR-3** report has been verified by the user and the tax amount "
"on the **GST portal** has been paid. Once paid, the report can be **closed** "
"by clicking :guilabel:`Closing Entry`;"
msgstr ""
"Når **GSTR-3**-rapporten er blevet verificeret af brugeren, og skattebeløbet "
"på **GST-portalen** er blevet betalt, kan rapporten **lukkes** ved at klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Closing Entry`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-3"
msgstr "GSTR-3"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:620
msgid ""
"In :guilabel:`Closing Entry`, add the tax amount paid on the **GST portal** "
"using challan, and click :guilabel:`POST` to post the :guilabel:`Closing "
"Entry`;"
msgstr ""
"I :guilabel:`Closing Entry` tilføjes det skattebeløb, der er betalt på **GST-"
"portalen** ved hjælp af challan, og klik på :guilabel:`POST` for at bogføre "
":guilabel:`Closing Entry`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-3 Post Entry"
msgstr "GSTR-3 bogfør post"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:626
msgid "Once posted, the **GSTR-3** report status changes to :guilabel:`Filed`."
msgstr ""
"Når den er bogført, ændres **GSTR-3**-rapportens status til "
":guilabel:`Filed`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-3 Filed"
msgstr "GSTR-3 indsendt"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:634
msgid "Tax reports"
msgstr "Skatterapport"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:639
msgid "GSTR-1 report"
msgstr "GSTR-1-rapport"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:641
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`GSTR-1` report is divided into sections. It displays "
"the :guilabel:`Base` amount, :abbr:`CGST (Central Goods and Services "
"Tax)`, :abbr:`SGST (State Goods and Service Tax)`, :abbr:`IGST (Integrated "
"Goods and Services Tax)`, and :guilabel:`CESS` for each section."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`GSTR-1`-rapporten er opdelt i sektioner. Den "
"viser :guilabel:`grundbeløbet`, :abbr:`CGST (Central Goods and Services "
"Tax)`, :abbr:`SGST (State Goods and Service Tax)`, :abbr:`IGST (Integrated "
"Goods and Services Tax)` og :guilabel:`CESS` for hver sektion."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-1 Report"
msgstr "GSTR-1-rapport"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:653
msgid "The :guilabel:`GSTR-3` report contains different sections:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`GSTR-3`-rapporten indeholder forskellige sektioner:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:655
msgid "Details of inward and outward supply subject to a **reverse charge**;"
msgstr ""
"Detaljer om indgående og udgående leverancer underlagt **omvendt "
"betalingspligt**;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:656
msgid "Eligible :abbr:`ITC (Income Tax Credit)`;"
msgstr "Berettiget :abbr:`ITC (Income Tax Credit)`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:657
msgid "Values of **exempt**, **Nil-rated**, and **non-GST** inward supply;"
msgstr ""
"Værdier af **fritaget**, **nul-sats** og **ikke-GST** indgående leverancer;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:658
msgid "Details of inter-state supplies made to **unregistered** persons."
msgstr ""
"Detaljer om leverancer mellem delstater til **uregistrerede** personer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-3 Report"
msgstr "GSTR-3-rapport"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:664
msgid "Profit and Loss (IN) report"
msgstr "Resultatopgørelse (IN)-rapport"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:666
msgid ""
"This is a :guilabel:`Profit and Loss` report that displays the balances for "
"**Opening Stock** and **Closing Stock**. It helps users using Continental "
"accounting to accurately determine the cost of goods (i.e :guilabel:`Opening "
"Stock` + purchases during the period - :guilabel:`Closing Stock`)."
msgstr ""
"Dette er en :guilabel:`Resultatopgørelse`-rapport, der viser saldoene for "
"**Primobeholdning** og **Ultimobeholdning**. Den hjælper brugere, der bruger "
"kontinental bogføring, med at bestemme vareomkostningerne nøjagtigt "
"(dvs. :guilabel:`Primobeholdning` + køb i perioden "
"- :guilabel:`Ultimobeholdning`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "Profit and Loss report"
msgstr "Resultatopgørelsesrapport"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:676
msgid "TDS/TCS threshold alert"
msgstr "TDS/TCS-tærskeladvarsler"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:678
msgid ""
":abbr:`TDS (tax deducted at source)` and :abbr:`TCS (tax collected at "
"source)` are tax provisions under Indian law, triggered when transaction "
"amounts exceed specified thresholds. This alert notifies users when the "
"value of invoices or bills surpasses these limits, prompting the application "
"of the appropriate TDS/TCS."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`TDS (tax deducted at source)` og :abbr:`TCS (tax collected at "
"source)` er skattebestemmelser under indisk lovgivning, der udløses, når "
"transaktionsbeløb overstiger specificerede tærskler. Denne advarsel "
"informerer brugere, når værdien af fakturaer eller regninger overstiger "
"disse grænser, hvilket kræver anvendelse af den relevante TDS/TCS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:683
msgid ""
"To configure Odoo to advise you on when to apply TDS/TCS, set "
"the :guilabel:`TDS/TCS section` field on the corresponding account in the "
"chart of accounts. Odoo will display a banner suggesting the TDS/TCS section "
"under which tax might be applicable when recording an invoice or bill."
msgstr ""
"For at konfigurere Odoo til at rådgive dig om, hvornår TDS/TCS skal "
"anvendes, skal du indstille feltet :guilabel:`TDS/TCS-sektion` på den "
"tilsvarende konto i kontoplanen. Odoo viser et banner, der foreslår TDS/TCS-"
"sektionen, under hvilken skat kan være gældende, når du registrerer en "
"faktura eller regning."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:690
msgid "Navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""
"Naviger til :menuselection:`Bogføring --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:691
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Indian Integration` section, enable the :guilabel:`TDS and "
"TCS` feature."
msgstr ""
"I sektionen :guilabel:`Indian Integration` aktiveres funktionen "
":guilabel:`TDS and TCS`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:692
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Chart of "
"Accounts`."
msgstr ""
"Naviger til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Konfiguration --> Kontoplaner`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:693
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`View` on the desired account, and set the :guilabel:`TDS/"
"TCS Section` field."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Vis` på den ønskede konto, og indstil "
"feltet :guilabel:`TDS/TCS-sektion`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:696
msgid ""
"The TDS/TCS sections are pre-configured with threshold limits. If you need "
"to modify these limits, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --"
"> Taxes`. In the :guilabel:`Advanced Options` tab, click on the  :icon:`fa-"
"arrow-right` :guilabel:`(internal link)` icon of the :guilabel:`Section` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"TDS/TCS-sektionerne er forudkonfigureret med tærskelgrænser. Hvis du skal "
"ændre disse grænser, skal du gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> "
"Konfiguration --> Skatter`. I fanen :guilabel:`Avancerede indstillinger` "
"skal du klikke på ikonet :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(internt link)` i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Sektion`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "TDS/TCS section modify"
msgstr "Ændring af TDS/TCS-sektion"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:705
msgid "Applying TCS/TDS on invoices and bills"
msgstr "Anvende TCS/TDS på fakturaer og regninger"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:707
msgid ""
"Based on the account used on the customer invoice or vendor bill, Odoo "
"checks the TCS/TDS threshold limit. If the limit specified in "
"the :guilabel:`TCS/TDS Section` of the account is exceeded, Odoo displays an "
"alert that suggests applying the appropriate TCS/TDS. The alert will "
"disappear once the TCS/TDS is applied."
msgstr ""
"Baseret på den konto, der bruges på kundefakturaen eller "
"leverandørregningen, kontrollerer Odoo TCS/TDS-tærskelgrænsen. Hvis grænsen "
"specificeret i :guilabel:`TCS/TDS-sektionen` for kontoen overskrides, viser "
"Odoo en advarsel, der foreslår at anvende den relevante TCS/TDS. Advarslen "
"forsvinder, når TCS/TDS er anvendt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:None
msgid "TCS advice"
msgstr "TCS-rådgivning"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:715
msgid ""
"**TCS** is directly applicable in the tax on the invoice lines. To apply "
"**TDS**, click the :guilabel:`TDS Entry` smart button on the vendor bill/"
"payment. The popup window allows specifying the TDS details. Confirm the "
"entry to apply the TDS."
msgstr ""
"**TCS** kan anvendes direkte i skatten på fakturalinjerne. For at anvende "
"**TDS** skal du klikke på smartknappen :guilabel:`TDS-post` på "
"kreditorfakturaen/betalingen. Popup-vinduet giver mulighed for at angive TDS-"
"detaljerne. Bekræft posten for at anvende TDS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:None
msgid "TDS application"
msgstr "TDS-anvendelse"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:722
msgid ""
"In Odoo, the aggregate total is calculated for partners sharing the same PAN "
"number, across all company branches."
msgstr ""
"I Odoo beregnes den samlede total for partnere, der deler det samme PAN-"
"nummer, på tværs af alle virksomhedsafdelinger."

