#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:204
msgid "Insurance"
msgstr "Forsikring"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:206
msgid ""
"For **health service providers**, you can send insurance information about "
"the parent and branch companies and update it in eTIMS. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll to "
"the :guilabel:`Kenya eTIMS Integration` section, and fill in "
"the :guilabel:`Code`, :guilabel:`Name`, and :guilabel:`Rate` fields. "
"Click :guilabel:`Send Insurance Details` when done."
msgstr ""
"For **sundhedstjenesteudbydere** kan du sende forsikringsoplysninger om "
