#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/luxembourg.rst:256
msgid "FAIA audit file export"
msgstr "FAIA-revisionsfil eksport"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/luxembourg.rst:258
msgid ""
":abbr:`FAIA (Fichier d’Audit Informatisé AED)` is the Luxembourgish version "
"of the SAF-T format for accounting data interchange. It allows exporting "
"complete accounting data for a period from a taxpayer's accounting system to "
"the tax office."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`FAIA (Fichier d'Audit Informatisé AED)` er den luxembourgske version "
"af SAF-T-formatet til udveksling af regnskabsdata. Det giver mulighed for at "
"eksportere komplette regnskabsdata for en periode fra en skatteyders "
"regnskabssystem til skatteforvaltningen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/luxembourg.rst:262
msgid ""
"Odoo can generate an XML file in the FAIA format that contains the entire "
"accounting data for a period."
msgstr ""
"Odoo kan generere en XML-fil i FAIA-formatet, der indeholder alle "
"regnskabsdata for en periode."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/luxembourg.rst:265
msgid ""
"To generate and download the FAIA file, open :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Reporting --> General Ledger`, choose the desired period, click "
"the :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`action menu`) icon, and "
"click :guilabel:`Export FAIA`."
msgstr ""
"For at generere og downloade FAIA-filen skal du "
"åbne :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Rapportering --> Hovedbog`, vælge den "
"ønskede periode, klikke på :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`handlingsmenu`) ikonet "
"og klikke på :guilabel:`Eksporter FAIA`."

