msgid ""
"To have a direct connection between Odoo and a PoS terminal, a :doc:`Stripe "
"terminal <../../../applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/"
"terminals/stripe>` is needed. Odoo supports the **EFTPOS** payment solution."
msgstr ""
"For at have en direkte forbindelse mellem Odoo og en POS-terminal er der "
"brug for en :doc:`Stripe-terminal <../../../applications/sales/point_of_sale/"
"payment_methods/terminals/stripe>`. Odoo understøtter **EFTPOS**-"
"betalingsløsningen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:338
msgid ""
"A Stripe payment terminal is not needed to use Odoo as the main POS system. "
"The only drawback of not using Stripe is that cashiers must manually enter "
"the final payment amount on the terminal."
msgstr ""
"En Stripe-betalingsterminal er ikke nødvendig for at bruge Odoo som "
"hovedsystem til POS. Den eneste ulempe ved ikke at bruge Stripe er, at "
"kasserere skal indtaste det endelige betalingsbeløb manuelt på terminalen."

