"drive.google.com/file/d/1BkrMTZIiJyi5XI0lGMi3rbMzHddOL1pa/view?"
"usp=sharing>`_."
msgstr ""
"Da Digiflow er den OSE, der bruges i IAP, skal du tilknytte den som den "
"officielle OSE for din virksomhed på SUNAT-hjemmesiden. Dette er en enkel "
"proces. For mere information, se venligst `OSE Affiliation guide <https://"
"drive.google.com/file/d/1BkrMTZIiJyi5XI0lGMi3rbMzHddOL1pa/view?"
"usp=sharing>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:240
msgid ""
"Register Digiflow as the authorized PSE, please check `PSE Affiliation guide "
"<https://drive.google.com/file/d/1QZoqWvtQERpS0pqp6LcKmw7EBlm9EroU/view?"
"usp=sharing>`_."
msgstr ""
"Registrer Digiflow som den autoriserede PSE, se venligst `PSE Affiliation "
"guide <https://drive.google.com/file/d/1QZoqWvtQERpS0pqp6LcKmw7EBlm9EroU/"
"view?usp=sharing>`_."

