msgstr ""
"Hvis din virksomhed ønsker at underskrive direkte med SUNAT, er det muligt "
"at vælge denne mulighed i din konfiguration. I dette tilfælde skal du "
"overveje: - Få godkendt SUNAT-certificeringsprocessen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:270
msgid "Provide you SOL credentials."
msgstr "Angiv dine SOL-legitimationsoplysninger."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:273
msgid ""
"When using direct connection with the SUNAT, the SOL User must be set with "
"the Company RUT + User Id. Example: ``20121888549JOHNSMITH``"
msgstr ""
"Når der bruges direkte forbindelse med SUNAT, skal SOL-brugeren angives med "
"virksomhedens RUT + bruger-id. Eksempel: ``20121888549JOHNSMITH``"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:277
msgid "Testing environment"
msgstr "Testmiljø"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:279
msgid ""
"Odoo provides a testing environment that can be activated before your "
"company goes into production."
msgstr ""
"Odoo tilbyder et testmiljø, der kan aktiveres, før din virksomhed går i "
"produktion."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:281
msgid ""
"When using the testing environment and the IAP signature, you don’t need to "
"buy testing credits for your transactions as all of them are validated by "
"default."
msgstr ""
"Når du bruger testmiljøet og IAP-signaturen, behøver du ikke købe testkredit "
"til dine transaktioner, da de alle valideres som standard."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:285
msgid ""
"By default the databases are set to work on production, make sure to enable "
"the testing mode if needed."
msgstr ""
"Som standard er databaserne indstillet til at arbejde i produktion. Sørg for "
"at aktivere testtilstand, hvis det er nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:291
msgid ""
"In case you don’t use Odoo IAP, in order to generate the electronic invoice "
"signature, a digital certificate with the extension ``.pfx`` is required. "
"Proceed to this section and load your file and password."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du ikke bruger Odoo IAP, kræves et digitalt certifikat med udvidelsen "
"``.pfx`` for at generere den elektroniske fakturasignatur. Gå til dette "
"afsnit og indlæs din fil og adgangskode."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "EDI Certificate wizard."
msgstr "EDI-certifikatguide."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:301
msgid ""
"The official currency exchange rate in Peru is provided by the SUNAT. Odoo "
"can connect directly to its services and get the currency rate either "
"automatically or manually."
msgstr ""
"Den officielle valutakurs i Peru leveres af SUNAT. Odoo kan oprette "
"forbindelse direkte til deres tjenester og hente valutakursen enten "
"automatisk eller manuelt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "SUNAT displayed in Multicurrency Service option."
msgstr "SUNAT vist i valget Flervalutaservice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:307
msgid ""
"Please refer to the next section in our documentation for more information "
"about :doc:`multicurrencies <../accounting/get_started/multi_currency>`."
msgstr ""
"Se venligst næste afsnit i vores dokumentation for mere information "
"om :doc:`flervalutaer <../accounting/get_started/multi_currency>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:313
msgid "Configure Master data"
msgstr "Konfigurer Hoveddata"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:318
msgid ""
"As part of the localization module the taxes are created automatically with "
"their related financial account and electronic invoice configuration."
msgstr ""
"Som en del af lokaliseringsmodulet oprettes skatterne automatisk med deres "
"tilknyttede finanskonto og konfiguration af elektronisk faktura."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "List of default taxes."
msgstr "Liste over standardskatter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:325
msgid "EDI Configuration"
msgstr "EDI-konfiguration"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:327
msgid ""
"As part of the taxes configuration, there are three new fields required for "
"electronic invoice, the taxes created by default have this data included, "
"but in case you create new taxes make sure you fill in the fields:"
msgstr ""
"Som en del af skattekonfigurationen er der tre nye påkrævede felter til "
"elektronisk faktura. De skatter, der oprettes som standard, har disse data "
"inkluderet, men hvis du opretter nye skatter, skal du sørge for at udfylde "
"felterne:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Taxes EDI data for Peru."
msgstr "Skatter EDI-data for Peru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:335
msgid "Fiscal Positions"
msgstr "Bogføringsgrupper"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:337
msgid ""
"There are two main fiscal positions included by default when you install the "
"Peruvian localization."
msgstr ""
"Der er to hovedskattepositioner inkluderet som standard, når du installerer "
"den peruvianske lokalisering."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:339
msgid ""
"**Extranjero - Exportación**: Set this fiscal position on customers for "
"Exportation transactions."
msgstr ""
"**Extranjero - Exportación**: Angiv denne skatteposition på kunder til "
"eksporttransaktioner."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:341
msgid "**Local Peru**: Set this fiscal position on local customers."
msgstr "**Local Peru**: Angiv denne skatteposition på lokale kunder."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:346
msgid ""
"In some Latin American countries, including Peru, some accounting "
"transactions like invoices and vendor bills are classified by document "
"types, defined by the government fiscal authorities, in this case by the "
"SUNAT."
msgstr ""
"I nogle latinamerikanske lande, herunder Peru, klassificeres nogle "
"regnskabstransaktioner som fakturaer og kreditorfakturaer efter "
"dokumenttyper, der er defineret af statens skattemyndigheder, i dette "
"tilfælde af SUNAT."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:350
msgid ""
"Each document type can have a unique sequence per journal where it is "
"assigned. As part of the localization, the Document Type includes the "
"country on which the document is applicable;the data is created "
"automatically when the localization module is installed."
msgstr ""
"Hver dokumenttype kan have en unik sekvens pr. journal, hvor den er tildelt. "
"Som en del af lokaliseringen inkluderer dokumenttypen det land, som "
"dokumentet gælder for; dataene oprettes automatisk, når lokaliseringsmodulet "
"installeres."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:354
msgid ""
"The information required for the document types is included by default so "
"the user does not need to fill anything on this view:"
msgstr ""
"De oplysninger, der kræves til dokumenttyperne, er inkluderet som standard, "
"så brugeren ikke behøver at udfylde noget i denne visning:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Document Type list."
msgstr "Dokumenttypeliste."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:361
msgid ""
"Currently the documents supported on customer invoices are: Invoice, Boleta, "
"Debit Note and Credit Note."
msgstr ""
"I øjeblikket er de understøttede dokumenter på kundefakturaer: faktura, "
"boleta, debetnota og kreditnota."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:367
msgid ""
"When creating Sales Journals, the following information must be filled, in "
"addition to the standard fields on the Journals:"
msgstr ""
"Når der oprettes salgsjournaler, skal følgende oplysninger udfyldes ud over "
"standardfelterne på journalerne:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:371
msgid "Use Documents"
msgstr "Brug dokumenter"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:373
msgid ""
"This field is used to define if the journal uses Document Types. It is only "
"applicable to Purchase and Sales journals, which are the ones that can be "
"related to the different set of document types available in Peru. By "
"default, all the sales journals created use documents."
msgstr ""
"Dette felt bruges til at definere, om journalen bruger dokumenttyper. Det "
"gælder kun for indkøbs- og salgsjournaler, som er dem, der kan relateres til "
"det forskellige sæt af dokumenttyper, der er tilgængelige i Peru. Som "
"standard bruger alle oprettede salgsjournaler dokumenter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:378
msgid "Electronic Data Interchange"
msgstr "Elektronisk Data Udveksling"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:380
msgid ""
"This section indicates which EDI workflow is used in the invoice, for Peru "
"we must select “Peru UBL 2.1”."
msgstr ""
"Dette afsnit angiver, hvilken EDI-arbejdsgang der bruges i fakturaen, for "
"Peru skal vi vælge \"Peru UBL 2.1\"."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Journal EDI field."
msgstr "Journal EDI-felt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:387
msgid ""
"By default, the value Factur-X (FR) is always displayed, make sure you can "
"uncheck it manually."
msgstr ""
"Som standard vises værdien Factur-X (FR) altid, sørg for at du kan fravælge "
"den manuelt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:393
msgid "Identification Type and VAT"
msgstr "Identificeringstype og moms"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:395
msgid ""
"As part of the Peruvian localization, the identification types defined by "
"the SUNAT are now available on the Partner form, this information is "
"essential for most transactions either on the sender company and in the "
"customer, make sure you fill in this information in your records."
msgstr ""
"Som en del af den peruvianske lokalisering er de identifikationstyper, der "
"er defineret af SUNAT, nu tilgængelige på partnerformularen. Disse "
"oplysninger er essentielle for de fleste transaktioner, både for den "
"afsendende virksomhed og for kunden. Sørg for at udfylde disse oplysninger i "
"dine poster."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Partner identification type."
msgstr "Partneridentifikationstype."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:403
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:113
msgid "Product"
msgstr "Produkt"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:405
msgid ""
"Additional to the basic information in your products, for the Peruvian "
"localization, the UNSPC Code on the product is a required value to be "
"configured."
msgstr ""
"Ud over de grundlæggende oplysninger i dine produkter er UNSPC-koden på "
"produktet en påkrævet værdi, der skal konfigureres for den peruvianske "
"lokalisering."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "UNSPC Code on products."
msgstr "UNSPC-kode på produkter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:418
msgid "EDI Elements"
msgstr "EDI-elementer"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:420
msgid ""
"Once you have configured your master data, the invoices can be created from "
"your sales order or manually. Additional to the basic invoice information "
"described on :doc:`our page about the invoicing process <../accounting/"
"customer_invoices/overview>`, there are a couple of fields required as part "
"of the Peru EDI:"
msgstr ""
"Når du har konfigureret dine stamdata, kan fakturaerne oprettes fra din "
"salgsordre eller manuelt. Ud over de grundlæggende fakturainformationer "
"beskrevet på :doc:`vores side om faktureringsprocessen <../accounting/"
"customer_invoices/overview>` er der et par felter påkrævet som del af Peru "
"EDI:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:425
msgid ""
"**Document type**: The default value is “Factura Electronica” but  you can "
"manually change the document type if needed and select Boleta for example."
msgstr ""
"**Dokumenttype**: Standardværdien er \"Factura Electronica\", men du kan "
"manuelt ændre dokumenttypen, hvis det er nødvendigt, og vælge f.eks. Boleta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:0
msgid "Invoice document type field on invoices."
msgstr "Fakturadokumenttypefelt på fakturaer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:431
msgid ""
"**Operation type**: This value is required for Electronic Invoice and "
"indicates the transaction type, the default value is “Internal Sale” but "
"another value can be selected manually when needed, for example Export of "
"Goods."
msgstr ""
"**Operationstype**: Denne værdi er påkrævet for elektronisk faktura og "
"angiver transaktionstypen. Standardværdien er \"Internal Sale\", men en "
"anden værdi kan vælges manuelt, når det er nødvendigt, f.eks. eksport af "
"varer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:0
msgid "Invoice operation type field on invoices."
msgstr "Fakturaoperationstypefelt på fakturaer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:438
msgid ""
"**EDI Affectation Reason**: In the invoice lines, additional to the Tax "
"there is a field “EDI Affectation Reason” that determines the tax scope "
"based on the SUNAT list that is displayed. All the taxes loaded by default "
"are associated with a default EDI affection reason, if needed you can "
"manually select another one when creating the invoice."
msgstr ""
"**EDI-påvirkningsårsag**: I fakturalinjerne er der ud over afgiften et felt "
"\"EDI-påvirkningsårsag\", der bestemmer afgiftsomfanget baseret på SUNAT-"
"listen, der vises. Alle afgifter, der er indlæst som standard, er tilknyttet "
"en standard-EDI-påvirkningsårsag. Hvis det er nødvendigt, kan du manuelt "
"vælge en anden, når du opretter fakturaen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:0
msgid "Tax affectation reason in invoice line."
msgstr "Skatteindvirkningsårsag i fakturalinje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:449
msgid ""
"Once you check all the information in your invoice is correct, you can "
"proceed to validate it. This action registers the account move and triggers "
"the Electronic invoice workflow to send it to the OSE and the SUNAT. The "
"following message is displayed at the top of the invoice:"
msgstr ""
"Når du har kontrolleret, at alle oplysninger på din faktura er korrekte, kan "
"du fortsætte med at validere den. Denne handling registrerer "
"kontoposteringen og udløser workflowet for elektronisk faktura for at sende "
"den til OSE og SUNAT. Følgende meddelelse vises øverst på fakturaen:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Sending of EDI Invoice in blue."
msgstr "Afsendelse af EDI-faktura i blåt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:456
msgid ""
"Asynchronous means that the document is not sent automatically after the "
"invoice has been posted."
msgstr ""
"Asynkron betyder, at dokumentet ikke sendes automatisk, efter fakturaen er "
"bogført."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:461
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:548
msgid "Electronic Invoice Status"
msgstr "Status for elektronisk faktura"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:463
msgid ""
"**To be Sent**: Indicates the document is ready to be sent to the OSE, this "
"can be done either automatically by Odoo with a *cron* that runs every hour, "
"or the user can send it immediately by clicking on the button “Sent now”."
msgstr ""
"**Skal sendes**: Angiver, at dokumentet er klar til at blive sendt til OSE. "
"Dette kan ske enten automatisk af Odoo med en *cron*, der kører hver time, "
"eller brugeren kan sende det øjeblikkeligt ved at klikke på knappen \"Send "
"nu\"."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Send EDI manually."
msgstr "Send EDI manuelt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:470
msgid ""
"**Sent**: Indicates the document was sent to the OSE and was successfully "
"validated. As part of the validation a ZIP file is downloaded and a message "
"is logged in the chatter indicating the correct Government validation."
msgstr ""
"**Sendt**: Angiver, at dokumentet blev sendt til OSE og blev valideret "
"korrekt. Som en del af valideringen downloades en ZIP-fil, og en besked "
"logges i chatten, der angiver den korrekte myndighedsvalidering."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Message on chatter when the invoice is valid."
msgstr "Besked i chatten, når fakturaen er gyldig."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:477
msgid ""
"In case there is a validation error the Electronic Invoice status remains in "
"“To be sent” so the corrections can be made and the invoice can be sent "
"again."
msgstr ""
"I tilfælde af en valideringsfejl forbliver statusen for elektronisk faktura "
"\"Skal sendes\", så rettelserne kan foretages, og fakturaen kan sendes igen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:481
msgid ""
"One credit is consumed each time that you send a document for validation, in "
"this sense if an error is detected on an invoice and you send it one more "
"time, two credits are consumed in total."
msgstr ""
"Der forbruges én kredit, hver gang du sender et dokument til validering. "
"Hvis der opdages en fejl på en faktura, og du sender den én gang til, "
"forbruges der i alt to kreditter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:486
msgid "Common Errors"
msgstr "Almindelige fejl"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:488
msgid ""
"There are multiple reasons behind a rejection from the OSE or the SUNAT, "
"when this happens Odoo sends a message at the top of the invoice indicating "
"the error details and in the most common cases a hint to fix the issue."
msgstr ""
"Der er flere årsager til en afvisning fra OSE eller SUNAT. Når dette sker, "
"sender Odoo en besked øverst på fakturaen, der angiver fejldetaljerne og i "
"de mest almindelige tilfælde et hint til at løse problemet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:492
msgid "If a validation error is received, you have two options:"
msgstr "Hvis du modtager en valideringsfejl, har du to muligheder:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:494
msgid ""
"In case the error is related to master data on the partner, customer or "
"taxes, you can simply apply the change on the record (example customer "
"identification type) and once it is done click on the Retry button."
msgstr ""
"Hvis fejlen er relateret til stamdata på partneren, kunden eller afgifterne, "
"kan du blot anvende ændringen på posten (f.eks. kundens "
"identifikationstype), og når det er gjort, klikke på knappen Prøv igen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:497
msgid ""
"If the error is related to some data recorded on the invoice directly "
"(Operation type, missing data on the invoice lines), the correct solution is "
"to reset the invoice to Draft, apply the changes, and then send the invoice "
"again to the SUNAT for another validation."
msgstr ""
"Hvis fejlen er relateret til nogle data, der er registreret direkte på "
"fakturaen (operationstype, manglende data på fakturalinjerne), er den "
"korrekte løsning at nulstille fakturaen til kladde, anvende ændringerne og "
"derefter sende fakturaen igen til SUNAT for en ny validering."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:0
msgid "List of common errors on invoices."
msgstr "Liste over almindelige fejl på fakturaer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:504
msgid ""
"For more detail please refert to `Common errors in SUNAT <https://"
"www.nubefact.com/codigos-error-sunat/>`_."
msgstr ""
"For mere information, se venligst `Common errors in SUNAT <https://"
"www.nubefact.com/codigos-error-sunat/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:508
msgid "Invoice PDF Report"
msgstr "Faktura PDF-rapport"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:510
msgid ""
"After the invoice is accepted and validated by the SUNAT, the invoice PDF "
"report can be printed. The report includes a QR code, indicating the invoice "
"is a valid fiscal document."
msgstr ""
"Efter at fakturaen er accepteret og valideret af SUNAT, kan faktura-PDF-"
"rapporten udskrives. Rapporten indeholder en QR-kode, som angiver, at "
"fakturaen er et gyldigt regnskabsdokument."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Invoice PDF report."
msgstr "Faktura PDF-rapport."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:517
msgid "IAP Credits"
msgstr "IAP Kredit"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:519
msgid ""
"Odoo’s Electronic IAP offers 1000 credits for free, after these credits are "
"consumed in your production database, your company must buy new credits in "
"order to process your transactions."
msgstr ""
"Odoos Electronic IAP tilbyder 1000 kreditter gratis. Efter at disse "
"kreditter er brugt i din produktionsdatabase, skal din virksomhed købe nye "
"kreditter for at behandle dine transaktioner."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:522
msgid ""
"Once you run out of credits a red label is displayed at the top of the "
"invoice indicating that additional credits are required, you can easily buy "
"them by accessing the link provided in the message."
msgstr ""
"Når du løber tør for kreditter, vises en rød etiket øverst på fakturaen, som "
"angiver, at yderligere kreditter er påkrævet. Du kan nemt købe dem ved at "
"klikke på linket i meddelelsen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Buying credits in the IAP."
msgstr "Køb af kreditter i IAP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:529
msgid ""
"In the IAP service includes packages with different pricing based on the "
"number of credits. The price list in the IAP is always displayed in EUR."
msgstr ""
"IAP-tjenesten inkluderer pakker med forskellig prissætning baseret på "
"antallet af kreditter. Prislisten i IAP vises altid i EUR."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:533
msgid "Special Use cases"
msgstr "Særlige anvendelsestilfælde"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:536
msgid "Cancellation process"
msgstr "Annulleringsproces"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:538
msgid ""
"Some scenarios require an invoice cancellation, for example, when an invoice "
"was created by mistake. If the invoice was already sent and validated by the "
"SUNAT, the correct way to proceed is by clicking on the button Request "
"Cancellation:"
msgstr ""
"Nogle scenarier kræver annullering af en faktura, for eksempel når en "
"faktura er oprettet ved en fejl. Hvis fakturaen allerede er sendt og "
"valideret af SUNAT, er den korrekte fremgangsmåde at klikke på knappen Anmod "
"om annullering:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Request invoice cancellation button."
msgstr "Knap til anmodning om annullering af faktura."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:545
msgid "In order to cancel an invoice, please provide a cancellation Reason."
msgstr "For at annullere en faktura skal du angive en årsag til annulleringen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:550
msgid ""
"**To Cancel**:  Indicates the cancellation request is ready to be sent to "
"the OSE, this can be done either automatically by Odoo with a *cron* that "
"runs every hour, or the user can send it immediately by clicking on the "
"button “Send now”. Once it is sent, a cancellation ticket is created, as a "
"result the next message and CDR File are logged in the chatter:"
msgstr ""
"**At annullere**: Angiver at annulleringsanmodningen er klar til at blive "
"sendt til OSE. Dette kan enten gøres automatisk af Odoo med en *cron*, der "
"kører hver time, eller brugeren kan sende den med det samme ved at klikke på "
"knappen \"Send nu\". Når den er sendt, oprettes en annulleringsbillet, og "
"som resultat logges følgende besked og CDR-fil i chatten:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Cancellation CDR sent by the SUNAT."
msgstr "Annullerings-CDR sendt af SUNAT."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:558
msgid ""
"**Cancelled**: Indicates the cancellation request was sent to the OSE and "
"was successfully validated. As part of the validation a ZIP file is "
"downloaded and a message is logged in the chatter indicating the correct "
"Government validation."
msgstr ""
"**Annulleret**: Angiver at annulleringsanmodningen blev sendt til OSE og "
"blev valideret korrekt. Som en del af valideringen downloades en ZIP-fil, og "
"en besked logges i chatten, som angiver den korrekte myndighedsvalidering."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Invoice after cancellation."
msgstr "Faktura efter annullering."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:566
msgid "One credit is consumed on each cancellation request."
msgstr "Én kredit forbruges ved hver annulleringsanmodning."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:571
msgid ""
"When creating exportation invoices, take into account the next "
"considerations:"
msgstr "Når du opretter eksportfakturaer, skal du tage højde for følgende:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:573
msgid "The Identification type on your customer must be Foreign ID."
msgstr "Identificeringstypen på din kunde skal være Udenlandsk ID."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:574
msgid "Operation type in your invoice must be an Exportation one."
msgstr "Operationstypen på din faktura skal være en eksporttype."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:575
msgid "The taxes included in the invoice lines should be EXP taxes."
msgstr "Skatterne inkluderet på fakturalinjerne skal være EXP-skatter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:581
msgid "Advance Payments"
msgstr "Forskudsbetalinger"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:584
msgid ""
"Because the SUNAT does not allow negative in filings, a workaround is "
"required when reporting down payments."
msgstr ""
"Da SUNAT ikke tillader negative værdier i indberetninger, kræves en løsning, "
"når der rapporteres acontobetalinger."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:587
msgid "Open the sales order requiring a down payment."
msgstr "Åbn salgsordren, der kræver en acontobetaling."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:588
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Create Invoice` and select :guilabel:`Down payment "
"(percentage)` or :guilabel:`Down payment (fixed amount)`. Enter the amount, "
"then click :guilabel:`Create Draft`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Opret faktura` og vælg :guilabel:`Acontobetaling "
"(procent)` eller :guilabel:`Acontobetaling (fast beløb)`. Indtast beløbet og "
"klik derefter på :guilabel:`Opret udkast`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:590
msgid ""
"Check that all information is correct. If yes, click :guilabel:`Confirm`. If "
"not, make the necessary changes before confirming."
msgstr ""
"Kontroller, at alle oplysninger er korrekte. Hvis ja, klik "
"på :guilabel:`Bekræft`. Hvis ikke, foretag de nødvendige ændringer før "
"bekræftelse."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:592
msgid ""
"Navigate back to the sales order and click :menuselection:`Create Invoice --"
"> Regular Invoice --> Create Draft` to proceed with invoice creation."
msgstr ""
"Naviger tilbage til salgsordren og klik på :menuselection:`Opret faktura --> "
"Almindelig faktura --> Opret kladde` for at fortsætte med fakturaoprettelse."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:594
msgid ""
"From the invoice, remove the section separation *and* the down payment "
"invoice line by clicking the :icon:`fa-trash-o` :guilabel:`(trash bin)` "
"icon, and :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Fra fakturaen skal du fjerne sektionsadskillelsen *og* linjen med "
"acontobetalingsfakturaen ved at klikke på :icon:`fa-trash-"
"o` :guilabel:`(papirkurv)`-ikonet og :guilabel:`Bekræft`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:0
msgid "Removing invoice lines and section."
msgstr "Fjernelse af fakturalinjer og sektion."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:600
msgid ""
"Once confirmed, click :guilabel:`Credit Note`, then :guilabel:`Reverse`, and "
"finally remove all invoice lines by clicking the :icon:`fa-trash-"
"o` :guilabel:`(trash bin)` icon. The invoice should be clear of any product."
msgstr ""
"Når den er bekræftet, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Kreditnota`, "
"derefter :guilabel:`Tilbagefør`, og til sidst fjerne alle fakturalinjer ved "
"at klikke på :icon:`fa-trash-o` :guilabel:`(papirkurv)`-ikonet. Fakturaen "
"skal være fri for alle produkter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:603
msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Add a line`. Click the :icon:`fa-"
"bars` :guilabel:`(bars)` icon, enter a description (e.g., `Down Payment`), "
"and input the :guilabel:`Price`. Click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Tilføj en linje`. Klik på :icon:`fa-"
"bars` :guilabel:`(streger)`-ikonet, indtast en beskrivelse (f.eks. "
"`Acontobetaling`), og indtast :guilabel:`Pris`. Klik på :guilabel:`Bekræft`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:0
msgid "Adding down payment description."
msgstr "Tilføjelse af acontobetalingsbeskrivelse."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:609
msgid ""
"After issuing the credit note and if not done automatically, reconcile it "
"with the final invoice."
msgstr ""
"Efter udstedelse af kreditnotaen, og hvis det ikke sker automatisk, skal du "
"afstemme den med den endelige faktura."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:610
msgid ""
"The final invoice's remaining balance **must** be paid with a regular "
"payment transaction."
msgstr ""
"Den endelige fakturas resterende saldo **skal** betales med en almindelig "
"betalingstransaktion."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:613
msgid "Detraction Invoices"
msgstr "Fradragsfakturaer"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:615
msgid ""
"When creating invoices that is subject to Detractions, take into account the "
"next considerations:"
msgstr ""
"Når du opretter fakturaer, der er underlagt fradrag, skal du tage højde for "
"følgende:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:617
msgid ""
"All the products included in the invoice must have these fields configured:"
msgstr ""
"Alle produkter inkluderet på fakturaen skal have disse felter konfigureret:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:0
msgid "Detraction fields on products."
msgstr "Fradragsfelter på produkter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:622
msgid "Operation type in your invoice must be ``1001``"
msgstr "Operationstypen på din faktura skal være ``1001``"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:0
msgid "Detraction code on invoices."
msgstr "Fradragskode på fakturaer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:628
msgid "Credit Notes"
msgstr "Kreditnotaer"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:630
msgid ""
"When a correction or refund is needed over a validated invoice, a credit "
"note must be generated, for this just click on the button “Add Credit Note”, "
"a part of the Peruvian localization you need to prove a Credit Reason "
"selecting one of the options in the list."
msgstr ""
"Når en korrektion eller refusion er nødvendig for en valideret faktura, skal "
"der oprettes en kreditnota. Klik blot på knappen \"Tilføj kreditnota\". Som "
"en del af den peruvianske lokalisering skal du angive en kreditårsag ved at "
"vælge en af mulighederne på listen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Add Credit Note from invoice."
msgstr "Tilføj kreditnota fra faktura."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:638
msgid ""
"When creating your first credit Note, select the Credit Method: Partial "
"Refund, this allows you to define the credit note sequence."
msgstr ""
"Při vytváření první kreditní faktury vyberte metodu kreditace: Částečný "
"refundace, což vám umožní definovat sekvenci kreditní faktury."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:641
msgid "By default the Credit Note is set in the document type:"
msgstr "Ve výchozím nastavení je kreditní faktura nastavena v typu dokumentu:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Credit Note document type."
msgstr "Kreditnota dokumenttype."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:646
msgid ""
"To finish the workflow please follow the instructions on :doc:`our page "
"about Credit Notes <../accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes>`."
msgstr ""
"For at afslutte arbejdsgangen skal du følge instruktionerne på :doc:`vores "
"side om kreditnotaer <../accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:650
msgid ""
"The EDI workflow for the Credit notes works in the same way as the invoices."
msgstr ""
"EDI workflow pro kreditní faktury funguje stejným způsobem jako faktury."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:653
msgid "Debit Notes"
msgstr "Debetnoter"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:655
msgid ""
"As part of the Peruvian localization, besides creating credit notes from an "
"existing document you can also create debit Notes. For this just use the "
"button “Add Debit Note”."
msgstr ""
"V rámci peruánské lokalizace můžete kromě vytváření kreditních faktur z "
"existujícího dokumentu také vytvářet debetní faktury. K tomu stačí použít "
"tlačítko „Přidat debetní fakturu\"."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:658
msgid "By default the Debit Note is set in the document type."
msgstr "Ve výchozím nastavení je debetní faktura nastavena v typu dokumentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:663
msgid "Electronic delivery guide 2.0"
msgstr "Elektronisk leveringsguide 2.0"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:665
msgid ""
"The *Guía de Remisión Electrónica* (GRE) is an electronic document generated "
"by the shipper to support the transportation or transfer of goods from one "
"place to another, such as a warehouse or establishment. In Odoo, there are "
"several configuration steps needed before you can successfully use this "
"feature."
msgstr ""
"*Guía de Remisión Electrónica* (GRE) er et elektronisk dokument genereret af "
"afsenderen til at understøtte transporten eller overførslen af varer fra ét "
"sted til et andet, såsom et lager eller en virksomhed. I Odoo er der flere "
"konfigurationstrin, der er nødvendige, før du kan bruge denne funktion."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:670
msgid ""
"The use of the *guía de remisión electrónica* electronic document is "
"mandatory and required by |SUNAT| for taxpayers who need to transfer their "
"products, except those under the *Single Simplified Regime* (régimen único "
"simplificado or RUS)."
msgstr ""
"Brugen af det elektroniske dokument *guía de remisión electrónica* er "
"obligatorisk og krævet af |SUNAT| for skatteydere, der har brug for at "
"transportere deres produkter, undtagen dem under *Single Simplified Regime* "
"(régimen único simplificado eller RUS)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:675
msgid "Delivery guide types"
msgstr "Leveringsguidetyper"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:678
msgid "Sender"
msgstr "Afsender"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:680
msgid ""
"The *Sender* delivery guide type is issued when a sale is made, a service is "
"rendered (including processing), goods are assigned for use, or goods are "
"transferred between premises of the same company and others."
msgstr ""
"Leveringsguidetypen *afsender* udstedes, når der foretages et salg, leveres "
"en service (herunder forarbejdning), tildeles varer til brug, eller varer "
"overføres mellem lokaler i samme virksomhed og andre."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:684
msgid ""
"This delivery guide is issued by the owner of the goods (i.e., the sender) "
"at the beginning of the shipment. The sender delivery guide is supported in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Denne leveringsguide udstedes af ejeren af varerne (dvs. afsenderen) ved "
"forsendelsens begyndelse. Afsenderleveringsguiden understøttes i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:688
msgid "`SUNAT guía de remisión <https://www.gob.pe/7899-guia-de-remision>`_"
msgstr "`SUNAT guía de remisión <https://www.gob.pe/7899-guia-de-remision>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:691
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:820
msgid "Carrier"
msgstr "Fragtfirma"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:693
msgid ""
"The *Carrier* delivery guide type justifies the transportation service the "
"driver (or carrier) performs."
msgstr ""
"Leveringsguidetypen *transportør* begrunder den transportservice, som "
"chaufføren (eller transportøren) udfører."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:696
msgid ""
"This delivery guide is issued by the carrier and must be issued to each "
"shipper when the shipment goes through public transport."
msgstr ""
"Denne leveringsguide udstedes af transportøren og skal udstedes til hver "
"afsender, når forsendelsen foregår via offentlig transport."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:700
msgid "The carrier delivery guide is **not** supported in Odoo."
msgstr "Transportørleveringsguiden understøttes **ikke** i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:703
msgid ""
"`SUNAT guía de remisión transportista <https://tefacturo.pe/blog/sunat/guia-"
"de-remision-electronica/guia-de-remision-transportista/>`_"
msgstr ""
"`SUNAT guía de remisión transportista <https://tefacturo.pe/blog/sunat/guia-"
"de-remision-electronica/guia-de-remision-transportista/>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:707
msgid "Transportation types"
msgstr "Transporttyper"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:710
msgid "Private"
msgstr "Privat"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:712
msgid ""
"The *Private* transportation type option is used when the owner transfers "
"goods using their own vehicles. In this case, a sender's delivery guide must "
"be issued."
msgstr ""
"Transporttypen *privat* anvendes, når ejeren overfører varer ved hjælp af "
"egne køretøjer. I dette tilfælde skal der udstedes en afsenderleveringsguide."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:716
msgid "Public"
msgstr "Offentlig"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:718
msgid ""
"The *Public* transportation type option is used when an external carrier "
"moves the goods. In this case, two delivery guides must be issued: the "
"sender's delivery guide and the carrier's delivery guide."
msgstr ""
"Transporttypen *offentlig* anvendes, når en ekstern transportør flytter "
"varerne. I dette tilfælde skal der udstedes to leveringsguider: "
"afsenderleveringsguiden og transportørleveringsguiden."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:723
msgid "Direct submission to SUNAT"
msgstr "Direkte indsendelse til SUNAT"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:725
msgid ""
"The creation of the |GRE| delivery guide in Odoo **must** be sent directly "
"to the |SUNAT|, regardless of the electronic document provider: IAP, "
"Digiflow, or |SUNAT|."
msgstr ""
"Oprettelsen af |GRE|-leveringsguiden i Odoo **skal** sendes direkte til |"
"SUNAT|, uanset udbyderen af elektroniske dokumenter: IAP, Digiflow eller |"
"SUNAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:729
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:476
msgid "Required information"
msgstr "Påkrævet information"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:731
msgid ""
"Version 2.0 of the electronic delivery guide requires additional information "
"on the general configuration, vehicles, contacts, and products. In the "
"general configuration, it is necessary to add new credentials that you can "
"retrieve from the |SUNAT| portal."
msgstr ""
"Version 2.0 af den elektroniske leveringsguide kræver yderligere information "
"om den generelle konfiguration, køretøjer, adressebog og produkter. I den "
"generelle konfiguration er det nødvendigt at tilføje nye loginoplysninger, "
"som du kan hente fra |SUNAT|-portalen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:736
msgid "Cancellations"
msgstr "Annulleringer"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:738
msgid ""
"**Both** the sender and the carrier can cancel the electronic waybill as "
"long as the following conditions are met:"
msgstr ""
"**Både** afsenderen og transportøren kan annullere den elektroniske "
"fragtseddel, så længe følgende betingelser er opfyldt:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:741
msgid "The shipment has not been initiated."
msgstr "Forsendelsen er ikke blevet påbegyndt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:742
msgid ""
"If the shipment has been initiated, the receiver **must** be changed before "
"reaching the final destination."
msgstr ""
"Hvis forsendelsen er blevet påbegyndt, **skal** modtageren ændres, før den "
"endelige destination nås."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:746
msgid ""
"The |SUNAT| no longer uses the term \"Anula\", but now uses the term \"Dar "
"de baja\" for cancellations."
msgstr ""
"|SUNAT| bruger ikke længere udtrykket \"Anula\", men bruger nu udtrykket "
"\"Dar de baja\" for annulleringer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:750
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:108
#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/paypal.rst:56
msgid "Testing"
msgstr "Afprøver"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:752
msgid ""
"The |SUNAT| does not support a test environment. This means that any "
"delivery guides that were generated by mistake **will** be sent to the |"
"SUNAT|."
msgstr ""
"|SUNAT| understøtter ikke et testmiljø. Dette betyder, at eventuelle "
"leveringsguider, der blev genereret ved en fejl, **vil** blive sendt til |"
"SUNAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:755
msgid ""
"If, by mistake, the waybill was created in this environment, it is necessary "
"to delete it from the |SUNAT| portal."
msgstr ""
"Hvis fragtsedlen ved en fejl blev oprettet i dette miljø, er det nødvendigt "
"at slette den fra |SUNAT|-portalen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:762
msgid ""
"Electronic sender's |GRE| is currently the only supported type of waybill in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Elektronisk afsenders |GRE| er i øjeblikket den eneste understøttede type "
"fragtseddel i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:763
msgid ""
"The delivery guide is dependent on the Odoo *Inventory* app, "
"the :guilabel:`l10n_pe_edi` and :guilabel:`l10n_pe` modules."
msgstr ""
"Leveringsguiden er afhængig af Odoo-appen *Lager*, :guilabel:`l10n_pe_edi`- "
"og :guilabel:`l10n_pe`-modulerne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:765
msgid ""
"A second user **must** be added for the creation of electronic documents."
msgstr ""
"En anden bruger **skal** tilføjes for at oprette elektroniske dokumenter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:767
msgid ""
"After following the steps to configure the :ref:`electronic invoicing <peru-"
"accounting-settings>` and the :ref:`master data <peru-"
"master_data>`, :ref:`install <general/install>` the :guilabel:`Peruvian - "
