msgstr ""
"Efter at have fulgt trinene til at konfigurere :ref:`elektronisk fakturering "
"<peru-accounting-settings>` og :ref:`stamdata <peru-master_data>`, skal "
"du :ref:`installere <general/install>` modulet :guilabel:`Peruvian - "
"Electronic Delivery Note 2.0` (`l10n_pe_edi_stock_20`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:771
msgid ""
"Next, you need to retrieve the *client ID* and *client secret* from |SUNAT|. "
"To do so, follow the `manual de servicios web plataforma nueva GRE <https://"
"cpe.sunat.gob.pe/sites/default/files/inline-files/"
"Manual_Servicios_GRE%20%281%29.pdf>`_."
msgstr ""
"Dernæst skal du hente *klient-id* og *klienthemmelighed* fra |SUNAT|. For at "
"gøre dette skal du følge `manual de servicios web plataforma nueva GRE "
"<https://cpe.sunat.gob.pe/sites/default/files/inline-files/"
"Manual_Servicios_GRE%20%281%29.pdf>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:776
msgid ""
"In the |SUNAT| portal, it is important to have the correct access rights "
"enabled, as they may differ from the user set for electronic invoicing."
msgstr ""
"På |SUNAT|-portalen er det vigtigt at have de korrekte adgangsrettigheder "
"aktiveret, da de kan adskille sig fra den bruger, der er indstillet til "
"elektronisk fakturering."

