#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:899
msgid "`Diferente prefijo para productos (T001 en algunos, T002 en otros)`"
msgstr "`Diferente prefijo para productos (T001 en algunos, T002 en otros)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:901
msgid ""
"At the moment, Odoo does not support the automation of prefixes for "
"products. This can be done manually for each product output. This can also "
"be done for non-storable products. However, keep in mind that there will be "
"no traceability."
msgstr ""
"I øjeblikket understøtter Odoo ikke automatisering af præfikser for "
"produkter. Dette kan gøres manuelt for hvert produktoutput. Dette kan også "
"gøres for ikke-lagrbare produkter. Husk dog, at der ikke vil være nogen "
"sporbarhed."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:904
msgid ""
"`2325 - GrossWeightMeasure - El dato no cumple con el formato establecido "
"\"Hace falta el campo\" \"Peso\"\" en el producto`"
msgstr ""
"`2325 - GrossWeightMeasure - El dato no cumple con el formato establecido "
"\"Hace falta el campo\" \"Peso\"\" en el producto`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:907
msgid ""
"This error occurs when the weight on the product is set as `0.00`. To fix "
"this, you need to cancel the waybill and recreate it. Make sure that you fix "
"the weight on the product before creating the new waybill, or it will result "
"in the same error."
msgstr ""
"Denne fejl opstår, når vægten på produktet er indstillet til `0.00`. For at "
"løse dette skal du annullere fragtsedlen og genoprette den. Sørg for at "
"rette vægten på produktet, før du opretter den nye fragtseddel, ellers vil "
"det resultere i samme fejl."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:910
msgid ""
"`JSONDecodeError: Expecting value: line 1 column 1 (char 0) when creating a "
"Delivery Guide`"
msgstr ""
"`JSONDecodeError: Expecting value: line 1 column 1 (char 0) when creating a "
"Delivery Guide`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:912
msgid ""
"This error is typically generated due to SOL user issues. Verify the user's "
"connection with the |SUNAT|; the SOL user must be established with the "
"company RUT + user ID. For example `2012188549JOHNSMITH`."
msgstr ""
"Denne fejl genereres typisk på grund af SOL-brugerproblemer. Verificer "
"brugerens forbindelse til |SUNAT|; SOL-brugeren skal være oprettet med "
"virksomhedens RUT + bruger-id. For eksempel `2012188549JOHNSMITH`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:915
msgid ""
"`El número de documento relacionado al traslado de mercancía no cumple con "
"el formato establecido: error: documento relacionado`"
msgstr ""
"`El número de documento relacionado al traslado de mercancía no cumple con "
"el formato establecido: error: documento relacionado`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:918
msgid ""
"The *Related Document Type* and *Related Document Number* fields only apply "
"to invoices and receipts."
msgstr ""
"Felterne *Relateret dokumenttype* og *Relateret dokumentnummer* gælder kun "
"for fakturaer og kvitteringer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:920
msgid "`400 Client error: Bad Request for URL`"
msgstr "`400 Client error: Bad Request for URL`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:922
msgid ""
"This error is not solvable from Odoo; it is advised you reach out to the |"
"SUNAT| and verify the user. It may be necessary to create a new user."
msgstr ""
"Denne fejl kan ikke løses fra Odoo; det anbefales, at du kontakter |SUNAT| "
"og verificerer brugeren. Det kan være nødvendigt at oprette en ny bruger."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:925
msgid ""
"`Invalid content was found starting with element 'cac:BuyerCustomerParty'`"
msgstr ""
"'Neplatný obsah byl nalezen začínající prvkem 'cac:BuyerCustomerParty''"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:927
msgid ""
"This error occurs when the transfer reason is set as *other*. Please select "
"another option. Following to the official documentation of the |SUNAT|'s "
"waybill guide, the transfer reasons *03 (sale with shipment to third party)* "
"or *12 (others)* does not work in Odoo, since you should not have an empty "
"or blank customer."
msgstr ""
"Tato chyba se vyskytuje, když je důvod přesunu nastaven jako *jiný*. Vyberte "
"prosím jinou možnost. Podle oficiální dokumentace průvodce nákladním listem |"
"SUNAT| důvody přesunu *03 (prodej s dodáním třetí straně)* nebo *12 "
"(ostatní)* v Odoo nefungují, protože byste neměli mít prázdného nebo "
"nespecifikovaného zákazníka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:931
msgid "`Duda cliente: consumo de créditos IAP al usar GRE 2.0`"
msgstr "Dotaz klienta: spotřeba kreditů IAP při použití GRE 2.0"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:933
msgid ""
"For live clients using IAP, no credit is consumed (in theory) because it "
"does not go through the OSE, i.e., these documents are directly sent to the |"
"SUNAT|."
msgstr ""
"U živých klientů používajících IAP se nespotřebovává žádný kredit "
"(teoreticky), protože to neprochází OSE, tj. tyto dokumenty jsou odesílány "
"přímo do |SUNAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:935
msgid "`Errores con formato credenciales GRE 2.0 (traceback error)`"
msgstr "Chyby s formátem pověření GRE 2.0 (chyba traceback)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:937
msgid ""
"Odoo currently throws an error with a traceback instead of a message that "
"the credentials are not correctly configured in the database. If this occurs "
"on your database, please verify your credentials."
msgstr ""
"Odoo v současnosti vyvolá chybu s traceback místo zprávy, že pověření nejsou "
"správně nakonfigurována v databázi. Pokud k tomu ve vaší databázi dojde, "
"ověřte prosím svá pověření."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:944
msgid ""
"First, :ref:`install <general/install>` the **Peruvian eCommerce** "
"(`l10n_pe_website_sale`) module."
msgstr ""
"Nejprve :ref:`nainstalujte <general/install>` modul **Peruvian eCommerce** "
"(`l10n_pe_website_sale`)."

