msgstr ""
"Indtast et navn til dit KSeF-certifikat i det nyligt aktiverede felt, og "
"vælg derefter :guilabel:`Opret og rediger...` fra rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:87
msgid ""
"In the pop-up window, click :guilabel:`Upload your file` and select your "
"**certificate** (`.pem`). In the :guilabel:`Certificate Password` field, "
"enter the password created during the certificate application on the KSeF "
"platform."
msgstr ""
"I pop op-vinduet skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Upload din fil` og vælge dit "
"**certifikat** (`.pem`). I feltet :guilabel:`Certifikatadgangskode` skal du "
"indtaste den adgangskode, der blev oprettet under certifikatansøgningen på "
"KSeF-platformen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:90
msgid ""
"Once the certificate is uploaded, the :guilabel:`Private Key` field appears. "
"Click the empty field, select :guilabel:`Create` from the drop-down menu, "
"and enter your **private key**. The **public key** is embedded within the "
"`.pem` file and is automatically filled in."
msgstr ""
"Når certifikatet er uploadet, vises feltet :guilabel:`Privat nøgle`. Klik på "
"det tomme felt, vælg :guilabel:`Opret` fra rullemenuen, og indtast din "
"**private nøgle**. Den **offentlige nøgle** er indlejret i `.pem`-filen og "
"udfyldes automatisk."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:93
msgid "Finally, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr "Til sidst klik :guilabel:`Gem`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:100
msgid ""
"The KSeF invoicing workflow requires address information related to the "
"company that sends the invoices and the customers who receive them:"
msgstr ""
"KSeF-faktureringsarbejdsgangen kræver adresseoplysninger relateret til det "
"firma, der sender fakturaerne, og de kunder, der modtager dem:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:103
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Users & Companies --> Companies` and "
"select the company that will use KSeF."
msgstr ""
"Gå til :menuselection:`Indstillinger --> Brugere & Virksomheder --> "
"Virksomheder`, og vælg det firma, der skal bruge KSeF."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:105
msgid ""
"Fill in the :guilabel:`Company Name`, :guilabel:`VAT` (Tax ID), "
"and :guilabel:`Country`. If desired, fill in additional optional fields such "
"as :guilabel:`Street`, :guilabel:`City`, :guilabel:`State`, "
"and :guilabel:`ZIP`."
msgstr ""
"Udfyld :guilabel:`Firmanavn`, :guilabel:`Moms` (skatte-id) "
"og :guilabel:`Land`. Udfyld om ønsket yderligere valgfrie felter "
"såsom :guilabel:`Gade`, :guilabel:`By`, :guilabel:`Delstat` "
"og :guilabel:`Postnummer`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:110
msgid "The :guilabel:`Country` must be set to :guilabel:`Poland`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Land` skal være indstillet til :guilabel:`Polen`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:111
msgid "The company must have a valid Polish VAT (**NIP**) number."
msgstr "Firmaet skal have et gyldigt polsk momsnummer (**NIP**)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:113
msgid ""
"Open the **Accounting** app, and go to :menuselection:`Customers --> "
"Customers`."
msgstr "Åbn **Bogføring**-appen, og gå til :menuselection:`Kunder --> Kunder`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:114
msgid ""
"For each customer whose invoices will be sent to KSeF, click on the customer "
"to open the form view, and complete the :guilabel:`Country` "
"and :guilabel:`VAT`. If desired, fill in additional optional fields such "
"as :guilabel:`Street`, :guilabel:`City`, :guilabel:`State`, "
"and :guilabel:`ZIP`."
msgstr ""
"For hver kunde, hvis fakturaer skal sendes til KSeF, skal du klikke på "
"kunden for at åbne formularvisningen og udfylde :guilabel:`Land` "
"og :guilabel:`Moms`. Udfyld om ønsket yderligere valgfrie felter "
"såsom :guilabel:`Gade`, :guilabel:`By`, :guilabel:`Delstat` "
"og :guilabel:`Postnummer`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:122
msgid "Sending invoices to KSeF via Odoo"
msgstr "Afsendelse af fakturaer til KSeF via Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:124
msgid ""
"Once you have :ref:`linked your company with KSeF <localizations/poland/"
"linking-ksef>` and :ref:`configured your company and contacts <localizations/"
"poland/company-and-contacts>`, you can send invoices to KSeF directly "
