#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:128
msgid ""
"Open the **Accounting** app, go to :menuselection:`Customers --> Invoices`, "
"and select a posted invoice."
msgstr ""
"Åbn **Bogføring**-appen, gå til :menuselection:`Kunder --> Fakturaer`, og "
"vælg en bogført faktura."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:131
msgid ""
"In the pop-up window, check :guilabel:`Send via KSeF (e-Faktura)` and "
"click :guilabel:`Send`."
msgstr ""
"I pop op-vinduet skal du markere :guilabel:`Send via KSeF (e-Faktura)` og "
"klikke på :guilabel:`Send`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:133
msgid "When an invoice is sent, Odoo automatically:"
msgstr "Når en faktura sendes, udfører Odoo automatisk:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:135
msgid "Generates the invoice in the required FA(3) XML format."
msgstr "Genererer fakturaen i det krævede FA(3) XML-format."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:136
msgid "Submits the file to KSeF for validation."
msgstr "Indsender filen til KSeF til validering."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:137
msgid "Saves a copy of the XML file in the invoice's chatter."
msgstr "Gemmer en kopi af XML-filen i fakturaens chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:139
msgid ""
"You can also manually export the FA(3) XML and check the invoice's "
"processing status:"
msgstr ""
"Du kan også manuelt eksportere FA(3) XML og kontrollere fakturaens "
"behandlingsstatus:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:141
msgid "Open a posted invoice."
msgstr "Åbn en bogført faktura."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:142
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Export FA(3) XML` to download the invoice as an XML file to "
"your browser's download folder."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Eksporter FA(3) XML` for at downloade fakturaen som en "
"XML-fil til din browsers downloadmappe."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:144
msgid ""
"To check its processing status, click :guilabel:`Check invoice status` next "
"to the export option."
msgstr ""
"For at kontrollere dens behandlingsstatus skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Kontroller fakturastatus` ved siden af eksportindstillingen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:145
msgid ""
"The live status is displayed on the invoice under the :guilabel:`eInvoice "
"status` field."
msgstr ""
"Statusen for live vises på fakturaen under feltet :guilabel:`eInvoice "
"status`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:147
msgid ""
"Once the Polish government officially registers the invoice on the KSeF "
"platform, it assigns an **Official Receipt Certificate (UPO)**. To view it, "
"open the invoice and click :guilabel:`Check invoice UPO`."
msgstr ""
"Når den polske regering officielt registrerer fakturaen på KSeF-platformen, "
"tildeler den en **Officiel modtagelsesattest (UPO)**. For at se den skal du "
"åbne fakturaen og klikke på :guilabel:`Tjek faktura UPO`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:154
msgid "Automatic bill import"
msgstr "Automatisk regningsimport"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:156
msgid ""
"By default, the Polish localization automatically fetches vendor bills from "
"KSeF every three hours. To adjust this frequency or toggle the feature:"
msgstr ""
"Som standard henter den polske lokaliseringsversion automatisk "
"leverandørregninger fra KSeF hver tredje time. For at justere denne frekvens "
"eller skifte funktionen til/fra:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:159
msgid ""
"With :doc:`developer mode <../../general/developer_mode>` activated, open "
"the **Settings** app and go to :menuselection:`Technical --> Scheduled "
"Actions`."
msgstr ""
"Med :doc:`udviklertilstand <../../general/developer_mode>` aktiveret skal du "
"åbne appen **Indstillinger** og gå til :menuselection:`Teknisk --> Planlagte "
"handlinger`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:161
msgid ""
"Search for and open :guilabel:`Polish eInvoice: Download vendor bills from "
"KSeF`."
msgstr ""
"Søg efter og åbn :guilabel:`Polsk eFaktura: Download leverandørregninger fra "
"KSeF`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:162
msgid "Use the :guilabel:`Execute Every` field to change the frequency."
msgstr "Brug feltet :guilabel:`Udfør hver` til at ændre frekvensen."

