#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:8
msgid ""
"PayNow is a payment service platform that allows customers to make instant "
"domestic payments to individuals and merchants in Singapore dollars via "
"online and mobile banking."
msgstr ""
"PayNow er en betalingstjenesteplatform, der giver kunder mulighed for at "
"foretage øjeblikkelige indenlandske betalinger til enkeltpersoner og "
"forretninger i singaporeanske dollars via online- og mobilbank."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:18
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:None
msgid "PayNow bank account configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguration af PayNow bankkonto"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:20
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Contacts --> Configuration --> Bank Accounts` and "
"select the bank account to activate PayNow. Set the :guilabel:`Proxy Type` "
"and fill in the :guilabel:`Proxy Value` field depending on the chosen type."
msgstr ""
"Gå til :menuselection:`Adressebog --> Konfiguration --> Bankkonti` og vælg "
"den bankkonto, du vil aktivere PayNow for. Indstil :guilabel:`Proxy-type` og "
"udfyld feltet :guilabel:`Proxy-værdi` afhængigt af den valgte type."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:25
msgid ""
"The account holder's country must be set to `Singapore` on its contact form."
msgstr ""
"Kontohaverens land skal være sat til `Singapore` på dennes kontaktformular."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:None
msgid "Bank Account's journal configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguration af bankkontoens kladde"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:46
msgid "Issue invoices with PayNow QR codes"
msgstr "Udsted fakturaer med PayNow QR-koder"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:48
msgid ""
"When creating a new invoice, open the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab and set "
"the :guilabel:`Payment QR-code` option to *EMV Merchant-Presented QR-code*."
msgstr ""
"Når du opretter en ny faktura, åbn fanen :guilabel:`Anden info` og "
"indstil :guilabel:`Betalings-QR-kode` til *EMV Merchant-Presented QR-code*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:None
msgid "Select EMV Merchant-Presented QR-code option"
msgstr "Vælg indstillingen EMV Merchant-Presented QR-code"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:54
msgid ""
"Ensure that the :guilabel:`Recipient Bank` is the one you configured, as "
"Odoo uses this field to generate the PayNow QR code."
msgstr ""
"Sørg for, at :guilabel:`Modtagerbank` er den, du har konfigureret, da Odoo "
"bruger dette felt til at generere PayNow QR-koden."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/singapore.rst:67
msgid ""
"To :ref:`configure the Employment Hero API <employment_hero/configuration>` "
"for **Singapore**, use the following value as :guilabel:`Payroll URL`: "
"`HTTPS://apisg.yourpayroll.io/`."
msgstr ""
"For at :ref:`konfigurere Employment Hero API <employment_hero/"
"configuration>` til **Singapore** skal du bruge følgende værdi "
"som :guilabel:`Løn-URL`: `HTTPS://apisg.yourpayroll.io/`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:3
msgid "Spain"
msgstr "Spanien"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:10
msgid ""
