#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid "Chart of Accounts grouped by Account Type."
msgstr "Kontoplaner grupperet efter kontotype."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:208
msgid ""
"Besides structure, there are other key differences in the chart of accounts "
"in the United States, compared to other countries:"
msgstr ""
"Udover strukturen er der andre væsentlige forskelle i kontoplanen i USA "
"sammenlignet med andre lande:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:211
msgid ""
"**Specificity**: US |GAAP| often requires more detailed accounts compared to "
"some other countries. This can include separate accounts for various types "
"of revenue, expenses, and assets, providing more granular information in "
"financial reports."
msgstr ""
"**Specificitet**: Amerikansk |GAAP| kræver ofte mere detaljerede konti "
"sammenlignet med nogle andre lande. Dette kan omfatte separate konti til "
"forskellige typer indtægter, udgifter og aktiver, hvilket giver mere "
"detaljerede oplysninger i finansielle rapporter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:214
msgid ""
"**Regulatory Requirements**: In the United States, there are specific "
"regulatory requirements set by bodies such as the |SEC| for publicly traded "
"companies. These requirements may influence the structure and content of the "
"|COA| to ensure compliance with reporting standards."
msgstr ""
"**Lovkrav**: I USA er der specifikke lovkrav fastsat af organer som |SEC| "
"for børsnoterede virksomheder. Disse krav kan påvirke strukturen og "
"indholdet af |COA| for at sikre overholdelse af rapporteringsstandarder."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:217
msgid ""
"**Industry Practices**: Certain industries in the United States may have "
"unique accounting requirements or specialized |COA| structures. For example, "
"financial institutions often have specific accounts related to loans, "
"investments, and interest income."
msgstr ""
"**Branchepraksis**: Visse brancher i USA kan have unikke regnskabskrav eller "
"specialiserede |COA|-strukturer. For eksempel har finansielle institutioner "
"ofte specifikke konti relateret til lån, investeringer og renteindtægter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:220
msgid ""
"**Tax Considerations**: The |COA| may also reflect tax considerations, such "
"as accounts for deductible expenses, deferred tax assets, and liabilities, "
"to ensure compliance with tax laws and facilitate tax reporting."
msgstr ""
"**Skattemæssige hensyn**: |COA| kan også afspejle skattemæssige hensyn, "
"såsom konti for fradragsberettigede omkostninger, udskudte skatteaktiver og "
"forpligtelser for at sikre overholdelse af skattelovgivningen og lette "
"skatterapportering."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:224
msgid ""
"These differences, ultimately, should be reflected in the |COA| structure "
"itself, with the addition of new accounts, as needed, in order to meet the "
"demands of US accounting reporting requirements."
msgstr ""
"Disse forskelle bør i sidste ende afspejles i selve |COA|-strukturen med "
"tilføjelse af nye konti efter behov for at opfylde kravene til amerikansk "
"regnskabsrapportering."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:228
msgid ":ref:`Create a new account <chart-of-account/create>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Opret en ny konto <chart-of-account/create>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:236
msgid ""
"In the United States, tax rates and what is considered taxable vary by "
"jurisdiction. Default *Sales* and *Purchase* taxes are created automatically "
"when the Odoo *Accounting* application is installed. To manage existing or "
"configure additional taxes, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Taxes`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:246
msgid ""
"**Avalara AvaTax** is a cloud-based tax calculation and compliance software "
"that integrates with Odoo for several localizations. Integrating AvaTax with "
"Odoo provides real-time and region-specific tax calculations when items are "
"sold, purchased, and invoiced in the database."
msgstr ""
"**Avalara AvaTax** er en cloudbaseret software til skatteberegning og "
"compliance, der integreres med Odoo til flere lokaliseringer. Integration af "
"AvaTax med Odoo giver realtids- og regionsspecifikke skatteberegninger, når "
"varer sælges, købes og faktureres i databasen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:251
msgid ""
"AvaTax is available for integration with databases/companies that have "
"locations in the United States and Canada. Reference the :ref:`accounting/"
"avatax/fiscal_country` documentation for more information."
msgstr ""
"AvaTax er tilgængelig til integration med databaser/virksomheder, der har "
"lokationer i USA og Canada. Se :ref:`accounting/avatax/fiscal_country`-"
"dokumentationen for mere information."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:262
msgid ""
"`US Tax Compliance: AvaTax elearning video <https://www.odoo.com/slides/"
"slide/us-tax-compliance-avatax-2858?fullscreen=1>`_"
msgstr ""
"`US Tax Compliance: AvaTax eLearning-video <https://www.odoo.com/slides/"
"slide/us-tax-compliance-avatax-2858?fullscreen=1>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:272
msgid ""
"A number of :doc:`report selections <../accounting/reporting>` are readily "
"available for the US localization, under the :menuselection:`Accounting app "
"--> Reporting` drop-down menu:"
msgstr ""
"En række :doc:`rapportvalg <../accounting/reporting>` er let tilgængelige "
"for USA-lokaliseringen under rullemenuen :menuselection:`Regnskab --> "
"Rapportering`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:281
msgid ""
":ref:`Cash Flow Statement <l10n_us/cash-flow-statement>`: shows how much "
"cash and cash equivalents a company has received and spent in a given period."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:291
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Check Register`: a report that displays cash transactions "
"(regardless of the journal) with their running balance after the "
"transaction. Only visible with the *US - Accounting Reports* "
"(`l10n_us_reports`) module installed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:294
msgid ""
":ref:`1099 Report <l10n_us/1099-report>`: a CSV download of payments made to "
"non-employees in a period to file electronically in a third-party service. "
"Only visible with the *1099 Reporting* (`l10n_us_1099`) module installed."
msgstr ""
":ref:`1099-rapport <l10n_us/1099-report>`: en CSV-download af betalinger til "
"ikke-ansatte i en periode til elektronisk indsendelse i en "
"tredjepartstjeneste. Kun synlig med modulet *1099 Reporting* "
"(`l10n_us_1099`) installeret."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:300
msgid ""
"Depending on the type of report, certain filters are available at the top of "
"the dashboard:"
msgstr ""
"Afhængigt af rapporttypen er visse filtre tilgængelige øverst på dashboardet:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:302
msgid ""
"a *date* filter, indicated by a :icon:`fa-calendar` :guilabel:`(calendar)` "
"icon that precedes a date in *MM/DD/YYYY* format. Use this to select a "
"specific date or date range for the report."
msgstr ""
"et *dato*-filter, angivet med et :icon:`fa-calendar` :guilabel:`(kalender)`-"
"ikon, der står foran en dato i formatet *DD/MM/ÅÅÅÅ*. Brug dette til at "
"vælge en specifik dato eller datoperiode for rapporten."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:304
msgid ""
"a :icon:`fa-bar-chart` :guilabel:`Comparison` filter, to compare reporting "
"periods against each other"
msgstr ""
"et :icon:`fa-bar-chart` :guilabel:`Sammenligning`-filter til at sammenligne "
"rapporteringsperioder med hinanden"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:306
msgid ""
"a *journal* filter, as indicated by a :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`(book)` "
"icon and the default setting of :guilabel:`All Journals`. Use this filter to "
"specify which journals should be included in the report."
msgstr ""
"et *kladde*-filter, som angivet af et :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`(bog)`-ikon "
"og standardindstillingen :guilabel:`Alle kladder`. Brug dette filter til at "
"angive, hvilke kladder der skal medtages i rapporten."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:309
msgid ""
"an *entries type* filter, as indicated by a :icon:`fa-"
"filter` :guilabel:`(filter)` icon, with the default setting "
"of :guilabel:`Posted Entries Only, Accrual Basis`. Use this filter to "
"determine which type of journal entries should be included in the report "
"(e.g. posted or draft), along with the type of accounting method (e.g. "
"accrual or cash basis)."
msgstr ""
"et *posteringstype*-filter, som angivet af et :icon:`fa-filter` :guilabel:`"
"(filter)`-ikon, med standardindstillingen :guilabel:`Kun bogførte "
"posteringer, periodiseringsbasis`. Brug dette filter til at bestemme, "
"hvilken type kladdeposteringer der skal medtages i rapporten (f.eks. "
"bogførte eller kladder), sammen med regnskabsmetoden (f.eks. periodisering "
"eller kassebasis)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:314
msgid ""
"There are view options in this filter, as well, one that "
"will :guilabel:`Hide lines at 0` for more relevant viewing, along with "
"a :guilabel:`Split Horizontally` option to keep the report above the "
"screen's fold, removing the need to scroll."
msgstr ""
"Der er også visningsmuligheder i dette filter, en der vil :guilabel:`Skjul "
"linjer på 0` for mere relevant visning sammen med en :guilabel:`Opdel "
"horisontalt`-mulighed for at holde rapporten oven for skærmens fold og "
"fjerne behovet for at rulle."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:0
msgid ""
"Accounting method filter menu for reports, covering accrual vs. cash basis "
"methods."
msgstr ""
"Regnskabsmetodefilter-menu til rapporter, der dækker periodiserings- vs. "
"likviditetsmetoder."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:322
msgid ""
"a *decimal* filter, that by default, includes figures with cents, as "
"indicated by the :guilabel:`In .$` setting. Use the other options in the "
"drop-down menu to change figures in the report to whole numbers "
"(:guilabel:`In $`), thousands (:guilabel:`In K$`), or millions "
"(:guilabel:`In M$`) formats."
msgstr ""
"et *decimal*-filter, der som standard inkluderer tal med øre, som angivet af "
"indstillingen :guilabel:`I kr.`. Brug de andre valgmuligheder i rullemenuen "
"til at ændre tal i rapporten til hele tal (:guilabel:`I kr`), tusinder "
"(:guilabel:`I t.kr`) eller millioner (:guilabel:`I mio.kr`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:326
msgid ""
"a report *customization* filter, indicated by the :icon:`fa-"
"cogs` :guilabel:`(gears)` icon. Use this filter to customize the current "
"report's sections and line items, or build new reports, as desired."
msgstr ""
"et rapport-*tilpasnings*filter, angivet med :icon:`fa-cogs` :guilabel:`"
"(tandhjul)`-ikonet. Brug dette filter til at tilpasse den aktuelle rapports "
"sektioner og linjeposter eller bygge nye rapporter efter behov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:339
msgid ""
"The 1099 report, available by :ref:`installing <general/install>` the *1099 "
"Reporting* (`l10n_us_1099`) module, includes payments that are made to non-"
"employees across a given reporting period. Use the available CSV download "
"from the report in Odoo to file 1099 payments electronically via a third-"
"party service."
msgstr ""
"1099-rapporten, tilgængelig ved :ref:`installation <general/install>` af "
"modulet *1099 Reporting* (`l10n_us_1099`), inkluderer betalinger til ikke-"
"ansatte over en given rapporteringsperiode. Brug den tilgængelige CSV-"
"download fra rapporten i Odoo til at indberette 1099-betalinger elektronisk "
"via en tredjepartstjeneste."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:344
msgid ""
"To generate a 1099 report, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting app --> "
"Reporting --> Management: 1099 Report` to open a :guilabel:`1099 Report` "
"wizard."
msgstr ""
"For at generere en 1099-rapport skal du gå til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> "
"Rapportering --> Ledelse: 1099-rapport` for at åbne en :guilabel:`1099-"
"rapport`-guide."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:347
msgid ""
"First, enter the date range of the transactions to report in "
"the :guilabel:`Start Date` and :guilabel:`End Date` fields."
msgstr ""
"Indtast først datoområdet for de transaktioner, der skal rapporteres, i "
"felterne :guilabel:`Startdato` og :guilabel:`Slutdato`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:350
msgid ""
"Then, edit the journal items that appear on the wizard. Click :guilabel:`Add "
"a line` to add any items that are missing. Be sure to remove any items that "
"should not be included in the report by clicking :icon:`fa-"
"times` :guilabel:`(delete)` on the row."
msgstr ""
"Rediger derefter de kladdeposter, der vises i guiden. Klik "
"på :guilabel:`Tilføj en linje` for at tilføje eventuelle manglende "
"elementer. Sørg for at fjerne alle elementer, der ikke skal inkluderes i "
"rapporten, ved at klikke på :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`(slet)` på rækken."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:354
msgid ""
"Finally, once all necessary items are included in the 1099 report, click on "
"the :guilabel:`Generate` button. Doing so downloads a CSV file that groups "
"transactions by the partner that received the payments."
msgstr ""
"Når alle nødvendige elementer er inkluderet i 1099-rapporten, skal du "
"endelig klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Generer`. Dette downloader en CSV-fil, "
"der grupperer transaktioner efter den partner, der modtog betalingerne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:363
msgid ""
"Navigate to the *Cash Flow Statement* (CFS) dashboard by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Reporting --> Statement Reports: Cash "
"Flow Statement`. From here, |CFS| reports can be generated using the "
"various :ref:`filters <l10n_us/report-filters>` that are available at the "
"top of the dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Gå til *Cash Flow Statement* (CFS)-dashboardet ved at gå "
"til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Rapportering --> Opgørelsesrapporter: Cash "
"Flow Statement`. Herfra kan |CFS|-rapporter genereres ved hjælp af de "
"forskellige :ref:`filtre <l10n_us/report-filters>`, der er tilgængelige "
"øverst på dashboardet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:368
msgid ""
"Odoo uses the *direct* cash flow method to compile cash flow statements, "
"which measures actual cash inflows and outflows from the company's "
"operations, such as when cash is received from customers or when cash "
"payments are made to suppliers."
msgstr ""
"Odoo bruger den *direkte* cash flow-metode til at sammensætte "
"pengestrømsopgørelser, som måler faktiske pengestrømme ind og ud fra "
"virksomhedens aktiviteter, såsom når der modtages kontanter fra kunder, "
"eller når der foretages kontante betalinger til leverandører."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:372
msgid ""
"By default, an account labeled with any of the three "
"default :guilabel:`Tags` on the :guilabel:`Chart of Accounts` dashboard will "
"be included in the report, which includes: :guilabel:`Operating "
"Activities`, :guilabel:`Financing Activities`, and :guilabel:`Investing & "
"Extraordinary Activities`."
msgstr ""
"Som standard vil en konto mærket med en af de tre standard-:guilabel:`Tags` "
"på :guilabel:`Kontoplaner`-dashboardet blive inkluderet i rapporten, hvilket "
"omfatter: :guilabel:`Driftsaktiviteter`, "
":guilabel:`Finansieringsaktiviteter` og :guilabel:`Investerings- og "
"ekstraordinære aktiviteter`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid ""
"Examples of tagged accounts that are included in the Cash Flow Statement in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Eksempler på taggede konti, der er inkluderet i pengestrømsopgørelsen i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:381
msgid "Additionally, the cash flow statement in Odoo:"
msgstr "Derudover gælder følgende for pengestrømsopgørelsen i Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:383
msgid ""
"is limited to the *Bank* and *Cash* journals to reflect money coming in or "
"out; and"
msgstr ""
"er begrænset til *Bank* og *Kontant* journaler for at afspejle penge, der "
"kommer ind eller går ud; og"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:384
msgid ""
"also contains *Expenses* accounts, to show the counterpart transactions "
"versus *Bank* or *Cash* journal entries, while excluding |AR| and |AP| "
"activity."
msgstr ""
"indeholder også *Øvrige omkostninger* konti for at vise modposttransaktioner "
"i forhold til *Bank* eller *Kontant* journalposteringer, samtidig med at |"
"AR| og |AP| aktivitet ekskluderes."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:388
msgid ""
"Create a vendor bill for $100, as an operating expense (not |AP|). Doing so "
"will **not** reflect a transaction on the cash flow statement. However, "
"register a corresponding payment for $100, and the transaction **will** "
"reflect on the cash flow statement as :guilabel:`Cash paid for operating "
"activities`."
msgstr ""
"Opret en leverandørfaktura for $100 som en driftsomkostning (ikke |AP|). "
"Dette vil **ikke** afspejle en transaktion på pengestrømsopgørelsen. Hvis du "
"derimod registrerer en tilsvarende betaling på $100, **vil** transaktionen "
"blive afspejlet på pengestrømsopgørelsen som :guilabel:`Kontanter betalt for "
"driftsaktiviteter`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:0
msgid ""
"Example of a bill registered as an operating expense as part of a cash flow "
"statement."
msgstr ""
"Eksempel på en faktura registreret som en driftsomkostning som del af en "
"pengestrømsopgørelse."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:413
msgid ""
"Using checks is still a common payment practice in the US. Be sure the *US "
"Checks Layout* (`l10n_us_check_printing`) module for the US localization "
"is :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Brug af checks er stadig en almindelig betalingspraksis i USA. Sørg for, at "
"modulet *US Checks Layout* (`l10n_us_check_printing`) til den amerikanske "
"lokalisering er :ref:`installeret <general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:420
msgid ""
"Select a pre-printed or blank :guilabel:`Check Layout` from the drop-down "
"menu:"
msgstr "Vælg et fortrykt eller tomt :guilabel:`Check-layout` fra rullelisten:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:422
msgid ":guilabel:`Print Check (Top) - US`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Udskriv check (top) - US`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:423
msgid ":guilabel:`Print Check (Middle) - US`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Udskriv check (midt) - US`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:424
msgid ":guilabel:`Print Check (Bottom) - US`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Udskriv check (bund) - US`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:425
msgid ":guilabel:`Print Blank Check (Top) - US`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Udskriv tom check (top) - US`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:426
msgid ":guilabel:`Print Blank Check (Middle) - US`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Udskriv tom check (midt) - US`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:427
msgid ":guilabel:`Print Blank Check (Bottom) - US`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Udskriv tom check (bund) - US`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:431
msgid ""
"Optionally set a :guilabel:`Check Top Margin` and :guilabel:`Check Left "
"Margin`, if required."
msgstr ""
"Angiv eventuelt en :guilabel:`Øverste checkmargen` og :guilabel:`Venstre "
"checkmargen`, hvis det er nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:436
msgid ""
"Pre-printed check formats (non-blank checks) require pre-printed paper from "
"a third-party vendor. `Pre-printed checks from checkdepot.net <https://"
"checkdepot.net/collections/odoo-checks>`_ are recommended."
msgstr ""
"Fortrykte checkformater (ikke-tomme checks) kræver fortrykt papir fra en "
"tredjepartsleverandør. `Fortrykte checks fra checkdepot.net <https://"
"checkdepot.net/collections/odoo-checks>`_ anbefales."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:441
msgid ""
"Use one of the blank check formats to print the information of the check ad-"
"hoc when needed. This requires the use of both :abbr:`MICR (Magnetic Ink "
"Character Recognition)` ink or toner complying with the standards for check "
"printing, as well as `check quality paper <https://checkdepot.net/"
"collections/blank-check-paper/products/top-format-blank-check-paper-"
"cdt164>`_. Other information, such as the company name, bank account, and "
"check number, is printed when creating the blank check."
msgstr ""
"Brug et af de tomme checkformater til at udskrive checkoplysningerne ad hoc, "
"når det er nødvendigt. Dette kræver brug af både :abbr:`MICR (Magnetic Ink "
"Character Recognition)` blæk eller toner, der overholder standarderne for "
"checkudskrivning, samt `checkpapir af høj kvalitet <https://checkdepot.net/"
"collections/blank-check-paper/products/top-format-blank-check-paper-"
"cdt164>`_. Andre oplysninger, såsom firmanavn, bankkonto og checknummer, "
"udskrives ved oprettelse af den tomme check."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:456
msgid ""
"The *Payroll* application is responsible for calculating an employee's pay, "
"taking into account all work, vacation, and sick time, benefits, and "
"deductions. The *Payroll* app pulls information from the *Attendances*, "
"*Timesheets*, *Time Off*, *Employees* and *Expenses* applications, to "
"calculate the worked hours and compensation for each employee."
msgstr ""
"*Lønadministration*-applikationen er ansvarlig for at beregne en "
"medarbejders løn under hensyntagen til alt arbejde, ferie og sygetid, goder "
"og fradrag. *Lønadministration*-appen trækker information fra *Fremmøde*-, "
"*Tidsregistreringer*-, *Fravær*-, *Medarbejdere*- og *Udgifter*-"
"applikationerne for at beregne de arbejdede timer og kompensationen for hver "
"medarbejder."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:461
msgid ""
"When using an external payroll provider, such as *ADP*, it is necessary to "
"export the various payroll-related data, such as work entries, repayment of "
"expenses, taxes, commissions, and any other relevant data, so the data can "
"be uploaded into the payroll provider, who then issues the actual paychecks "
"or directly deposits the funds into an employee's bank account."
msgstr ""
"Når du bruger en ekstern lønudbyder, såsom *ADP*, er det nødvendigt at "
"eksportere de forskellige lønrelaterede data, såsom arbejdsposteringer, "
"tilbagebetaling af udgifter, skatter, provisioner og andre relevante data, "
"så dataene kan uploades til lønudbyderen, som derefter udsteder de faktiske "
"lønchecks eller direkte indsætter midlerne på en medarbejders bankkonto."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:466
msgid ""
"In order to export the payroll data, the work entries must first be "
"validated and correct. Refer to the :doc:`work entries <../../hr/payroll/"
"work_entries>` documentation for more information regarding validating work "
"entries."
msgstr ""
"For at eksportere løndata skal arbejdsposteringerne først valideres og være "
"korrekte. Se dokumentationen om :doc:`arbejdsposteringer <../../hr/payroll/"
"work_entries>` for mere information om validering af arbejdsposteringer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:470
msgid ""
"Once work entries are validated, the information can be :ref:`exported to "
"ADP <l10n_us/adp>`."
msgstr ""
"Når arbejdsposteringer er valideret, kan oplysningerne :ref:`eksporteres til "
"ADP <l10n_us/adp>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:472
msgid ""
"After payments have been issued to employees, payslips can be processed into "
"batches, validated, and posted to the corresponding accounting journals to "
"keep all financial records in Odoo current."
msgstr ""
"Efter at betalinger er udstedt til medarbejdere, kan lønsedler behandles i "
"batches, valideres og bogføres i de tilsvarende regnskabsjournaler for at "
"holde alle finansielle optegnelser i Odoo opdateret."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:478
msgid ""
"It is important to have the *Employees* application installed, and all "
"employee information populated. Several fields in both the :ref:`employee "
"records <l10n_us/payroll-employee-records>`, as well as in an :ref:`employee "
"contracts <l10n_us/payroll-employee-contracts>`, are necessary to properly "
"process the employee's pay. Ensure the following fields are filled out in "
"their respective places."
msgstr ""
"Det er vigtigt at have *Medarbejdere*-applikationen installeret og alle "
"medarbejderoplysninger udfyldt. Flere felter både i "
":ref:`medarbejderregistreringerne <l10n_us/payroll-employee-records>` samt i "
":ref:`medarbejderkontrakter <l10n_us/payroll-employee-contracts>` er "
"nødvendige for korrekt at behandle medarbejderens løn. Sørg for, at følgende "
"felter er udfyldt på deres respektive steder."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:487
msgid "Employee records"
msgstr "Medarbejderoplysninger"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:489
msgid ""
"In each employee record, there is various information the *Payroll* "
"application requires to properly process payslips, including various "
"banking, tax, and work information."
msgstr ""
"I hver medarbejderregistrering er der forskellige oplysninger, som "
"*Lønadministration*-applikationen kræver for korrekt at behandle lønsedler, "
"herunder diverse bank-, skatte- og arbejdsoplysninger."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:492
msgid ""
"Navigate to the :menuselection:`Employees app` and select an employee record "
"to view the sections of the employee form that directly affect *Payroll*:"
msgstr ""
"Naviger til :menuselection:`Medarbejdere-appen` og vælg en medarbejderpost "
"for at se de afsnit af medarbejderformularen, der direkte påvirker *løn*:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:495
msgid ":guilabel:`Work Information` tab:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Arbejdsoplysninger`-fanen:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:497
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Work Address`: indicates where the employee is located, including "
"the state, which affects the tax calculations."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Arbejdsadresse`: angiver, hvor medarbejderen er placeret, "
"inklusive staten, hvilket påvirker skatteberegningerne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:499
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Working Hours`: determines how pay is calculated, and determines "
"if an employee earns overtime."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Arbejdstid`: bestemmer, hvordan løn beregnes, og afgør, om en "
"medarbejder optjener overtidsbetaling."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:502
msgid ":guilabel:`Private Information` tab:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Private oplysninger`-fanen:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:504
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:538
msgid ""
":guilabel:`SSN No`: the last four digits of the employee's Social Security "
"Number (SSN) appears on payslips."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`CPR-nr.`: de sidste fire cifre af medarbejderens CPR-nummer vises "
"på lønsedler."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:506
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bank Account Number`: the bank account associated with the NACHA "
"payment file."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bankkontonummer`: den bankkonto, der er knyttet til NACHA-"
"betalingsfilen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:508
msgid ":guilabel:`HR Settings` tab:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`HR-indstillinger`-fanen:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:510
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Federal Tax Filing Status`: the tax status an employee uses for "
"Payroll tax calculations, which can be different from their state status."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Føderal skattestatus`: den skattestatus, en medarbejder bruger "
"til lønskatte-beregninger, som kan være anderledes end deres delstatsstatus."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:512
msgid ""
":guilabel:`State Tax Filing Status`: the tax status an employee uses for "
"their state portion of the Payroll tax calculation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Delstatsskattestatus`: den skattestatus, en medarbejder bruger "
"til deres delstatsdel af lønskatteberegningen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:514
msgid ""
":guilabel:`W-2 Form`: a US tax form indicating the summary of wages, taxes, "
"and benefits paid to an employee during a tax period (typically one year)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`W-2-formular`: en amerikansk skatteformular, der angiver "
"oversigten over løn, skatter og goder udbetalt til en medarbejder i løbet af "
"en skatteperiode (typisk ét år)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:516
msgid ""
":guilabel:`W-4 Form`: an IRS form that helps outline the amount of federal "
"taxes to withhold for an employee, which is paid to the IRS by the company."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`W-4-formular`: en IRS-formular, der hjælper med at beskrive det "
"beløb af føderale skatter, der skal tilbageholdes for en medarbejder, som "
"betales til IRS af virksomheden."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:522
msgid "Employee contracts"
msgstr "Medarbejderkontrakter"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:524
msgid ""
"Additionally, there is information that is found in an employee contract "
"that also affects the *Payroll* application."
msgstr ""
"Derudover er der information, der findes i en medarbejderkontrakt, som også "
"påvirker *Lønadministration*-applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:527
msgid ""
"Navigate to the :menuselection:`Employees app --> Employees --> Contracts` "
"and select a contract record to view the sections of a contract that "
"directly affect *Payroll*:"
msgstr ""
"Naviger til :menuselection:`Medarbejdere-appen --> Medarbejdere --> "
"Kontrakter` og vælg en kontraktpost for at se de afsnit af en kontrakt, der "
"direkte påvirker *løn*:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:530
msgid ":guilabel:`General Information`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Generelle oplysninger`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:532
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Salary Structure Type: United States: Employee`: defines when the "
"employee is paid, their working schedule, and the work entry type."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lønstrukturtype: United States: Employee`: definerer, hvornår "
"medarbejderen bliver betalt, deres arbejdsplan og arbejdsindgangstypen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:534
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Work Entry source`: determines how work entries are calculated."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Arbejdsindgangskilde`: bestemmer, hvordan arbejdsindgange "
"beregnes."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:536
msgid ":guilabel:`Salary Information` tab:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Lønoplysninger`-fanen:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:540
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Wage type`: determines how the employee is paid, wether a Fixed "
"wage (salary) or Hourly wage."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Løntype`: bestemmer, hvordan medarbejderen betales, enten en fast "
"løn eller timeløn."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:542
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Schedule Pay`: defines how often the employee is paid, "
"either :guilabel:`Annually`, :guilabel:`Semi-"
"annually`, :guilabel:`Quarterly`, :guilabel:`Bi-"
"monthly`, :guilabel:`Monthly`, :guilabel:`Semi-monthly`, :guilabel:`Bi-"
"weekly`, :guilabel:`Weekly`, or :guilabel:`Daily`. In the US, Semi-monthly "
"(24 payments a year) or bi-weekly (26 payments a year) are the most common."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lønplan`: definerer, hvor ofte medarbejderen betales, "
"enten :guilabel:`Årligt`, :guilabel:`Halvårligt`, :guilabel:`Kvartalsvis`, :guilabel:`To "
"gange om "
"måneden`, :guilabel:`Månedligt`, :guilabel:`Halvmånedligt`, :guilabel:`Hver "
"anden uge`, :guilabel:`Ugentligt` eller :guilabel:`Dagligt`. I USA er "
"halvmånedligt (24 betalinger om året) eller hver anden uge (26 betalinger om "
"året) de mest almindelige."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:546
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Wage, Yearly, and Monthly cost`: used to show the total cost of "
"an employee. It is recommended to populate the :guilabel:`Yearly` wage "
"first, as it auto-populates the other fields."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Løn, årlig og månedlig omkostning`: bruges til at vise de samlede "
"omkostninger for en medarbejder. Det anbefales først at udfylde "
"den :guilabel:`Årlige` løn, da den automatisk udfylder de øvrige felter."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:549
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pre-tax benefits`: populate this section according to the "
"employee's selections. Pre-tax benefits decrease the gross wage, which "
"lowers the base amount that is taxed. These are displayed at the beginning "
"of the payslip."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fradrag før skat`: udfyld dette afsnit i henhold til "
"medarbejderens valg. Fradrag før skat reducerer bruttolønnen, hvilket sænker "
"det grundbeløb, der beskattes. Disse vises i begyndelsen af lønsedlen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:552
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Post-tax benefits`: these benefits are deductions made *after* "
"taxes are calculated. These appear towards the end of the payslip before the "
"net amount is displayed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fradrag efter skat`: disse fradrag foretages *efter*, at "
"skatterne er beregnet. De vises mod slutningen af lønsedlen, før "
"nettobeløbet vises."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:556
msgid ":doc:`Employees documentation <../../hr/employees/new_employee>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Medarbejderdokumentation <../../hr/employees/new_employee>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:561
msgid "Export work entries to ADP"
msgstr "Eksportér arbejdsposter til ADP"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:566
msgid ""
"In order to create a report that can be uploaded to ADP, there are some "
"initial configuration steps that must be completed first."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en rapport, der kan uploades til ADP, er der nogle indledende "
"konfigurationstrin, der først skal gennemføres."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:569
msgid ""
"First, ensure the *United States - Payroll - Export to ADP* "
"(`l10n_us_hr_payroll_adp`) module is :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Sørg først for, at modulet *United States - Payroll - Export to ADP* "
"(`l10n_us_hr_payroll_adp`) er :ref:`installeret <general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:572
msgid ""
"Then, the company **must** have an *ADP Code* entered in the company "
"settings. To do so, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. Enter the :guilabel:`ADP Code` in "
"the :guilabel:`US Localization` section."
msgstr ""
"Derefter **skal** virksomheden have en *ADP-kode* indtastet i "
"virksomhedsindstillingerne. Gå til :menuselection:`Lønadministration-app --> "
"Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`. Indtast :guilabel:`ADP-kode` i "
"afsnittet :guilabel:`US-lokalisering`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:576
msgid ""
"Next, work entry types **must** have the correct ADP code listed in the "
"*External Code* field for each work entry type that is being referenced."
msgstr ""
"Dernæst **skal** arbejdsposttyper have den korrekte ADP-kode angivet i "
"feltet *Ekstern kode* for hver arbejdsposttype, der refereres til."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:579
msgid ""
"Lastly, every employee **must** have an *ADP Code* entered on their employee "
"form. To do so, navigate to :menuselection:`Employees app`, select an "
"employee record, and open the :guilabel:`HR Settings` tab. Enter "
"the :guilabel:`ADP Code` in the :guilabel:`ADP Information` section."
msgstr ""
"Endelig **skal** hver medarbejder have en *ADP-kode* indtastet på deres "
"medarbejderformular. Gå til :menuselection:`Medarbejdere-app`, vælg en "
"medarbejderpost, og åbn fanen :guilabel:`HR-indstillinger`. "
"Indtast :guilabel:`ADP-kode` i afsnittet :guilabel:`ADP-information`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:583
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`ADP Code` code is how ADP identifies that particular "
"employee, and is typically a six-digit number."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ADP-koden` er den måde, ADP identificerer den pågældende "
"medarbejder på, og er typisk et sekscifret tal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:587
msgid ":ref:`payroll/new-work-entry`"
msgstr ":ref:`payroll/new-work-entry`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:588
msgid ":doc:`../../hr/employees/new_employee`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../hr/employees/new_employee`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:591
msgid "Export data"
msgstr "Eksportdata"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:593
msgid ""
"Once :doc:`work entries <../../hr/payroll/work_entries>` have been verified, "
"the information can be exported to a CSV file, which can then be uploaded "
"into ADP."
msgstr ""
"Når :doc:`arbejdsposter <../../hr/payroll/work_entries>` er blevet "
"verificeret, kan informationen eksporteres til en CSV-fil, som derefter kan "
"uploades til ADP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:596
msgid ""
"To export the data, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Reporting --"
"> United States: ADP Export`, then click :guilabel:`New`. Next, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Start Date` and :guilabel:`End Date` for the work entries "
"using the calendar pop-over."
msgstr ""
"For at eksportere dataene skal du gå til :menuselection:`Lønadministration-"
"app --> Rapportering --> USA: ADP-eksport` og derefter klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Ny`. Indtast herefter :guilabel:`Startdato` "
"og :guilabel:`Slutdato` for arbejdsposterne ved hjælp af kalendervinduet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:600
msgid ""
"Then, enter a :guilabel:`Batch ID` in the corresponding field. The "
"recommendation for this field is to enter the date in a `YY-MM-DD` format, "
"followed by any other characters to distinguish that specific batch, such as "
"a department name, or any other defining characteristics for the batch."
msgstr ""
"Indtast derefter et :guilabel:`Batch-ID` i det tilsvarende felt. "
"Anbefalingen til dette felt er at indtaste datoen i formatet `YY-MM-DD`, "
"efterfulgt af eventuelle andre tegn til at skelne den specifikke batch, "
"såsom et afdelingsnavn eller andre kendetegn for batchen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:604
msgid ""
"Enter a :guilabel:`Batch Description` in the corresponding field. This "
"should be short and descriptive, but distinct from the :guilabel:`Batch "
"Name`."
msgstr ""
"Indtast en :guilabel:`Batchbeskrivelse` i det tilsvarende felt. Dette bør "
"være kort og beskrivende, men forskelligt fra :guilabel:`Batchnavn`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:607
msgid ""
"Ensure the correct company populates the :guilabel:`Company` field. Change "
"the selected company with the drop-down menu, if needed."
msgstr ""
"Sørg for, at det korrekte firma udfylder feltet :guilabel:`Virksomhed`. "
"Skift den valgte virksomhed med rullemenuen, hvis det er nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:610
msgid ""
"Lastly, add the employee's work entry information to the list. "
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` and an :guilabel:`Add: Employee` pop-up window "
"loads. The list can be :doc:`filtered <../../essentials/search>` to more "
"easily find the employees to add to the list."
msgstr ""
"Til sidst skal du tilføje medarbejderens arbejdsoplysninger til listen. Klik "
"på :guilabel:`Tilføj en linje`, og et :guilabel:`Tilføj: Medarbejder`-pop op-"
"vindue indlæses. Listen kan :doc:`filtreres <../../essentials/search>` for "
"lettere at finde de medarbejdere, der skal tilføjes til listen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:615
msgid ""
"Process the data export in multiple groups instead of in one large group "
"that contains all employees. This helps to meaningfully differentiate the "
"batches and makes processing more tenable, overall. The most common ways to "
"group employees is by department, or by wage type (hourly or salaried)."
msgstr ""
"Behandl dataeksporten i flere grupper i stedet for i én stor gruppe, der "
"indeholder alle medarbejdere. Dette hjælper med meningsfuldt at skelne "
"batcherne og gør behandlingen mere håndterbar overordnet set. De mest "
"almindelige måder at gruppere medarbejdere på er efter afdeling eller efter "
"løntype (timelønnede eller fastlønnede)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:620
msgid ""
"Select the employees to add to the list by ticking the box to the left of "
"their name. Once all desired employees have been selected, click "
"the :guilabel:`Select` button in the lower-left corner, and the employees "
"appear in the list."
msgstr ""
"Vælg de medarbejdere, der skal tilføjes til listen, ved at sætte flueben i "
"boksen til venstre for deres navn. Når alle ønskede medarbejdere er blevet "
"valgt, skal du klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Vælg` i nederste venstre hjørne, "
"så vises medarbejderne på listen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:624
msgid ""
"To create the CSV file, click the :guilabel:`Generate` button in the top-"
"left corner."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette CSV-filen, klik på knappen :guilabel:`Generer` i øverste "
"venstre hjørne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:629
msgid "ACH - electronic transfers"
msgstr "ACH - elektroniske overførsler"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:631
msgid ""
"Automated Clearing House (ACH) payments are a modern way to transfer funds "
"electronically between bank accounts, replacing traditional paper-based "
"methods. |ACH| payments are commonly used for direct deposits, bill "
"payments, and business transactions."
msgstr ""
"Automated Clearing House (ACH)-betalinger er en moderne måde at overføre "
"midler elektronisk mellem bankkonti på og erstatter traditionelle "
"papirbaserede metoder. |ACH|-betalinger bruges almindeligvis til direkte "
"indbetalinger, regningsbetalinger og forretningstransaktioner."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:636
msgid "Receive ACH payments: payment provider integration"
msgstr "Modtag ACH-betalinger: integration af betalingsudbyder"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:638
msgid ""
"|ACH| payments are supported by *Authorize.net* and *Stripe* payment "
"integrations in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"|ACH|-betalinger understøttes af *Authorize.net* og *Stripe* "
"betalingsintegrationer i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:641
msgid ""
":ref:`Setting up Authorize.net for ACH payments (Odoo) <authorize/"
"ach_payments>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Opsætning af Authorize.net til ACH-betalinger (Odoo) <authorize/"
"ach_payments>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:642
msgid ""
"`Authorize.net's ACH payment processing for small businesses documentation "
"<https://www.authorize.net/resources/blog/2021/ach-payments-for-small-"
"businesses.html>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Authorize.nets ACH-betalingsbehandling til små virksomheder dokumentation "
"<https://www.authorize.net/resources/blog/2021/ach-payments-for-small-"
"businesses.html>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:644
msgid ""
":doc:`Setting up Stripe for ACH payments (Odoo) <../payment_providers/"
"stripe>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Opsætning af Stripe til ACH-betalinger (Odoo) <../payment_providers/"
"stripe>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:645
msgid ""
"`Stripe's ACH Direct Debit documentation <https://docs.stripe.com/payments/"
"ach-debit>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Stripes ACH Direct Debit dokumentation <https://docs.stripe.com/payments/"
"ach-debit>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:650
msgid "Send payments: NACHA files"
msgstr "Send betalinger: NACHA-filer"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:652
msgid ""
"Odoo can generate a National Automated Clearing House Association (NACHA) "
"compatible |ACH| file to send to a company's bank. For each individual "
"*Bank* journal that the company wishes to pay vendors with, a |NACHA| "
"configuration section needs to be filled out on the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Odoo kan generere en National Automated Clearing House Association (NACHA)-"
"kompatibel |ACH|-fil, der skal sendes til en virksomheds bank. For hver "
"enkelt *Bank*-journal, som virksomheden ønsker at betale leverandører med, "
"skal der udfyldes et |NACHA|-konfigurationsafsnit i Odoo-databasen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:659
msgid ""
"First, navigate to the :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Configuration --> "
"Journals`. Open the bank journal and click into the :guilabel:`Outgoing "
"Payments` tab."
msgstr ""
"Naviger først til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Konfiguration --> Journaler`. "
"Åbn bankjournalen og klik på fanen :guilabel:`Udgående betalinger`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid ""
"NACHA (National Automated Clearing House Association) configuration settings "
"on Odoo."
msgstr ""
"NACHA (National Automated Clearing House Association) "
"konfigurationsindstillinger i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:667
msgid ""
"The following |NACHA| configuration information is normally provided by the "
"company's financial institution once they have been approved to send "
"payments via their account."
msgstr ""
"Følgende |NACHA|-konfigurationsinformation leveres normalt af virksomhedens "
"finansielle institution, når de er blevet godkendt til at sende betalinger "
"via deres konto."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:670
msgid ""
"Under the section labeled, :guilabel:`NACHA configuration` are the fields "
"required to generate a |NACHA| compatible |ACH| file to send to a company's "
"bank. First, enter the routing number of the financial institution in the "
"field labeled, :guilabel:`Immediate Destination`. This information is widely "
"available on the Internet and generally varies by bank location. This number "
"is usually provided during the initial account setup."
msgstr ""
"Under afsnittet mærket :guilabel:`NACHA-konfiguration` er felterne, der "
"kræves for at generere en |NACHA|-kompatibel |ACH|-fil, der skal sendes til "
"en virksomheds bank. Indtast først registreringsnummeret for den finansielle "
"institution i feltet mærket :guilabel:`Umiddelbar destination`. Disse "
"oplysninger er bredt tilgængelige på internettet og varierer generelt efter "
"bankens placering. Dette nummer gives normalt under den første "
"kontoopsætning."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:676
msgid ""
"Next, enter the registered name of the financial institution in the field "
"called, :guilabel:`Destination`. This information will be provided by the "
"bank or credit union."
msgstr ""
"Indtast dernæst det registrerede navn på pengeinstituttet i feltet kaldet "
":guilabel:`Destination`. Disse oplysninger vil blive leveret af banken eller "
"sparekassen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:679
msgid ""
"Following the :guilabel:`Destination` field is the :guilabel:`Immediate "
"Origin` field. Enter the 9-digit company ID or Employer Identification "
"Number (EIN) into this field. This information is provided by the financial "
"institution."
msgstr ""
"Efter feltet :guilabel:`Destination` følger feltet :guilabel:`Umiddelbar "
"oprindelse`. Indtast det 9-cifrede virksomheds-id eller arbejdsgiver-"
"identifikationsnummer (EIN) i dette felt. Disse oplysninger leveres af den "
"finansielle institution."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:683
msgid ""
"Next, enter the :guilabel:`Company Identification` number, which is a 10-"
"digit number made from combining the 9-digit company ID or Employer "
"Identification Number (EIN), along with an additional number at the start of "
"the sequence. This number is often a `1`. Check with the financial "
"institution should this first number differ to verify that it is correct, as "
"this number is provided for |ACH| approved accounts."
msgstr ""
"Indtast derefter :guilabel:`Virksomhedsidentifikation`snummeret, som er et "
"10-cifret nummer, der er sammensat af det 9-cifrede virksomheds-id eller "
"arbejdsgiver-identifikationsnummer (EIN) sammen med et ekstra nummer i "
"starten af sekvensen. Dette nummer er ofte et `1`. Tjek med den finansielle "
"institution, hvis dette første tal afviger, for at verificere, at det er "
"korrekt, da dette nummer leveres for |ACH|-godkendte konti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:689
msgid ""
"Enter the :guilabel:`Originating DFI Identification` number next, which "
"should contain an assigned 8-digit number from the financial institution."
msgstr ""
"Indtast derefter :guilabel:`Oprindelig DFI-identifikation`snummeret, som "
"skal indeholde et tildelt 8-cifret nummer fra den finansielle institution."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:693
msgid ""
"Enter the numerical values in this section *exactly* as the company's "
"financial institution (e.g. bank or credit union) has provided them, "
"otherwise risk failing a successful |NACHA| configuration in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Indtast de numeriske værdier i dette afsnit *nøjagtigt*, som virksomhedens "
"finansielle institution (f.eks. bank eller kreditforening) har leveret dem, "
"ellers risikerer man at mislykkes med en vellykket |NACHA|-konfiguration i "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid ""
"NACHA settings with the standard entry class code drop-down menu highlighted."
msgstr ""
"NACHA-indstillinger med rullemenu for standard entry class code fremhævet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:701
msgid ""
"There are two options for the next field: :guilabel:`Standard Entry Class "
"Code`. Select the drop-down menu to the right of the field and pick "
"either :guilabel:`Corporate Credit or Debit (CCD)` or :guilabel:`Prearranged "
"Payment and Deposit (PPD)`. Again, this information will be provided by the "
"financial institution. By default :guilabel:`Corporate Credit or Debit "
"(CCD)` is selected."
msgstr ""
"Der er to muligheder for det næste felt: :guilabel:`Standard Entry Class "
"Code`. Vælg rullemenuen til højre for feltet og vælg enten "
":guilabel:`Corporate Credit or Debit (CCD)` eller :guilabel:`Prearranged "
"Payment and Deposit (PPD)`. Igen vil disse oplysninger blive leveret af "
"pengeinstituttet. Som standard er :guilabel:`Corporate Credit or Debit (CCD)"
"` valgt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:706
msgid ""
"Finally, the last option is for :guilabel:`Generated Balanced Files`. Tick "
"the checkbox to the right of the field to enable :guilabel:`Generated "
"Balanced Files`. Consult the company's accountant or financial advisor to "
"make an informed decision for this field."
msgstr ""
"Endelig er den sidste mulighed for :guilabel:`Generated Balanced Files`. "
"Marker afkrydsningsfeltet til højre for feltet for at aktivere "
":guilabel:`Generated Balanced Files`. Konsulter virksomhedens revisor eller "
"finansiel rådgiver for at træffe en informeret beslutning om dette felt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:710
msgid ""
"Manually save the configuration by clicking the :icon:`fa-cloud-"
"upload` :guilabel:`(cloud upload)` icon, or navigate away from this screen "
"to auto-save. The configuration is now complete."
msgstr ""
"Gem konfigurationen manuelt ved at klikke på :icon:`fa-cloud-"
"upload` :guilabel:`cloud upload`-ikonet, eller naviger væk fra denne skærm "
"for at gemme automatisk. Konfigurationen er nu fuldført."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:716
msgid "Create batch payment"
msgstr "Opret parti betaling"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:718
msgid "Now, record each payment in Odoo using the |NACHA| payment method."
msgstr ""
"Registrer nu hver betaling i Odoo ved hjælp af |NACHA|-betalingsmetoden."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:721
msgid ""
":ref:`Register Payments in Odoo <accounting/payments/from-invoice-bill>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Registrer betalinger i Odoo <accounting/payments/from-invoice-bill>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:724
msgid ""
"Be aware of the cut-off time for same-day payments. Either the file needs to "
"have a future date associated with each payment or the file needs to be sent "
"prior to the cut-off, if the dates included in it match today's date. "
"Consult the financial institution for the exact cut-off time for their "
"processing of same-day payments."
msgstr ""
"Vær opmærksom på fristen for betalinger samme dag. Enten skal filen have en "
"fremtidig dato knyttet til hver betaling, eller filen skal sendes før "
"fristen, hvis datoerne i den matcher dags dato. Kontakt pengeinstituttet for "
"at få oplyst den præcise frist for deres behandling af betalinger samme dag."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:729
msgid ""
"Once all the payments to be included in the |NACHA| |ACH| file have been "
"made, a batch payment needs to be made from the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Action` menu."
msgstr ""
"Når alle de betalinger, der skal inkluderes i |NACHA| |ACH|-filen, er "
"foretaget, skal der oprettes en batchbetaling fra :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Handling`-menuen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:732
msgid ""
"To create the batch payments, access the payments page, by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Payments`. Select all the "
"payments that should be included in the |NACHA| |ACH| file, by ticking the "
"checkboxes to the far-left of the rows."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette batchbetalingerne skal du gå til betalingssiden ved at "
"navigere til :menuselection:`Regnskab --> Leverandører --> Betalinger`. Vælg "
"alle de betalinger, der skal inkluderes i |NACHA| |ACH|-filen, ved at "
"markere afkrydsningsfelterne helt til venstre i rækkerne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid ""
"On the payments screen, the action menu is highlighted with create a batch "
"payment\n"
"selected."
msgstr ""
"På betalingsskærmen er handlingsmenuen fremhævet med opret en batchbetaling\n"
"valgt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:742
msgid ""
"All payments in the batch **must** share the same |NACHA| payment method."
msgstr "Alle betalinger i batchen **skal** dele samme |NACHA|-betalingsmetode."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:744
msgid ""
"Next, navigate to the batched payment (:menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Vendors --> Batch Payments`). Click into the payment just created and then "
"click into the :guilabel:`Exported File` tab. The generated file is listed "
"with the :guilabel:`Generation Date`. Click the :icon:`fa-"
"download` :guilabel:`(download)` button to download the file."
msgstr ""
"Gå derefter til batchbetalingen (:menuselection:`Bogføring --> "
"Leverandører --> Batchbetalinger`). Klik ind på den netop oprettede betaling "
"og klik derefter ind på fanen :guilabel:`Eksporteret fil`. Den genererede "
"fil er vist med :guilabel:`Genereringsdato`. Klik på :icon:`fa-download` "
":guilabel:`(download)`-knappen for at downloade filen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid ""
"The exported file tab highlighted in the batch payment with the download "
"circled."
msgstr ""
"Fanen eksporteret fil fremhævet i batchbetalingen med download indkredset."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:753
msgid ""
"If any adjustments need to be made, click the :guilabel:`Re-generate Export "
"File` button to recreate a new |NACHA| |ACH| file."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der skal foretages justeringer, skal du klikke på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Gengenerer eksportfil` for at genskabe en ny |NACHA| |"
"ACH|-fil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:758
msgid ":doc:`Europe's direct debiting <../accounting/payments/sepa_payments>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Europas direkte debitering <../accounting/payments/sepa_payments>`"

