msgstr "For eksempel `https://ditfirma.odoo.com/payment/aps/return`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/amazon_payment_services.rst:0
msgid ""
"Enter your database URL followed by `/payment/aps/webhook` in "
