msgstr ""
"Indtast din database-URL efterfulgt af `/payment/aps/webhook` i "
"felterne :guilabel:`Direct Transaction Feedback` og :guilabel:`Notification "
"URL`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/amazon_payment_services.rst:0
