#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/sdd.rst:7
msgid ""
"SEPA (Single Euro Payments Area) is a payment-integration initiative of the "
"European Union that facilitates standardized and simplified electronic "
"payments in euros across participating countries."
msgstr ""
"SEPA (Single Euro Payments Area) er et betalingsintegrations-initiativ fra "
"Den Europæiske Union, der letter standardiserede og forenklede elektroniske "
"betalinger i euro på tværs af deltagende lande."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/sdd.rst:10
msgid ""
"SEPA Direct Debit (SDD) is a payment provider that allows future payments to "
"be collected from customers' bank accounts based on a signed :ref:`SEPA "
"Direct Debit mandate <accounting/sepa_payments/sdd>`. This is particularly "
"useful for recurring payments based on a :doc:`subscription </applications/"
"sales/subscriptions>`."
msgstr ""
"SEPA Direct Debit (SDD) er en betalingsudbyder, der gør det muligt at "
"opkræve fremtidige betalinger fra kunders bankkonti baseret på et "
"underskrevet :ref:`SEPA Direct Debit-mandat <accounting/sepa_payments/sdd>`. "
"Dette er særligt nyttigt til tilbagevendende betalinger baseret på et "
":doc:`abonnement </applications/sales/subscriptions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/sdd.rst:16
msgid ""
"To use the SEPA Direct Debit (SDD) payment provider and create :ref:`SEPA "
"Direct Debit mandates <accounting/sepa_payments/sdd>`:"
msgstr ""
"For at bruge SEPA Direct Debit (SDD) betalingsudbyderen og oprette "
":ref:`SEPA Direct Debit-mandater <accounting/sepa_payments/sdd>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/sdd.rst:19
msgid "The invoice being paid must be for an amount in euros."
msgstr "Fakturaen, der betales, skal være for et beløb i euro."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/sdd.rst:20
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`SEPA Direct Deposit (SDD)` feature must be enabled, and the "
"company's :guilabel:`Creditor Identifier` must be defined in "
"the :ref:`Accounting or Invoicing settings <accounting/sepa_payments/"
"sdd_configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen :guilabel:`SEPA Direct Deposit (SDD)` skal være aktiveret, og "
