msgid "Worldline"
msgstr "Worldline"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:5
msgid ""
"`Worldline <https://worldline.com/>`_ is a France-based company and the "
"world's fourth largest payment provider."
msgstr ""
"<https://worldline.com/> er en Frankrig-baseret virksomhed og verdens "
"fjerdestørste betalingsudbyder."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:9
msgid "Settings in Worldline"
msgstr "Indstillinger i Worldline"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:14
msgid "Create an API user"
msgstr "Opret en API-bruger"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:16
msgid ""
"It is recommended to set up an **API user** to create transactions from Odoo "
"to ensure that your Worldline configuration remains safe even if credentials "
"are compromised. Additionally, API users do not require frequent password "
"updates like regular accounts."
msgstr ""
"Det anbefales at oprette en **API-bruger** til at oprette transaktioner fra "
"Odoo for at sikre, at din Worldline-konfiguration forbliver sikker, selv "
"hvis legitimationsoplysninger kompromitteres. Derudover kræver API-brugere "
"ikke hyppige adgangskodeopdateringer som almindelige konti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:20
msgid "To create an **API user**, proceed as follows:"
msgstr "For at oprette en **API-bruger** skal du gøre følgende:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:22
msgid ""
"Log into your `Worldline Merchant Portal <https://merchant-portal.worldline-"
"solutions.com/>`_, click the :icon:`fa-th` (:guilabel:`menu`) icon, and "
"select :guilabel:`Back Office`."
msgstr ""
"Log ind på din <https://merchant-portal.worldline-solutions.com/>, klik "
"på :icon:`fa-th`-ikonet (:guilabel:`menu`) og vælg :guilabel:`Back Office`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:24
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Users` and click on :guilabel:`New "
"User`."
msgstr ""
"Gå til :menuselection:`Configuration --> Users` og klik på :guilabel:`New "
"User`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:25
msgid "Configure the following fields:"
msgstr "Konfigurer følgende felter:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:27
msgid ""
"Specify a :guilabel:`UserID`, :guilabel:`User's name`, :guilabel:`E-mail "
"address`, and :guilabel:`Timezone` of your choice."
msgstr ""
"Angiv et :guilabel:`UserID`, :guilabel:`User's name`, :guilabel:`E-mail "
"address` og :guilabel:`Timezone` efter eget valg."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:29
msgid "Set the :guilabel:`Profile` field to :guilabel:`Admin`."
msgstr "Indstil feltet :guilabel:`Profile` til :guilabel:`Admin`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:30
msgid "Enable :guilabel:`Special user for API`."
msgstr "Aktiver :guilabel:`Special user for API`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:33
msgid ""
"If you have already set up a user, make sure it is activated without any "
"error."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du allerede har oprettet en bruger, skal du sikre dig, at den er "
"aktiveret uden fejl."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:34
msgid ""
"To test the payment flow with Worldline, use their `test environment "
"<https://merchant-portal.preprod.worldline-solutions.com/>`_ together with "
"the :ref:`test mode <payment_providers/test-mode>`."
msgstr ""
"For at teste betalingsflowet med Worldline skal du bruge deres <https://"
"merchant-portal.preprod.worldline-solutions.com/> sammen "
"med :ref:`testtilstand <payment_providers/test-mode>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:41
msgid "Set up Worldline for Odoo"
msgstr "Konfigurer Worldline til Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:43
msgid "Worldline must now be configured to accept payments from Odoo."
msgstr "Worldline skal nu konfigureres til at acceptere betalinger fra Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:45
msgid ""
"From your merchant portal, go to :menuselection:`Developer --> Payment API` "
"and click on :guilabel:`Generate API key`. Copy the :guilabel:`API key ID` "
"and the :guilabel:`Secret API key` and save them for :ref:`later <wordline/"
"odoo-configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Fra din handelsportal skal du gå til :menuselection:`Developer --> Payment "
"API` og klikke på :guilabel:`Generate API key`. Kopier :guilabel:`API key "
"ID` og :guilabel:`Secret API key` og gem dem til :ref:`senere <wordline/odoo-"
"configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:48
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Developer --> Webhooks` and click "
"on :guilabel:`Generate webhook keys`. Copy the :guilabel:`Webhook ID` and "
"the associated :guilabel:`Secret webhook key` and save them for :ref:`later "
"<wordline/odoo-configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Gå til :menuselection:`Developer --> Webhooks` og klik "
"på :guilabel:`Generate webhook keys`. Kopier :guilabel:`Webhook ID` og den "
"tilhørende :guilabel:`Secret webhook key` og gem dem til :ref:`senere "
"<wordline/odoo-configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:0
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add webhook endpoint`, enter your Odoo database's URL "
"followed by `/payment/worldline/webhook` in the :guilabel:`Endpoint url` "
"field, and :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Add webhook endpoint`, indtast din Odoo-databases URL "
"efterfulgt af `/payment/worldline/webhook` i feltet :guilabel:`Endpoint "
"url`, og :guilabel:`Confirm`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:0
msgid "For example: `https://example.odoo.com/payment/worldline/webhook`."
msgstr "For eksempel: `https://example.odoo.com/payment/worldline/webhook`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:58
msgid "Settings in Odoo"
msgstr "Indstillinger i Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:60
msgid "To set up Worldline in Odoo:"
msgstr "Sådan opsættes Worldline i Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:62
msgid ""
":ref:`Navigate to the payment provider Worldline <payment_providers/"
"add_new>` and change its state to :guilabel:`Enabled`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Naviger til betalingsudbyderen Worldline <payment_providers/add_new>`, "
"og ændr dens tilstand til :guilabel:`Enabled`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:64
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Credentials` tab, enter the :guilabel:`PSPID` of your "
"Worldline account and fill in the :guilabel:`API Key`, :guilabel:`API "
"Secret`, :guilabel:`Webhook Key`, and :guilabel:`Webhook Secret` with the "
"values you saved at the step :ref:`Set up Worldline for Odoo <worldline/set-"
"up>`."
msgstr ""
"Under fanen :guilabel:`Credentials` indtastes :guilabel:`PSPID` for din "
"Worldline-konto, og udfyld :guilabel:`API Key`, :guilabel:`API "
"Secret`, :guilabel:`Webhook Key` og :guilabel:`Webhook Secret` med de "
"værdier, du gemte i trinnet :ref:`Set up Worldline for Odoo <worldline/set-"
"up>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:3
msgid "Xendit"
msgstr "Xendit"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:5
msgid ""
"`Xendit <https://www.xendit.co>`_ is an Indonesian-based payment solution "
"provider that covers several Southeast Asian countries. It allows businesses "
"to accept credit cards as well as several local payment methods."
msgstr ""
"`Xendit <https://www.xendit.co>`_ er en indonesisk-baseret "
"betalingsløsningsudbyder, der dækker flere sydøstasiatiske lande. Den giver "
"virksomheder mulighed for at acceptere kreditkort samt flere lokale "
"betalingsmetoder."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:10
msgid ""
"Credit card payments are processed through Odoo, while all other payment "
"methods are handled via Xendit's website."
msgstr ""
"Kreditkortbetalinger behandles gennem Odoo, mens alle andre betalingsmetoder "
"håndteres via Xendits hjemmeside."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:12
msgid ""
"Xendit supports card payment tokenization, provided the customer has "
"requested Merchant Initiated Transaction (MIT) from `Xendit Support <https://"
"www.xendit.co/en/contact/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Xendit understøtter tokenisering af kortbetalinger, forudsat at kunden har "
"anmodet om Merchant Initiated Transaction (MIT) fra `Xendit Support <https://"
"www.xendit.co/en/contact/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:18
msgid "Configuration on the Xendit Dashboard"
msgstr "Konfiguration på Xendit Dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:20
msgid ""
"`Create a Xendit account <https://dashboard.xendit.co/register/1?"
"referral_code=odooid&countr_code=ID>`_ if necessary and log in to the "
"`Xendit Dashboard <https://dashboard.xendit.co>`_."
msgstr ""
"`Opret en Xendit-konto <https://dashboard.xendit.co/register/1?"
"referral_code=odooid&countr_code=ID>`_, hvis nødvendigt, og log ind på "
"`Xendit Dashboard <https://dashboard.xendit.co>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:23
msgid ""
"Check your account mode in the top left corner of the page. Use "
"the :guilabel:`Test Mode` to try the integration without charging your "
"customers. Switch to :guilabel:`Live Mode` once you are ready to accept "
"payments."
msgstr ""
"Kontroller din kontotilstand i øverste venstre hjørne af siden. "
"Brug :guilabel:`Test Mode` til at afprøve integrationen uden at opkræve dine "
"kunder. Skift til :guilabel:`Live Mode`, når du er klar til at acceptere "
"betalinger."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:26
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Configuration: Settings` in the left part of the "
"application page. In the :guilabel:`Developers` section, click `API Keys "
"<https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/developers#api-keys>`_."
msgstr ""
"Naviger til :menuselection:`Configuration: Settings` i venstre del af "
"applikationssiden. I afsnittet :guilabel:`Developers` klikkes på `API Keys "
"<https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/developers#api-keys>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:29
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Generate Secret Key`. In the popup box, enter "
"any :guilabel:`API key name`, select :guilabel:`Write` for "
"the :guilabel:`Money-in Products` permission and :guilabel:`None` for all "
"other permissions then click :guilabel:`Generate key`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Generate Secret Key`. I popup-boksen indtastes et "
"valgfrit :guilabel:`API key name`, vælg :guilabel:`Write` for "
"tilladelsen :guilabel:`Money-in Products` og :guilabel:`None` for alle andre "
"tilladelser, og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Generate key`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:32
msgid ""
"Confirm your password to display your API key. Copy or download the key and "
"**save this information securely for later**. This is the only time the API "
"key can be viewed or downloaded."
msgstr ""
"Bekræft din adgangskode for at vise din API-nøgle. Kopier eller download "
"nøglen, og **gem disse oplysninger sikkert til senere**. Dette er den eneste "
"gang, API-nøglen kan ses eller downloades."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:35
msgid ""
"Once completed, scroll down the page to the `Webhooks <https://"
"dashboard.xendit.co/settings/developers#webhooks>`_ section to generate the "
"webhook token."
msgstr ""
"Når det er færdigt, rulles der ned på siden til afsnittet `Webhooks <https://"
"dashboard.xendit.co/settings/developers#webhooks>`_ for at generere webhook-"
"token."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:38
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Webhook verification token`, click :guilabel:`View Webhook "
"Verification Token`, then confirm your password to display the token. Save "
"it for later."
msgstr ""
"Under :guilabel:`Webhook verification token` klikkes på :guilabel:`View "
"Webhook Verification Token`, og bekræft derefter din adgangskode for at vise "
"token. Gem det til senere."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:40
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Webhook URL` section, enter your Odoo database's URL, "
"followed by `/payment/xendit/webhook` (e.g., `https://example.odoo.com/"
"payment/xendit/webhook`) in the field :guilabel:`Invoices paid` and click "
"the :guilabel:`Test and save` button next to it."
msgstr ""
"I afsnittet :guilabel:`Webhook URL` indtastes din Odoo-databases URL "
"efterfulgt af `/payment/xendit/webhook` (f.eks. `https://example.odoo.com/"
"payment/xendit/webhook`) i feltet :guilabel:`Invoices paid`, og klik på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Test and save` ved siden af det."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:43
msgid ""
"To allow recurring payments for credit cards, go "
"to :menuselection:`Configuration: Payment Channels` in the left part of the "
"application page. Then, hover your mouse over the :guilabel:`Visa, "
"Mastercard, JCB, Amex` channel, click :guilabel:`View Details`, and "
"enable :guilabel:`Recurring Payments` by toggling the related switch."
msgstr ""
"For at tillade tilbagevendende betalinger for kreditkort, gå "
"til :menuselection:`Configuration: Payment Channels` i venstre del af "
"applikationssiden. Før derefter musen hen over kanalen :guilabel:`Visa, "
"Mastercard, JCB, Amex`, klik på :guilabel:`View Details`, og "
"aktiver :guilabel:`Recurring Payments` ved at skifte den relaterede kontakt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:51
msgid ""
":ref:`Navigate to the payment provider Xendit <payment_providers/add_new>` "
"and change its state to :guilabel:`Enabled`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Naviger til betalingsudbyderen Xendit <payment_providers/add_new>`, og "
"ændr dens tilstand til :guilabel:`Enabled`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:53
msgid ""
"Fill in the :guilabel:`Secret Key` and :guilabel:`Webhook Token` fields with "
"the information saved at the step :ref:`payment_providers/xendit/"
"configure_dashboard`."
msgstr ""
"Udfyld felterne :guilabel:`Hemmelig nøgle` og :guilabel:`Webhook-token` med "
"oplysningerne gemt i trin :ref:`payment_providers/xendit/"
"configure_dashboard`."

