#~ msgid ""
#~ "During your first synchronization, you will be asked for a phone number "
#~ "to secure your account. The reason we ask for such information is that we "
#~ "don't want your data falling into the wrong hands. Therefore, if we "
#~ "detect suspicious activity on your account, we block all requests coming "
#~ "from your account, and you need to reactivate it using that phone number. "
